{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/vyvojari-tretich-stran-konecne-mohou-vytvaret-vlastni-povely-pro-google-assistant/sc-3-a-192191/default.aspx", "title": "V\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159i t\u0159et\u00edch stran kone\u010dn\u011b mohou vytv\u00e1\u0159et vlastn\u00ed povely pro Google Assistant ", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "11. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Google kone\u010dn\u011b umo\u017enil firm\u00e1m t\u0159et\u00edch stran vytv\u00e1\u0159et vlastn\u00ed povely a nastaven\u00ed pro pomocn\u00edka Google Assistant. To by mohlo otev\u0159\u00edt \u0159adu nov\u00fdch mo\u017enost\u00ed pro produkty dal\u0161\u00edch v\u00fdrobc\u016f.Doned\u00e1vna byl toti\u017e asistent limitov\u00e1n jen p\u0159ednastaven\u00fdmi v\u00fdrazy, nyn\u00ed ale bude mo\u017en\u00e9 naprogramovat t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 cokoliv. To mimo jin\u00e9 znamen\u00e1, \u017ee nap\u0159. v\u00fdrobce pra\u010dky m\u016f\u017ee p\u0159idat do sv\u00e9ho za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed asistenta s podporou unik\u00e1tn\u00edch povel\u016f, jako \"\" \u010di \"\".Google tak douf\u00e1, \u017ee roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00edm mo\u017enost\u00ed pro dal\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdrobce umo\u017en\u00ed v\u00fdvoj mnohem variabiln\u011bj\u0161\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed a p\u0159itom ud\u011bl\u00e1 sv\u00e9ho Assistanta mnohem l\u00e1kav\u011bj\u0161\u00ed a p\u0159\u00ednosn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed volbou pro integraci do dal\u0161\u00edch produkt\u016f.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Software", "Google", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Google Asistent", "Povel", "V\u00fdrobce", "Mo\u017enost", "Nov\u00e1 mo\u017enost", "Za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed mo\u017enost\u00ed", "V\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159", "T\u0159et\u00ed strana", "Asistent", "Produkt"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/facebook-lite-konecne-podporuje-videohovory-zatim-jen-na-androidu/sc-3-a-192194/default.aspx", "title": "Facebook Lite kone\u010dn\u011b podporuje videohovory, zat\u00edm jen na Androidu", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "11. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Facebook Messenger Lite je odleh\u010denou verz\u00ed mobiln\u00ed aplikace Messengeru ur\u010den\u00e1 pro slab\u0161\u00ed telefony, ale tak\u00e9 pro u\u017eivatele, kte\u0159\u00ed necht\u011bj\u00ed vyu\u017e\u00edvat pokro\u010dil\u00fdch funkc\u00ed. Doposud byl Lite z\u00e1kladem pro textovou komunikaci, nyn\u00ed u\u017e ale aplikace .Funkce funguje jednodu\u0161e. Otev\u0159ete konverzaci s n\u011bkter\u00fdm ze sv\u00fdch p\u0159\u00e1tel, stiskn\u011bte ikonku kamery a videohovor m\u016f\u017ee za\u010d\u00edt. Jde rozhodn\u011b o skv\u011bl\u00fd p\u0159\u00eddavek do komunik\u00e1toru, kter\u00fd zab\u00edr\u00e1 m\u00e9n\u011b ne\u017e 10 MB m\u00edsta v telefonu.Messenger Lite je dostupn\u00fd ve v\u00edce jak 100 zem\u00edch sv\u011bta a stahovat jej m\u016f\u017eete na . ", "tags": ["Software", "Google", "Facebook", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Facebook Messenger", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Android", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "Funkce", "Telefon", "Pokro\u010dil\u00e1 funkce", "Messenger", "Brzk\u00e1 doba", "Verze", "Slab\u00fd telefon", "Videohovor", "Textov\u00e1 komunikace", "Aplikace", "Lite"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-dog-view-japonsky-google-pripevnil-kameru-na-psa-a-jeho-zabery-pouzil-do-street-view/sc-3-a-192138/default.aspx", "title": "Google \u201edog view\u201c: Japonsk\u00fd Google p\u0159ipevnil kameru na psa a jeho z\u00e1b\u011bry pou\u017eil do Street View", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "9. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Japonsk\u00e9 m\u011bsto \u00d3date le\u017e\u00ed v prefektu\u0159e Akita a je tak\u00e9 domovem stejnojmenn\u00e9 ps\u00ed rasy \u2013 Akita Inu. Japonsk\u00fd Google se nyn\u00ed rozhodl pro netradi\u010dn\u00ed prohl\u00eddku a p\u0159ipevnil na z\u00e1da dv\u011bma ps\u016fm 360stup\u0148ov\u00e9 kamery. Jejich putov\u00e1n\u00ed po vybran\u00fdch m\u00edstech m\u011bsta si m\u016f\u017eete prohl\u00e9dnout v r\u00e1mci .Ako a Asuka pro\u0161li hlavn\u00ed m\u011bstsk\u00e9 atrakce, tedy minim\u00e1ln\u011b co se t\u00fd\u010de jejich pohledu. Nav\u0161t\u00edvili tedy ps\u00ed muzeum, zasn\u011b\u017een\u00e9 cesty kolem m\u011bsta \u010di l\u00e1zn\u011b pod \u0161ir\u00fdm nebem.Kompletn\u00ed p\u0159ehled m\u00edst, kde se m\u016f\u017eete na ps\u00edch z\u00e1dech proj\u00edt, naleznete na .Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Mapy Google", "Google", "Street View", "Mapy", "Japonsko", "Kamera", "Turistika", "Navigace", "Pes", "View", "Z\u00e1da", "Z\u00e1b\u011br", "Japonsk\u00e9 m\u011bsto", "Vybran\u00e9 m\u00edsto", "Kompletn\u00ed p\u0159ehled"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/mcafee-koupilo-tunnelbear-popularni-vpnko-ktere-zvladne-i-vase-mama/sc-3-a-192173/default.aspx", "title": "McAfee koupilo TunnelBear. Popul\u00e1rn\u00ed VPNko, kter\u00e9 zvl\u00e1dne i va\u0161e m\u00e1ma", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "9. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Popul\u00e1rn\u00ed VPN s nep\u0159ehl\u00e9dnuteln\u00fdm medv\u011bdem  . Nen\u00ed jim nikdo jin\u00fd ne\u017e McAfee, jeho\u017e bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed software byl sv\u00e9ho \u010dasu p\u0159edinstalovan\u00fd snad na ka\u017ed\u00e9m nov\u00e9m po\u010d\u00edta\u010di, a tak si mnoz\u00ed tropili \u017eerty, \u017ee na n\u011b vysko\u010d\u00ed i z mraz\u00e1ku.Pro kanadsk\u00fd startup se v ka\u017ed\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b akvizic\u00ed alespo\u0148 prozat\u00edm nic nem\u011bn\u00ed. Nov\u00fd majitel toti\u017e v tiskov\u00e9 zpr\u00e1v\u011b p\u00ed\u0161e, \u017ee jej sice integruje do sv\u00e9ho \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed Safe Connect, ale ponech\u00e1 jej i jako samostatn\u00fd produkt. TunnelBear se toti\u017e t\u011b\u0161\u00ed velk\u00e9 popularit\u011b p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm d\u00edky sv\u00e9mu jednoduch\u00e9mu ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed i rychlosti, tak\u017ee jeho provoz zvl\u00e1dne i naprost\u00fd za\u010d\u00e1te\u010dn\u00edk.Program nab\u00edz\u00ed v bezplatn\u00e9m provozu 500 MB m\u011bs\u00ed\u010dn\u011b, kter\u00e9 m\u016f\u017eete vy\u010derpat pro komunikaci skrze zahrani\u010dn\u00ed server, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e slu\u017eba v\u00e1m d\u00e1 na v\u00fdb\u011br z n\u011bkolika destinac\u00ed v Evrop\u011b, USA i na dal\u0161\u00edch kontinentech. V tom se program podob\u00e1 t\u0159eba integrovan\u00e9mu VPN klientu v Ope\u0159e. TunnelBear se li\u0161\u00ed v tom, \u017ee skrze sv\u00e9 servery p\u0159emost\u00ed jakoukoliv komunikaci po\u010d\u00edta\u010de \u2013 nejen tu v prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010di.McAfee jej chce podle tiskov\u00e9 zpr\u00e1vy propagovat jako bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed \u0161ifrovan\u00e9 \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed na otev\u0159en\u00fdch Wi-Fi s\u00edt\u00edch t\u0159eba v kav\u00e1rn\u00e1ch, kde hroz\u00ed nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed riziko napaden\u00ed a odposlechu. VPN v\u00e1m toti\u017e nep\u0159id\u011bl\u00ed pouze ciz\u00ed IP adresu, ale ve\u0161ker\u00e1 komunikace  mezi v\u00e1mi a serverem slu\u017eby je z\u00e1rove\u0148 siln\u011b \u0161ifrovan\u00e1, tak\u017ee ji nemohu odposlechnout, pokud budu zrovna s Kali Linuxem v laptopu sed\u011bt u sousedn\u00edho stolu.", "tags": ["Byznys", "Linux", "Bezpe\u010dnost", "USA", "Evropa", "VPN", "Akvizice", "Odposlech", "Komunikace", "McAfee", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed riziko", "Safe Connect", "Zahrani\u010dn\u00ed server", "Naprost\u00fd za\u010d\u00e1te\u010dn\u00edk", "TunnelBear", "Velk\u00e1 popularita", "Otev\u0159en\u00e1 wi-fi", "Bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed software", "Samostatn\u00fd produkt", "Jednoduch\u00e9 ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed", "Bezplatn\u00fd provoz", "Nov\u00fd majitel", "Ciz\u00ed IP", "M\u00e1ma"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/upgrade-z-windows-10-s-na-plnou-verzi-bude-zdarma-pro-vsechny-edice/sc-3-a-192166/default.aspx", "title": "Upgrade z Windows 10 S na plnou verzi bude zdarma. Pro v\u0161echny edice", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "9. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Kdy\u017e loni Microsoft uvedl syst\u00e9m Windows 10 S, m\u011bl b\u00fdt ur\u010den\u00fd hlavn\u011b \u0161kol\u00e1m a podnik\u016fm. Hlavn\u00ed rozd\u00edl byl v omezen\u00ed na instalaci aplikac\u00ed pouze z Microsoft Store. Nyn\u00ed ale doch\u00e1z\u00ed k  strategie a m\u00edsto samostatn\u00e9 verze syst\u00e9mu bude mo\u017en\u00e9 v klasick\u00e9 zapnout speci\u00e1ln\u00ed \u201eS m\u00f3d\u201c. Jeho vypnut\u00ed pak bude zcela zdarma.Od p\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u00ed aktualizace Windows 10, tedy , bude mo\u017en\u00e9 speci\u00e1ln\u00ed m\u00f3d zapnout \u010di vypnout. V\u00fdrobci tak\u00e9 z\u00edskaj\u00ed mo\u017enost uv\u00e1d\u011bt na trh za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed, kter\u00e1 jej budou m\u00edt od z\u00e1kladu zapnut\u00e1. Ji\u017e nyn\u00ed jsou na trhu za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed s Windows 10 S, doposud byl ale upgrade na klasickou verzi syst\u00e9mu placen\u00fd (\u010di v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b  od Microsoftu do\u010dasn\u011b zdarma).Mezi hlavn\u00ed v\u00fdhody upraven\u00e9ho re\u017eimu pak dle Microsoftu pat\u0159\u00ed zv\u00fd\u0161en\u00e1 bezpe\u010dnost a rychlost. Instalace program\u016f je toti\u017e omezena pouze na . Eliminuje se t\u00edm mo\u017enost zavle\u010den\u00ed necht\u011bn\u00fdch program\u016f do po\u010d\u00edta\u010de v pr\u016fb\u011bhu instalace m\u00e9n\u011b znal\u00fdmi u\u017eivateli. Mezi v\u011bt\u0161inou se ale s p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 kladn\u00fdm p\u0159ijet\u00edm nesetkal, i kdy\u017e do obchodu neust\u00e1le p\u0159ib\u00fdvaj\u00ed nov\u00e9 aplikace, v\u010detn\u011b t\u011bch desktopov\u00fdch.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Windows 10", "Spring Creators Update", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Surface Laptop", "Microsoft Store", "Aktualizace", "Hlavn\u00ed v\u00fdhoda", "M\u00f3d", "Necht\u011bn\u00fd program", "Edice", "Instalace", "Verze syst\u00e9mu", "Hlavn\u00ed rozd\u00edl", "Klasick\u00e1 verze", "Speci\u00e1ln\u00ed m\u00f3d", "Pln\u00e1 verze", "Znal\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Kladn\u00e9 p\u0159ijet\u00ed", "Verze", "Samostatn\u00e1 verze", "P\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u00ed aktualizace", "Zv\u00fd\u0161en\u00e1 bezpe\u010dnost", "Aplikace"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/ivysilani-se-behem-olympiady-rekordne-zapotilo-protekalo-jim-az-600-gb/s/sc-3-a-192152/default.aspx", "title": "iVys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed se b\u011bhem olympi\u00e1dy rekordn\u011b zapotilo. Prot\u00e9kalo j\u00edm a\u017e 600 Gb/s", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Jak u\u017e se v \u00fanoru pochlubil jeden z nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edch \u010desk\u00fdch peering\u016f NIX.CZ, \u010de\u0161t\u00ed fanou\u0161ci hokeje 23.2 dos\u00e1hli nov\u00e9ho rekordu, Nixem toti\u017e b\u011bhem rann\u00edho p\u0159enosu olympijsk\u00e9ho utk\u00e1n\u00ed \u010cesko \u00d7 Rusko prot\u00e9kalo 629,6 Gb/s. Za anom\u00e1ln\u00ed \u0161pi\u010dkou, ke kter\u00e9 jinak doch\u00e1z\u00ed okolo osm\u00e9 hodiny ve\u010dern\u00ed, st\u00e1lo samoz\u0159ejm\u011b streamov\u00e1n\u00ed hokeje p\u0159es internet.Nyn\u00ed s vlastn\u00edmi daty p\u0159isp\u011bchala i spole\u010dnost , o kter\u00e9 nejsp\u00ed\u0161e v\u011bt\u0161ina \u010dten\u00e1\u0159\u016f v \u017eivot\u011b nesly\u0161ela, a\u010dkoliv jej\u00edch slu\u017eeb \u010dasto vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1. Nangu je toti\u017e poskytovatelem IPTV/OTT syst\u00e9m\u016f, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e jedn\u00edm z nejd\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00edch \u010desk\u00fdch klient\u016f nen\u00ed nikdo jin\u00fd ne\u017e \u010cesk\u00e1 televize a jej\u00ed televizn\u00ed archiv iVys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed.\u201eB\u011bhem hokejov\u00e9ho z\u00e1pasu bylo z platformy Nangu vystreamov\u00e1no p\u0159es 600 Gb/s datov\u00e9ho toku, z\u00e1pas z\u00e1rove\u0148 sledoval i rekordn\u00ed po\u010det 164 000 div\u00e1k\u016f, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e \u0161pi\u010dka sledovanosti pak dosahovala 500 000 div\u00e1k\u016f a bylo tak v\u00fdznamn\u011b p\u0159ekon\u00e1no dosavadn\u00ed maximum z roku 2015. Semifin\u00e1lov\u00fd hokejov\u00fd z\u00e1pas zimn\u00edch olympijsk\u00fdch her se tak stal historicky nejsledovan\u011bj\u0161\u00ed ud\u00e1lost\u00ed, kter\u00e1 byla vys\u00edl\u00e1na prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm internetu na platform\u011b iVys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed \u010cesk\u00e9 televize,\u201c p\u00ed\u0161e se v tiskov\u00e9 zpr\u00e1v\u011b Nagu.tv.To odpov\u00edd\u00e1 i proklamovan\u00e9 z\u00e1t\u011b\u017ei NIxu nebo t\u0159eba konkuren\u010dn\u00edho Peering.cz \u2013 v\u011bt\u0161ina \u010desk\u00fdch surfa\u0159\u016f tedy v onu rann\u00ed hodinu nejsp\u00ed\u0161e skute\u010dn\u011b sledovala hokej skrze internet.", "tags": ["\u010cT Sport", "Internet", "iVys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed", "Sport", "Olympijsk\u00e9 hry", "Statistiky", "Rusko", "Televizn\u00ed archiv", "Naga", "Nejsledovan\u011bj\u0161\u00ed ud\u00e1lost", "Nov\u00fd rekord", "Olympi\u00e1da", "\u010cesk\u00e1 televize", "Dosavadn\u00ed maximum", "Peering", "\u010cesk\u00fd surfa\u0159", "Platforma", "\u0160pi\u010dka", "Mobiln\u00ed za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "Webov\u00fd prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d", "Hokej", "Hokejov\u00fd z\u00e1pas", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Rekordn\u00ed po\u010det"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/amazon-echo-strasi-sve-uzivatele-bez-varovani-jim-v-noci-pousti-desivy-smich/sc-3-a-192155/default.aspx", "title": "Amazon Echo stra\u0161\u00ed sv\u00e9 u\u017eivatele. Bez varov\u00e1n\u00ed jim v noci pou\u0161t\u00ed d\u011bsiv\u00fd sm\u00edch", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "8. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Alexa se ned\u00e1vno  a vyd\u00e1vat dal\u0161\u00ed zvuky pro dod\u00e1n\u00ed osobn\u00edho rozm\u011bru, z\u0159ejm\u011b to ale m\u011blo vedlej\u0161\u00ed \u00fa\u010dinky. Asistentka se toti\u017e n\u011bkter\u00fdm majitel\u016fm chytr\u00e9ho reproduktoru  sama od sebe v noci probouz\u00ed a pou\u0161t\u00ed d\u011bsiv\u00fd sm\u00edch.N\u011bkolik dot\u010den\u00fdch u\u017eivatel\u016f, kte\u0159\u00ed se s probl\u00e9mem sv\u011b\u0159ili na Twitteru, nav\u00edc uv\u00e1d\u011bj\u00ed, \u017ee v mobiln\u00ed aplikaci nen\u00ed \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd z\u00e1znam o aktivaci Alexy a tud\u00ed\u017e nelze ov\u011b\u0159it, \u017ee by t\u0159eba jen \u0161patn\u011b interpretovala okoln\u00ed zvuky. Jedn\u00e9 z u\u017eivatelek se sm\u00edch poda\u0159ilo nahr\u00e1t za pomoci p\u0159\u00edkazu , kdy Alexa zopakuje to, co \u0159\u00edkala naposledy.Podle dal\u0161\u00edch reakc\u00ed to vypad\u00e1, \u017ee se spou\u0161t\u00ed v noci, kdy je ticho, co\u017e je o to d\u011bsiv\u011bj\u0161\u00ed. Je ale mo\u017en\u00e9, \u017ee se m\u00edsto softwarov\u00e9 chyby jedn\u00e1 o vt\u00edpek a n\u011bkdo v\u017edy po\u017e\u00e1dal Alexu o zasm\u00e1n\u00ed.Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Amazon", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Twitter", "Alexa", "Amazon Echo", "Chytr\u00e1 dom\u00e1cnost", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Zvuk", "Softwarov\u00e1 chyba", "Alexa", "Dot\u010den\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Vedlej\u0161\u00ed \u00fa\u010dinek", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Replay", "Sm\u00edch", "Noc", "Chytr\u00fd reproduktor", "Varov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Okoln\u00ed zvuk"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/peklo-opet-zamrzlo-v-microsoft-storu-je-hackersky-kali-linux/sc-3-a-192153/default.aspx", "title": "Peklo op\u011bt zamrzlo: V Microsoft Storu je hackersk\u00fd Kali Linux", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "8. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "V souvislosti s p\u0159\u00edchodem Windows 10 u\u017e v minulosti n\u011bkolikr\u00e1t  a padl cel\u00fd z\u00e1stup n\u011bkdej\u0161\u00edch tabu. T\u00edm nejzaj\u00edmav\u011bj\u0161\u00edm je voliteln\u00fd linuxov\u00fd subsyst\u00e9m integrovan\u00fd hned nad j\u00e1dro Windows, kter\u00fd umo\u017e\u0148uje nativn\u00ed b\u011bh hromady linuxov\u00fdch textov\u00fdch termin\u00e1l\u016f \u2013 v podstat\u011b t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 kompletn\u00edho textov\u00e9ho Ubuntu, Fedory aj., kter\u00e9 m\u016f\u017eete st\u00e1hnout z Microsoft Storu.Nyn\u00ed v pekle op\u011bt tro\u0161ku p\u0159ituhuje, Microsoft se toti\u017e na sv\u00e9m blogu , \u017ee do Windows Storu dostal dal\u0161\u00ed linuxovou distribuci \u2013 .Asi ho nemus\u00edme p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 p\u0159edstavovat, v minulosti jsme si toti\u017e na n\u011bm vyzkou\u0161eli n\u011bkolik jednoduch\u00fdch kybernetick\u00fdch \u00fatok\u016f. Kali je distribuce ur\u010den\u00e1 k penetra\u010dn\u00edm s\u00ed\u0165ov\u00fdm test\u016fm, a tak je vybaven\u00e1 hromadou n\u00e1stroj\u016f pro tvorbu \u00fatok\u016f, kter\u00fdmi lze sledovat, jak je proti nim ochr\u00e1n\u011bn\u00e1 t\u0159eba podnikov\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165.Jen\u017ee jak u\u017e tomu b\u00fdv\u00e1, mezi simulac\u00ed \u00fatoku a re\u00e1ln\u00fdm z\u00e1\u0161kodnick\u00fdm \u00fatokem je vlastn\u011b jen form\u00e1ln\u00ed rozd\u00edl, d\u00edky Kali se tak i Des\u00edtky mohou prom\u011bnit v kybernetickou zbra\u0148. Tedy a\u017e na n\u011bkter\u00e9 drobnosti, ve kter\u00fdch se Windows principi\u00e1ln\u011b li\u0161\u00ed od Linuxu a kter\u00e9 nejsou v linuxov\u00e9m subsyst\u00e9mu zat\u00edm pln\u011b implementovan\u00e9.To se t\u00fdk\u00e1 t\u0159eba ovlada\u010d\u016f hardwaru a typicky \u00fatok\u016f na Wi-Fi, kdy je t\u0159eba p\u0159istupovat hluboko do s\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e9 karty. Pro b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 s\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e9 \u00fatoku v LANu a na internetu v\u0161ak Kali na Windows bez probl\u00e9mu poslou\u017e\u00ed.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Windows 10", "Linux", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Programov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Open source", "Microsoft Store", "Hacking", "Ubuntu", "Cel\u00fd z\u00e1stup", "Termin\u00e1l", "Peklo", "Nativn\u00ed b\u011bh", "S\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e1 karta", "N\u011bkdej\u0161\u00ed tab", "Kybernetick\u00e1 zbra\u0148", "Kali", "\u00datok", "Souborov\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Store", "Linuxov\u00fd subsyst\u00e9m"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/windows-10-nabidnou-nove-nastaveni-soukromi-pri-instalaci-microsoft-testuje-ruzne-varianty/sc-3-a-192150/default.aspx", "title": "Windows 10 nab\u00eddnou nov\u00e9 nastaven\u00ed soukrom\u00ed p\u0159i instalaci. Microsoft testuje r\u016fzn\u00e9 varianty", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "8. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Microsoft se pomalu p\u0159ipravuje na vyd\u00e1n\u00ed  Windows 10. Jej\u00ed sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed budou i p\u0159epracovan\u00e9 mo\u017enosti nastaven\u00ed soukrom\u00ed v syst\u00e9mu p\u0159i jeho instalaci. Aktu\u00e1ln\u011b spole\u010dn\u011b s  testuje, jak\u00e9 proveden\u00ed bude nejlep\u0161\u00ed.Nov\u00e9 nastaven\u00ed soukrom\u00ed se v\u011bnuje krom rozpozn\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed \u0159e\u010di a zaznamen\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed lokace za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed i psan\u00ed perem a funkci . Nov\u011b tak bude snaz\u0161\u00ed vypnout odes\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed dat o vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed, p\u0159\u00edpadn\u011b slu\u017ebu nezap\u00ednat.N\u011bkter\u00e9 mo\u017enosti tu ji\u017e byly d\u0159\u00edve, Microsoft ale nyn\u00ed experimentuje s nov\u00fdm designem obrazovky, kdy se n\u011bkter\u00e9 mo\u017enosti do\u010dkaj\u00ed samostatn\u00fdch dialog\u016f a podrobn\u011bj\u0161\u00edch popisk\u016f. Redmondsk\u00fd gigant tak pokra\u010duje ve snaze zp\u0159ehlednit nastaven\u00ed soukrom\u00ed pro u\u017eivatele a vyvarovat se p\u0159\u00edpadn\u00fdm spor\u016fm, kdy by u\u017eivatel\u016fm nemuselo b\u00fdt z\u0159ejm\u00e9, co v\u0161e zapnut\u00ed konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed funkce znamen\u00e1.Jednotliv\u00e9 designy jsou nyn\u00ed testov\u00e1ny v r\u00e1mci programu Windows Insider a Microsoft se n\u00e1sledn\u011b dle zp\u011btn\u00e9 vazby rozhodne, jak\u00fd fin\u00e1ln\u00ed vzhled nasad\u00ed. Novinka bude dostupn\u00e1 v r\u00e1mci aktualizace .", "tags": ["Software", "Microsoft", "Windows", "Windows 10", "Spring Creators Update", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Aktualizace", "Soukrom\u00ed", "P\u0159\u00edpadn\u00fd spor", "Zp\u011btn\u00e1 vazba", "Instalace", "Jarn\u00ed aktualizace", "Nastaven\u00ed", "Nov\u00e9 nastaven\u00ed", "Insider", "Samostatn\u00fd dialog", "Fin\u00e1ln\u00ed vzhled", "Nov\u00fd design", "Hlavn\u00ed p\u0159ednost"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/microsoft-store-se-konecne-plni-poradnymi-programy-dnes-pribyl-debian/sc-3-a-192169/default.aspx", "title": "Microsoft Store se kone\u010dn\u011b pln\u00ed po\u0159\u00e1dn\u00fdmi programy. Dnes p\u0159ibyl Debian", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "8. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "V\u010dera se Microsoft pochlubil, \u017ee na Windows 10 m\u016f\u017eete rozjet i hackerskou linuxovou distribuci Kali \u2013 tedy jej\u00ed textov\u00fd termin\u00e1l, a dnes se sb\u00edrka  roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159ila o legendu v\u0161ech legend \u2013 .Linuxov\u00e1 distribuce na Windows 10 pob\u011b\u017e\u00ed jako textov\u00fd termin\u00e1l, nejedn\u00e1 se p\u0159itom o izolovanou virtualizaci, ale sp\u00ed\u0161e o podobn\u00fd p\u0159\u00edstup jako v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b aplikace  pro Linux, kter\u00e1 umo\u017e\u0148uje b\u011bh EXE program\u016f ze sv\u011bta Windows. To znamen\u00e1, \u017ee v takov\u00e9m linuxov\u00e9m termin\u00e1lu na Windows m\u016f\u017eete bez probl\u00e9mu p\u0159istupovat do souborov\u00e9ho syst\u00e9mu Windows a dokonce z n\u011bj spou\u0161t\u011bt EXE aplikace.A\u010dkoliv se Microsoft ji\u017e loni chlubil, \u017ee lze v jeho syst\u00e9mu WSL (Windows Subsystem for Linux) pou\u017e\u00edvat i Fedoru, v Microsoft Storu je zat\u00edm nedohledateln\u00e1. Na Mediu nicm\u00e9n\u011b z\u00e1jemci  z konce lo\u0148sk\u00e9ho roku, jak ji na Des\u00edtky opravdu dostat.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Windows 10", "Linux", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Programov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Open source", "Microsoft Store", "Debian", "Ubuntu", "Fedora", "Termin\u00e1l", "Lo\u0148sk\u00fd rok", "Linuxov\u00fd termin\u00e1l", "Linuxov\u00e1 distribuce", "Kali", "WSL", "Textov\u00fd termin\u00e1l", "Program", "Souborov\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Po\u0159\u00e1dn\u00fd program"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/chcete-znicit-internet-na-githubu-najdete-drobny-skript-v-pythonu/sc-3-a-192170/default.aspx", "title": "Chcete zni\u010dit internet? Na GitHubu najdete drobn\u00fd skript v Pythonu", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "8. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Leto\u0161n\u00edm trendem DDoS je zneu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed ve\u0159ejn\u011b dostupn\u00fdch  server\u016f, kter\u00e9 mohou ohromn\u00fdm zp\u016fsobem zesilovat snahu o tot\u00e1ln\u00ed zahlcen\u00ed c\u00edlov\u00e9ho po\u010d\u00edta\u010de nebo cel\u00e9 internetov\u00e9 infrastruktury. Pr\u00e1v\u011b t\u00edmto zp\u016fsobem \u00fato\u010dn\u00edci ned\u00e1vno zahltili GitHub a nejmenovan\u00e9ho americk\u00e9ho oper\u00e1tora datov\u00fdm tokem a\u017e 1,7 Tb/s.Na stejn\u00e9m GitHubu je nyn\u00ed  , kter\u00fd \u00fatok \u201eMemcrashed\u201c s\u00e1m vytvo\u0159\u00ed. Jedin\u00e9, co k jeho b\u011bhu budete pot\u0159ebovat, je adekv\u00e1tn\u00ed API \u00fa\u010det na vyhled\u00e1va\u010di internetu v\u011bc\u00ed . Program toti\u017e t\u00edmto zp\u016fsobem z\u00edsk\u00e1 datab\u00e1zi napadnuteln\u00fdch memcached server\u016f.Memcached server slou\u017e\u00ed u\u017e podle sv\u00e9ho n\u00e1zvu ke cachov\u00e1n\u00ed, a pokud nen\u00ed adekv\u00e1tn\u011b zabezpe\u010den\u00fd, \u00fato\u010dn\u00edk mu m\u016f\u017ee poslat dotaz, na kter\u00fd jako ka\u017ed\u00fd jin\u00fd server odpov\u00ed. \u00dato\u010dn\u00edk v\u0161ak dotaz uprav\u00ed tak, aby server neodpov\u011bd\u011bl jeho IP adrese, ale IP adrese ob\u011bti. A jeliko\u017e bude odpov\u011b\u010f mnohem v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e samotn\u00fd dotaz, \u00fatok bude o to siln\u011bj\u0161\u00ed.Dotaz na memcached, kter\u00fd m\u011bl d\u00e9lku 15 B, v pr\u016fm\u011bru vytvo\u0159\u00ed odpov\u011b\u010f o velikosti , tak\u017ee se jedn\u00e1 o ohromn\u00fd zesilova\u010d, kter\u00fd p\u0159i zapojen\u00ed tis\u00edc\u016f zraniteln\u00fdch server\u016f vytvo\u0159\u00ed ony ohromn\u00e9 datov\u00e9 toky, kter\u00e9 a\u017e n\u011bkolikan\u00e1sobn\u011b p\u0159esahuj\u00ed t\u0159eba ve\u010dern\u00ed \u0161pi\u010dky na cel\u00e9m \u010desk\u00e9m internetu.Po medializaci v posledn\u00edch dnech majitel\u00e9 server\u016f postupn\u011b sjedn\u00e1vaj\u00ed n\u00e1pravu, skript tedy p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm ukazuje, jak \u00fato\u010dn\u00edci nejsp\u00ed\u0161e postupovali.", "tags": ["Internet", "Bezpe\u010dnost", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "Python", "DDoS", "GitHub", "API", "Botnet", "Kyberv\u00e1lka", "Skript", "\u00dato\u010dn\u00edk", "Tot\u00e1ln\u00ed zahlcen\u00ed", "Dostupn\u00fd server", "Server", "Ve\u010dern\u00ed \u0161pi\u010dka", "Zraniteln\u00fd server", "Dotaz", "Leto\u0161n\u00ed trend", "Drobn\u00fd skript", "Komer\u010dn\u00ed banka", "Shodan", "C\u00edlov\u00fd po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Datov\u00fd tok"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/cim-vice-messengeru-tim-vice-google-pridal-chat-do-platebni-aplikace/sc-3-a-192142/default.aspx", "title": "\u010c\u00edm v\u00edce messenger\u016f, t\u00edm v\u00edce Google. P\u0159idal chat do platebn\u00ed aplikace", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "8. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "V Indii se schyluje k dal\u0161\u00edmu souboji platforem. Ned\u00e1vno zde  p\u0159idal mo\u017enost placen\u00ed a pos\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed pen\u011bz a Google nyn\u00ed reaguje roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00edm sv\u00e9 aplikace Tez. Ta doposud slou\u017eila pr\u00e1v\u011b k platb\u00e1m, nov\u011b se z n\u00ed stane i klasick\u00fd messenger. T\u011bch m\u00e1 p\u0159itom Google v\u00edce ne\u017e dost.Tez jako takov\u00fd m\u00e1 na tamn\u00edm trhu p\u0159es 15 milion\u016f u\u017eivatel\u016f, WhatsApp na 200. Rozd\u00edl je to sice velk\u00fd, Google se ale nevzd\u00e1v\u00e1 a hlavn\u00edm l\u00e1kadlem jsou pr\u00e1v\u011b ony platby. Aplikace je napojen\u00e1 na m\u00edstn\u00ed univerz\u00e1ln\u00ed syst\u00e9m plateb a umo\u017e\u0148uje i snadnou platbu \u00fa\u010dt\u016f za elekt\u0159inu, televizi, internet a dal\u0161\u00ed slu\u017eby od v\u00edce ne\u017e 80 spole\u010dnost\u00ed.Celosv\u011btov\u011b se ale jedn\u00e1 o dal\u0161\u00ed z \u0159ady messenger\u016f, kter\u00e9 Google aktu\u00e1ln\u011b provozuje. Ps\u00e1t si m\u016f\u017eete v r\u00e1mci aplikac\u00ed Allo, Hangouts, YouTube, Voice \u010di Android Zpr\u00e1vy, volat skrze Duo a ve firm\u00e1ch m\u016f\u017eete vyu\u017e\u00edt Hangouts Chat a Hangouts Meet. Jeden by si \u0159ekl, zda u\u017e Google nem\u00e1 t\u011bch komunika\u010dn\u00edch aplikac\u00ed p\u0159\u00edli\u0161...", "tags": ["Google", "YouTube", "Android", "WhatsApp", "Instant Messaging", "Chat", "Komunikace", "Indie", "Placen\u00ed mobilem", "Hangouts Meet", "Hangouts chat", "Voice", "Hangouts", "Allo", "Hlavn\u00ed l\u00e1kadlo", "Aplikace", "Platba", "Pos\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed pen\u011bz", "Platebn\u00ed aplikace", "Messenger", "Komunika\u010dn\u00ed aplikace"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/chrome-je-konecne-opravdu-open-source-coze-nebyl-uz-davno/sc-3-a-192121/default.aspx", "title": "Chrome je kone\u010dn\u011b opravdu open-source. Co\u017ee, nebyl u\u017e d\u00e1vno?", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Chrome je kone\u010dn\u011b opravdov\u00fd open-source. Co\u017ee? V\u017edy\u0165 jeho  je p\u0159eci open-source u\u017e od za\u010d\u00e1tku! Ano, nicm\u00e9n\u011b zdrojov\u00e9 k\u00f3dy lze nyn\u00ed na Windows p\u0159elo\u017eit . Doposud k tomu byl pot\u0159eba p\u0159eklada\u010d propriet\u00e1rn\u00edho Visual Studia od Microsoftu (MSVC).Chromium t\u00edmto krokem sjednotilo v\u00fdvoj nejpou\u017e\u00edvan\u011bj\u0161\u00edho prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de na sv\u011bt\u011b, kter\u00fd je z\u00e1rove\u0148 k dispozici na hromad\u011b platforem a lze jej ze zdrojov\u00fdch k\u00f3d\u016f p\u0159elo\u017eit sjednocen\u00fdm open-source bal\u00edkem n\u00e1stroj\u016f.Komunitn\u00ed Clang je v tuto chv\u00edli z\u00e1rove\u0148 jedin\u00fdm p\u0159eklada\u010dem pro Windows, jeho\u017e v\u00fdstupy jsou  s p\u0159eklada\u010dem Visual Studia. V\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159 tedy m\u016f\u017ee bez probl\u00e9mu p\u0159elo\u017eit \u010d\u00e1st projektu ve Visual Studiu a \u010d\u00e1st pomoc\u00ed Clangu, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e to bude fungovat.A co to znamen\u00e1 pro samotn\u00e9 u\u017eivatele? Pokud m\u00e1te na Windows Chrome ve verzi 64, u\u017e je p\u0159elo\u017een\u00fd pomoc\u00ed Clangu. Tato sestaven\u00ed jsou podle \u010d\u00edsel v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159\u016f na 64bitov\u00fdch syst\u00e9mech o p\u00e1r MB men\u0161\u00ed, z hlediska v\u00fdkonu je to ale +/- stejn\u00e9. Podstatn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed je to, \u017ee v\u00fdvoj Chromia nap\u0159\u00ed\u010d platformami bude v\u00edce jednotn\u00fd a potenci\u00e1ln\u011b rychlej\u0161\u00ed.Rozhodnut\u00ed Chromia m\u016f\u017ee m\u00edt v\u00fdhledov\u011b i  efekt. Chrome je obrovsk\u00fd softwarov\u00fd projekt \u2013 v\u017edy\u0165 modern\u00ed webov\u00fd prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d, kter\u00fd spou\u0161t\u00ed komplikovan\u00e9 webov\u00e9 aplikace, je ve sv\u00e9 podstat\u011b takov\u00fd dal\u0161\u00ed opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m.Mohl by b\u00fdt tedy p\u0159\u00edkladem i pro dal\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159e a kdo v\u00ed, \u010dasem by mohl za\u010d\u00edt Clang propagovat ve Visual Studiu i samotn\u00fd Microsoft. Ostatn\u011b do v\u00fdvoje komunitn\u00edho Clangu p\u0159isp\u00edvaj\u00ed i in\u017een\u00fd\u0159i z Redmondu.T\u0159eba se jednoho dne do\u010dk\u00e1me, \u017ee drtiv\u00e1 v\u011bt\u0161ina C/C++ k\u00f3du nehled\u011b na platformu a syst\u00e9m bude p\u0159elo\u017een\u00e1 pomoc\u00ed Clangu, kter\u00fd tak napln\u00ed dns ji\u017e prehistorickou vizi GNU \u2013 ostatn\u011b s\u00e1m se pasuje do role n\u00e1stupce .", "tags": ["Software", "Microsoft", "Windows", "P\u0159eklada\u010d", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "Programov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Open source", "Chrome", "Visual Studio", "Redmond", "C++", "K\u00f3d", "V\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159", "GNU", "Drtiv\u00e1 v\u011bt\u0161ina", "Zdrojov\u00fd k\u00f3d", "MSVC", "GCC", "Chrom"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/microsoft-classic-intellimouse-jaka-je-znovuzrozena-mysi-legenda/sc-3-a-192035/default.aspx", "title": "Microsoft Classic Intellimouse: Jak\u00e1 je znovuzrozen\u00e1 my\u0161\u00ed legenda", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Na konci minul\u00e9ho roku Microsoft p\u0159edstavil novou generaci legend\u00e1rn\u00ed my\u0161i Intellimouse, kter\u00e1 v historii p\u0159inesla \u0159adu revolu\u010dn\u00edch v\u011bc\u00ed, kter\u00e9 se pot\u00e9 staly postupn\u011b standardem. Novinku jsme vyzkou\u0161eli a m\u016f\u017eeme ji tedy srovnat s origin\u00e1lem, kter\u00fd jsme pou\u017e\u00edvali p\u0159ed dvaceti lety. Prvn\u00ed my\u0161 Intellimouse od Microsoftu (n\u00e1stupce Microsoft Mouse 2.0 z roku 1993) p\u0159inesla jako prvn\u00ed n\u011bkolik v\u011bc\u00ed, kter\u00e9 dnes pova\u017eujeme u my\u0161\u00ed za standardn\u00ed sou\u010d\u00e1st. V roce 1996 toti\u017e prvn\u00ed generace Intellimouse p\u0159inesla mezi lev\u00fdm a prav\u00fdm tla\u010d\u00edtkem, kter\u00e9 p\u0159enesly funkce tla\u010d\u00edtek Page Up a Page Down z kl\u00e1vesnice do mnohem p\u0159irozen\u011bj\u0161\u00ed podoby. D\u00edky tomu bylo skrolov\u00e1n\u00ed jednodu\u0161\u0161\u00ed a rychlej\u0161\u00ed. V t\u00e9 dob\u011b toti\u017e za\u010d\u00ednal rozmach internetu a posouv\u00e1n\u00ed u\u017e tak nebylo ot\u00e1zkou pouh\u00fdch dokument\u016f, ale i proch\u00e1zen\u00ed del\u0161\u00edch internetov\u00fdch str\u00e1nek.Dal\u0161\u00ed generace v podob\u011b Intellimouse Explorer v roce 1999 poprv\u00e9 p\u0159inesla optick\u00e9 sn\u00edm\u00e1n\u00ed povrchu  a nahradila tak mechanickou konstrukci s kuli\u010dkou. Microsoft byl tak\u00e9 prvn\u00ed, kdo p\u0159inesl dodate\u010dn\u00e1 postrann\u00ed tla\u010d\u00edtka, kter\u00e1 v dob\u011b internetu na\u0161la skv\u011bl\u00e9 uplatn\u011bn\u00ed pro funk\u010dnost zp\u011bt-dop\u0159edu.Microsoft dnes nab\u00edz\u00ed velkou spoustu my\u0161\u00ed s \u0159adou dal\u0161\u00edch inovac\u00ed a po dlouh\u00e9 pauze se v nab\u00eddce objevil i model s n\u00e1zvem . Ten se hl\u00e1s\u00ed pr\u00e1v\u011b k p\u016fvodn\u00ed generaci jednoduch\u00fdch, ale \u00fa\u010deln\u011b navr\u017een\u00fdch my\u0161\u00ed Intellimouse.S Classic Intellimouse se Microsoft dr\u017eel jednoduchosti p\u016fvodn\u00edch model\u016f my\u0161\u00ed a design je tak na prvn\u00ed pohled zcela oby\u010dejn\u00fd. Kombinuje \u0161ed\u00fd povrch s \u010dern\u00fdmi gumov\u00fdmi okraji.My\u0161 je ur\u010den\u00e1 pro prav\u00e1ky a m\u00e1 jen , p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e jednotliv\u00e9 stupn\u011b kole\u010dka jsou pom\u011brn\u011b tlumen\u00e9. Pokud budete cht\u00edt skrolovat dlouh\u00fd dokument nebo webovou str\u00e1nku, po\u010d\u00edtejte s t\u00edm, \u017ee kole\u010dko nem\u00e1 \u017e\u00e1dnou simulaci zrychlen\u00e9ho skrolov\u00e1n\u00ed a cel\u00e9 si to mus\u00edte \u201eproto\u010dit\u201c sami. Kole\u010dko rovn\u011b\u017e nepodporuje horizont\u00e1ln\u00ed n\u00e1klon, ale m\u016f\u017eete si pomoc\u00ed dodate\u010dn\u00e9ho softwaru Mouse and Keyboard Center 3.2 naprogramovat funk\u010dnost stisku kole\u010dka.Konstrukce p\u016fsob\u00ed robustn\u00edm dojmem a velikost je vhodn\u011b zvolen\u00e1 tak, aby my\u0161 zapadla do dlan\u011b. Nepat\u0159\u00ed k nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edm my\u0161\u00edm, z\u00e1rove\u0148 to ale nen\u00ed \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd notebookov\u00fd prcek. Konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed rozm\u011bry jsou 13,2 \u00d7 6,9 \u00d7 4,3 cm a hmotnost 100 g (bez kabelu). Jedn\u00e1 se o my\u0161 do USB, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e kabel je pevn\u011b p\u0159ipevn\u011bn k my\u0161i.Velmi p\u011bkn\u00fdm designov\u00fdm prvkem je elegantn\u00edm b\u00edl\u00e9 podsv\u00edcen\u00ed, kter\u00e9 je um\u00edst\u011bn\u00e9 v zadn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1sti my\u0161i a p\u016fsob\u00ed futuristicky. Microsoft u t\u00e9to my\u0161i pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 pokro\u010dil\u00fd patentovan\u00fd senzor , kter\u00fd m\u00e1 typick\u00e9 modr\u00e9 zabarven\u00ed a porad\u00ed si nejen se sklen\u011bn\u00fdm, ale t\u0159eba i mramorov\u00fdm povrchem. Rozli\u0161en\u00ed pou\u017eit\u00e9ho sn\u00edma\u010de je 3 200 DPI a my\u0161i vys\u00edl\u00e1 sign\u00e1l 1 000\u00d7 za sekundu.V praxi m\u016f\u017ee trochu vadit hladk\u00fd povrch postrann\u00edch \u010d\u00e1st\u00ed my\u0161i, po kter\u00fdch maj\u00ed prsty tendenci sklouznout. D\u00e1 se na to ale zvyknout a my\u0161 se po p\u00e1r hodin\u00e1ch pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed ovl\u00e1d\u00e1 dob\u0159e, hlavn\u011b d\u00edky n\u00edzk\u00e9 hmotnosti.My\u0161 Microsoft Classic stoj\u00ed . Pokud hled\u00e1te kabelovou my\u0161, kter\u00e1 m\u00e1 modern\u00ed senzor a jednoduch\u00fd styl, je Classic Intellimouse ur\u010dit\u011b dobrou volbou. Pokud ale v\u00edce hrajete nebo pot\u0159ebujete my\u0161 i \u010dasto p\u0159en\u00e1\u0161et na cest\u00e1ch, je vhodn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed zvolit specializovan\u00e9 modely na hran\u00ed \u010di mobilitu.To sam\u00e9 plat\u00ed i pro n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00e9 profesion\u00e1ly, kte\u0159\u00ed ve velk\u00e9m pou\u017e\u00edvaj\u00ed nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed zkratky. Na trhu je \u0159ada my\u0161\u00ed, kter\u00e9 obsahuj\u00ed v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed po\u010det programovateln\u00fdch tla\u010d\u00edtek, tomu ale pochopiteln\u011b odpov\u00edd\u00e1 konstrukce i v\u00fdsledn\u00e1 vy\u0161\u0161\u00ed cena.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "USB", "My\u0161i", "P\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed", "Inovace", "Standardn\u00ed sou\u010d\u00e1st", "Postrann\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st", "Mechanick\u00e1 konstrukce", "N\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00fd profesion\u00e1l", "BlueTrack", "Jednoduch\u00fd styl", "N\u00edzk\u00e1 hmotnost", "Tla\u010d\u00edtko", "Minul\u00fd rok", "Jednoduchost", "IntelliMouse", "Star\u00fd model", "Prvn\u00ed pohled", "Revolu\u010dn\u00ed v\u011bc", "IntelliEye", "Dodate\u010dn\u00fd software", "Lev\u00e9 tla\u010d\u00edtko", "IntelliMouse Explorer", "Pou\u017eit\u00fd sn\u00edma\u010d", "Modern\u00ed senzor"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/novy-android-ma-premenit-mobily-na-mysi-a-klavesnice/sc-3-a-192133/default.aspx", "title": "Nov\u00fd Android m\u00e1 p\u0159em\u011bnit mobily na my\u0161i a kl\u00e1vesnice", "author": "Martin Kov\u00e1\u010d", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Zd\u00e1 se, \u017ee chystan\u00e1 nov\u00e1 verze opera\u010dn\u00edho syst\u00e9mu Android, kter\u00e1 je p\u0159edb\u011b\u017en\u011b zn\u00e1m\u00e1 jako \"Android P\", p\u0159inese vcelku zaj\u00edmavou novinku z pohledu vyu\u017eit\u00ed mobilu jako standardn\u00ed periferie pro ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed.Na z\u00e1klad\u011b zkoum\u00e1n\u00ed zdrojov\u00fdch k\u00f3d\u016f toti\u017e Xda-developers  , \u017ee sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed syst\u00e9mu by m\u011bla b\u00fdt mo\u017enost nativn\u00ed prom\u011bny telefon\u016f \u010di tablet\u016f na my\u0161i, resp. kl\u00e1vesnice.Pomoc\u00ed mobilu \u010di tabletu tak budeme moci jednodu\u0161e ovl\u00e1dat jin\u00e1 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed, typicky multimedi\u00e1ln\u00ed p\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010de nebo chytr\u00e9 televize, ale klidn\u011b tak\u00e9 po\u010d\u00edta\u010de nebo jin\u00e9 telefony. Mobil se p\u0159ipoj\u00ed p\u0159es bluetooth prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm standardn\u00edho profilu HID (Human Interface Device), kter\u00fd vyu\u017e\u00edvaj\u00ed b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 kl\u00e1vesnice a my\u0161i. Nen\u00ed tedy pot\u0159eba \u0159e\u0161it oboustrannou instalaci aplikac\u00ed, aby mohl mobil poslou\u017eit jako bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e1 kl\u00e1vesnice \u010di touchpad.P\u0159edb\u011b\u017en\u011b nen\u00ed jasn\u00e9, jak p\u0159esn\u011b bude podpora HID implementov\u00e1na. Zda p\u016fjde o n\u011bjakou zabudovanou aplikaci, nastaven\u00ed nebo speci\u00e1ln\u00ed u\u017eivatelsk\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed Androidu P.", "tags": ["Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Mobility", "Android", "Kl\u00e1vesnice", "My\u0161i", "P\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed", "Standardn\u00ed profil", "Zaj\u00edmav\u00e1 novinka", "Standardn\u00ed periferie", "Z\u00e1klad zkoum\u00e1n\u00ed", "Tablety", "Multimedi\u00e1ln\u00ed p\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010d", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e1 kl\u00e1vesnice", "Chytr\u00e1 televize", "Bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e1 kl\u00e1vesnice", "Zdrojov\u00fd k\u00f3d", "Aplikace", "Mobil", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/otestovali-jsme-6-pocitacu-v-monitoru-v-cem-jsou-lepsi-nez-tradicni-pocitace/sc-3-a-192144/default.aspx", "title": "Otestovali jsme 6 po\u010d\u00edta\u010d\u016f v monitoru: v \u010dem jsou lep\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e tradi\u010dn\u00ed po\u010d\u00edta\u010de?", "author": "\u010casopis Computer", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010de v monitoru jsou elegantn\u00ed a p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm ji\u017e dostate\u010dn\u011b rychl\u00e9. Za posledn\u00ed rok se v\u00fdrazn\u011b zlep\u0161ila jejich v\u00fdbava i v\u00fdkon a za rozumnou cenu z\u00edsk\u00e1te \"bezstarostn\u00e9\" \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed. Skv\u011ble se hod\u00ed do nen\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00e9 dom\u00e1cnosti s omezen\u00fdm prostorem, do kancel\u00e1\u0159e nebo na recepci.Otestovali jsme \u0161est po\u010d\u00edta\u010d\u016f ve dvou kategori\u00edch, s cenou do 17 a 25 tis\u00edc korun.Napi\u0161te SMS na \u010d\u00edslo  ve tvaru:P\u0159\u00edklad: COMPUTER 1803 Jan Novak Prubezna 233 Olomouc 77900Cena ka\u017ed\u00e9 p\u0159ijat\u00e9 SMS je 89 K\u010d, stejn\u011b jako \u010dasopis na st\u00e1nc\u00edch. Zahrnuje po\u0161tovn\u00e9 i baln\u00e9. Provozuje CN INVEST, a. s., infolinka 296 363 199 ve v\u0161edn\u00ed dny 8\u201316 hod., , .Otestovali jsme tyto po\u010d\u00edta\u010de v monitoru:Tento velk\u00fd test i velk\u00fd test hern\u00edch monitor\u016f najdete v Computeru 3/18. ", "tags": ["\u010casopis Computer", "Lenovo", "Testlab", "All-in-one", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Rozumn\u00e1 cena", "Computer", "Nen\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00e1 dom\u00e1cnost", "Monitor", "Cenn\u00e1 koruna", "SMS", "Olomouc", "Velk\u00fd test", "Bezstarostn\u00e9 \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed", "Chlazen\u00ed", "Omezen\u00fd prostor", "Tradi\u010dn\u00ed po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Aspire", "Hern\u00ed monitor", "Acer Aspire", "V\u00fdbava", "Mezera"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/na-street-view-se-podivate-uz-do-jedenacti-disneylandu-treba-do-sveta-avatara-ci-strazcu-galaxie/sc-3-a-192131/default.aspx", "title": "Na Street View se pod\u00edv\u00e1te u\u017e do jeden\u00e1cti Disneyland\u016f. T\u0159eba do sv\u011bta Avatara \u010di Str\u00e1\u017ec\u016f Galaxie", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Dnes se Google pochlubil, \u017ee se v r\u00e1mci sv\u00e9ho Street View pod\u00edval do 11 r\u016fzn\u00fdch Disneyland\u016f a d\u00edky tomu se v nich nyn\u00ed m\u016f\u017eete virtu\u00e1ln\u011b proj\u00edt. Nemus\u00edte tak cestovat tis\u00edce kilometr\u016f, abyste se pod\u00edvali na d\u016fm my\u0161\u00e1ka Mickeyho \u010di na planetu Pandoru z Avatara.()()()()()()()()()()()()()()()()", "tags": ["Mapy Google", "Google", "Street View", "Link", "Disneyland", "Hollywood", "Mickey", "Avatar"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/suskanda-apple-prestane-prodavat-muziku/sc-3-a-192151/default.aspx", "title": "\u0160u\u0161kanda: Apple p\u0159estane prod\u00e1vat muziku", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Apple podle britsk\u00e9ho pl\u00e1tku pl\u00e1nuje  prodeje muziky ve sv\u00e9m iTunes. Tamn\u00ed Metro cituje e-mail odeslan\u00fd t\u00fdmem hudebn\u00edho obchodu vydavatel\u016fm s t\u00edm, \u017ee brzy p\u0159estanou p\u0159ij\u00edmat nov\u00e9 desky ke klasick\u00e9mu prodeji.Pakli\u017ee je zpr\u00e1va pravdiv\u00e1, znamen\u00e1 to, \u017ee by Apple nap\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u011b nab\u00edzel hudbu jen jako p\u0159edplatn\u00e9 a tedy definitivn\u011b p\u0159e\u0161el na obchodn\u00ed model podobn\u00fd t\u0159eba Spotify. O ukon\u010den\u00ed prodeje muziky se spekulovalo u\u017e v minulosti, Apple v\u0161ak podobn\u00e9 zpr\u00e1vy v\u017edy dementoval. V ka\u017ed\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, i podle hudebn\u00edch analytik\u016f se trh definitivn\u011b m\u011bn\u00ed a klasick\u00fd prodej rok od roku kles\u00e1, Apple by se tedy pouze p\u0159izp\u016fsobil aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed situaci.Apple pat\u0159il k hlavn\u00edm propag\u00e1tor\u016fm digit\u00e1ln\u00edho prodeje muziky u\u017e p\u0159ed lety, tak\u017ee zat\u00edmco ostatn\u00ed si je\u0161t\u011b st\u00e1le kupovali , majitel\u00e9 iPod\u016f a iPhon\u016f si po\u0159\u00eddili muziku rovnou v elektronick\u00e9 podob\u011b. Zpo\u010d\u00e1tku byla distribuce omezen\u00e1 DRM, to v\u0161ak pozd\u011bji padlo a iTunes si k n\u00e1kupu muziky v AAC (M4A) obl\u00edbili i ostatn\u00ed \u2013 nakupovat bylo mo\u017en\u00e9 t\u0159eba i z iTunes pro Windows.Pak v\u0161ak na sc\u00e9nu p\u0159i\u0161ly slu\u017eby jako Deezer, Spotify, Play Music od Googlu a o streamov\u00e1n\u00ed a syst\u00e9m hudebn\u00edho p\u0159edplatn\u00e9ho se za\u010dal zaj\u00edmat i Apple, kter\u00fd na tomto poli tro\u0161ku zaspal a situaci doh\u00e1n\u011bl a\u017e v posledn\u00edch letech.  ", "tags": ["Google", "Apple", "Windows", "P\u0159edplatn\u00e9", "Spotify", "iPhone", "Deezer", "iTunes", "iPod", "Muzika", "AAC", "Digit\u00e1ln\u00ed prodej", "\u0160u\u0161kanda", "Brzk\u00e9 ukon\u010den\u00ed", "Elektronick\u00e1 podoba", "Ukon\u010den\u00ed prodeje", "Hlavn\u00ed propag\u00e1tor", "Obchodn\u00ed model", "Prodej", "Play Music", "Nov\u00e1 deska", "Hudebn\u00ed p\u0159edplatn\u00e9", "Klasick\u00fd prodej", "Hudebn\u00ed obchod"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/diody-na-hernim-hardwaru-nemusi-jen-hloupe-svitit-far-cry-5-umozni-zmenu-barev-podle-deni-ve-hre/sc-3-a-192100/default.aspx", "title": "Diody na hern\u00edm hardwaru nemus\u00ed jen hloup\u011b sv\u00edtit. Far Cry 5 umo\u017en\u00ed zm\u011bnu barev podle d\u011bn\u00ed ve h\u0159e", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Podsv\u00edcen\u00e9 po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed v\u0161eho druhu \u2013 my\u0161i, podlo\u017eky pod my\u0161, kl\u00e1vesnice, sluch\u00e1tka, ventil\u00e1tory, opera\u010dn\u00ed pam\u011bti, sk\u0159\u00edn\u011b a dal\u0161\u00ed... v\u0161ude u\u017e dnes najdete LED osv\u011btlen\u00ed s celou \u0161k\u00e1lou RGB. U nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00edch produkt\u016f renomovan\u00fdch zna\u010dek u\u017e je k dispozici i pokro\u010dil\u00fd ovl\u00e1dac\u00ed software, kter\u00fd dok\u00e1\u017ee synchronizovat efekty i mezi jednotliv\u00fdm p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00edm a jde se je\u0161t\u011b d\u00e1l.U\u017e d\u0159\u00edve se objevily prvn\u00ed n\u00e1znaky propojen\u00ed interaktivity s konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed b\u011b\u017e\u00edc\u00ed aplikac\u00ed \u010di hrou, Corsair ale nyn\u00ed ohl\u00e1sil ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed spolupr\u00e1ci a podporu u nadch\u00e1zej\u00edc\u00ed nov\u00e9 hry Far Cry 5 od spole\u010dnosti Ubisoft.D\u00edky nov\u00e9mu univerz\u00e1ln\u00edmu \u0159\u00eddic\u00edmu softwaru, kter\u00fd Corsair vypust\u00ed 27. b\u0159ezna, tak bude mo\u017en\u00e9 roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159it z\u00e1\u017eitek ze hry i mimo monitor. Software toti\u017e ovl\u00e1dne v\u0161echny druhy p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed Corsairu s RGB LED podsv\u00edcen\u00edm.Podsv\u00edcen\u00ed \u010d\u00e1sti kl\u00e1vesnice a dal\u0161\u00edho p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed bude reagovat na aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed d\u011bn\u00ed ve h\u0159e Far Cry 5, kter\u00e1 vyjde rovn\u011b\u017e 27. b\u0159ezna. Podsv\u00edcen\u00ed se bude p\u0159izp\u016fsobovat nap\u0159\u00edklad podle toho, jak bl\u00edzko je nep\u0159\u00edtel a zda v\u00e1s vid\u00ed, pokud m\u00e1te m\u00e1lo \u017eivota, ryba\u0159\u00edte nebo se t\u0159eba jen tak voln\u011b proch\u00e1z\u00edte hern\u00edm sv\u011btem. Takov\u00fdch situac\u00ed bude implementov\u00e1no v\u00edce ne\u017e 35, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e lze o\u010dek\u00e1vat, \u017ee se v aktualizac\u00edch objev\u00ed t\u0159eba i dal\u0161\u00ed.Corsait s Ubisoftem utvo\u0159ili i spolupr\u00e1ci na prodej podsv\u00edcen\u00e9ho p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed. Pokud si p\u0159\u00edmo z e-shopu Corsair objedn\u00e1te RGB LED p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed v hodnot\u011b v\u00edce ne\u017e 150 dolar\u016f, dostanete v obdob\u00ed 23. b\u0159ezna a\u017e 30 dubna hru Far Cry 5 zdarma.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Hry", "Kl\u00e1vesnice", "My\u0161i", "P\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed", "Zm\u011bna barev", "Ubisoft", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed pam\u011b\u0165", "Prvn\u00ed n\u00e1znak", "Dioda", "RGB LED", "Podsv\u00edcen\u00ed", "Cel\u00e1 \u0161k\u00e1la", "RGB", "Corsair", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed produkt", "Hern\u00ed sv\u011bt", "Hern\u00ed hardware", "Dolar", "D\u011bn\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/nejhruznejsi-ddos-historie-byl-silnejsi-nez-cely-cesky-internet-ve-spicce/sc-3-a-192122/default.aspx", "title": "Nejhr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed DDoS historie: Byl siln\u011bj\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e cel\u00fd \u010desk\u00fd internet ve \u0161pi\u010dce", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Zat\u00edmco je\u0161t\u011b p\u0159ed rokem dosahovala s\u00edla t\u011bch nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edch \u00fatok\u016f DDoS  stovek Gb/s, letos to jsou u\u017e Tb/s. P\u0159ed p\u00e1r dny se musel s  pot\u00fdkat GitHub a v\u010dera se bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed experti z Arbor Networks pochlubili, \u017ee ochr\u00e1nili nejmenovan\u00e9ho americk\u00e9ho internetov\u00e9ho poskytovatele p\u0159ed masivn\u00ed d\u011blost\u0159elbou, Jen pro p\u0159edstavu, dv\u011bma nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edmi \u010desk\u00fdmi peeringy, co\u017e jsou uzly, kter\u00e9 propojuj\u00ed tuzemsk\u00e9 oper\u00e1tory a hostingov\u00e1 centra, b\u011bhem denn\u00ed \u0161pi\u010dky prote\u010de okolo 600 Gb/s (, ). \u00datok na GitHub byl tedy nejsp\u00ed\u0161e siln\u011bj\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e aktivita cel\u00e9ho tuzemsk\u00e9ho internetu b\u011bhem obvykl\u00e9 ve\u010dern\u00ed \u0161pi\u010dky. No a ten n\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00ed \u00fatok, kter\u00fd byl je\u0161t\u011b masivn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed, pak p\u0159ekonal aktivitu v cel\u00e9m \u201e\u010ceskoslovensku.\u201cZa \u00fatokem st\u00e1lo zneu\u017eit\u00ed ve\u0159ejn\u011b dostupn\u00fdch  server\u016f, kter\u00e9 zrychluj\u00ed na\u010d\u00edt\u00e1n\u00ed webov\u00fdch str\u00e1nek.A p\u0159esto\u017ee jsou motivy \u00fato\u010dn\u00edk\u016f r\u016fznorod\u00e9 od aktivizmu po st\u00e1tn\u00ed kyber\u00fatok, s\u00edl\u00ed i po\u010det t\u011bch, kte\u0159\u00ed se skrze DDoS sna\u017e\u00ed z\u00edskat v\u00fdkupn\u00e9 \u2013 typicky v kryptom\u011bn\u00e1ch. Po\u017eaduj\u00ed tedy od ob\u011bti zaplatit t\u0159eba v bitcoinech nebo moneru, jinak nep\u0159estanou.", "tags": ["Web", "Internet", "Bezpe\u010dnost", "Statistiky", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "Hacking", "Malware", "Poskytovatel\u00e9 internetu", "DDoS", "GitHub", "Denn\u00ed \u0161pi\u010dka", "Datov\u00fd tok", "Arbor Networks", "Tuzemsk\u00fd oper\u00e1tor", "NIX", "\u00datok", "Bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed expert", "\u010ceskoslovensko", "Webov\u00e1 str\u00e1nka", "\u0160pi\u010dka", "Dostupn\u00fd server", "Posledn\u00ed rok", "\u010cesk\u00fd internet", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed DDOS", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed \u00fatok"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/co-nabidne-teched-devcon-2018-databazistum/sc-3-a-192130/default.aspx", "title": "Co nab\u00eddne TechEd-DevCon 2018 datab\u00e1zist\u016fm?", "author": null, "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed IT konference v \u010cR, TechEd-DevCon, vznikla spojen\u00edm p\u016fvodn\u011b samostatn\u00fdch akc\u00ed TechEd a DevCon (Technical Education & Developer Database Conference), tak\u017ee je z\u010d\u00e1sti ur\u010dena pr\u00e1v\u011b pro datab\u00e1zov\u00e9 specialisty. Jej\u00ed koncepce je v sou\u010dasn\u00e9 dob\u011b takov\u00e1, \u017ee p\u0159edn\u00e1\u0161ky a prezentace prob\u00edhaj\u00ed soub\u011b\u017en\u011b v p\u011bti tematicky zam\u011b\u0159en\u00fdch s\u00e1lech.Tzv. BigData Hall s p\u0159edn\u00e1\u0161kami p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm z oblast\u00ed SQL Serveru a Business Intelligence, je ur\u010den\u00e1 pr\u00e1v\u011b pro odborn\u00edky na spr\u00e1vu, zpracov\u00e1n\u00ed a vyt\u011b\u017een\u00ed dat. Ti se letos krom\u011b informac\u00ed o novink\u00e1ch (mj. z nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed konference Microsoftu Build v Seattlu, kter\u00e1 prob\u011bhne kr\u00e1tce p\u0159ed konferenc\u00ed Gopasu) mohou t\u011b\u0161it na pestrou paletu dal\u0161\u00edch t\u00e9mat.O \u010dem bude konkr\u00e9tn\u011b \u0159e\u010d? P\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm o SQL Serveru, ale opomenuty nebudou ani cloudov\u00e9 technologie nebo Power BI. Pokud jde o SQL Server, mluvit se bude o administraci, instalaci a konfiguraci, tvorb\u011b dotaz\u016f v jazyce T-SQL, Azure a spr\u00e1v\u011b rela\u010dn\u00edch datab\u00e1z\u00ed, anal\u00fdze dat s SQL Server Reporting Services, v\u00fdvoji datov\u00fdch model\u016f, spr\u00e1v\u011b \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed SQL BI, Data Science v cloudu a Azure Machine Learning, \u010di zpracov\u00e1n\u00ed dat v cloudu.A jak je u odborn\u00fdch konferenc\u00ed po\u0159\u00e1dan\u00fdch Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dovou \u0161kolou Gopas dobr\u00fdm zvykem, informace o novink\u00e1ch a jednotliv\u00fdch n\u00e1stroj\u00edch budou dopln\u011bn\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edklady jejich praktick\u00e9ho uplatn\u011bn\u00ed a uk\u00e1zkami \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed probl\u00e9m\u016f z re\u00e1ln\u00e9 praxe. Chyb\u011bt nebude ani \u201eAsk the expert\u201c st\u00e1nek, kde je mo\u017en\u00e9 v pr\u016fb\u011bhu konference prodiskutovat konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed probl\u00e9my s odborn\u00edky z \u0159ad p\u0159edn\u00e1\u0161ej\u00edc\u00edch.P\u0159\u00edprava odborn\u00e9 konference TechEd-DevCon 2018, kter\u00e1 tentokr\u00e1t prob\u011bhne ve dnech 14. a\u017e 17. kv\u011btna, pr\u00e1v\u011b vrchol\u00ed. Informace o jej\u00edm programu i jednotliv\u00fdch p\u0159edn\u00e1\u0161ej\u00edc\u00edch budou postupn\u011b dopl\u0148ov\u00e1ny na . Ale u\u017e te\u010f je mo\u017en\u00e9 \u0159\u00edci, \u017ee v\u00edce ne\u017e t\u0159etina vstupenek na \u0161estn\u00e1ct\u00fd ro\u010dn\u00edk konference TechEd-DevCon je ji\u017e vyprod\u00e1na a kapacita se rychle zapl\u0148uje.Pro datab\u00e1zov\u00e9 specialisty a odborn\u00edky na zpracov\u00e1n\u00ed dat p\u0159ipravuje Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e1 \u0161kola Gopas i \u0159adu \u0161kolen\u00ed a kurz\u016f. Podrobn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed informace o nab\u00eddce k MS SQL Serveru najdete .", "tags": []}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/chytre-tenisky-pizza-hut-objednaji-pizzu-a-pozastavi-televizi-jakmile-dorazi/sc-3-a-192134/default.aspx", "title": "Chytr\u00e9 tenisky Pizza Hut objednaj\u00ed pizzu. A pozastav\u00ed televizi, jakmile doraz\u00ed", "author": "Mark\u00e9ta Mike\u0161ov\u00e1", "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Pokud se tr\u00e1p\u00edte, \u017ee v\u00e1m tenisky nezvl\u00e1dnou objednat pizzu, pak m\u00e1me dobrou zpr\u00e1vu \u2013 u\u017e i n\u011bco takov\u00e9ho existuje. S chytr\u00fdmi teniskami p\u0159i\u0161el americk\u00fd \u0159et\u011bzec rychl\u00e9ho ob\u010derstven\u00ed Pizza Hut, kter\u00fd je zam\u011b\u0159en pr\u00e1v\u011b na pizzu. Za\u0159adil se tak ke KFC, kter\u00e9 tak\u00e9 r\u00e1do vytv\u00e1\u0159\u00ed podivn\u00e9 technologick\u00e9 gadgety.Tenisky se naz\u00fdvaj\u00ed Pie Tops II a jsou ve skute\u010dnosti ji\u017e druhou generac\u00ed. \u00dapln\u011b prvn\u00ed Pie Tops p\u0159i\u0161ly minul\u00fd rok. Rovn\u011b\u017e um\u011bly objednat pizzu, ale nebylo je mo\u017en\u00e9 b\u011b\u017en\u011b koupit. To te\u010f p\u016fjde.Princip chytr\u00fdch tenisek je naprosto trivi\u00e1ln\u00ed. P\u0159es bluetooth se spoj\u00ed s telefonem a v tenisk\u00e1ch implementovan\u00e9 tla\u010d\u00edtko vys\u00edl\u00e1 povely do aplikace Pie Tops, kter\u00e1 n\u00e1sledn\u011b objedn\u00e1vku obl\u00edben\u00e9 pizzy u\u010din\u00ed. Dvojit\u00fd klik ud\u011bl\u00e1 p\u0159\u00edmou objedn\u00e1vku p\u0159edefinovan\u00e9 obl\u00edben\u00e9 pizzy, ani\u017e byste na telefon museli s\u00e1hnout (zobraz\u00ed se jen notifikace o objedn\u00e1vce).  Aby to nebylo a\u017e tak primitivn\u00ed, maj\u00ed boty vychyt\u00e1vku, \u017ee automaticky pozastav\u00ed va\u0161\u00ed televizi (pokud ji m\u00e1te chytrou), kdy\u017e vstanete z gau\u010de, abyste si pizzu od dve\u0159\u00ed p\u0159inesli. Jakmile se vr\u00e1t\u00edte, televize se zase pust\u00ed. Do prodeje p\u016fjde zpo\u010d\u00e1tku pouze 50 p\u00e1r\u016f, kter\u00e9 bude mo\u017en\u00e9 po\u0159\u00eddit v\u00fdhradn\u011b na str\u00e1nce . Prodej bude zah\u00e1jen 19. b\u0159ezna leto\u0161n\u00edho roku. U\u017e je ov\u0161em ozn\u00e1meno, \u017ee \u010dasem jich bude dostupn\u00fdch v\u00edce. Po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 se s dv\u011bma barevn\u00fdmi variantami - \u010dervenou a b\u00e9\u017eovou. Jak\u00e1 bude cena se je\u0161t\u011b nev\u00ed.", "tags": ["Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Televize", "Nositelnosti", "Leto\u0161n\u00ed rok", "Americk\u00fd \u0159et\u011bzec", "Druh\u00e1 generace", "Dvojit\u00fd klik", "Telefon", "Objedn\u00e1vka", "Gadget", "Rychl\u00e9 ob\u010derstven\u00ed", "Pizza Hut", "Prodej", "Dobr\u00e1 zpr\u00e1va", "KFC"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jak-spravovat-hesla/sc-3-a-192182/default.aspx", "title": "Jak spravovat hesla", "author": null, "date": "7. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Jako u\u017eivatel\u00e9 internetu jist\u011b m\u00e1te n\u011bkolik str\u00e1nek, na kter\u00e9 se vrac\u00edte ka\u017ed\u00fd den. Po n\u011bjak\u00e9m \u010dase u\u017e za\u010dne b\u00fdt otrava zdlouhav\u011b se p\u0159ihla\u0161ovat znovu a znovu. Jak si u\u0161et\u0159it \u010das a spravovat hesla se dozv\u00edte v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu. ", "tags": ["Tipy", "Heslo", "Jak na Internet", "\u010cas", "Otrava", "U\u017eivatel internetu", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video"]}
