{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/elonovinky-jak-elon-musk-stoura-do-umele-inteligence/sc-3-a-192124/default.aspx", "title": "ELONOVINKY: Jak Elon Musk \u0161\u0165our\u00e1 do um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence", "author": "Petr Melechin", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Je tu \u00fater\u00fd a s n\u00edm dal\u0161\u00ed d\u00edl po\u0159adu Elonovinky, kter\u00fd ka\u017ed\u00fd t\u00fdden informuje o aktivit\u00e1ch firem Elona Muska. Dnes bude \u0159e\u010d o firm\u011b , kterou Elon Musk zalo\u017eil docela ned\u00e1vno. Bude se v\u011bnovat propojen\u00ed lidsk\u00e9 mysli s po\u010d\u00edta\u010dem a v\u00fdvoji um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence.V oblasti um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence je Elon Musk aktivn\u00ed u\u017e dlouh\u00e9 roky. Investoval nap\u0159\u00edklad do projekt\u016f DeepMind nebo OpenAI, aby byl v t\u011bsn\u011bj\u0161\u00edm kontaktu s nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00edmi objevy. Vyjad\u0159uje p\u0159itom obavu z toho, \u017ee pokro\u010dil\u00e1 um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt velk\u00fdm nebezpe\u010d\u00edm pro lidstvo.Elonovinky vych\u00e1z\u00ed ve spolupr\u00e1ci s webem .", "tags": ["Video", "Elonovinky", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Elon Musk", "Mozek", "DeepMind", "Lidsk\u00e1 mysl", "Neuralink", "V\u00fdvoj", "Velk\u00e9 nebezpe\u010d\u00ed", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Inteligence", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed objev", "Lidstvo", "D\u00edl po\u0159adu"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/hraci-maji-jasno-zdaleka-nejoblibenejsi-kombinaci-hardwaru-je-procesor-intel-a-grafika-nvidia/sc-3-a-192112/default.aspx", "title": "Hr\u00e1\u010di maj\u00ed jasno, zdaleka nejobl\u00edben\u011bj\u0161\u00ed kombinac\u00ed hardwaru je procesor Intel a grafika Nvidia", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Steam od Valve je nejpopul\u00e1rn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed platformou pro distribuci a n\u00e1kup po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00fdch her, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e z\u00e1rove\u0148 slou\u017e\u00ed i jako ochrann\u00fd syst\u00e9m, p\u0159es kter\u00fd se hry spou\u0161t\u00ed a aktualizuj\u00ed. D\u00edky tomu poskytuje pravideln\u011b podrobn\u00e9 statistiky, kter\u00e9 ukazuj\u00ed aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed stav a trendy. V nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00edm p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b se pod\u00edv\u00e1me, jak\u00e1 byla situace v .St\u00e1le plat\u00ed, \u017ee kombinace Intelu a Nvidie pat\u0159\u00ed mezi hr\u00e1\u010di mezi nejobl\u00edben\u011bj\u0161\u00ed. Procesory Intel maj\u00ed pod\u00edl 91 % a Nvidia se sv\u00fdmi grafick\u00fdmi kartami pak rovn\u011b\u017e vysok\u00fdch 85 %. V\u011bt\u0161ina hr\u00e1\u010d\u016f u\u017e je vybaven\u00e1 \u010dty\u0159j\u00e1drov\u00fdmi procesory, kter\u00e9 tvo\u0159\u00ed 72 % v\u0161ech sestav.Hran\u00ed je v drtiv\u00e9 v\u011bt\u0161in\u011b p\u0159\u00edpad\u016f provozov\u00e1no na opera\u010dn\u00edm syst\u00e9mu Windows, kter\u00fd m\u00e1 98,3 % hr\u00e1\u010d\u016f. Apple a jeho macOS pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 pro hran\u00ed 1,3 % hr\u00e1\u010d\u016f, kte\u0159\u00ed hraj\u00ed nejv\u00edce na MacBooku Pro. Linux pak pro hran\u00ed her vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 pouze 0,3 % u\u017eivatel\u016f.Zat\u00edmco nyn\u00ed m\u00e1 nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed pod\u00edl (68,5 %) Windows 7 a Windows 10 jen 25 %, minul\u00fd rok byla situace jin\u00e1 \u2013 Windows 10 m\u011bla polovina hr\u00e1\u010d\u016f. D\u016fvodem zm\u011bny pod\u00edlu je obrovsk\u00fd n\u00e1stup hr\u00e1\u010d\u016f z asijsk\u00e9ho trhu, kde maj\u00ed hr\u00e1\u010di obvykle star\u0161\u00ed po\u010d\u00edta\u010de a rovn\u011b\u017e slab\u0161\u00ed komponenty. Tomu odpov\u00eddaj\u00ed i propady pod\u00edl\u016f nap\u0159\u00edklad monitor\u016f s rozli\u0161en\u00edm Full HD a naopak zvy\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed pod\u00edlu monitor\u016f s rozli\u0161en\u00edm t\u0159eba jen 1 366 \u00d7 768 pixel\u016f.Zaj\u00edmavost\u00ed jsou ale i zm\u011bny v oblasti headset\u016f pro virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed realitu. Zat\u00edmco d\u0159\u00edve m\u011blo HTC Vive n\u00e1skok oproti Oculus Rift, nyn\u00ed u\u017e se situace obr\u00e1tila a naopak Oculus Rift m\u00e1 47,3 % majitel\u016f a HTC Vive pak 45,4 % majitel\u016f VR syst\u00e9m\u016f. Situace je tak hodn\u011b vyrovnan\u00e1 a ur\u010dit\u011b tomu pomohly i velk\u00e9 slevy. Tak\u00e9 m\u016f\u017eeme vid\u011bt men\u0161\u00ed n\u00e1stup syst\u00e9m\u016f Windows Mixed Reality, kter\u00e9 u\u017e maj\u00ed pod\u00edl 5,3 %.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Windows", "Linux", "Intel", "Steam", "Nvidia", "Virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed realita", "Statistiky", "Oculus Rift", "Hry", "HTC", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed pod\u00edl", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed p\u0159\u00edpad", "Kombinace", "Velk\u00e1 sleva", "Full HD", "Star\u00fd po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Pod\u00edl", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e1 hra", "Asijsk\u00fd trh", "Podrobn\u00e1 statistika", "Drtiv\u00e1 v\u011bt\u0161ina", "Grafick\u00e1 karta", "Procesor"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/klicovani-pozadi-v-realnem-case-i-bez-zeleneho-platna-nova-funkce-youtube-stories/sc-3-a-192109/default.aspx", "title": "Kl\u00ed\u010dov\u00e1n\u00ed pozad\u00ed v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase i bez zelen\u00e9ho pl\u00e1tna: nov\u00e1 funkce YouTube Stories", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "YouTube p\u0159ed ned\u00e1vnem  s vybran\u00fdmi tv\u016frci sv\u016fj vlastn\u00ed klon Snapchat Stories. Nyn\u00ed p\u0159id\u00e1v\u00e1 u\u017eivatel\u016fm mo\u017enost vyu\u017e\u00edt obli\u010dejov\u00e9 filtry. M\u00edsto ps\u00edch o\u010d\u00ed ale dok\u00e1\u017e\u00ed p\u0159en\u00e9st na libovoln\u00e9 m\u00edsto, zvl\u00e1dnou v\u00e1s toti\u017e v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase vykl\u00ed\u010dovat i bez pou\u017eit\u00ed zelen\u00e9ho pozad\u00ed.Google k tomuto \u00fa\u010delu vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 neuronov\u00fdch s\u00edt\u00ed, jak se pochlubil na sv\u00e9m . D\u00edky tomu si porad\u00ed i s pohybuj\u00edc\u00edmi se objekty \u010di t\u0159eba dal\u0161\u00ed osobou v z\u00e1b\u011bru. V\u00fdsledky sice nejsou dokonal\u00e9 a ob\u010das se objevuj\u00ed fragmenty v oblasti o\u0159ezu, celkov\u011b se ale jedn\u00e1 o p\u016fsobivou a slibnou technologii.Nic toti\u017e nebr\u00e1n\u00ed postupn\u00e9mu zlep\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed a roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed i do dal\u0161\u00edch aplikac\u00ed pracuj\u00edc\u00edch nap\u0159\u00edklad s , co\u017e m\u00e1 ostatn\u011b Google v pl\u00e1nu. Nov\u00e9 filtry, stejn\u011b jako samotn\u00e9 Stories, prozat\u00edm b\u011b\u017e\u00ed v uzav\u0159en\u00e9 bet\u011b a na vybran\u00fdch telefonech vy\u0161\u0161\u00ed t\u0159\u00eddy. Na roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed mezi b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 u\u017eivatele si je\u0161t\u011b budeme muset po\u010dkat.Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Google", "YouTube", "Snapchat", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Strojov\u00e9 u\u010den\u00ed", "Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e1 realita", "Neuronov\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165", "Filtr", "Pl\u00e1tno", "Vybran\u00fd tv\u016frce", "B\u011b\u017en\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Pohybuj\u00edc\u00ed objekt", "Pozad\u00ed", "Uzav\u0159en\u00e1 beta", "Stories", "Obli\u010dejov\u00fd filtr", "Re\u00e1ln\u00fd \u010das", "Vysok\u00e1 t\u0159\u00edda", "Postupn\u00e9 zlep\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Nov\u00fd filtr", "Snapchat Stories", "Nov\u00e1 funkce", "Libovoln\u00e9 m\u00edsto", "Zelen\u00e9 pozad\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jak-zhubnout-portraitpro-body-2-vas-zbavi-tuku-i-bez-cinek-a-draheho-fitka/sc-3-a-192128/default.aspx", "title": "Jak zhubnout: PortraitPro Body 2 v\u00e1s zbav\u00ed tuku i bez \u010dinek a drah\u00e9ho fitka", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Zku\u0161en\u00fd grafik prom\u011bn\u00ed  d\u00edvku v bohyni tituln\u00edch str\u00e1nek m\u00f3dn\u00edch \u010dasopis\u016f a leckter\u00e9mu politikovi ubere p\u00e1r (des\u00edtek) let, anebo p\u0159ifoukne bicepsy. No, a pokud Photoshopu nevl\u00e1dne,  cel\u00fd internet.Kosmetick\u00e9 opravy lidsk\u00fdch nedokonalost\u00ed jsou hotov\u00e1 v\u011bda, a proto se tuto oblast sna\u017e\u00ed b\u011b\u017en\u00fdm smrteln\u00edk\u016fm p\u0159ibl\u00ed\u017eit hromada grafick\u00fdch n\u00e1stroj\u016f, kter\u00e9 na to jdou tro\u0161ku jinak.Jedn\u00edm z nich je  od britsk\u00e9ho studia , kter\u00e9 se u\u017e podle sv\u00e9ho n\u00e1zvu v\u011bnuje fyziologii lidsk\u00e9ho t\u011bla a do sv\u011bta chrl\u00ed hromadu desktopov\u00fdch i mobiln\u00edch aplikac\u00ed, kter\u00e9 se nam\u00edsto primitivn\u00edch deforma\u010dn\u00edch n\u00e1stroj\u016f pokou\u0161ej\u00ed analyzovat lidskou tv\u00e1\u0159 nebo i cel\u00e9 t\u011blo a nab\u00eddnout \u00fapravu opravdu jen t\u011bch \u010d\u00e1st\u00ed, kde to je t\u0159eba.A p\u0159esn\u011b to d\u011bl\u00e1 Portrait Pro Body 2. Ve sv\u00e9 podstat\u011b nen\u00ed ni\u010d\u00edm jin\u00fdm ne\u017e velmi pokro\u010dil\u00fdm editorem deforma\u010dn\u00edch \u00faprav, kter\u00e9 jsou v tomto p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b namapovan\u00e9 na jednotliv\u00e9 \u010d\u00e1sti t\u011bla. A pokud nebudete cht\u00edt zrovna prom\u011bnit sv\u016fj  v muskulaturu mlad\u00e9ho Arnolda Schwarzeneggera, bude v\u00fdsledek vypadat docela v\u011brohodn\u011b.Poj\u010fme si to vyzkou\u0161et v praxi. Jeliko\u017e jsem cht\u011bl, aby byl test co nejv\u011brohodn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed, vyzval jsem sv\u00e9 kamar\u00e1dky, aby mi zaslaly fotografie ve spodn\u00edm pr\u00e1dle. Tato prosba v\u0161ak z\u016fstala nevysly\u0161ena, a tak jsem si vzal na pomoc Shutterstock, kter\u00fd mi poskytl n\u011bkolik siln\u011bj\u0161\u00edch modelek, na kter\u00fdch si vyzkou\u0161\u00edme \u010dasto naprosto zbyte\u010dn\u00e9 pok\u0159ivov\u00e1n\u00ed reality.Na\u0161e hypotetick\u00e1 modelka \u2013 \u0159\u00edkejme ji t\u0159eba Eva \u2013 se domn\u00edv\u00e1, \u017ee by m\u011bla zapracovat na sv\u00fdch boc\u00edch, aby se mohla pochlubit na Facebooku. P\u0159edplatn\u00e9 do  je v\u0161ak drah\u00e9, a tak boky zmen\u0161\u00edme v pon\u011bkud levn\u011bj\u0161\u00edm Portrait Pro. Ano, m\u00e1lem bych zapomn\u011bl, nejedn\u00e1 se o freeware \u2013 p\u0159ijde v\u00e1s na ba\u0165ovsk\u00fdch , tedy cirka . Platit m\u016f\u017eete kartou i PayPalem.Kdy\u017e si Evu otev\u0159eme v editoru, bude vypadat asi takto:Jak vidno, v tomto kroku zat\u00edm nem\u016f\u017eeme nic upravovat. Program netu\u0161\u00ed, co je na fotografii. V n\u011bkolika \u00favodn\u00edch kroc\u00edch tedy mus\u00edme ozna\u010dit nos, pohlav\u00ed, ramena, lokty, b\u0159icho, boky, kolena a kotn\u00edky.Diskr\u00e9tn\u00edmi body to ale nekon\u010d\u00ed, jen co je toti\u017e vyzna\u010d\u00edme, editor se p\u0159epne do re\u017eimu, ve kter\u00e9m budeme muset pomoc\u00ed k\u0159ivek vyzna\u010dit kontury jednotliv\u00fdch \u010d\u00e1st\u00ed t\u011bla.D\u00edky tomu bude program p\u0159esn\u011b v\u011bd\u011bt t\u0159eba to, jak siln\u00e9 pa\u017ee a stehna na\u0161e figurantka opravdu m\u00e1, abychom mohli sn\u00ed\u017eili jejich obvod o 20 %.Na\u0161e figurantka nestoj\u00ed \u00fapln\u011b v pozoru jako vycepovan\u00fd voj\u00edn, a tak n\u00e1s editor p\u0159ed vytvo\u0159en\u00edm modelu kostry je\u0161t\u011b po\u017e\u00e1d\u00e1, abychom ur\u010dili t\u0159eba to, kter\u00e1 ruka a noha je v pop\u0159ed\u00ed.Tak, model kostry je hotov\u00fd a te\u010f kone\u010dn\u011b za\u010dne ta nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed legrace. V hlavn\u00edm panelu najdeme des\u00edtky posuvn\u00edk\u016f organizovan\u00fdch do n\u011bkolika skupin. Jeliko\u017e u\u017e program tu\u0161\u00ed, jak na\u0161e Eva vypad\u00e1, m\u016f\u017eeme si pohr\u00e1t t\u0159eba s posuvn\u00edkem , kter\u00fd se pokus\u00ed ubrat, nebo naopak p\u0159idat t\u011blesnou hmotu a jeho zm\u011bnou se adekv\u00e1tn\u011b uprav\u00ed i dal\u0161\u00ed parametry.Optikou fotoeditor\u016f je slim vlastn\u011b takov\u00e9 tla\u010d\u00edtko pro automatick\u00e9 vylep\u0161en\u00ed, kter\u00e9 v sob\u011b integruje hromadu krok\u016f.Slim adekv\u00e1tn\u011b upravil i parametr curve (k\u0159ivka), ov\u0161em Eva kritizovala p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm sv\u00e9 spodn\u00ed t\u011blesn\u00e9 partie. \u017d\u00e1dn\u00fd probl\u00e9m! Od toho tu jsou podskupiny pro detailn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed \u00fapravu t\u011bla (torso), ale p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm nohou (legs). jak vidno, nechyb\u00ed ani ramena a pa\u017ee (arms) a nakonec cel\u00fd skeleton, pomoc\u00ed kter\u00e9ho bychom Evu prom\u011bnili v podstat\u011b v libovoln\u00e9ho mutanta.Pokud nepom\u016f\u017ee ani jeden z dosavadn\u00edch n\u00e1stroj\u016f, p\u0159ich\u00e1z\u00ed \u0159ada na hrubou s\u00edlu a tedy klasick\u00e9 deforma\u010dn\u00ed n\u00e1stroje, jak je zn\u00e1te z Photoshopu a mnoha dal\u0161\u00edch fotoeditor\u016f. Najdete je v sekci  a \u0161t\u011btcem pak m\u016f\u017eete libovolnou \u010d\u00e1st t\u011bla zv\u011bt\u0161ovat, zmen\u0161ovat a posouvat. Pr\u00e1v\u011b v t\u00e9to \u010d\u00e1sti se nejv\u00edce projev\u00ed deformace pozad\u00ed a ka\u017ed\u00fd pozn\u00e1, \u017ee do fotografie kdosi nepat\u0159i\u010dn\u011b zasahoval.Proto je dobr\u00e9 m\u00edt k dispozici studiovou fotografii s homogenn\u00edm pozad\u00edm jako v na\u0161em p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b. Program na to nicm\u00e9n\u011b p\u0159eci jen tro\u0161ku pamatuje a nab\u00edz\u00ed funkci , pomoc\u00ed kter\u00e9 ozna\u010d\u00edte linie pozad\u00ed, kter\u00e9 maj\u00ed z\u016fstat rovn\u00e9 i po deformaci. Ob\u010das to pom\u016f\u017ee, ob\u010das bude v\u00fdsledek je\u0161t\u011b hor\u0161\u00ed.PortraitPro Body m\u00e1 nicm\u00e9n\u011b zpracovan\u00fd model kostry, \u010dili vedle primitivn\u00ed deformace mohu lok\u00e1ln\u011b a \u0161etrn\u011bji posunout i jednotliv\u00e9 partie.Tak, to by mohlo na doln\u00edch kon\u010detin\u00e1ch sta\u010dit a je\u0161t\u011b se pod\u00edv\u00e1me na tv\u00e1\u0159, kter\u00e9 se v\u011bnuje samostatn\u00e1 sekce programu. D\u00edky tomu, \u017ee jsme p\u0159i tvorb\u011b kostry ozna\u010dili nos, program dopo\u010d\u00edtal um\u00edst\u011bn\u00ed \u00fast, o\u010d\u00ed a tv\u00e1\u0159e. Dodate\u010dn\u011b m\u016f\u017eeme upravit t\u0159eba nasv\u00edcen\u00ed, co\u017e by mohlo skr\u00fdt .Dobr\u00e1, jak to tedy cel\u00e9 dopadlo? Pod\u00edvejte se na animaci n\u00ed\u017ee, kter\u00e1 p\u0159ehraje celou deformaci.Jak vidno, nejedn\u00e1 se o primitivn\u00ed deformaci konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1sti, ale deformaci, kter\u00e1 se v\u017edy projevila na cel\u00e9 kost\u0159e. V ka\u017ed\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, jeliko\u017e nen\u00ed prom\u011bna a\u017e tak drastick\u00e1, je docela uv\u011b\u0159iteln\u00e1. Figurantka by si nicm\u00e9n\u011b k dokonalosti zaslou\u017eila je\u0161t\u011b n\u011bkolik drobn\u011bj\u0161\u00edch korekc\u00ed.Pod\u00edvejme se je\u0161t\u011b na druh\u00fd p\u0159\u00edklad s je\u0161t\u011b siln\u011bj\u0161\u00ed figurantkou. Program ji ubere v pase i p\u00e1r des\u00edtek centimetr\u016f p\u0159i zachov\u00e1n\u00ed v\u011brohodnosti.PortraitPro Body tedy opravdu funguje, pokud v\u0161ak podobn\u00fd program skute\u010dn\u011b pou\u017eijete na sv\u00e9 vlastn\u00ed fotografie, nebo dokonce fotografie bl\u00edzk\u00fdch, m\u011bjte na pam\u011bti, \u017ee by ji\u017e nap\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u011b nem\u011bli opou\u0161t\u011bt domov, v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m sv\u011bt\u011b z masa a kost\u00ed toti\u017e ka\u017ed\u00fd pozn\u00e1 skute\u010dnost na prvn\u00ed pohled. Nakonec se tomu fitku tedy stejn\u011b neubr\u00e1n\u00edte.", "tags": ["Software", "Facebook", "Windows", "Zdrav\u00ed", "Fotografov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Hubnut\u00ed", "Grafick\u00fd editor", "T\u011blo", "Nadv\u00e1ha", "M\u00f3dn\u00ed \u010dasopis", "Tuk", "Re\u00e1ln\u00fd sv\u011bt", "Tituln\u00ed str\u00e1nka", "Slim", "Cel\u00fd den", "Automatick\u00e9 vylep\u0161en\u00ed", "Hlavn\u00ed panel", "Grafick\u00fd n\u00e1stroj", "Dosavadn\u00ed n\u00e1stroj", "Kl\u00ed\u010dov\u00fd bod", "Samostatn\u00e1 sekce", "Slab\u00fd po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Studiov\u00e1 fotografie", "Eva", "Hrub\u00e1 s\u00edla"]}
