{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/soundscape-od-microsoftu-umi-navigovat-slepe-pomoci-3d-zvuku/sc-3-a-192090/default.aspx", "title": "Soundscape od Microsoftu um\u00ed navigovat slep\u00e9 pomoc\u00ed 3D zvuk\u016f", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "5. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Po t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 p\u011bti letech v\u00fdvoje se kone\u010dn\u011b na trh ve Spojen\u00fdch st\u00e1tech a Velk\u00e9 Brit\u00e1nii dost\u00e1v\u00e1 unik\u00e1tn\u00ed aplikace , kter\u00e1 pom\u00e1h\u00e1 slep\u00fdm lidem s navigac\u00ed m\u011bstem a prost\u0159ed\u00edm okolo. Aplikace je prozat\u00edm dostupn\u00e1 pouze  ve vybran\u00fdch zem\u00edch, brzy by se v\u0161ak m\u011bla roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159it i do zbytku sv\u011bta. Aplikace Sounscape dok\u00e1\u017ee popsat, co se nach\u00e1z\u00ed v okol\u00ed prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm zvukov\u00e9ho popisu s 3D efektem. Funguje to podobn\u011b jako v po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00fdch hr\u00e1ch, popisy objekt\u016f sly\u0161\u00edte jakoby z ur\u010dit\u00e9ho sm\u011bru. Vyu\u017e\u00edt se d\u00e1 s b\u011b\u017en\u00fdmi sluch\u00e1tky, ale nevidom\u00ed aplikaci nej\u010dast\u011bji vyu\u017eij\u00ed se speci\u00e1ln\u00edmi p\u0159\u00edslechov\u00fdmi sluch\u00e1tky, kter\u00e1 jim umo\u017en\u00ed netlumen\u00fd poslech okoln\u00edch zvukov\u00fdch vjem\u016f.V b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 praxi to pak funguje tak, \u017ee jde u\u017eivatel po ulici a aplikace mu hl\u00e1s\u00ed nap\u0159\u00edklad jm\u00e9na p\u0159ilehl\u00fdch ulic, n\u00e1zvy obchod\u016f, kter\u00e9 zrovna m\u00edj\u00ed, atp. A\u010dkoli se jedn\u00e1 o aplikaci v\u00fdvojov\u00e9ho t\u00fdmu Microsoftu, mapov\u00e9 podklady nejsou br\u00e1ny kupodivu z Bing map, ale z otev\u0159en\u00e9 mapov\u00e9 platformy Open Street Map, kde m\u016f\u017ee komunita dopl\u0148ovat pot\u0159ebn\u00e9 podklady. U\u017eivatel\u00e9 aplikace si p\u0159itom mohou ve m\u011bst\u011b sami zaznamenat vlastn\u00ed d\u016fle\u017eit\u00e9 body, podle kter\u00fdch se mohu nechat navigovat.  Aplikace b\u011b\u017e\u00ed na pozad\u00ed, informace o okoln\u00edch objektech poskytne na vy\u017e\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed. Krom\u011b toho dok\u00e1\u017ee navigovat na zvolen\u00e9 m\u00edsto, k \u010demu\u017e na rozd\u00edl od b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 hlasov\u00e9 navigace rovn\u011b\u017e vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 3D zvukov\u00e9ho efektu a popisu trasy v\u010detn\u011b okoln\u00edch objekt\u016f. Aplikace se d\u00e1 pou\u017e\u00edt samostatn\u011b i ve spojen\u00ed s dal\u0161\u00edmi pom\u016fckami, jako jsou nap\u0159. vod\u00edc\u00ed psi. Na jej\u00edm v\u00fdvoji se pod\u00edlely tak\u00e9 organizace Guide Dogs UK, Guide Dogs for the Blind \u010di LightHouse for the Blind. A p\u0159\u00edmo se nab\u00edz\u00ed, aby \u010dasem spolupracovala se syst\u00e9my pro roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159enou realitu, kter\u00e9 um\u00ed rozpoznat fyzick\u00e9 objekty v okol\u00ed. ", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "USA", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "iOS", "Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e1 realita", "3D", "Velk\u00e1 Brit\u00e1nie", "Sluch\u00e1tka", "Navigace", "Open Street map", "Sluch\u00e1tko", "Popis", "Okoln\u00ed objekt", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "V\u00fdvojov\u00fd t\u00fdm", "Zvolen\u00e9 m\u00edsto", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e1 praxe", "Objekt", "Aplikace", "Ur\u010dit\u00fd sm\u011br", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e1 hra"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-vypustil-dalsi-experiment-webovou-aplikaci-na-tvorbu-hudby-v-prohlizeci/sc-3-a-192089/default.aspx", "title": "Google vypustil dal\u0161\u00ed experiment, webovou aplikaci na tvorbu hudby v prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010di", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "5. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "V r\u00e1mci v\u00fdvojov\u00fdch webov\u00fdch experiment\u016f Google nab\u00edz\u00ed i soubor hudebn\u00edch aplikac\u00ed , kter\u00fd nyn\u00ed obohatil o novinku . A jak ji\u017e n\u00e1zev napov\u00edd\u00e1, umo\u017en\u00ed p\u0159\u00edmo v prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010di vytvo\u0159it jednoduch\u00e9 hudebn\u00ed skladby.Google spustil  u\u017e v roce 2016. Jedn\u00e1 se o bal\u00ed\u010dek r\u016fznorod\u00fdch experiment\u00e1ln\u00edch n\u00e1stroj\u016f pro audiotvorbu v\u0161eho druhu.  v\u00e1s p\u0159itom z\u00e1bavnou formou nau\u010d\u00ed n\u011bco o frekvenci,  pak vizu\u00e1ln\u011b ukazuje, jak se zvukov\u00e9 vibrace pohybuj\u00ed vzduchem.Song Maker je o n\u011bco propracovan\u011bj\u0161\u00ed, av\u0161ak st\u00e1le dost jednoduch\u00fd na to, abyste mohli ihned tvo\u0159it. K dispozici m\u00e1te m\u0159\u00ed\u017eku, ve kter\u00e9 ozna\u010dujete jednotliv\u00e9 t\u00f3ny, dole pak vyb\u00edr\u00e1te tempo, n\u00e1stroje a p\u0159\u00edpadn\u011b i vyu\u017eit\u00ed mikrofonu, tak\u017ee m\u016f\u017eete melodii zazp\u00edvat. Aplikace rovn\u011b\u017e umo\u017e\u0148uje p\u0159ipojit extern\u00ed MIDI n\u00e1stroj. A pochopiteln\u011b nechyb\u00ed mo\u017enost snadn\u00e9ho sd\u00edlen\u00ed v\u00fdsledku.Zaj\u00edmav\u00e9 na t\u011bchto experimentech je p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm technick\u00e9 pozad\u00ed, vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1ny jsou nov\u00e9 technologie HTML5 a webov\u00e9ho k\u00f3du. V\u0161e si m\u016f\u017eete prostudovat .", "tags": ["Software", "Google", "Web", "Technologie", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "Chrome", "GitHub", "Experiment", "N\u00e1stroj", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d", "Snadn\u00e9 sd\u00edlen\u00ed", "Aplikace", "Webov\u00e1 aplikace", "Zvukov\u00e1 vibrace", "Tvorba", "Tvorba hudby", "Music Lab", "Webov\u00fd k\u00f3d", "Nov\u00e1 technologie", "Hudebn\u00ed aplikace", "Technick\u00e9 pozad\u00ed", "Midi"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-vypustil-sveho-konkurenta-slacku-hangouts-chat/sc-3-a-192050/default.aspx", "title": "Google vypustil sv\u00e9ho konkurenta Slacku: Hangouts Chat", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Google dnes, po v\u00edce jak ro\u010dn\u00edm uzav\u0159en\u00e9m testov\u00e1n\u00ed, vypustil mezi firmy svou nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed slu\u017ebu \u2013 . Funguje nad dosavadn\u00edm kec\u00e1lkem Hangouts a p\u0159in\u00e1\u0161\u00ed firm\u00e1m lep\u0161\u00ed mo\u017enosti komunikace v r\u00e1mci t\u00fdm\u016f v\u010detn\u011b propojen\u00ed s nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00edmi roboty a slu\u017ebami. Je tak p\u0159\u00edmou konkurenc\u00ed pro  \u010di .Slu\u017eba je \u010d\u00e1ste\u010dnou nadstavbou klasick\u00fdch . V r\u00e1mci konverzace s konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed osobou tak m\u016f\u017eete napsat i t\u011bm, kte\u0159\u00ed Chat aktu\u00e1ln\u011b nepou\u017e\u00edvaj\u00ed. Pro v\u0161echny ostatn\u00ed funkce je ale nutn\u00e9 b\u00fdt p\u0159epnut\u00fd do nov\u00e9ho rozhran\u00ed.Zde je mo\u017en\u00e9 komunikovat v r\u00e1mci t\u00fdmu, vyu\u017e\u00edvat napojen\u00ed na nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed roboty a automatizovan\u00e9 procesy \u010di vyu\u017e\u00edvat videohovory. Dostupn\u00e9 jsou ji\u017e i aplikace pro ,  a p\u0159ekvapiv\u011b i Windows. Pon\u011bvad\u017e se jedn\u00e1 o podnikovou slu\u017ebu, nebude dostupn\u00e1 pro b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 u\u017eivatele Gmailu, slou\u017e\u00ed pouze pro komunikaci v r\u00e1mci konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed firmy.Pokud Hangouts Chat nem\u00e1te dostupn\u00e9 v r\u00e1mci sv\u00e9ho , sta\u010d\u00ed je aktivovat v administr\u00e1torsk\u00e9 konzoli. Pokud zde tuto mo\u017enost nem\u00e1te, po\u010dkejte, Google slu\u017ebu zap\u00edn\u00e1 postupn\u011b.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Google", "Windows", "Slack", "Android", "Gmail", "iOS", "G Suite", "Google Hangouts", "Rozhran\u00ed", "Konkurent", "Administr\u00e1torsk\u00e1 konzole", "Nov\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed", "Robot", "Konkuren\u010dn\u00ed program", "Automatizovan\u00fd proces", "Hangouts", "Dobr\u00e1 mo\u017enost", "Hangouts chat", "P\u0159\u00edm\u00e1 konkurence", "B\u011b\u017en\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Slu\u017eba", "R\u00e1mec", "Ostatn\u00ed funkce"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/alexa-muze-mnoukat-amazon-sve-asistence-nadelil-nastvane-kocky/sc-3-a-192103/default.aspx", "title": "Alexa m\u016f\u017ee m\u0148oukat. Amazon sv\u00e9 asistence nad\u011blil na\u0161tvan\u00e9 ko\u010dky", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Pro\u010d by m\u011bli dom\u00e1c\u00ed asistenti odpov\u00eddat jen nudn\u00fdm syntetick\u00fdm hlasem, kdy\u017e se m\u016f\u017ee z reproduktoru ozvat t\u0159eba frenetick\u00e9 zak\u0148u\u010den\u00ed nerudn\u00e9 ko\u010dky? P\u0159esn\u011b na to pomysleli in\u017een\u00fd\u0159i Amazonu a v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159\u016fm aplikac\u00ed pro chytrou asistentku Alexa v\u011bnovali cel\u00fd set zvuk\u016f, kter\u00e9 mohou v odpov\u011bd\u00edch pou\u017e\u00edt.Amazon novinku pojmenoval  a jedn\u00e1 se skute\u010dn\u011b o knihovnu rozd\u011blenou do n\u011bkolika sekc\u00ed. V sekci Human Sounds tak najdete t\u0159eba nespo\u010det zvuk\u016f zaka\u0161l\u00e1n\u00ed a v sekci Animals hromadu ko\u010dek.V\u0161echny zvuky si m\u016f\u017eete p\u0159\u00edmo v prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010di p\u0159ehr\u00e1t a zvesela prokrastinovat.", "tags": ["Web", "Programov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Amazon", "Alexa", "Amazon Echo", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Ko\u010dky", "Zvuk", "Ko\u010dka", "Chytr\u00e1 asistentka", "Zvukov\u00e1 knihovna", "Asistence", "Hromada", "Knihovna", "Dom\u00e1c\u00ed asistent", "Cel\u00fd set", "Alexa Skills", "Sekce"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/instagram-zjevne-chysta-hlasove-a-videohovory-stane-se-tak-dalsim-plnohodnotnym-komunikatorem/sc-3-a-192087/default.aspx", "title": "Instagram zjevn\u011b chyst\u00e1 hlasov\u00e9 a videohovory. Stane se tak dal\u0161\u00edm plnohodnotn\u00fdm komunik\u00e1torem", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "5. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Pohled mezi soubory instala\u010dn\u00edho bal\u00ed\u010dku nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verze aplikace Instagram prozradil, \u017ee se aplikace p\u0159ipravuje funkci hovor\u016f a videohovor\u016f. Mezi ikonami funk\u010dn\u00edch tla\u010d\u00edtek aplikace nov\u011b p\u0159ibyly symboly pr\u00e1v\u011b pro tyto funkce, a to i s v\u00fdmluvn\u00fdmi n\u00e1zvy. Instagram by se tak stal dal\u0161\u00edm plnohodnotn\u00fdm komunik\u00e1torem.O n\u00e1lezu informuje zpravodajsk\u00fd web  a jak se m\u016f\u017eete p\u0159esv\u011bd\u010dit na obr\u00e1zku v\u00fd\u0161e, soubory nesou n\u00e1zev \"Call\" a \"Videocall\", nechyb\u00ed ani ikonky sluch\u00e1tka a kamery. Tv\u016frci se k tomu ofici\u00e1ln\u011b nevyj\u00e1d\u0159ili a je pochopiteln\u011b mo\u017en\u00e9 i to, \u017ee funkce ve fin\u00e1le nebude nasazena. To je ale celkem nepravd\u011bpodobn\u00e9.Obliba Instagramu v posledn\u00edch letech prudce stoup\u00e1 a zat\u00edm si sv\u016fj r\u016fst dr\u017e\u00ed. To u\u017e tak \u00fapln\u011b neplat\u00ed o Facebooku, kter\u00fd u\u017e nap\u0159\u00edklad v USA zaznamenal . Facebook jako\u017eto vlastn\u00edk Instagramu se tak logicky sna\u017e\u00ed paraleln\u011b budovat z\u00e1stupnou platformu. V z\u00e1loze m\u00e1 mimochodem je\u0161t\u011b Whats App.", "tags": ["Software", "Web", "Facebook", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Instagram", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "USA", "Android", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "iOS", "Funkce", "Mlad\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Komunik\u00e1tor", "Aplikace", "Soubor", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verze", "Funk\u010dn\u00ed tla\u010d\u00edtko", "Videohovor", "Bal\u00ed\u010dek", "N\u00e1zev", "Instala\u010dn\u00ed bal\u00ed\u010dek"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-vytvoril-robotickou-ruku-ktera-se-sama-nauci-co-ma-delat/sc-3-a-192092/default.aspx", "title": "Google vytvo\u0159il robotickou ruku, kter\u00e1 se sama nau\u010d\u00ed, co m\u00e1 d\u011blat", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "5. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "DeepMind je experiment\u00e1ln\u00ed laborato\u0159\u00ed Googlu, kter\u00e1 se zab\u00fdv\u00e1 v\u00fdvojem um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence. Nyn\u00ed ozn\u00e1mila dal\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdznamn\u00fd krok. , aby se samostatn\u011b u\u010dily b\u011bhem vykon\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed \u00fakon\u016f.Na rozd\u00edl od b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch aplikac\u00ed strojov\u00e9ho u\u010den\u00ed a um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence nen\u00ed tento p\u0159\u00edklad \u010dist\u011b softwarov\u00fd. Robot p\u0159itom nen\u00ed p\u0159edem nau\u010den, jak se m\u00e1 v dan\u00fdch situac\u00edch zachovat, podobn\u011b jako v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b  nebo chod\u00edc\u00edch robot\u016f z . Robotick\u00e1 ruka Googlu si na v\u0161echno mus\u00ed p\u0159ij\u00edt sama na z\u00e1klad\u011b informac\u00ed ze senzor\u016f a pohybu v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m prostoru. Ve v\u00fdsledku se tedy mus\u00ed poprat s mnohem v\u011bt\u0161\u00edm mno\u017estv\u00edm informac\u00ed ne\u017e t\u0159eba v p\u0159\u00edpadech, kdy um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence rozpozn\u00e1v\u00e1 objekty v obraze atp.  Za \u00fa\u010delem v\u00fduky robota vytvo\u0159ili v\u00fdzkumn\u00edci nov\u00fd vzorov\u00fd u\u010debn\u00ed algoritmus s jednoduch\u00fdmi \u00fakoly jako nap\u0159\u00edklad \u201e\u201c. DeepMind ale robot\u016fm neup\u0159esn\u00ed, jak maj\u00ed tento \u00fakon vykonat, jednodu\u0161e jim p\u0159ipevn\u00ed r\u016fznorod\u00e9 senzory a nechaj\u00ed je popostrkovat krychli\u010dky po pracovn\u00ed desce tak dlouho, dokud se nenau\u010d\u00ed s nimi manipulovat a nezjist\u00ed, \u017ee ke k\u00fd\u017een\u00e9mu v\u00fdsledku vede jejich odstran\u011bn\u00ed za hranice pracovn\u00ed plochy.Propojen\u00ed u\u010d\u00edc\u00ed se um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence s fyzick\u00fdm robotem je dal\u0161\u00edm krokem ve v\u00fdvoji pln\u011b autonomn\u00edch syst\u00e9m\u016f. Uplatn\u011bn\u00ed mohou v budoucnu naj\u00edt jak v pr\u016fmyslu, tak v dom\u00e1cnostech. ", "tags": ["Hardware", "Google", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Strojov\u00e9 u\u010den\u00ed", "Neuronov\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165", "DeepMind", "Boston", "Robotick\u00e1 ruka", "Pracovn\u00ed plocha", "Senzor", "Re\u00e1ln\u00fd prostor", "K\u00fd\u017een\u00fd v\u00fdsledek", "Jednoduch\u00fd \u00fakol", "Autonomn\u00ed v\u016fz", "Robot", "Inteligence", "R\u016fznorod\u00fd senzor", "Krychli\u010dka", "Autonomn\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "\u00dakon", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e1 aplikace", "Velk\u00e9 mno\u017estv\u00ed", "Chod\u00edc\u00ed robot"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/amazon-chce-z-alexy-udelat-chytreho-tlumocnika-nejenze-prelozi-v-realnem-case-ale-take-poradi-podle-situace/sc-3-a-192088/default.aspx", "title": "Amazon chce z Alexy ud\u011blat chytr\u00e9ho tlumo\u010dn\u00edka: nejen\u017ee p\u0159elo\u017e\u00ed v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase, ale tak\u00e9 porad\u00ed podle situace", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "5. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Amazon p\u0159ipravuje novou a zna\u010dn\u011b pokrokovou funkci pro digit\u00e1ln\u00ed asistentku Alexa \u2013 m\u011blo by se jednat o p\u0159ekl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase. Alexa by nav\u00edc nejen p\u0159ekl\u00e1dala fr\u00e1ze, ale vyu\u017e\u00edvala by k tomu i m\u00edstn\u00ed zvyky a zp\u016fsob mluvy, informuje , ale tak\u00e9 kontext. Ot\u00e1zka \u201e tedy dostane jinou odpov\u011b\u010f, ne\u017e nap\u0159. \u201e\u201c V\u00fdsledkem bude vhodn\u00e1 p\u0159elo\u017een\u00e1 fr\u00e1ze vhodn\u011b zvolen\u00e1 tak, abyste se nedopustili faux pas. Amazon se sna\u017e\u00ed j\u00edt nad r\u00e1mec b\u011b\u017en\u00e9ho p\u0159eklada\u010de. Nep\u016fjde jen o samotn\u00fd p\u0159eklad, ale p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm o p\u0159izp\u016fsoben\u00ed situaci a konkr\u00e9tn\u00edmu jazyku. Propojuje znalostn\u00ed b\u00e1zi s p\u0159eklada\u010dem a m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt d\u00edky tomu velmi u\u017eite\u010dn\u00fdm pomocn\u00edkem p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm na cest\u00e1ch. Alexa by m\u011bla nap\u0159\u00edklad pomoci i v takov\u00e9to situaci: \u201eAlexo, pr\u00e1v\u011b jsem vstoupil do restaurace v Dill\u00ed. Koho m\u00e1m oslovit a co m\u00e1m \u0159\u00edct, abych z\u00edskal st\u016fl?\u201cAmazon se mimo to sna\u017e\u00ed, aby Alexa um\u011bla poslouchat a p\u0159ekl\u00e1dat n\u011bkolik konverzac\u00ed najednou v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase. O podobnou funkci se pokusil u\u017e Google se sv\u00fdmi sluch\u00e1tky  a nedopadlo to moc dob\u0159e. P\u0159eklada\u010d je v praxi zdlouhav\u00fd a nep\u0159esn\u00fd. Uvid\u00edme tedy, co dok\u00e1\u017ee Alexa.", "tags": ["Software", "Google", "Technologie", "P\u0159eklada\u010d", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Mobility", "Amazon", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Alexa", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "Yahoo", "Nov\u00e1 funkce", "Dill\u00ed", "Svatba", "M\u00edstn\u00ed zvyk", "Finance", "Pixel Buds", "Digit\u00e1ln\u00ed asistentka", "Re\u00e1ln\u00fd \u010das", "Faux Pas", "U\u017eite\u010dn\u00fd pomocn\u00edk", "Znalostn\u00ed b\u00e1ze", "Tlumo\u010dn\u00edk", "Fr\u00e1ze"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jak-sledovat-televizi-na-internetu/sc-3-a-192181/default.aspx", "title": "Jak sledovat televizi na internetu", "author": null, "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "V dne\u0161n\u00ed dob\u011b u\u017e nen\u00ed televize tak popul\u00e1rn\u00ed, p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm u mlad\u0161\u00ed generace. Ob\u010das se ale na n\u011bjak\u00fd ten po\u0159ad pod\u00edv\u00e1 ka\u017ed\u00fd a te\u010f k tomu nepot\u0159ebuje ani televizi. Jak naj\u00edt vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed na internetu si pov\u00edme v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu.", "tags": ["Internet", "Tipy", "Televize", "Jak na Internet", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed doba", "Mlad\u00e1 generace"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/prvni-testy-odhaluji-vykon-mobilniho-sestijadra-core-i7-8750h-od-intelu/sc-3-a-192056/default.aspx", "title": "Prvn\u00ed testy odhaluj\u00ed v\u00fdkon mobiln\u00edho \u0161estij\u00e1dra Core i7-8750H od Intelu", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "1. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "V\u00fdkonn\u00e9 desktopov\u00e9 \u010dipy Intel osm\u00e9 generace (Coffee Lake) jsou na trhu u\u017e od minul\u00e9ho roku, st\u00e1le v\u0161ak \u010dek\u00e1me na v\u00fdkonn\u00e9 mobiln\u00ed \u010dipy nov\u00e9 generace, kter\u00e9 by novou architekturu p\u0159inesly i v \u0161estij\u00e1drov\u00e9m proveden\u00ed na notebooky. A tato chv\u00edli u\u017e je za rohem.V datab\u00e1zi testovac\u00edho programu  (4.2) se toti\u017e objevily prvn\u00ed r\u016fzn\u00e9 v\u00fdsledky \u0161estij\u00e1drov\u00e9ho procesoru Intel Core i7-8750H, kter\u00fd by dle \u00fadaj\u016f m\u011bl m\u00edt z\u00e1kladn\u00ed frekvenci 2,2 GHz a maxim\u00e1ln\u00ed Turbo s jedn\u00edm j\u00e1drem a\u017e 4,1 GHz. I to je jeden z d\u016fvod\u016f, pro\u010d je v\u00fdkon tohoto procesoru na mobiln\u00ed pom\u011bry opravdu skv\u011bl\u00fd. toti\u017e v r\u00e1mci jednoj\u00e1drov\u00e9ho testu z\u00edskal p\u0159ibli\u017en\u011b 5 tis\u00edc bod\u016f, v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b zapojen\u00ed v\u0161ech jader pak kolem 20 tis\u00edc bod\u016f. Velk\u00fd rozd\u00edl je to v porovn\u00e1n\u00ed s minulou generac\u00ed, konkr\u00e9tn\u011b procesorem Intel Core i7-7700HQ, kter\u00fd v jednoj\u00e1drov\u00e9m testu dosahuje v\u00fdkonu kolem 4 100 bod\u016f, ale p\u0159i zapojen\u00ed v\u0161ech jader pak pouze asi 13 tis\u00edc bod\u016f. Jedn\u00e1 se toti\u017e o \u010dty\u0159j\u00e1dro a dv\u011b fyzick\u00e1 j\u00e1dra nav\u00edc tak u nov\u00e9ho modelu hraj\u00ed obrovskou roli. Procesor pochopiteln\u011b podporuje multithreading, tak\u017ee zvl\u00e1dne najednou zpracov\u00e1vat a\u017e 12 vl\u00e1ken. Dle programu m\u00e1 procesor 9 MB L3 cache. TDP by m\u011blo b\u00fdt 45 W.Prvn\u00ed v\u00fdkonn\u00e9 notebooky nebo t\u0159eba i All-in-One po\u010d\u00edta\u010de vybaven\u00e9 t\u00edmto procesorem lze o\u010dek\u00e1vat b\u011bhem n\u011bkolika m\u011bs\u00edc\u016f. Podobn\u011b jako u ostatn\u00edch model\u016f budou sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed t\u011bchto procesor\u016f integrovan\u00e9 grafick\u00e9 \u010dipy Intel UHD 630.", "tags": ["Notebooky", "Intel", "\u010cipy", "Procesory", "Notebook", "Mobiln\u00ed pom\u011bry", "V\u00fdkon", "GeekBench", "Minul\u00e1 generace", "J\u00e1dro", "Nov\u00e1 generace", "Coffee Lake", "Minul\u00fd rok", "Testovac\u00ed program", "Nov\u00fd model", "Prvn\u00ed test", "Procesor", "GHz", "Generace", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed frekvence", "Velk\u00fd rozd\u00edl", "\u010cip", "Turbo", "\u0160estij\u00e1drov\u00fd procesor", "Fyzick\u00e9 j\u00e1dro"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/pokrok-ve-striptyzu-misto-penez-za-kalhotky-prilozite-telefon-a-tanecnici-poslete-bitcoiny/sc-3-a-192059/default.aspx", "title": "Pokrok ve stript\u00fdzu: m\u00edsto pen\u011bz za kalhotky p\u0159ilo\u017e\u00edte telefon a tane\u010dnici po\u0161lete bitcoiny", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "1. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Klasick\u00e1 p\u0159edstava stript\u00fdzov\u00e9ho baru, ve kter\u00e9m n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvn\u00edci strkaj\u00ed hotovost d\u00edvk\u00e1m (\u010di mu\u017e\u016fm) za spodn\u00ed pr\u00e1dlo, bude mo\u017en\u00e1 za p\u00e1r let p\u0159e\u017eitkem. I do tohoto segmentu toti\u017e p\u0159ich\u00e1z\u00ed revoluce v podob\u011b kryptom\u011bn a mobiln\u00edch technologi\u00ed.Ve vyhl\u00e1\u0161en\u00e9m klubu , kter\u00fd se nach\u00e1z\u00ed v Las Vegas, toti\u017e za\u010daly stript\u00e9rky nosit na k\u016f\u017ei do\u010dasn\u00e1 tetov\u00e1n\u00ed, kter\u00e1 jsou v podob\u011b velk\u00e9ho QR k\u00f3du. Ten obsahuje unik\u00e1tn\u00ed bitcoinovou adresu, kam m\u016f\u017ee n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvn\u00edk pos\u00edlat bitcoinov\u00e9 \u201eodm\u011bny\u201c. V\u00fdhodou pochopiteln\u011b je, \u017ee lze t\u00edmto zp\u016fsobem pos\u00edlat pen\u00edze zcela anonymn\u011b.Dle informac\u00ed  a zpov\u011bd\u00ed jednotliv\u00fdch tane\u010dnic preferuj\u00ed tento zp\u016fsob odm\u011bny i samotn\u00e9 stript\u00e9rky. N\u011bkolik z nich u\u017e pou\u017e\u00edvaj\u00ed bitcoin n\u011bkolik let a vyzdvihuj\u00ed hlavn\u011b rychl\u00fd a snadn\u00fd p\u0159enos s t\u00edm, \u017ee pro \u0159adu \u201eklient\u016f\u201c je to bezpe\u010dn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed forma platby. N\u011bkter\u00e9 banky nav\u00edc maj\u00ed dle jejich zku\u0161enost\u00ed probl\u00e9my s pen\u011bzi, kter\u00e9 poch\u00e1z\u00ed z tohoto pr\u016fmyslu, a tak klidn\u011b ru\u0161\u00ed i bankovn\u00ed \u00fa\u010dty.Zaj\u00edmavost\u00ed je, \u017ee klub m\u00e1 i vlastn\u00ed kryptom\u011bnu Legends Room (LGD) postavenou na platform\u011b Ethereum, se kterou se d\u00e1 rovn\u011b\u017e v\u0161e v klubu platit a nav\u00edc z\u00edsk\u00e1te 20 % slevu na v\u0161e. Pokud nejste fandou nov\u00fdch technologi\u00ed, nemus\u00edte se ale je\u0161t\u011b b\u00e1t \u2013 platit se d\u00e1 st\u00e1le i klasickou kreditn\u00ed kartou nebo hotovost\u00ed.Jak to v klubu vypad\u00e1, si m\u016f\u017eete prohl\u00e9dnout na tomto videu s 360stup\u0148ov\u00fdmi z\u00e1b\u011bry:", "tags": ["Kryptom\u011bny", "Bitcoin", "Ethereum", "Banka", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Pokrok", "Las Vegas", "LGD", "Kreditn\u00ed karta", "Mobiln\u00ed technologie", "Tane\u010dnice", "Hotovost", "Stript\u00fdz", "Spodn\u00ed pr\u00e1dlo", "Do\u010dasn\u00e9 tetov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Rychl\u00fd p\u0159enos", "Stript\u00e9rka", "Nov\u00e1 technologie"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/anketa-hodinky-naramek-nebo-staci-fitness-aplikace-s-cim-sportujete-vy/sc-3-a-192102/default.aspx", "title": "Anketa: Hodinky, n\u00e1ramek nebo sta\u010d\u00ed fitness aplikace? S \u010d\u00edm sportujete vy?", "author": "\u010casopis Computer", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Sportovn\u00ed n\u00e1ramky, chytr\u00e9 hodinky, krokom\u011bry, bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9 sn\u00edma\u010de \u2013 dopl\u0148k\u016f, kter\u00e9 maj\u00ed za \u00fakol zkvalitnit \u010di zp\u0159\u00edjemnit sportovn\u00ed aktivitu je velk\u00e1 spousta. Nav\u00edc v posledn\u00edch letech zaznamenaly v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed posun i aplikace pro smartphony, ze kter\u00fdch se staly regul\u00e9rn\u00ed sporttestery podporuj\u00edc\u00ed extern\u00ed senzory a d\u00edky \u00fasporn\u00fdm technologi\u00edm v telefonech mohou b\u011b\u017eet t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 cel\u00fd den.Proto\u017ee p\u0159ipravujeme do dubnov\u00e9ho \u010d\u00edsla  velk\u00e9 t\u00e9ma pr\u00e1v\u011b o sportov\u00e1n\u00ed s elektronikou, zaj\u00edm\u00e1 n\u00e1s, zda p\u0159i aktivit\u00e1ch vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1te pouze smartphone s obl\u00edbenou aplikac\u00ed nebo i n\u011bkter\u00e9 z dal\u0161\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed.Krom\u011b hlasov\u00e1n\u00ed v anket\u00e1ch budeme rovn\u011b\u017e r\u00e1di, kdy\u017e se pod\u011bl\u00edte o va\u0161e zku\u0161enosti s aplikacemi a dopl\u0148ky pro sportov\u00e1n\u00ed v diskuzi.", "tags": ["Sport", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Ankety", "Smartphone", "Hodinky", "Aktivita", "\u00dasporn\u00e1 technologie", "Sportovn\u00ed n\u00e1ramek", "Sportov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Velk\u00fd posun", "Dopl\u0148ky", "Cel\u00fd den", "Fitness aplikace", "Dubnov\u00e9 \u010d\u00edslo", "Sportovn\u00ed aktivita", "Anketa", "Aplikace", "Obl\u00edben\u00e1 aplikace", "Chytr\u00e9 hodinky", "N\u00e1ramek", "Velk\u00e9 t\u00e9ma"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jak-vybrat-kryptomenovou-burzu-a-zacit-obchodovat-nejen-s-bitcoinem/sc-3-a-192066/default.aspx", "title": "Jak vybrat kryptom\u011bnovou burzu a za\u010d\u00edt obchodovat nejen s bitcoinem", "author": "Martin Miksa", "date": "2. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "", "tags": ["Web", "Kryptom\u011bny", "Bitcoin", "Ethereum", "Bitcoin Cash", "Banka", "Litecoin", "Ripple", "Monero", "Pen\u00edze", "Cena bitcoinu", "Bitcoin kurz", "Poplatek", "Cel\u00fd internet", "Nov\u00e1 registrace", "Velk\u00fd zisk", "\u010casov\u00fd interval", "Euro", "Facebookov\u00e1 skupina", "Evropsk\u00e9 s\u00eddlo", "P\u0159edchoz\u00ed n\u00e1stroj", "Coinbase", "Graf", "Ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed str\u00e1nka", "D\u016fle\u017eit\u00e9 krit\u00e9rium"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/levny-notebook-od-applu-letos-bychom-se-meli-cekat-inovovaneho-a-pritom-zlevneneho-macbooku-air/sc-3-a-192105/default.aspx", "title": "Levn\u00fd notebook od Applu: Letos bychom se m\u011bli \u010dekat inovovan\u00e9ho a p\u0159itom zlevn\u011bn\u00e9ho MacBooku Air", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": ", coby extr\u00e9mn\u011b tenk\u00fd notebook, p\u0159edstavil Apple v lednu roku 2008. Postupn\u011b se dostal do pozice nejlevn\u011bj\u0161\u00edho notebooku od Applu, \u010demu\u017e odpov\u00eddaj\u00ed i pou\u017eit\u00e9 komponenty. I nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed generace toti\u017e obsahuje t\u0159i roky star\u00e9 procesory Intel 5. generace (Broadwell, 14 nm, rok 2015) a n\u00edzk\u00e9 rozli\u0161en\u00ed displeje 1 440 \u00d7 900 bod\u016f. To by se ale u\u017e brzy m\u011blo zm\u011bnit.Podle informac\u00ed KGI Securities chyst\u00e1 Apple na druh\u00e9 \u010dtvrtlet\u00ed novou generaci MacBooku Air, kter\u00e1 p\u0159inese nejen modern\u011bj\u0161\u00ed komponenty, ale hlavn\u011b je\u0161t\u011b ni\u017e\u0161\u00ed cenu. Nejni\u017e\u0161\u00ed prod\u00e1van\u00e1 varianta m\u00e1 na na\u0161em trhu v sou\u010dasnosti cenu 30 990 korun s DPH.Zat\u00edm nen\u00ed jasn\u00e9, o kolik by se cena nejni\u017e\u0161\u00ed konfigurace m\u011bla sn\u00ed\u017eit, ale m\u016f\u017eeme trochu h\u00e1dat z minulosti. Obvykle toti\u017e Apple v podobn\u00e9 cenov\u00e9 kategorii jde nap\u0159\u00edklad o v\u00edce ne\u017e sto dolar\u016f dol\u016f, co\u017e je v na\u0161ich kon\u010din\u00e1ch kolem t\u0159\u00ed tis\u00edc korun. P\u0159\u00edli\u0161 tak nelze \u010dekat, \u017ee Apple bude prod\u00e1vat MacBook Air v cenov\u00e9 hranici kolem 20 tis\u00edc korun s DPH, ale sp\u00ed\u0161e v rozmez\u00ed 25 tis\u00edc a\u017e 30 tis\u00edc korun s DPH.", "tags": ["Notebooky", "Apple", "Intel", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "MacBook", "Notebook", "Nov\u00e1 generace", "Broadwell", "Levn\u00fd notebook", "Star\u00fd procesor", "DPH", "MacBook Air", "Odpov\u00eddaj\u00edc\u00ed komponenta", "Nejni\u017e\u0161\u00ed konfigurace", "Modern\u00ed komponenta", "Prvn\u00ed Macbook", "N\u00edzk\u00e9 rozli\u0161en\u00ed", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed generace", "Generace", "Cenov\u00e1 hranice", "Druh\u00e9 \u010dtvrtlet\u00ed", "N\u00edzk\u00e1 cena", "KGI Securities", "Tenk\u00fd notebook", "Nejlevn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed notebook"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/tretina-internetu-jede-na-wordpressu-tipuji-rakousti-analytici/sc-3-a-192107/default.aspx", "title": "T\u0159etina internetu jede na WordPressu, tipuj\u00ed rakou\u0161t\u00ed analytici", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "6. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "A\u0165 u\u017e nav\u0161t\u00edv\u00edte jakoukoliv str\u00e1nku, m\u00e1te velkou \u0161anci, \u017ee ji poh\u00e1n\u00ed WordPress. Zpo\u010d\u00e1tku p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm blogovac\u00ed a dnes v podstat\u011b univerz\u00e1ln\u00ed CMS platforma toti\u017e  .W3Techs pravideln\u011b zkoum\u00e1 10 milion\u016f nejnav\u0161t\u011bvovan\u011bj\u0161\u00edch web\u016f podle Alexy, co\u017e je snad dostate\u010dn\u011b siln\u00fd statistick\u00fd vzorek, aby byly v\u00fdsledky relevantn\u00ed. WordPress je podle t\u00e9to anal\u00fdzy zdaleka nejpou\u017e\u00edvan\u011bj\u0161\u00edm redak\u010dn\u00edm/CMS syst\u00e9mem (60,2 %) a z\u00e1rove\u0148 se jeho k\u00f3d nach\u00e1z\u00ed na 30 % v\u0161ech zkouman\u00fdch web\u016f.V\u00fdvoj komunitn\u00edho WordPressu dnes zaji\u0161\u0165uje jeho  a komer\u010dn\u00ed hosting pak sanfrancisk\u00fd Automattic, do jeho\u017e portoflia pat\u0159\u00ed dom\u00e9na .", "tags": ["Web", "Internet", "Alexa", "WordPress", "Statistika", "Anal\u00fdza", "Blog", "Blogov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Zkouman\u00fd web", "Analytik", "Velk\u00e1 \u0161ance", "CMS", "Komer\u010dn\u00ed hosting", "Wordpress", "Nejnav\u0161t\u011bvovan\u011bj\u0161\u00ed web"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/v-cine-na-webu-zakazali-pismeno-n/sc-3-a-192063/default.aspx", "title": "V \u010c\u00edn\u011b na webu zak\u00e1zali p\u00edsmeno N", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "2. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "\u010c\u00edna se u\u017e p\u0159ed lety proslavila sv\u00fdm nechvaln\u011b zn\u00e1m\u00fdm , o kter\u00e9m je nyn\u00ed op\u011bt sly\u0161et, m\u00e9dia se toti\u017e bav\u00ed t\u00edm, jak\u00e9 v\u00fdrazy jsou, nebo alespo\u0148 v posledn\u00edch dnech byly, zak\u00e1zan\u00e9 t\u0159eba na soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u00ed Weibo, kter\u00e1 je \u010d\u00ednskou paralelou americk\u00e9ho Twitteru.Cenzura nyn\u00ed zes\u00edlila zejm\u00e9na v souvislosti s touhou gener\u00e1ln\u00edho tajemn\u00edka \u00dast\u0159edn\u00edho v\u00fdboru Komunistick\u00e9 strany \u010c\u00edny a prezidenta Si \u0164in-pchinga st\u00e1t se v podstat\u011b do\u017eivotn\u00edm vlada\u0159em zru\u0161en\u00edm klauzule, kter\u00e1 omezuje mand\u00e1t jen na dv\u011b po sob\u011b jdouc\u00ed obdob\u00ed (stejn\u011b jako v \u010cesku).Tyto n\u00e1pady zdaleka nekvituj\u00ed v\u0161ichni, a tak si dali cenzo\u0159i p\u0159es\u010das a seznam zak\u00e1zan\u00fdch v\u00fdraz\u016f se za\u010dali pov\u00e1\u017eliv\u011b roz\u0161i\u0159ovat. Web China Digital Times jejich neofici\u00e1ln\u00ed seznam v posledn\u00edch dnech pr\u016fb\u011b\u017en\u011b aktualizoval a .Leckoho by napadlo, \u017ee se bude jednat o dostate\u010dn\u011b p\u0159\u00edmo\u010dar\u00e9 term\u00edny, mnohdy to jsou v\u0161ak spojen\u00ed, u kter\u00fdch \u010dlov\u011bk neznal\u00fd \u010d\u00ednsk\u00fdch re\u00e1li\u00ed jen t\u00e1pe, pro\u010d se dostala na seznam. Kr\u00e1tce to dokonce platilo i o p\u00edsmeno \u201eN,\u201c kter\u00e9mu se  t\u0159eba The Guardian.Na seznam zak\u00e1zan\u00fdch v\u00fdraz\u016f se z t\u011bch pochopiteln\u011bj\u0161\u00edch dostala t\u0159eba tato spojen\u00ed:Dlouhodob\u011b pak maj\u00ed na pevninsk\u00e9 \u010c\u00edn\u011b probl\u00e9my tradi\u010dn\u00ed komunitn\u00ed weby \u2013 a\u0165 u\u017e ty od Googlu jako t\u0159eba YouTube, nebo americk\u00e9 soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b.", "tags": ["Google", "Web", "YouTube", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Twitter", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "\u010c\u00edna", "Cenzura", "Politika", "Vl\u00e1da", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Konec civilizace", "The Guardian", "P\u00edsmeno", "China", "Neofici\u00e1ln\u00ed seznam", "Seznam", "Gener\u00e1ln\u00ed tajemn\u00edk", "Posledn\u00ed den", "Ob\u010dansk\u00e1 v\u00e1lka"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/podle-dxomark-jiz-neni-pixel-2-nejlepsi-fotomobil-sveta-prekonala-ho-cerstva-novinka/sc-3-a-192061/default.aspx", "title": "Podle DxOMark ji\u017e nen\u00ed Pixel 2 nejlep\u0161\u00ed fotomobil sv\u011bta. P\u0159ekonala ho \u010derstv\u00e1 novinka", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "2. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Web DxOMark pravideln\u011b testuje nov\u00e9 telefony a fotoapar\u00e1ty a sestavuje \u017eeb\u0159\u00ed\u010dek t\u011bch nejlep\u0161\u00edch. Doposud kraloval lo\u0148sk\u00fd Google Pixel 2 s v\u00fdsledkem 98, nyn\u00ed jej ale porazil Samsung se svou novou vlajkovou lod\u00ed . Rozd\u00edl ale nen\u00ed nijak velk\u00fd, pouh\u00fd jeden bod.Samsung se u sv\u00e9ho nov\u00e9ho modelu chlub\u00ed zejm\u00e9na sn\u00edmky za zhor\u0161en\u00fdch sv\u011bteln\u00fdch podm\u00ednek, kde nab\u00eddne prom\u011bnlivou clonu. D\u00edky rekordn\u00ed sv\u011btelnosti f1,5 se pak ke sn\u00edma\u010di dostane o 20 % v\u00edce sv\u011btla, ne\u017e u p\u0159edchoz\u00ed generace.Pod\u00edv\u00e1me-li se ale na konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed v\u00fdsledky, tak souboj byl pom\u011brn\u011b vyrovnan\u00fd a v n\u011bkter\u00fdch oblastech dokonce v\u00edt\u011bz\u00ed Pixel. Ten si mnohem l\u00e9pe vede u videa, zato S9+ jej drt\u00ed v hodnocen\u00ed \u0161umu, zoomu a mo\u017enostech tzv. , tedy efektu rozmazan\u00e9ho pozad\u00ed.Zde je nutno dodat, \u017ee Samsung u modelu Plus pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 dv\u011b \u010do\u010dky oproti jedn\u00e9 u Googlu. Ten se v\u0161e sna\u017e\u00ed dohnat um\u011blou inteligenc\u00ed, jak jde ale vid\u011bt, v n\u011bkter\u00fdch ohledech nesta\u010d\u00ed. Jihokorejsk\u00fd v\u00fdrobce si odn\u00e1\u0161\u00ed prozat\u00edmn\u00ed prvenstv\u00ed.Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Google", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Samsung", "Fotografov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Smartphone", "Pixel", "Novinka", "Efekt", "\u010cerstv\u00e1 novinka", "Rozmazan\u00e9 pozad\u00ed", "Jihokorejsk\u00fd v\u00fdrobce", "Nejlep\u0161\u00ed fotomobil", "DxOMark", "P\u0159edchoz\u00ed generace", "Nov\u00fd model", "Nov\u00fd telefon", "Prvn\u00ed dojem"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/amazon-foti-dorucene-zasilky-tim-by-se-mohla-inspirovat-i-ceska-posta/sc-3-a-192073/default.aspx", "title": "Amazon fot\u00ed doru\u010den\u00e9 z\u00e1silky. T\u00edm by se mohla inspirovat i \u010cesk\u00e1 po\u0161ta", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "2. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Amazon v z\u00e1mo\u0159\u00ed  drobn\u00e9 vylep\u0161en\u00ed p\u0159i doru\u010dov\u00e1n\u00ed z\u00e1silek. Nejen \u017ee lidem doraz\u00ed notifikace na mobil o tom, \u017ee maj\u00ed p\u0159ed dve\u0159mi bal\u00ed\u010dek (to by v na\u0161ich kon\u010din\u00e1ch asi fungovat nemohlo), ale doru\u010dovatel jej z\u00e1rove\u0148 vyfot\u00ed a v\u00e1m doraz\u00ed fotografie.Jedn\u00e1 se samoz\u0159ejm\u011b i o obranu samotn\u00e9ho Amazonu, kter\u00fd t\u00edmto dokl\u00e1d\u00e1, \u017ee z jeho strany v\u0161e prob\u011bhlo v po\u0159\u00e1dku, a pokud bal\u00ed\u010dek pozd\u011bji n\u011bkdo odcizil, nen\u00ed to jeho probl\u00e9m. Lze p\u0159edpokl\u00e1dat, \u017ee p\u0159i vyu\u017eit\u00ed slu\u017eby p\u0159\u00edjemce souhlas\u00ed s touto formou nejist\u00e9ho doru\u010den\u00ed.N\u011bco podobn\u00e9ho by mohla nasadit i \u010dasto kritizovan\u00e1 \u010cesk\u00e1 po\u0161ta, jej\u00ed\u017e klienti si mnohdy st\u011b\u017euj\u00ed, \u017ee a\u010dkoliv byli cel\u00fd den doma, ve schr\u00e1nce nalezli jen l\u00edste\u010dek o tom, \u017ee nebyli zasti\u017eeni a musej\u00ed tedy zaj\u00edt na po\u0161tu vyst\u00e1t mnohdy pekeln\u011b dlouhou frontu.", "tags": ["Byznys", "Amazon", "Logistika", "\u010cesk\u00e1 po\u0161ta", "Schr\u00e1nka", "Spodn\u00ed okraj", "Drobn\u00e9 vylep\u0161en\u00ed", "Bal\u00ed\u010dek", "Cel\u00fd den", "Klient", "Z\u00e1silka", "Dlouh\u00e1 fronta", "P\u0159\u00edjemce"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/je-lepsi-vlastni-spickova-meteostanice-anebo-bezplatna-appka-v-mobilu/sc-3-a-192076/default.aspx", "title": "Je lep\u0161\u00ed vlastn\u00ed \u0161pi\u010dkov\u00e1 meteostanice, anebo bezplatn\u00e1 appka v mobilu?", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "3. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Do redakce n\u00e1m dorazila Wi-Fi meteostanice . Zat\u00edmco Kuba nad\u0161en\u011b j\u00e1sal ze sm\u011brov\u00fdch r\u016f\u017eic, anemometru m\u011b\u0159\u00edc\u00edho rychlost v\u011btru, sr\u00e1\u017ekom\u011bru a dal\u0161\u00edch specialit, David vyt\u00e1hl z kapsy telefon s bezplatnou aplikac\u00ed, kter\u00e1 uk\u00e1\u017ee (t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159) to sam\u00e9. Kter\u00e1 cesta je tedy lep\u0161\u00ed?", "tags": ["Video", "Hardware", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Netatmo", "Meteorologie", "Atmosf\u00e9ra", "Po\u010das\u00ed", "Ekologie", "Glob\u00e1ln\u00ed oteplov\u00e1n\u00ed", "David", "Kuba", "Bezplatn\u00e1 aplikace", "Meteostanice", "P\u0159\u00edstup", "Wi-fi meteostanice", "Mobil", "Tis\u00edc", "M\u011b\u0159\u00edc\u00ed rychlost", "Garni", "Geekov\u00e9"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/flash-player-v-chromu-uz-skoro-nikdo-nepouziva-od-leta-to-budou-mit-jeho-fandove-tezke/sc-3-a-192062/default.aspx", "title": "Flash Player v Chromu u\u017e skoro nikdo nepou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1. Od l\u00e9ta to budou m\u00edt jeho fandov\u00e9 t\u011b\u017ek\u00e9", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "2. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Spole\u010dnost Adobe loni v l\u00e9t\u011b ozn\u00e1mila postupn\u00fd \u00fatlum Flash Playeru, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e k nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edm pomocn\u00edk\u016fm, kte\u0159\u00ed to zajist\u00ed, pat\u0159\u00ed Google \u2013 respektive jeho prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de Chrome a Chromium.Zat\u00edmco je\u0161t\u011b v roce 2014  u\u017eivatel\u016f Chromu alespo\u0148 jednou denn\u011b narazilo na n\u011bjak\u00fd web s Flashem, na po\u010d\u00e1tku leto\u0161n\u00edho roku to bylo  pouze ! D\u016fvod\u016f je hned n\u011bkolik. Weby samoz\u0159ejm\u011b postupn\u011b p\u0159ech\u00e1zej\u00ed na nov\u00e9 technologie z ranku HTML5, nicm\u00e9n\u011b sna\u017e\u00ed se i Chrome a na\u010d\u00edt\u00e1n\u00ed Flashe s\u00e1m komplikuje.Produktov\u00fd t\u00fdm Chromia (open-source verze Chromu, ze kter\u00e9 vych\u00e1z\u00ed t\u0159eba i Opera) si ostatn\u011b vede i , jak bude Flash omezovat i nad\u00e1le. Dal\u0161\u00ed zm\u011bny se u\u017eivatel\u00e9 prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de do\u010dkaj\u00ed u\u017e brzy,  (\u010dervenec 2018) toti\u017e budou str\u00e1nky pot\u0159ebovat souhlas u\u017eivatele dokonce po ka\u017ed\u00e9m restartu prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de.Kdy\u017e tedy bude na webu X Flash, kter\u00fd budete cht\u00edt vid\u011bt, vysko\u010d\u00ed pruh, kter\u00fd v\u00e1s po\u017e\u00e1d\u00e1 o souhlas, nicm\u00e9n\u011b toto nastaven\u00ed se u\u017e neulo\u017e\u00ed, a kdy\u017e druh\u00fd den str\u00e1nky op\u011bt nav\u0161t\u00edv\u00edte, prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d v\u00e1s bude op\u011bt  nutn\u00fdm souhlasem.Rok pot\u00e9, , Google podle pl\u00e1nu p\u0159edstav\u00ed , kde by ji\u017e m\u011bl b\u00fdt Flash Player ve v\u00fdchoz\u00edm stavu vypnut\u00fd a bude to fakticky znamenat jeho konec pro drtivou v\u011bt\u0161inu surfa\u0159\u016f. P\u0159esto jej v\u0161ak budete moci v konfiguraci je\u0161t\u011b znovu zapnout, a\u010dkoliv pot\u00e9 budou op\u011bt vyskakovat obt\u011b\u017euj\u00edc\u00ed dialogy vy\u017eaduj\u00edc\u00ed souhlas po ka\u017ed\u00e9m restartu.Naprost\u00fd konec Flash Playeru nastane nejsp\u00ed\u0161e , kdy Google podle sou\u010dasn\u00e9ho pl\u00e1nu vyd\u00e1 . Tato verze u\u017e nebude obsahovat \u017e\u00e1dnou podporu Flash Playeru a jeho interaktivn\u00ed obsah nena\u010dte, ani kdyby se surfa\u0159 stav\u011bl na hlavu. Ostatn\u011b pr\u00e1v\u011b rokem 2020 m\u00e1 skon\u010dit podpora Flash Playeru i ze strany Adobe.Vzhledem k tomu, jak v posledn\u00edch letech c\u00edlen\u011b upad\u00e1, nicm\u00e9n\u011b k faktick\u00e9mu konci dojde mnohem d\u0159\u00edve. Mo\u017en\u00e1 je\u0161t\u011b letos, kdy se prom\u011bn\u00ed v irelevantn\u00ed technologii pro n\u011bjak\u00e9 to promile u\u017eivatel\u016f.", "tags": ["Software", "Google", "Web", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "Chrome", "Opera", "Flash Player", "HTML5", "Adobe", "Flash", "Souhlas", "Nov\u00e1 technologie", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed pomocn\u00edk", "L\u00e9to", "Bleeping Computer", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Necel\u00fd rok", "Produktov\u00fd t\u00fdm", "Sou\u010dasn\u00fd pl\u00e1n", "Drtiv\u00e1 v\u011bt\u0161ina", "Leto\u0161n\u00ed rok", "Postupn\u00fd \u00fatlum", "Interaktivn\u00ed obsah", "Fanda"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/doposud-antiviry-chranily-pc-a-mobily-ted-se-pokusi-ochranit-i-vsechny-krabicky/sc-3-a-192080/default.aspx", "title": "Doposud antiviry chr\u00e1nily PC a mobily. Te\u010f se pokus\u00ed ochr\u00e1nit i v\u0161echny krabi\u010dky", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "4. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010de u\u017e antiviry chr\u00e1n\u00ed d\u00e1vno, p\u0159ed lety za\u010daly auditovat i software na mobilech a nyn\u00ed p\u0159ich\u00e1z\u00ed na \u0159adu internet v\u011bc\u00ed. Avast na MWC uk\u00e1zal platformu Smart Life, kter\u00e1 pomoc\u00ed chytr\u00e9ho routeru nebo dedikovan\u00e9 krabi\u010dky ochr\u00e1n\u00ed lok\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165.", "tags": ["Video", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Bezpe\u010dnost", "IoT", "Antivirus", "Malware", "Avast", "ESET", "Webkamera", "MWC", "Krabi\u010dka", "Chytr\u00fd router", "Lok\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165", "Mobil", "Toustova\u010d"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-podporuje-sexualni-obtezovani-stezuje-si-byvala-zamestnankyne-v-zalobe/sc-3-a-192060/default.aspx", "title": "Google podporuje sexu\u00e1ln\u00ed obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed, st\u011b\u017euje si b\u00fdval\u00e1 zam\u011bstnankyn\u011b v \u017ealob\u011b", "author": "Mark\u00e9ta Mike\u0161ov\u00e1", "date": "2. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "S dal\u0161\u00ed \u017ealobou, tentokr\u00e1t v duchu #metoo, se pot\u00fdk\u00e1 Google. Podala ji b\u00fdval\u00e1 zam\u011bstnankyn\u011b firmy, kter\u00e1 tvrd\u00ed, \u017ee byla vystavena neust\u00e1l\u00e9mu sexu\u00e1ln\u00edmu obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed, kter\u00e9 zp\u016fsobila chlapsk\u00e1 kultura ve firm\u011b. \u00dadajn\u011b byla i napadena, informuje .Zam\u011bstnankyn\u011b se jmenuje Loretta Lee a v Googlu pracovala sedm let jako softwarov\u00e1 in\u017een\u00fdrka. Z firmy ode\u0161la v \u00fanoru 2016, kdy dostala v\u00fdpov\u011b\u010f. Za tu dobu podle textu \u017ealoby za\u017eila celou \u0159adu p\u0159\u00edpad\u016f sexu\u00e1ln\u00edho obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed, diskriminace a ur\u00e1\u017een\u00ed. Ani jej\u00ed propu\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed pr\u00fd nebylo od\u016fvodn\u011bn\u00e9.Lee dokonce popisuje konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed p\u0159\u00edpady obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed. Stalo se j\u00ed nap\u0159\u00edklad, \u017ee \u201ekolega lil do n\u00e1poj\u016f whiskey a sm\u00e1l se tomu\u201c, nebo j\u00ed \u201eopil\u00fd mu\u017esk\u00fd kolega z ni\u010deho nic dal na v\u00e1no\u010dn\u00edm ve\u010d\u00edrku facku\u201c. \u017daloba tak\u00e9 uv\u00e1d\u00ed incident, kdy se kolega m\u011bl \u017een\u011b schovat pod stolem a odm\u00edtal vysv\u011btlit, co tam d\u011bl\u00e1.\u017dena si podle \u017ealoby st\u011b\u017eovala u veden\u00ed, kter\u00e9 j\u00ed poradilo vyplnit form\u00e1ln\u00ed st\u00ed\u017enost. To neud\u011blala, proto\u017ee se b\u00e1la, \u017ee by j\u00ed kolegov\u00e9 obt\u011b\u017eovali je\u0161t\u011b v\u00edc. Person\u00e1ln\u00ed odd\u011blen\u00ed pak uvedlo, \u017ee \u201ese odm\u00edtala pod\u00edlet na vy\u0159e\u0161en\u00ed situace\u201c.Pozd\u011bji st\u00ed\u017enost p\u0159ece jen vyplnila. Google nejen, \u017ee podle \u017eeny nic nevy\u0161et\u0159il, ale je\u0161t\u011b j\u00ed kolegov\u00e9 p\u0159estali pom\u00e1hat s k\u00f3dov\u00e1n\u00edm a jej\u00ed pr\u00e1ci za\u010dali odm\u00edtat. Kr\u00e1tce pot\u00e9 obdr\u017eela v\u00fdpov\u011b\u010f kv\u016fli \u201enedostate\u010dn\u00e9mu v\u00fdkonu\u201c, navzdory tomu, \u017ee cel\u00e9 roky dost\u00e1vala v Googlu pozitivn\u00ed ohodnocen\u00ed.Google ve vyj\u00e1d\u0159en\u00ed pro Gizmondo uvedl, \u017ee ve firm\u011b plat\u00ed \u0159ada siln\u00fdch opat\u0159en\u00ed proti obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed a ka\u017ed\u00e1 st\u00ed\u017enost je \u0159\u00e1dn\u011b vy\u0161et\u0159ena. \u201eKdy\u017e zjist\u00edme poru\u0161en\u00ed na\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed, okam\u017eit\u011b zam\u011bstnance propust\u00edme,\u201c uvedl mluv\u010d\u00ed.Sou\u010dasn\u00e1 \u017ealoba je ji\u017e n\u011bkolik\u00e1t\u00e1, kter\u00e1 upozor\u0148uje, \u017ee v Silicon Valley panuje ne\u0161\u0165astn\u00e1 kultura. Vedle \u017ealob jako od Lee, je\u017e si st\u011b\u017euj\u00ed na sexu\u00e1ln\u00ed obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed, se objevuj\u00ed tak\u00e9 \u017ealoby upozor\u0148uj\u00edc\u00ed na diskriminaci. Do pop\u0159ed\u00ed se dostala nap\u0159\u00edklad \u017ealoba od b\u00fdval\u00e9ho zam\u011bstnance Googlu Jamese Damora, kter\u00fd uvedl, \u017ee \u017eeny a mu\u017ei jsou biologicky ur\u010deni pro jin\u00fd typ pr\u00e1ce, a \u017ee firma v\u0161emi mo\u017en\u00fdmi multikulti na\u0159\u00edzen\u00edmi a kv\u00f3tami diskriminuje \u201eklasick\u00e9 b\u00edl\u00e9 chlapy\u201c.", "tags": ["Google", "Pr\u00e1vo", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Soudy", "Nedostate\u010dn\u00fd v\u00fdkon", "St\u00ed\u017enost", "Sexu\u00e1ln\u00ed obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Gizmondo", "Obt\u011b\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Cel\u00fd rok", "Kolega", "Zam\u011bstnankyn\u011b", "Person\u00e1ln\u00ed odd\u011blen\u00ed", "Silicon Valley", "Form\u00e1ln\u00ed st\u00ed\u017enost", "\u017daloba", "B\u00fdval\u00fd zam\u011bstnanec", "Cel\u00e1 \u0159ada"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/experiment-konci-vypis-na-facebooku-se-delit-nebude-ale-upravy-feedu-prijdou/sc-3-a-192068/default.aspx", "title": "Experiment kon\u010d\u00ed, v\u00fdpis na Facebooku se d\u011blit nebude. Ale \u00fapravy feedu p\u0159ijdou", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "2. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Facebook loni na podzim spustil v \u0161esti vybran\u00fdch zem\u00edch test s rozd\u011blen\u00fdm v\u00fdpisem zpr\u00e1v. Nyn\u00ed tento test uzav\u0159el s t\u00edm, \u017ee toto \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed nenasad\u00ed na celou s\u00ed\u0165. V\u00fdpis p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f, neboli newsfeed, ale p\u0159ece jen uprav\u00ed, a to s d\u016frazem na up\u0159ednostn\u011bn\u00ed p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f p\u0159\u00e1tel a rodiny.Test rozd\u011blen\u00fdch feed\u016f prob\u00edhal mimo jin\u00e9 na Slovensku, tak\u017ee jsme k n\u011bmu m\u011bli docela bl\u00edzko a sly\u0161eli jsme o n\u011bm b\u011b\u017en\u011b od slovensk\u00fdch zn\u00e1m\u00fdch a p\u0159\u00edbuzn\u00fdch. N\u00e1zory byly vesm\u011bs negativn\u00ed, co\u017e nyn\u00ed p\u0159ipou\u0161t\u00ed i s\u00e1m Facebook v p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku . Experiment vyhodnotil s t\u00edm, \u017ee nevedl ke k\u00fd\u017een\u00e9mu v\u00fdsledku, aby lid\u00e9 v\u00edce komunikovali a sd\u00edleli v r\u00e1mci p\u0159\u00e1tel a rodiny.Pr\u00e1v\u011b v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed d\u016fraz na komunity, p\u0159\u00e1tel\u00e9 a rodinu ozn\u00e1mil jako hlavn\u00ed aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed strategii Facebooku jeho zakladatel a \u0161\u00e9f Mark Zuckerberg . Pro provozovatele str\u00e1nek to bude znamenat sn\u00ed\u017een\u00ed dosahu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f na sv\u00e9 fanou\u0161ky, pokud za n\u011b nebudou cht\u00edt platit. Pod rou\u0161kou c\u00edlen\u00ed na upev\u0148ov\u00e1n\u00ed vztah\u016f s bl\u00edzk\u00fdmi tedy m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt prost\u00fd tlak na zvy\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed prodej\u016f reklamy.Facebook mus\u00ed tak jako tak n\u011bco d\u011blat, proto\u017ee zlat\u00e1 \u00e9ra jeho r\u016fstu pomalu kon\u010d\u00ed a v USA dokonce postupn\u011b kles\u00e1 po\u010det mlad\u00fdch u\u017eivatel\u016f. Facebook u\u017e pro n\u011b nen\u00ed cool. Cekov\u011b u\u017eivatel\u016f Facebooku sice st\u00e1le hojn\u011b p\u0159ib\u00fdv\u00e1, ale je to t\u00edm, jak pronik\u00e1 do star\u0161\u00edch v\u011bkov\u00fdch skupin a geograficky do dal\u0161\u00edch region\u016f. Aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed situace v USA je v\u0161ak alarmem, \u017ee r\u016fst se m\u016f\u017ee i v glob\u00e1ln\u00edm m\u011b\u0159\u00edtku zastavit a p\u0159estat b\u00fdt atraktivn\u00ed pro mlad\u00e9.D\u016fraz na propojov\u00e1n\u00ed s bl\u00edzk\u00fdmi tedy d\u00e1v\u00e1 smysl. U\u017eivatel\u00e9 ve fin\u00e1le mohou na Facebooku tr\u00e1vit m\u00e9n\u011b \u010dasu a za z\u00e1bavou mohou chodit na jinou soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165, kter\u00e1 zrovna bude v kurzu. Ale na Facebook se budou vracet, proto\u017ee tam bude ka\u017ed\u00fd a poslou\u017e\u00ed jako komunitn\u00ed a komunika\u010dn\u00ed platforma. D\u00edky tomu se m\u016f\u017ee st\u00e1t Facebook t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 \u201enesmrteln\u00fd\u201c podobn\u011b jako e-mail. ", "tags": ["Web", "Facebook", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "USA", "Mark Zuckerberg", "Slovensko", "Koment\u00e1\u0159", "Experiment", "K\u00fd\u017een\u00fd v\u00fdsledek", "Zlat\u00e1 \u00e9ra", "Vybran\u00e1 zem\u011b", "V\u00fdpis", "P\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek", "Mlad\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Rodina", "P\u0159\u00edtel", "D\u016fraz", "Glob\u00e1ln\u00ed m\u011b\u0159\u00edtko", "Shutterstock", "Vybran\u00fd p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek", "Kan\u00e1l", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Cel\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/potvrzeno-chytry-reproduktor-od-samsungu-prijde-vdruhe-polovine-roku/sc-3-a-192014/default.aspx", "title": "Potvrzeno: Chytr\u00fd reproduktor od Samsungu p\u0159ijde v\u00a0druh\u00e9 polovin\u011b roku", "author": "Mark\u00e9ta Mike\u0161ov\u00e1", "date": "27. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Kdy\u017e se d\u0159\u00edve \u0159eklo chytr\u00fd reproduktor, ka\u017ed\u00fd si p\u0159edstavil Amazon Echo s jeho asistentkou Alexou. Takov\u00e9 \u010dasy u\u017e jsou ale d\u00e1vno pass\u00e9. Dnes tu m\u00e1me chytr\u00fdch reproduktor\u016f celou \u0159adu a po Applu se do party p\u0159ipojuje i Samsung. Po dlouh\u00fdch spekulac\u00edch, kdy se za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edm kone\u010dn\u011b p\u0159ijde, firma ozn\u00e1mila, \u017ee jej vyd\u00e1 v druh\u00e9 polovin\u011b leto\u0161n\u00edho roku.Respektive to ozn\u00e1mil \u0161\u00e9f mobiln\u00ed divize Samsungu DJ Koh, jen\u017e to \u0159ekl na akci , kter\u00e1 se kon\u00e1 tento t\u00fdden od pond\u011bl\u00ed do \u010dtvrtka. V p\u0159\u00edprav\u011b je chytr\u00fd reproduktor, kter\u00fd bude obsahovat virtu\u00e1ln\u00edho asistenta Bixby.Samsung poprv\u00e9 potvrdil, \u017ee na za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed pracuje loni v srpnu. Tehdy se za\u010dalo spekulovat, \u017ee firma by jej mohla vydat n\u011bkdy v prvn\u00ed polovin\u011b leto\u0161n\u00edho roku a prodejn\u00ed cena by se mohla pohybovat kolem 200 dolar\u016f (n\u011bco m\u00e1lo p\u0159es 4000 K\u010d plus DPH). Odhad nakonec nebyl tak daleko od pravdy, Samsung reproduktor vyd\u00e1 jen o n\u011bkolik m\u011bs\u00edc\u016f pozd\u011bji.V\u00edce informac\u00ed prezident nesd\u011blil. St\u00e1le nen\u00ed jasn\u00e9, jak za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed bude vypadat a co bude um\u011bt, ale d\u00e1 se p\u0159edpokl\u00e1dat, \u017ee minim\u00e1ln\u011b v\u0161echno, co um\u00ed jeho konkurenti. Plus je mo\u017en\u00e9, \u017ee bude fungovat i jako hub pro syst\u00e9m chytr\u00e9ho domova SmartThings.Jedinou informaci nav\u00edc Koh prozradil . Samsung se pr\u00fd s reproduktorem bude cht\u00edt zam\u011b\u0159it na pr\u00e9miovou kvalitu, tud\u00ed\u017e bude konkurovat sp\u00ed\u0161 , ne\u017e levn\u011bj\u0161\u00edm za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edm jako je Google Home Mini nebo Amazon Echo Dot.", "tags": ["Google", "Apple", "Samsung", "Chytr\u00e1 dom\u00e1cnost", "Prvn\u00ed polovina", "Jedin\u00e1 informace", "Dolar", "Levn\u00e9 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "Virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed asistent", "Bixby", "SmartThings", "Mobile World Congress", "Pr\u00e9miov\u00e1 kvalita", "Druh\u00e1 polovina", "Cel\u00e1 \u0159ada", "KOH", "Chytr\u00fd reproduktor", "Polovina", "Prodejn\u00ed cena", "Za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "Wall Street Journal", "Mobiln\u00ed divize", "Leto\u0161n\u00ed rok", "Chytr\u00fd domov", "Reproduktor"]}
