{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/legendarni-tamagotchi-se-vraci-hra-zamiri-na-smartphony-jiz-pristi-mesic/sc-3-a-192036/default.aspx", "title": "Legend\u00e1rn\u00ed Tamagotchi se vrac\u00ed. Hra zam\u00ed\u0159\u00ed na smartphony ji\u017e p\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u00ed m\u011bs\u00edc", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "28. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "V\u0161ichni, kte\u0159\u00ed netrp\u011bliv\u011b \u010dekali na uveden\u00ed ji\u017e d\u0159\u00edve ozn\u00e1men\u00e9 hry  se kone\u010dn\u011b do\u010dkali. Bandai Namco aplikaci vypust\u00ed k 20. v\u00fdro\u010d\u00ed Tamagotchi ji\u017e v polovin\u011b b\u0159ezna pro Android i iOS. Nov\u00e9 \u0161\u00edlenstv\u00ed tak m\u016f\u017ee za\u010d\u00edt.St\u00e1le se, stejn\u011b jako v origin\u00e1lu, budete starat o sv\u00e9ho dom\u00e1c\u00edho mazl\u00ed\u010dka, krmit jej, hr\u00e1t minihry a sledovat, jak roste. Hra je nav\u00edc um\u00edst\u011bna ve virtu\u00e1ln\u00edm m\u011bst\u011b Tamatown, kter\u00e9 budete moci prozkoum\u00e1vat a hledat nov\u00e9 p\u0159\u00e1tele. Sv\u016fj \u00fasp\u011bch a z\u00e1\u017eitky budete samoz\u0159ejm\u011b moci sd\u00edlet se sv\u00fdmi p\u0159\u00e1teli. Prozat\u00edm to ale vypad\u00e1, \u017ee hra nebude vyu\u017e\u00edvat prvky  podobn\u011b, jak to d\u011bl\u00e1 nap\u0159\u00edklad .Hra bude dostupn\u00e1 od 15. b\u0159ezna pro ob\u011b platformy, na Androidu ji\u017e nyn\u00ed m\u016f\u017eete . Obchod Play v\u00e1s pot\u00e9 automaticky upozorn\u00ed, jakmile bude titul dostupn\u00fd. Registrovat se tak\u00e9 m\u016f\u017eete na  a pokud budete m\u00edt \u0161t\u011bst\u00ed, vytvo\u0159\u00ed podle v\u00e1s nov\u00e9ho mazl\u00ed\u010dka, kter\u00fd pak bude dostupn\u00fd v\u0161em hr\u00e1\u010d\u016fm na sv\u011bt\u011b.", "tags": ["Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Android", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "iOS", "App Store", "Play Store", "Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e1 realita", "Hry", "Pok\u00e9mon Go", "Smartphone", "Dom\u00e1c\u00ed mazl\u00ed\u010dek", "Hra", "Virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed m\u011bsto", "Mazl\u00ed\u010dek", "Bandai Namco", "P\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u00ed m\u011bs\u00edc", "Ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed str\u00e1nka", "P\u0159\u00edtel", "B\u0159ezen"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/microsoft-teams-nabidne-verzi-zdarma-bude-tak-lepe-konkurovat-slacku/sc-3-a-192022/default.aspx", "title": "Microsoft Teams nab\u00eddne verzi zdarma. Bude tak l\u00e9pe konkurovat Slacku", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "28. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Konkurent z gar\u00e1\u017ee Microsoftu pro obl\u00edben\u00fd Slack, , je prozat\u00edm dostupn\u00fd pouze firm\u00e1m s podnikov\u00fdm p\u0159edplatn\u00fdm . To by se ale mohlo zm\u011bnit. Nyn\u00ed to vypad\u00e1, \u017ee redmondsk\u00fd gigant chyst\u00e1 i verzi zdarma \u2013 podobn\u011b, jako konkurence.N\u00e1znaky se objevily v nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed beta verzi aplikace, kdy je n\u011bkolikr\u00e1t referov\u00e1no pr\u00e1v\u011b na freemium model a mo\u017enost upgradu. Informoval o tom web . Verze zdarma bude pravd\u011bpodobn\u011b omezena limitem \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b \u010di velikost\u00ed sd\u00edlen\u00fdch soubor\u016f, stejn\u011b tak je mo\u017en\u00e9 i omezen\u00ed po\u010dtu lid\u00ed v t\u00fdmu.Prozat\u00edm ale nen\u00ed jasn\u00e9, kdy dojde ke spu\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed. Microsoft t\u00edmto krokem vyraz\u00ed do boje hlavn\u011b o men\u0161\u00ed firmy a t\u00fdmy, kter\u00e9 si budou moci slu\u017ebu vyzkou\u0161et v provozu v r\u00e1mci firmy. Omezen\u00e9 verze zdarma m\u00e1 pr\u00e1v\u011b i konkuren\u010dn\u00ed  \u010di Twist.Slu\u017eba, stejn\u011b jako konkurence, pak slou\u017e\u00ed jako n\u00e1hrada e-mail\u016f pro komunikaci pr\u00e1v\u011b v r\u00e1mci t\u00fdm\u016f. Umo\u017e\u0148uje m\u00edt odd\u011blen\u00e9 \u010di spole\u010dn\u00e9 konverzace v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase, sd\u00edlet spolu soubory \u010di po\u0159\u00e1dat konferen\u010dn\u00ed videohovory.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Slack", "Office 365", "Verze", "Podnikov\u00e9 p\u0159edplatn\u00e9", "Re\u00e1ln\u00fd \u010das", "Sd\u00edlen\u00fd soubor", "Soubor", "Petri", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed beta", "Konkurence", "Omezen\u00e1 verze", "Mal\u00e1 firma", "Twist", "Videohovor", "Freemium"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/autonomni-vozidla-si-nemohou-zajet-na-automatickou-mycku-budou-vyzadovat-lidske-rucni-myti/sc-3-a-192029/default.aspx", "title": "Autonomn\u00ed vozidla si nemohou zajet na automatickou my\u010dku. Budou vy\u017eadovat \u201elidsk\u00e9\u201c ru\u010dn\u00ed myt\u00ed", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "28. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "S p\u0159\u00edchodem autonomn\u00edch vozidel, kter\u00e9 odstra\u0148uj\u00ed nutnost pou\u017eit\u00ed lidsk\u00e9ho \u0159idi\u010de, p\u0159ich\u00e1z\u00ed pom\u011brn\u011b vtipn\u00e1 situace, kter\u00e1 souvis\u00ed s myt\u00edm t\u011bchto voz\u016f. V\u00fdrobci automobil\u016f se toti\u017e shoduj\u00ed v tom, \u017ee nen\u00ed mo\u017en\u00e9 tato auta um\u00fdt v b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch automatick\u00fdch my\u010dk\u00e1ch, kter\u00e9 jsou b\u011b\u017en\u011b dostupn\u00e9 u benz\u00ednov\u00fdch stanic.Hlavn\u00ed d\u016fvod je jasn\u00fd \u2013 \u010distota senzor\u016f a ochrana skel, kter\u00e9 by se p\u0159i klasick\u00e9m myt\u00ed v my\u010dce mohly nestandardn\u011b zne\u010distit (nap\u0159\u00edklad uschl\u00e9 kapky \u0161amponu, ne\u010dekan\u00e9 odlesky mastnoty a podobn\u011b) a tak\u00e9 se mohou relativn\u011b rychle po\u0161kr\u00e1bat. Automatick\u00e9 my\u010dky rovn\u011b\u017e mohou zp\u016fsobit zm\u011bnu um\u00edst\u011bn\u00ed senzoru a i kdy\u017e p\u016fjde o milimetry, m\u016f\u017ee to ve v\u00fdsledku znamenat v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed nep\u0159esnosti ve fin\u00e1ln\u00ed autonomn\u00edm \u0159\u00edzen\u00ed s nutnost\u00ed op\u011btovn\u00e9 kalibrace.Dle  se tak v\u00fdrobci autonomn\u00edch voz\u016f a syst\u00e9m\u016f (nap\u0159\u00edklad Toyota, Aptiv, Drive.AI, May Mobility, Waymo, Uber) shodli v tom, \u017ee je nutn\u00e9 prov\u00e1d\u011bt myt\u00ed t\u011bchto voz\u016f ru\u010dn\u011b. P\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm jednotliv\u00e9 senzory je nutn\u00e9 om\u00fdt pe\u010dliv\u011b alkoholem, \u010distou vodou a jemn\u00fdm hadrem nebo podobn\u00fdmi prost\u0159edky, kter\u00e9 se pou\u017e\u00edvaj\u00ed t\u0159eba pro \u010dist\u011bn\u00ed oken. Z\u00e1stupci Waymo (Google, Alphabet) nav\u00edc upozornili, \u017ee myt\u00ed senzor\u016f je nutn\u00e9 pom\u011brn\u011b \u010dasto.M\u011blo by ale j\u00edt pouze o chvilkov\u00fd \u201eprobl\u00e9m\u201c, proto\u017ee nap\u0159\u00edklad General Motors u\u017e s nov\u00fdmi vozy po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1, \u017ee budou m\u00edt integrovan\u00fd syst\u00e9m \u010di\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed v\u0161ech t\u011bchto senzor\u016f. Tak\u017ee ani p\u0159echod lidsk\u00fdch \u0159idi\u010d\u016f do oblasti ru\u010dn\u00edho myt\u00ed autonomn\u00edch vozidel nen\u00ed moc perspektivn\u00ed.", "tags": ["Google", "Technologie", "Automobily", "Waymo", "Alphabet", "Toyota", "Hlavn\u00ed d\u016fvod", "Nov\u00fd v\u016fz", "Lidsk\u00fd \u0159idi\u010d", "V\u016fz", "Myt\u00ed", "CNN", "General Motors", "Aptiv", "Autonomn\u00ed vozidlo", "Autonomn\u00ed v\u016fz", "\u010cist\u00e1 voda", "Benz\u00edn", "Wayma", "Vozidlo", "B\u011b\u017en\u00fd provoz", "My\u010dka", "Senzor", "Integrovan\u00fd syst\u00e9m"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/apple-si-patentoval-nabijeci-krabicku-pro-apple-watch-pocita-i-sbezdratovym-nabijenim-pasku/sc-3-a-192028/default.aspx", "title": "Apple si patentoval nab\u00edjec\u00ed krabi\u010dku pro Apple Watch. Po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 i s\u00a0bezdr\u00e1tov\u00fdm nab\u00edjen\u00edm p\u00e1sk\u016f", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "28. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Apple z\u00edskal dal\u0161\u00edch patent, kter\u00fd tentokr\u00e1t n\u00e1sleduje \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed pro bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e1 sluch\u00e1tka AirPods \u2013 jednoduchou krabi\u010dku pro bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9 nab\u00edjen\u00ed chytr\u00fdch hodinek \u010di podobn\u00fdch mal\u00fdch nositeln\u00fdch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed. prezentuje krabi\u010dku, do kter\u00e9 se samostatn\u011b vejde jak hlavn\u00ed v\u00fdpo\u010detn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st Apple Watch, tak i dva d\u00edly p\u00e1sk\u016f. Podobn\u011b jako u krabi\u010dky pro AirPods, i zde se po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 s magnetick\u00fdm uchycen\u00edm a bezdr\u00e1tov\u00fdm nab\u00edjen\u00edm. Krabi\u010dka tak bude obsahovat integrovanou baterii, kterou bude mo\u017en\u00e9 nab\u00edjet extern\u00edm p\u0159ipojen\u00edm nap\u0159\u00edklad do USB.Jedn\u00e1 se tak o ide\u00e1ln\u00ed \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed na cesty, ale to nejzaj\u00edmav\u011bj\u0161\u00ed je to, \u017ee Apple v tomto patentu po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 s t\u00edm, \u017ee krabi\u010dka bude schopn\u00e1 nab\u00edjet i jednotliv\u00e9 \u201echytr\u00e9\u201c p\u00e1sky. Lze tedy p\u0159edpokl\u00e1dat, \u017ee Apple rozhodn\u011b o nov\u00e9 generaci p\u00e1sk\u016f, kter\u00e9 budou m\u00edt senzory \u010di dal\u0161\u00ed baterie, uva\u017euje. Zat\u00edm se objevilo spoustu prototyp\u016f p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm v r\u00e1mci v\u011bdeck\u00e9 komunity (ohebn\u00e9 baterie, ohebn\u00e9 senzory), kdy se ale do\u010dk\u00e1me fin\u00e1ln\u00edho produktu od Applu, to zat\u00edm st\u00e1le nen\u00ed jasn\u00e9.Na podzim tohoto roku lze op\u011bt o\u010dek\u00e1vat p\u0159edstaven\u00ed nov\u00e9, v po\u0159ad\u00ed ji\u017e \u010dtvrt\u00e9 generace chytr\u00fdch hodinek Apple Watch.", "tags": ["Apple", "USB", "Baterie", "Patenty", "Apple Watch", "Bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9 nab\u00edjen\u00ed", "Nositelnosti", "Hodinky", "AirPods", "Ohebn\u00e1 baterie", "Fin\u00e1ln\u00ed produkt", "P\u00e1sek", "Nab\u00edjen\u00ed", "Patent", "Magnetick\u00e9 uchycen\u00ed", "Nov\u00fd patent", "Ide\u00e1ln\u00ed \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed", "Krabi\u010dka", "Bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9 sluch\u00e1tko", "T\u0159et\u00ed generace", "Nov\u00e1 generace", "Integrovan\u00e1 baterie", "Extern\u00ed p\u0159ipojen\u00ed", "Chytr\u00e9 hodinky", "\u010ctvrt\u00e1 generace"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/velky-test-all-in-one-pc-a-hernich-monitoru-v-novem-computeru/sc-3-a-192051/default.aspx", "title": "Velk\u00fd test All-in-One PC a hern\u00edch monitor\u016f v nov\u00e9m Computeru", "author": "\u010casopis Computer", "date": "1. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Na st\u00e1nky m\u00ed\u0159\u00ed b\u0159eznov\u00fd Computer, ve kter\u00e9m najdete spoustu zaj\u00edmav\u00fdch technologick\u00fdch t\u00e9mat a jako v\u017edy i dva velmi d\u016fkladn\u00e9 testy. Tentokr\u00e1t jsme do Testlabu pozvali  ve dvou v\u00fdkonov\u00fdch a cenov\u00fdch relac\u00edch, a . Cht\u011bli jsme zodpov\u011bd\u011bt ot\u00e1zku, zda m\u00e1 144 Hz skute\u010dn\u011b smysl. P\u0159edplatitel\u00e9 maj\u00ed cestu do trafiky u\u0161et\u0159enu, \u010dasopis na\u0161li ve sv\u00e9 schr\u00e1nce o den d\u0159\u00edve ne\u017e na st\u00e1nc\u00edch. Chcete m\u00edt Computer tak\u00e9 d\u0159\u00edve? P\u0159edpla\u0165te si jej \u010cten\u00e1\u0159i pap\u00edrov\u00e9 i elektronick\u00e9 verze tentokr\u00e1t z\u00edskaj\u00ed pln\u00e9 verze program\u016f   a p\u0159\u00edstup do  s bonusov\u00fdm redak\u010dn\u00edm materi\u00e1lem. Ka\u017ed\u00fd \u010dten\u00e1\u0159 z\u00edsk\u00e1v\u00e1 dv\u011b pln\u00e9 verze program\u016f a ro\u010dn\u00ed licenci pro studium jazyk\u016f.Napi\u0161te SMS na \u010d\u00edslo  ve tvaru:P\u0159\u00edklad: COMPUTER 1803 Jan Novak Prubezna 233 Olomouc 77900Cena ka\u017ed\u00e9 p\u0159ijat\u00e9 SMS je 89 K\u010d, stejn\u011b jako \u010dasopis na st\u00e1nc\u00edch. Zahrnuje po\u0161tovn\u00e9 i baln\u00e9. Provozuje CN INVEST, a. s., infolinka 296 363 199 ve v\u0161edn\u00ed dny 8\u201316 hod., , .V nov\u00e9m Computeru najdete od spole\u010dnosti .Po\u010d\u00edta\u010de v\u0161e v jednom dok\u00e1\u017eou u\u0161et\u0159it spoustu prostoru, zbavit v\u00e1s mnoha kabel\u016f a nab\u00eddnou v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed zobrazovac\u00ed plochu ne\u017e notebooky. N\u00e1ru\u017eiv\u00ed hr\u00e1\u010di rychl\u00fdch her