{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/5-grafickych-karet-ktere-lze-rozumne-koupit-i-pri-soucasne-krizi/sc-3-a-192040/default.aspx", "title": "5 grafick\u00fdch karet, kter\u00e9 lze rozumn\u011b koupit i p\u0159i sou\u010dasn\u00e9 krizi", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "28. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "", "tags": ["Hardware", "Amazon", "Nvidia", "Grafick\u00e9 karty", "AMD", "Asus", "Velk\u00e9 \u0161t\u011bst\u00ed", "Pohodln\u00e9 hran\u00ed", "Nejvy\u0161\u0161\u00ed detail", "Skv\u011bl\u00e1 volba", "Nejv\u00fdkonn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed karta", "Velk\u00e1 \u010d\u00e1st", "Kingdom Come", "Zotac", "Dostupn\u00e1 varianta", "P\u0159ijateln\u00e1 varianta", "Posledn\u00ed p\u016flrok", "Velk\u00e9 rozli\u0161en\u00ed", "Nejlevn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed kategorie", "Podobn\u00e1 cena", "Provozn\u00ed vlastnost", "Ur\u010dit\u00e1 hranice", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Vysok\u00e1 cena", "\u010cesk\u00e9 prost\u0159ed\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/facebook-v-cesku-spustil-svuj-vyhledavac-prace-pomuze-firmam-i-uchazecum/sc-3-a-192039/default.aspx", "title": "Facebook v \u010cesku spustil sv\u016fj vyhled\u00e1va\u010d pr\u00e1ce. Pom\u016f\u017ee firm\u00e1m i uchaze\u010d\u016fm", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "1. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "V minul\u00e9m roce Facebook p\u0159edstavil vlastn\u00ed platformu pro hled\u00e1n\u00ed pr\u00e1ce pojmenovanou jednodu\u0161e  (v \u010de\u0161tin\u011b Kari\u00e9ra). Dostupn\u00e1 byla prvn\u011b pouze v Americe a Kanad\u011b, na\u010de\u017e do\u0161lo k postupn\u00e9mu roz\u0161i\u0159ov\u00e1n\u00ed a nyn\u00ed je funkce aktivov\u00e1na pro v\u0161echny \u00fa\u010dty v t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 40 zem\u00edch v\u010detn\u011b \u010ceska.Umo\u017e\u0148uje, podobn\u011b jako specializovan\u00e9 port\u00e1ly, proch\u00e1zet z\u00e1jemc\u016fm nab\u00eddky pr\u00e1ce od firem z konkr\u00e9tn\u00edho m\u00edsta. Filtrovat je lze i podle odv\u011btv\u00ed \u010di typu \u00favazku. Hlavn\u00ed s\u00edla Facebooku ale je v datech, kter\u00e1 na s\u00edti m\u00e1te. Pokud toti\u017e chcete na inzer\u00e1t odpov\u011bd\u011bt, s\u00ed\u0165 v\u00e1m p\u0159edvypln\u00ed va\u0161e \u00fadaje, kter\u00e9 m\u00e1te zadan\u00e9 na profilu. V\u0161e m\u016f\u017eete samoz\u0159ejm\u011b upravit \u010di vymazat, pokud jste ale v minulosti na Facebook dali pravdiv\u00e9 informace, m\u00e1te pr\u00e1ci zjednodu\u0161enou.Pro firmy pak poskytuje jednoduchou mo\u017enost, jak nal\u00e1kat nov\u00e9 uchaze\u010de. Inzer\u00e1t se toti\u017e objev\u00ed jak ve speci\u00e1ln\u00ed z\u00e1lo\u017ece na hlavn\u00ed str\u00e1nce, tak i na profilu str\u00e1nky. P\u0159i vypisov\u00e1n\u00ed je mo\u017en\u00e9 doplnit r\u016fzn\u00e9 podrobnosti v\u010detn\u011b platu a je mo\u017en\u00e9 po uchaze\u010d\u00edch rovnou po\u017eadovat odpov\u011bdi na konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed ot\u00e1zky. P\u0159id\u00e1n\u00ed inzer\u00e1tu samotn\u00e9ho je bez poplatku. je p\u0159\u00edmou konkurenc\u00ed ji\u017e zab\u011bhl\u00fdm port\u00e1l\u016fm, jako je nap\u0159\u00edklad soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165  \u010di obl\u00edben\u00e9 Jobs.cz. T\u011bm by mohl do budoucna \u0159\u00e1dn\u011b zava\u0159it. \u00da\u010det na t\u00e9to soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edti m\u00e1 obrovsk\u00e9 mno\u017estv\u00ed lid\u00ed a pro n\u011bkter\u00e9 se jedn\u00e1 o prvn\u00ed m\u00edsto, kde hledaj\u00ed informace.", "tags": ["Facebook", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Linkedin", "Prvn\u00ed m\u00edsto", "Kari\u00e9ra", "Port\u00e1l", "P\u0159\u00edm\u00e1 konkurence", "Amerika", "Vyhled\u00e1va\u010d", "Jednoduch\u00e1 mo\u017enost", "Minul\u00fd rok", "Jobs", "S\u00ed\u0165", "Hlavn\u00ed str\u00e1nka", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Nov\u00fd uchaze\u010d", "Uchaze\u010d", "Inzer\u00e1t", "Poplatek", "Obrovsk\u00e9 mno\u017estv\u00ed", "Profil", "Specializovan\u00fd port\u00e1l", "Pravdiv\u00e1 informace", "Postupn\u00e9 roz\u0161i\u0159ov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Kanada"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/twitter-spustil-zalozky-zajimave-tweety-si-muzete-ulozit-na-pozdeji/sc-3-a-192055/default.aspx", "title": "Twitter spustil Z\u00e1lo\u017eky. Zaj\u00edmav\u00e9 tweety si m\u016f\u017eete ulo\u017eit na pozd\u011bji", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "1. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Twitter minul\u00fd rok testoval funkci Z\u00e1lo\u017eek a nyn\u00ed ji vypou\u0161t\u00ed do sv\u011bta. D\u00edky n\u00ed si budete moci soukrom\u011b ulo\u017eit zaj\u00edmav\u00e9 tweety a vr\u00e1tit se k nim pozd\u011bji. Novinky by m\u011bla b\u00fdt dostupn\u00e1 ji\u017e pro v\u0161echny \u00fa\u010dty v r\u00e1mci mobiln\u00ed aplikace.Tweet do z\u00e1lo\u017eek p\u0159id\u00e1te jednodu\u0161e za pomoci nov\u00e9ho tla\u010d\u00edtka pod ka\u017edou zpr\u00e1vou. To krom ukl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed slou\u017e\u00ed i ke klasick\u00e9mu sd\u00edlen\u00ed pomoc\u00ed soukrom\u00fdch zpr\u00e1v \u010di odkazu. V\u0161echny ulo\u017een\u00e9 zpr\u00e1vy pak naleznete v samostatn\u00e9 z\u00e1lo\u017ece v menu. Prozat\u00edm to vypad\u00e1, \u017ee funkce je dostupn\u00e1 pouze skrze mobiln\u00ed aplikace. Na roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed do webov\u00e9 verze si z\u0159ejm\u011b budeme muset po\u010dkat.", "tags": ["Web", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Twitter", "Soukrom\u00e1 zpr\u00e1va", "Samostatn\u00e1 z\u00e1lo\u017eka", "Tweet", "Nov\u00e9 tla\u010d\u00edtko", "Aplikace", "Klasick\u00e9 sd\u00edlen\u00ed", "Z\u00e1lo\u017eka", "Funkce", "Webov\u00e1 verze"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/kde-hledat-slevy-na-internetu/sc-3-a-192069/default.aspx", "title": "Kde hledat slevy na internetu", "author": null, "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Ob\u010das se vyplat\u00ed si po\u010dkat na n\u011bjakou p\u011bknou slevi\u010dku, ne\u017e si v\u011bc kupovat za plnou cenu. Kde ale naj\u00edt tu nejv\u00fdhodn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed nab\u00eddku? P\u0159esn\u011b v tomhle v\u00e1m porad\u00edme v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu. ", "tags": ["Internet", "Tipy", "Jak na Internet", "Sleva", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video", "Pln\u00e1 cena", "Nejv\u00fdhodn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed nab\u00eddka"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/cesky-loopgl-tak-trosku-dropbox-a-e-mail-v-jednom-nejen-pro-kreativce/sc-3-a-192052/default.aspx", "title": "\u010cesk\u00fd Loop.gl: Tak tro\u0161ku Dropbox a e-mail v jednom nejen pro kreativce", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "1. b\u0159ezna 2018", "content": "Rodinu webov\u00fdch \u00falo\u017ei\u0161\u0165 roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159ila dal\u0161\u00ed slu\u017eba. Tentokr\u00e1t za n\u00ed stoj\u00ed pra\u017esk\u00e9 studio , jmenuje se  a c\u00edl\u00ed na kreativce a tro\u0161ku jin\u00fd zp\u016fsob pr\u00e1ce. Loop je toti\u017e takov\u00fd \u201ee-mail\u201c na velk\u00e9 multimedi\u00e1ln\u00ed soubory.Co to znamen\u00e1 v praxi? Dejme tomu, \u017ee jste grafik nebo jin\u00fd kreativec a pot\u0159ebujete klientovi odeslat hotov\u00e9 d\u00edlo. Jist\u011b, mohli byste mu jednodu\u0161e sd\u00edlet slo\u017eku z b\u011b\u017en\u00e9ho \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b typu Dropbox, OneDrive a Google Drive, Loop ale do jednoho procesu integruje jak samotn\u00e1 data, tak komunikaci \u2013 v\u0161e toti\u017e vypad\u00e1 jako konverzace t\u0159eba na soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edti, anebo pr\u00e1v\u011b v e-mailu.Ov\u0161em s t\u00edm rozd\u00edlem, \u017ee do t\u00e9to konverzace m\u016f\u017eete vlo\u017eit obvykl\u00e9 grafick\u00e9, multimedi\u00e1ln\u00ed, dokumentov\u00e9 (PDF) nebo t\u0159eba archiva\u010dn\u00ed (ZIP) soubory a to v bezplatn\u00e9 verzi . U placen\u00fdch pau\u0161\u00e1l\u016f m\u016f\u017ee m\u00edt jedin\u00fd soubor i 200 GB.K soubor\u016fm nap\u00ed\u0161ete zpr\u00e1vu a z webov\u00e9ho rozhran\u00ed ji po\u0161lete na libovoln\u00fd e-mail, na kter\u00fd pot\u00e9 doraz\u00ed pozv\u00e1nka do va\u0161\u00ed konverzace. Pomoc\u00ed odkazu m\u016f\u017ee do konverzace z\u00e1rove\u0148 vstoupit i jak\u00e1koliv dal\u0161\u00ed osoba a po registraci tak\u00e9 p\u0159isp\u00edvat.V ka\u017ed\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, v\u0161ichni \u00fa\u010dastnici pak ve vl\u00e1kn\u011b mohou libovoln\u011b diskutovat, vkl\u00e1dat dal\u0161\u00ed soubory a\u017e do kapacity disku a p\u0159\u00edlohy z jednotliv\u00fdch zpr\u00e1v prohl\u00ed\u017eet, p\u0159ehr\u00e1vat, anebo stahovat bu\u010f po kusech, nebo v celku jako ZIP.", "tags": ["Web", "Webdisk", "Disk Google", "OneDrive", "\u00dalo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b", "Dropbox", "E-mail", "Zip", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165", "Jedin\u00fd soubor", "P\u0159\u00edloha", "Libovoln\u00fd e-mail", "Odeslan\u00e1 zpr\u00e1va", "Webov\u00e9 \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b", "Kreativec", "P\u0159\u00edjemce", "Loop", "Soubor", "Konverzace", "Green Light", "Webov\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed", "Placen\u00fd pau\u0161\u00e1l", "Google Drive", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e9 \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b", "Hotov\u00e9 d\u00edlo"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/microsoft-spoji-sily-s-xiaomi-vysledkem-muze-byt-chytry-reproduktor-s-cortanou/sc-3-a-191982/default.aspx", "title": "Microsoft spoj\u00ed s\u00edly s Xiaomi. V\u00fdsledkem m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt chytr\u00fd reproduktor s Cortanou", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "25. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Microsoft a Xiaomi podepsali  o vz\u00e1jemn\u00e9 t\u011bsn\u00e9 spolupr\u00e1ci v oblastech cloudu, um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence a hardwaru. Zat\u00edmco Microsoft dovol\u00ed Xiaomi vyu\u017e\u00edvat jeho cloudovou technologii a produkty, Xiaomi pro zm\u011bnu pom\u016f\u017ee Microsoftu proniknout hloub\u011bji na \u010d\u00ednsk\u00fd trh.Xiaomi by se mohlo tak\u00e9 do\u010dkat budouc\u00ed integrace asistentky Cortany do sv\u00e9ho chytr\u00e9ho repr\u00e1\u010dku Mi AI. Microsoft ji prozat\u00edm vyu\u017eil jen ve sv\u00e9m pokusu jm\u00e9nem Harmon Kardon Invoke, kter\u00fd rozhodn\u011b nep\u0159esv\u011bd\u010dil, p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm v tvrd\u00e9 konkurenci od Amazonu a Googlu.Krom\u011b v\u0161emo\u017en\u00fdch produkt\u016f by firmy mohly spolupracovat i na jin\u00fdch prototypech a slu\u017eb\u00e1ch s vyu\u017eit\u00edm um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence, jako je vyhled\u00e1va\u010d Bing, prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d Edge \u010di komunik\u00e1tor Skype.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Microsoft", "Google", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Byznys", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Mobility", "Amazon", "Edge", "Skype", "Cortana", "Bing", "Xiaomi", "Reproduktor", "Inteligence", "Produkt", "Cloudov\u00e1 technologie", "Chytr\u00fd reproduktor", "\u010c\u00ednsk\u00fd trh", "Tvrd\u00e1 konkurence"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-lens-konecne-opousti-pixel-a-miri-na-dalsi-telefony-dokonce-i-iphone/sc-3-a-191987/default.aspx", "title": "Google Lens kone\u010dn\u011b opou\u0161t\u00ed Pixel a m\u00ed\u0159\u00ed na dal\u0161\u00ed telefony, dokonce i iPhone", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "25. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Kdy\u017e byl v kv\u011btnu minul\u00e9ho roku p\u0159edstaven n\u00e1stroj Google Lens, \u0161lo sv\u00fdm zp\u016fsobem o vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed budoucnosti. Ji\u017e nebylo pot\u0159eba ps\u00e1t text, sta\u010dilo vyfotit v\u011bc, kter\u00e1 v\u00e1s zaj\u00edmala a algoritmus v\u00e1m na\u0161el v\u0161echny d\u016fle\u017eit\u00e9 informace, kter\u00e9 jste cht\u011bli v\u011bd\u011bt. Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edm nedostatkem v\u0161ak byla dostupnost pouze na mobiln\u00edm telefonu Google Pixel.Nyn\u00ed Google hodl\u00e1 postupn\u011b roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159it Lens tak\u00e9 na dal\u0161\u00ed mobily a opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my, aby mohli chytr\u00e9 vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed pou\u017e\u00edvat opravdu v\u0161ichni. Lens nav\u00edc nen\u00ed samostatnou aplikac\u00ed, Google tento n\u00e1stroj integruje do dal\u0161\u00edch aplikac\u00ed. Jmenovit\u011b nap\u0159\u00edklad Google Photos \u010di Google Assistant, kde dokonce nemus\u00edte ani objekt fotit. Sta\u010d\u00ed jen nam\u00ed\u0159it fo\u0165\u00e1kem a o v\u0161e se u\u017e postar\u00e1 chytr\u00fd algoritmus.Google Lens tak bude nov\u011b k dost\u00e1n\u00ed v nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verzi aplikace Google Photos, a to jak na , tak  a nov\u011bj\u0161\u00edm. Tak\u00e9 se dostane i do Google Assistanta na mobiln\u00edch telefonech Samsungu, Huawei, LG, Motoroly, Sony a dal\u0161\u00edch. Prozat\u00edm ale bohu\u017eel pouze ve Spojen\u00fdch st\u00e1tech, Anglii, Kanad\u011b, N\u011bmecku, Austr\u00e1lii, Indii, Francii, It\u00e1lii, \u0160pan\u011blsku a Singapuru.", "tags": ["Software", "Google", "Technologie", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "USA", "Android", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "iPhone", "iOS", "Samsung", "Sony", "Austr\u00e1lie", "N\u011bmecko", "Indie", "Francie", "Pixel", "Huawei", "Motorola", "Aplikace", "\u0160pan\u011blsko", "Samostatn\u00e1 aplikace", "Anglie", "Chytr\u00e9 vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/bezdratove-nabijeni-jednou-z-cest-je-mozna-laser-experimentalni-telefon-se-nabil-rychle-jako-z-usb/sc-3-a-191986/default.aspx", "title": "Bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9 nab\u00edjen\u00ed: Jednou z cest je mo\u017en\u00e1 laser, experiment\u00e1ln\u00ed telefon se nabil rychle jako z USB", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "25. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "V\u00fdzkumn\u00edci  zkoumali jin\u00e9 mo\u017enosti bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9ho nab\u00edjen\u00ed mobiln\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed. A poda\u0159ilo se jim nab\u00edt mobiln\u00ed telefon pomoc\u00ed laserov\u00e9ho paprsku nap\u0159\u00ed\u010d m\u00edstnost\u00ed, nav\u00edc stejnou rychlost\u00ed, jako p\u0159es klasick\u00e9 USB.T\u00fdm p\u0159ipevnil mal\u00fd nap\u00e1jec\u00ed \u010dl\u00e1nek na zadn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st mobiln\u00edho telefonu, kter\u00fd \"sb\u00edr\u00e1\" energii z laseru a postupn\u011b nab\u00edj\u00ed baterii. Aby nedo\u0161lo k p\u0159eh\u0159\u00e1t\u00ed, instalovali v\u00fdzkumn\u00edci vedle nap\u00e1jec\u00edho \u010dl\u00e1nku tak\u00e9 chladi\u010d a mechanismus, kter\u00fd vyp\u00edn\u00e1 laser v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, \u017ee mu n\u011bkdo zk\u0159\u00ed\u017e\u00ed cestu.V sou\u010dasn\u00e9 dob\u011b je laser schopen p\u0159enosu 2 watt\u016f za hodinu na plo\u0161e 9 cm ze vzd\u00e1lenosti necel\u00fdch 5 metr\u016f a tato \u010d\u00edsla je teoreticky mo\u017en\u00e9 mnohon\u00e1sobn\u011b nav\u00fd\u0161it. Z\u00e1sadn\u00ed nev\u00fdhodou prozat\u00edm z\u016fst\u00e1v\u00e1 zdroj laseru, kter\u00fd je pochopiteln\u011b zna\u010dn\u011b v\u00fdkonn\u00fd. Do b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 praxe se tedy tento zp\u016fsob dob\u00edjen\u00ed jen tak brzy nedostane, ale t\u0159eba se poda\u0159\u00ed syst\u00e9m n\u011bjak rozumn\u011b optimalizovat. ", "tags": ["Hardware", "Technika", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "USB", "Bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9 nab\u00edjen\u00ed", "Laser", "Americk\u00e1 univerzita", "\u010cl\u00e1nek", "Z\u00e1sadn\u00ed nev\u00fdhoda", "Laserov\u00fd paprsek", "Nab\u00edjen\u00ed", "Experiment\u00e1ln\u00ed telefon", "Zadn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st", "V\u00fdzkumn\u00edk", "Telefon", "Necel\u00fd metr", "Sou\u010dasn\u00e1 doba", "Mobiln\u00ed za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e1 praxe", "Stejn\u00e1 rychlost"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/tyden-zive-jak-psat-texty-na-mobilu-cisty-system-a-elonuv-internet/sc-3-a-191974/default.aspx", "title": "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b: Jak ps\u00e1t texty na mobilu, \u010dist\u00fd syst\u00e9m a Elon\u016fv internet", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "25. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "V dne\u0161n\u00edm d\u00edle T\u00fddnu \u017div\u011b byly t\u00e9matem t\u0159i zaj\u00edmav\u00e9 ud\u00e1losti z minul\u00e9ho t\u00fddne - , mo\u017enost instalovat  a nov\u00fd projekt Elona Muska - .", "tags": ["Video", "Windows", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Internet", "Linux", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Elon Musk", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "Ubuntu", "Syst\u00e9m", "Starlink", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed d\u00edl", "Mobil", "Satelitn\u00ed internet", "\u010cist\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Psan\u00ed", "Balast", "Pokrok", "Minul\u00fd t\u00fdden", "Nov\u00fd projekt", "P\u0159edchoz\u00ed d\u00edl", "Text", "Zaj\u00edmav\u00e1 ud\u00e1lost"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/apple-chysta-modernizaci-sluchatek-airpods-dostanou-siri-a-odolnost-vuci-vode/sc-3-a-191984/default.aspx", "title": "Apple chyst\u00e1 modernizaci sluch\u00e1tek AirPods. Dostanou Siri a odolnost v\u016f\u010di vod\u011b", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Sou\u010dasn\u00e1 generace sluch\u00e1tek AirPods od Applu rozhodn\u011b nen\u00ed posledn\u00ed, ostatn\u011b v\u00fdrobce sl\u00edbil nov\u00e9 u\u017e koncem uplynul\u00e9ho roku.  nyn\u00ed informuje o n\u011bkolika zaj\u00edmav\u00fdch inovac\u00edch, kter\u00e9 by se mohly objevit v dal\u0161\u00edch verz\u00edch sluch\u00e1tek.P\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm se do\u010dk\u00e1me vylep\u0161en\u00ed bezdr\u00e1tov\u00e9ho \u010dipu, kter\u00fd dovol\u00ed p\u0159\u00edstup k asistentce Siri bez dotyku, pouze hlasov\u00fdmi povely. Podobn\u011b, jako je tomu v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b \"\" v telefonu. To by m\u011blo uvolnit ruce a zp\u0159\u00edstupnit v\u00edce funkc\u00ed a slu\u017eeb.Dal\u0161\u00ed novinkou m\u00e1 b\u00fdt vodovzdornost, tak\u017ee o sluch\u00e1tka nep\u0159ijdete v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, \u017ee p\u016fjdete b\u011bhat v de\u0161ti. Bohu\u017eel zat\u00edm nev\u00edme, jak to bude s v\u00fddr\u017e\u00ed \u010di kvalitou zvuku, u\u017e tyto inovace v\u0161ak rozhodn\u011b pot\u011b\u0161\u00ed.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Apple", "Technologie", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "Siri", "Sluch\u00e1tka", "Voda", "AirPods", "Inovace", "Uplynul\u00fd rok", "Odolnost", "Zpravodajsk\u00fd web", "Hlasov\u00fd povel", "Generace", "Hey Siri", "Zaj\u00edmav\u00e1 inovace", "Bezdr\u00e1tov\u00fd \u010dip", "Sluch\u00e1tko", "Sou\u010dasn\u00e1 generace", "Bloomberg"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/bill-gates-byl-otestovan-ze-znalosti-cen-beznych-veci-ze-supermarketu-jeho-odhady-byly-silene/sc-3-a-192009/default.aspx", "title": "Bill Gates byl otestov\u00e1n ze znalosti cen b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch v\u011bc\u00ed ze supermarketu. Jeho odhady byly \u0161\u00edlen\u00e9", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Bill Gates se spoustu let dr\u017eel na pozici nejbohat\u0161\u00edho \u010dlov\u011bka na na\u0161\u00ed planet\u011b a i kdy\u017e ho nyn\u00ed vyst\u0159\u00eddal Jeff Bezos, st\u00e1le si dr\u017e\u00ed slu\u0161nou druhou pozici. V popul\u00e1rn\u00ed americk\u00e9 talk show ho ale Ellen Degeneres poprv\u00e9 vyzkou\u0161ela, jak moc si uv\u011bdomuje re\u00e1lnou cenu b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch produkt\u016f.Bill Gates se sv\u011b\u0159il, \u017ee v supermarketu u\u017e nebyl opravdu hodn\u011b dlouho a test tak bude pom\u011brn\u011b n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00fd. V testu musel uh\u00e1dnout cenu celkem p\u011bti rozli\u010dn\u00fdch produkt\u016f ze supermarketu, a to alespo\u0148 s p\u0159esnost\u00ed na jeden dolar. V\u00edce m\u00e9n\u011b se trefil pouze do jednoho produktu zam\u011b\u0159en\u00e9ho na zuby, jinak se m\u00fdlil i n\u011bkolikan\u00e1sobn\u011b. Nakonec si nechal sp\u00ed\u0161e poradit od publika.V rozhovoru se tak\u00e9 pochlubil t\u00edm, co \u201enejluxusn\u011bj\u0161\u00edho\u201c si koupil. Podle jeho slov je to Porsche a vlastn\u00ed letadlo, kter\u00e9 ale stejn\u011b pot\u0159ebuje pro neust\u00e1l\u00e9 cestov\u00e1n\u00ed. Prozradil, \u017ee si v\u016fbec nepotrp\u00ed na n\u011bjak\u00e9 zh\u00fdralosti typu vlastn\u00ed ostrov, sb\u00edrka luxusn\u00edch automobil\u016f a podobn\u011b. Nikdy nepo\u010d\u00edtal s t\u00edm, \u017ee by byl z v\u00fdvoje softwaru tak bohat\u00fd a d\u011blal to hlavn\u011b proto, \u017ee ho to bavilo.Tak\u00e9 se sv\u011b\u0159il, \u017ee ne\u017e se stal nejmlad\u0161\u00edm miliard\u00e1\u0159em p\u0159i vstupu Microsoftu na burzu, st\u00e1le m\u011bl obavy z p\u0159\u00edpadn\u00e9ho v\u00fdpadku financ\u00ed pro sv\u00e9 zam\u011bstnance a sna\u017eil se tak m\u00edrnit nab\u00edr\u00e1n\u00ed t\u011bch nov\u00fdch. Jeho ide\u00e1lem v t\u00e9 dob\u011b bylo, aby firma dok\u00e1zala fungovat (vyv\u00edjet software) i p\u0159es ro\u010dn\u00ed v\u00fdpadek p\u0159\u00edjm\u016f. V\u011bt\u0161ina zam\u011bstnanc\u016f v jeho firm\u011b toti\u017e byla star\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e byl on s\u00e1m, m\u011bla rodiny a hypot\u00e9ky, tak\u017ee za n\u011b c\u00edtil odpov\u011bdnost s t\u00edm, \u017ee je pot\u0159eba m\u00edt na v\u00fdplaty.B\u011bhem posledn\u00edch let u\u017e do sv\u00e9 nadace Bill & Melinda Gates p\u0159edal v\u00edce ne\u017e 40 miliard dolar\u016f.", "tags": ["Software", "Microsoft", "Bill Gates", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "IT Osobnosti", "Jeff Bezos", "Porsche", "Finance", "Luxusn\u00ed automobil", "Znalost", "Supermarket", "Bill", "B\u011b\u017en\u00fd produkt", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e1 v\u011bc", "Dolar", "V\u00fdpadek", "Nejmlad\u0161\u00ed miliard\u00e1\u0159", "P\u0159\u00edpadn\u00fd v\u00fdpadek", "Re\u00e1ln\u00e1 cena", "Nejbohat\u0161\u00ed \u010dlov\u011bk", "Melinda Gates", "Rozli\u010dn\u00fd produkt", "Hypot\u00e9ka", "Produkt"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/lenovo-ma-nove-notebooky-yoga-integrovalo-do-nich-alexu-od-amazonu/sc-3-a-192000/default.aspx", "title": "Lenovo m\u00e1 nov\u00e9 notebooky Yoga. Integrovalo do nich Alexu od Amazonu", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "V r\u00e1mci barcelonsk\u00e9ho MWC uk\u00e1zalo Lenovo inovovan\u00e9 modely konvertibiln\u00edch notebook\u016f Yoga 730 a Yoga 530. Druh\u00fd jmenovan\u00fd bude pod t\u00edmto ozna\u010den\u00edm dostupn\u00fd v Evrop\u011b, na americk\u00e9m trhu se bude prod\u00e1vat jako Flex 14.Yoga 730 nab\u00eddne dv\u011b varianty li\u0161\u00edc\u00ed se prim\u00e1rn\u011b \u00fahlop\u0159\u00ed\u010dkou displeje. Men\u0161\u00ed z nich bude m\u00edt 13 palc\u016f s rozli\u0161en\u00edm 3 840 \u00d7 2 160 nebo levn\u011bj\u0161\u00edm Full HD. Vedle procesor\u016f osm\u00e9 generace od Intelu zde najdeme pouze integrovan\u00e9 grafick\u00e9 j\u00e1dro Intel UHD 620.Druh\u00e1 v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed varianta bude dostupn\u00e1 s \u00fahlop\u0159\u00ed\u010dkou 15 palc\u016f rovn\u011b\u017e s mo\u017enost\u00ed zvolit rozli\u0161en\u00ed 4K nebo Full HD. Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edm rozd\u00edlem ale bude mo\u017enost vybrat variantu s dedikovanou grafickou kartou GTX 1050 od Nvidie. Ta nab\u00eddne grafick\u00fd v\u00fdkon vhodn\u00fd i pro nen\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00e9 hran\u00ed (p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b Full HD verze).Zat\u00edmco t\u0159in\u00e1ctipalcov\u00e1 Yoga 730 bude v\u00e1\u017eit asi 1,1 kg, u v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed verze to u\u017e bude 1,9 kg. Mezi konektory najdeme i dvojici USB-C s rozhran\u00edm Thunderbolt 3, standardn\u00ed USB 3.0 nebo HDMI.Opera\u010dn\u00ed pam\u011b\u0165 bude m\u00edt podle zvolen\u00e9 varianty kapacitu 8-16 GB a \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b p\u016fjde volit z 512GB \u010di 1TB varianty.P\u0159ekvapivou funkc\u00ed je integrov\u00e1n\u00ed hlasov\u00e9 asistentky Alexa od Amazonu, kter\u00e1 dopln\u00ed Cortanu standardn\u011b dostupnou ve Windows 10. Zat\u00edm nen\u00ed zcela jist\u00e9, jak\u00e9 mo\u017enosti Alexa nab\u00eddne. Nep\u016fjde v\u0161ak o u\u017e\u0161\u00ed implementaci, kter\u00e1 by nap\u0159\u00edklad umo\u017enila asistentku vyu\u017e\u00edvat i bez nutnosti odemknout syst\u00e9m. Na druhou stranu, mikrofony v za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed byly upraveny tak, aby hlas sn\u00edmaly a\u017e do vzd\u00e1lenosti 4 metr\u016f. Z velk\u00e9 \u010d\u00e1sti se tak mo\u017enosti p\u0159ibl\u00ed\u017e\u00ed samostatn\u00fdm za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edm Echo.Yoga 730 bude dostupn\u00e1 v pr\u016fb\u011bhu dubna v \u0161ed\u00e9, st\u0159\u00edbrn\u00e9 a bronzov\u00e9 variant\u011b za ceny za\u010d\u00ednaj\u00edc\u00ed na 880 dolar\u016f (13\") a 900 dolar\u016f (15\").Levn\u011bj\u0161\u00edm za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edm bude Yoga 530, kter\u00e9 v\u0161ak op\u011bt nab\u00eddne p\u0159ekl\u00e1p\u011bc\u00ed displej umo\u017e\u0148uj\u00edc\u00ed pracovat v re\u017eimu tabletu. Design se od p\u0159edch\u016fdce Yoga 520 p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 nezm\u011bnil, v\u011bt\u0161ina zm\u011bn se tak odehr\u00e1la pouze uvnit\u0159 notebooku. Maxim\u00e1ln\u00ed konfigurace bude znamenat Core i7 osm\u00e9 generace, 16 GB opera\u010dn\u00ed pam\u011bti a intern\u00ed SSD \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b s kapacitou 512 GB.Displej je typu IPS, s rozli\u0161en\u00edm Full HD a \u00fahlop\u0159\u00ed\u010dkou 14 palc\u016f. P\u0159\u00edjemnou vlastnost\u00ed je aktivn\u00ed dotykov\u00e9 pero p\u0159\u00edmo v balen\u00ed.Yoga 530 se od dra\u017e\u0161\u00ed Yogy 730 odli\u0161uje t\u0159eba absenc\u00ed rozhran\u00ed Thunderbolt 3. M\u00edsto toho zde najdeme pouze USB-C ve variant\u011b USB 3.1 Gen 1. HDMI pro p\u0159ipojen\u00ed monitoru v\u0161ak nechyb\u00ed, podobn\u011b jako \u010dte\u010dka pam\u011b\u0165ov\u00fdch karet nebo 3,5mm audio konektor.Yoga 530 se za\u010dne rovn\u011b\u017e prod\u00e1vat v dubnu za cenu 600 dolar\u016f. V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b tuzemsk\u00e9ho trhu by to mohlo znamenat \u010d\u00e1stku asi 15 000 korun.", "tags": ["Notebooky", "Intel", "Amazon", "Nvidia", "Alexa", "Cortana", "Evropa", "SSD", "Lenovo", "Konvertibiln\u00ed notebook", "Nov\u00fd notebook", "Barcelona", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed rozd\u00edl", "Hlasov\u00fd asistent", "Druh\u00e1 strana", "Notebook", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed pam\u011b\u0165", "Yoga", "Cena za\u010d\u00ednaj\u00edc\u00ed", "Rozli\u0161en\u00ed", "Tuzemsk\u00fd trh", "Echo", "Asistentka", "Samostatn\u00e9 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "P\u0159\u00edjemn\u00e1 vlastnost"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jak-se-da-vyuzit-hololens-v-praxi-aplikace-mr-guide-vytvori-holograficke-pruvodce/sc-3-a-191991/default.aspx", "title": "Jak se d\u00e1 vyu\u017e\u00edt HoloLens v praxi: aplikace MR Guide vytvo\u0159\u00ed holografick\u00e9 pr\u016fvodce", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Rusk\u00e1 firma  ned\u00e1vno vypustila velmi zaj\u00edmav\u00fd n\u00e1stroj pro tvorbu vlastn\u00edch holografick\u00fdch pr\u016fvodc\u016f pro br\u00fdle roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e9 reality HoloLens. Jmenuje se  a dok\u00e1\u017eete v n\u011bm vytvo\u0159it propracovan\u00e9 informativn\u00ed prohl\u00eddky v\u0161eho druhu bez nutnosti programov\u00e1n\u00ed. Vyjde v\u00e1s to na necel\u00fdch 1000 dolar\u016f.MR Guide toti\u017e dovoluje p\u0159en\u00e9st va\u0161e n\u00e1pady do reality p\u0159\u00edmo prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm u\u017eivatelsk\u00e9ho rozhran\u00ed HoloLens, bez nutnosti vyu\u017e\u00edvat n\u011bjak\u00fd dal\u0161\u00ed software. Jedin\u00e9, co pot\u0159ebujete, je prozat\u00edm dost drahou v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159skou edici br\u00fdl\u00ed od Microsoftu, kter\u00e1 sama o sob\u011b stoj\u00ed 3 tis\u00edce dolar\u016f.Nyn\u00ed tak m\u016f\u017eou muzea, v\u00fdstavy, showroomy a cel\u00e1 \u0159ada dal\u0161\u00edch m\u00edst dopl\u0148ovat sv\u00e9 prohl\u00eddky o digit\u00e1ln\u00ed obsah, kter\u00fd si u\u017eivatel\u00e9 sami zp\u0159\u00edstupn\u00ed p\u0159i proch\u00e1zen\u00ed prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm br\u00fdl\u00ed. Jak by to mohlo fungovat v praxi v\u00e1m dob\u0159e zn\u00e1zorn\u00ed video v\u00fd\u0161e.Z\u00e1sadn\u00ed p\u0159ek\u00e1\u017eku rozvoje si ur\u010dit\u011b sami domysl\u00edte \u2013 kdy\u017e u\u017e si bude moci HoloLens dovolit v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159, t\u011b\u017eko se jich koup\u00ed hned cel\u00e1 sada i pro pot\u0159eby n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvn\u00edk\u016f. Investice do v\u00fdvoje a tvorby virtu\u00e1ln\u00edch prohl\u00eddek tedy p\u0159edpokl\u00e1d\u00e1 v\u00edru v to, \u017ee se roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e1 realita \u010dasem stane masov\u011b dostupn\u00fdm standardem.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Software", "Microsoft", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e1 realita", "Investice", "Br\u00fdle", "HoloLens", "Dostupn\u00fd standard", "Z\u00e1sadn\u00ed p\u0159ek\u00e1\u017eka", "Zaj\u00edmav\u00fd n\u00e1stroj", "Cel\u00e1 \u0159ada", "Rusk\u00e1 firma", "Virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed prohl\u00eddka", "Aplikace", "Prohl\u00eddka", "Praxe", "Digit\u00e1ln\u00ed obsah", "U\u017eivatelsk\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed", "Pr\u016fvodce", "Dolar", "Cel\u00e1 sada", "Realita"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/podivejte-se-na-nove-thinkpady-od-lenova-pro-rok-2018/sc-3-a-191946/default.aspx", "title": "Pod\u00edvejte se na nov\u00e9 Thinkpady od Lenova pro rok 2018", "author": "Tom\u00e1\u0161 Hol\u010d\u00edk", "date": "22. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Lenovo na tiskov\u00e9 konferenci p\u0159edstavilo omlazen\u00e9 modelov\u00e9 \u0159ady Thinkpad\u016f pro rok 2018. Z\u00e1sadn\u00ed zm\u011bnou, kterou u\u017e zn\u00e1me z d\u0159\u00edve p\u0159edstaven\u00e9ho modelu E580, je kompletn\u00ed p\u0159echod na USB-C v\u010detn\u011b nap\u00e1jen\u00ed.Nejlevn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed \u0159ada E, trochu lep\u0161\u00ed L, mana\u017eersk\u00e1 T nebo pr\u00e9miov\u00e1 X a X1  nap\u00e1jen\u00ed a dlouh\u00e1 l\u00e9ta pou\u017e\u00edvan\u00fd hranat\u00fd nap\u00e1jec\u00ed konektor zmiz\u00ed. U v\u0161ech model\u016f lze USB-C pou\u017e\u00edt pro v\u00fdstup na monitor, tak\u017ee notebook m\u016f\u017eete p\u0159ipojit k monitoru jedin\u00fdm kabelem a p\u0159es tento kabel notebook i nap\u00e1jet.Vy\u0161\u0161\u00ed \u0159ady T a X1 nav\u00edc dostanou druh\u00fd USB-C konektor s podporou Thunderbolt 3 a s nezvykl\u00fdm roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00edm. Nov\u00fd typ dokovac\u00ed stanice se toti\u017e p\u0159icvakne na bo\u010dn\u00ed konektory v\u010detn\u011b toho nov\u00e9ho netradi\u010dn\u00edho, kter\u00fd krom\u011b USB-C nese bokem i klasick\u00fd Ethernet.Samoz\u0159ejm\u011b m\u016f\u017eete k notebooku p\u0159ipojit b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 dokovac\u00ed stanice pro USB-C a standardn\u00ed USB-C kabel p\u0159ipoj\u00edte p\u0159ipoj\u00edte i do tohoto nov\u00e9ho konektoru. Origin\u00e1ln\u00ed dokovac\u00ed stanice m\u00e1 v\u00fdhodu v pevn\u00e9m uchycen\u00ed notebooku, kdy m\u016f\u017eete notebook pevn\u011b uzamknout, b\u011b\u017en\u00fd USB-C adapt\u00e9r by mohl kdokoli odpojit a s notebookem odej\u00edt.Nov\u00e1 generace Thinkpadu X1 Carbon a p\u0159ekl\u00e1p\u011bc\u00edho Thinkpadu X1 Yoga dostane nov\u011b HDR displej s maxim\u00e1ln\u00edm jasem a\u017e 500 nit\u016f (b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 notebooky se pohybuj\u00ed kolem 300 nit\u016f).Velmi specifick\u00fdm notebookem bude . Dle n\u00e1zvu nepat\u0159\u00ed do rodiny Thinkpad\u016f, ale m\u00e1 s nimi spole\u010dn\u00fd vzhled a nap\u0159\u00edklad zp\u016fsob p\u0159\u00edstupu do \u00fatrob notebooku.Lenovo V330 ale bude extr\u00e9mn\u011b levn\u00fd stroj, prod\u00e1vat se bude za cenu od 11 190 K\u010d, ale pro b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 z\u00e1kazn\u00edky jej moc nedoporu\u010d\u00edme. M\u011bkk\u00e1 konstrukce nebud\u00ed d\u016fv\u011bru, na kterou jsme si u notebook\u016f Lenovo zvykli. Ostatn\u011b chyb\u011bj\u00edc\u00ed ozna\u010den\u00ed Thinkpad nazna\u010duje sn\u00ed\u017eenou odolnost.Sp\u00ed\u0161 bude V330 p\u0159edstavovat nejlevn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed notebook pro firmy, kter\u00e9 v r\u00e1mci IT zvol\u00ed jednotnou platformu Lenova. V330 tak nebude vy\u017eadovat jin\u00fd p\u0159\u00edstup IT odd\u011blen\u00ed ne\u017e tradi\u010dn\u00ed Thinkpady, ale opravdu nejde o n\u011bjak odoln\u00e9 notebooky pro \u010dast\u00e9 p\u0159en\u00e1\u0161en\u00ed.Thinkpady za\u010dnou na \u0159ad\u011b  s 14 a 15,6\" displejem. I kdy\u017e p\u016fjde o z\u00e1kladn\u00ed modely startuj\u00edc\u00ed na cen\u011b 19 590 K\u010d, nep\u016fjde o n\u011bjak\u00e9 nemotorn\u00e9 stroje. Nov\u00e1 generace je o p\u016fl centimetru ten\u010d\u00ed a o 200 gram\u016f leh\u010d\u00ed ne\u017e ta lo\u0148sk\u00e1.Nov\u011b bude v \u0159ad\u011b E existovat tak\u00e9 podsv\u00edcen\u00e1 kl\u00e1vesnice. Samoz\u0159ejm\u011b obsahuje Core osm\u00e9 generace, \u010dte\u010dku otisk\u016f, jedno USB-C pro nab\u00edjen\u00ed i DisplayPort a hlin\u00edkov\u00fd kryt displeje.O kousek v\u00fd\u0161 bude st\u00e1t \u0159ada. Tedy v \u00fahlop\u0159\u00ed\u010dk\u00e1ch 13,3, 14 a 15,6 palc\u016f. P\u016fjde st\u00e1le o levn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed Thinkpady, kde L480 za\u010dne na 24 990 K\u010d, L380 i L380 Yoga za\u010dnou na 27 490 K\u010d.V t\u00e9to cen\u011b dostanete procesory Core i osm\u00e9 generace, IPS displej, USB-C nap\u00e1jen\u00ed a rozumnou v\u00fddr\u017e a odolnost. Oproti E dostanete druh\u00fd USB-C konektor, voliteln\u011b infrakameru pro p\u0159ihla\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed a ve 13,3\" verzi cel\u00fd notebook v\u00e1\u017e\u00ed pod 1,5 kg. P\u0159ekl\u00e1p\u011bc\u00ed varianta Yoga s dotykov\u00fdm displejem se tlou\u0161\u0165kou vejde pod 19 mm a m\u00edrn\u011b p\u0159ekro\u010d\u00ed 1,5 kg.Etalonem t\u0159\u00eddy podnikov\u00fdch notebook\u016f z\u016fst\u00e1v\u00e1 modelov\u00e1 \u0159ada . Ten\u010d\u00ed varianta T480s je je\u0161t\u011b ten\u010d\u00ed a leh\u010d\u00ed ne\u017e p\u0159edchoz\u00ed T470s a nov\u011b m\u016f\u017eete m\u00edt v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed T580 s dotykov\u00fdm WQHD displejem.Standardn\u00ed kameru nad displejem nyn\u00ed m\u016f\u017eete zakr\u00fdt mechanick\u00fdm \u0161oup\u00e1tkem pro v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed pocit bezpe\u010d\u00ed a \u010dte\u010dka otisk\u016f prst\u016f dok\u00e1\u017ee zaznamen\u00e1vat pr\u016fb\u011b\u017en\u00e9 zm\u011bny va\u0161ich otisk\u016f, aby ji z\u00e1\u0161kodn\u00edk neo\u0161\u00e1lil n\u011bjak\u00fdm star\u0161\u00edm d\u0159\u00edve z\u00edskan\u00fdm otiskem.\u0158ada T u\u017e obsahuje dva konektory USB-C s podporou Thunderbolt 3 v\u010detn\u011b nov\u00e9ho bo\u010dn\u00edho konektoru pro dokovac\u00ed stanice. Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed T480 bude startovat na 34 990 K\u010d, zten\u010den\u00fd T480s na 41 490 K\u010d a velk\u00fd T580 na 33 590 K\u010d.Nejleh\u010d\u00ed a nejmen\u0161\u00ed \u0159ada X se tak\u00e9 do\u010dk\u00e1 vylep\u0161en\u00ed.  s p\u0159ekl\u00e1p\u011bc\u00edm displejem s podporou ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed perem dostane infrakameru pro p\u0159ihla\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed do Windows a  s 12\" displejem je 20% leh\u010d\u00ed a o 15% ten\u010d\u00ed ne\u017e p\u0159edchoz\u00ed generace. X280 za\u010dne na 42 290 K\u010d a X380 Yoga na 31 790 K\u010d.Thinkpady  a pak tradi\u010dn\u011b p\u0159edstavuj\u00ed to nejlep\u0161\u00ed (a nejdra\u017e\u0161\u00ed) co dok\u00e1\u017ee Lenovo v \u0159ad\u011b Thinkpad nab\u00eddnout. Oproti ostatn\u00edm model\u016fm se tady u\u017e nezte\u010dovalo a neodleh\u010dovalo, tyto modely jsou opravdu na hranici mo\u017en\u00e9ho.Thinkpad X1 Carbon 6. generace nab\u00eddne infrakameru pro p\u0159ihla\u0161ov\u00e1n\u00ed tv\u00e1\u0159\u00ed, \u010dte\u010dku otisk\u016f prst\u016f, 14\" HDR displej s WQHD rozli\u0161en\u00edm to v\u0161e v hmotnosti 1,13 kg a 16 mm tlou\u0161\u0165ky. P\u0159ekl\u00e1p\u011bc\u00ed X1 Yoga p\u0159id\u00e1 dotykov\u00fd displej ovladateln\u00fd perem v celkov\u00e9 hmotnosti 1,4 kg. X1 Carbon startuje na 50 790 K\u010d, X1 Yoga na 76 790 K\u010d.", "tags": ["Video", "Notebooky", "Windows", "Lenovo", "DisplayPort", "Celkov\u00e1 hmotnost", "Cel\u00fd notebook", "Nap\u00e1jen\u00ed", "Nejlevn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed \u0159ada", "Podsv\u00edcen\u00e1 kl\u00e1vesnice", "\u010cast\u00e9 p\u0159en\u00e1\u0161en\u00ed", "WQHD", "Usb-c nap\u00e1jen\u00ed", "Notebook", "Ethernet", "P\u0159ekl\u00e1p\u011bc\u00edm displej", "Jedin\u00fd kabel", "Z\u00e1sadn\u00ed zm\u011bna", "Bo\u010dn\u00ed konektor", "Modern\u00ed design", "Spole\u010dn\u00fd vzhled", "Nov\u00fd model", "Dlouh\u00fd rok", "Nov\u00e1 generace", "B\u011b\u017en\u00fd z\u00e1kazn\u00edk"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/street-view-smirovacka/sc-3-a-182241/default.aspx", "title": "Srandi\u010dky ze Street View: Pod\u00edvejte se, co zachytily kamery Googlu", "author": "redakce", "date": "10. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Panoramatick\u00e9 kamery Googlu um\u00edst\u011bn\u00e9 na autech, t\u0159\u00edkolk\u00e1ch i speci\u00e1ln\u00edch batoz\u00edch neust\u00e1le sn\u00edmaj\u00ed ulice a zaj\u00edmav\u00e1 m\u00edsta, aby jejich z\u00e1b\u011bry re\u00e1ln\u00e9ho sv\u011bta obohatily mapovou aplikaci.  je bezesporu u\u017eite\u010dn\u00e1, ale tak\u00e9 dok\u00e1\u017ee perfektn\u011b pobavit.  je toti\u017e hledat v t\u011bchto z\u00e1b\u011brech r\u016fzn\u00e9 bizarnosti, zaj\u00edmavosti, vtipn\u00e9 momenty, nebo t\u0159eba jen p\u011bkn\u00e9 holky.Po roce zase jednou odleh\u010d\u00edme od b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch t\u00e9mat a ty nejzaj\u00edmav\u011bj\u0161\u00ed \u00falovky ze Street View si uk\u00e1\u017eeme. Bavte se!Z\u00e1b\u011bry pochopiteln\u011b nehled\u00e1me sami, vych\u00e1zeli jsme z tip\u016f uve\u0159ejn\u011bn\u00fdch na  a . Pod ka\u017ed\u00fdm obr\u00e1zkem m\u00e1te odkaz (link), kter\u00fd vede na p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161n\u00e9 m\u00edsto na Street View a m\u016f\u017eete si tak prohl\u00e9dnout i okol\u00ed.()\n()\n()\n()()\n()()\n()\n()\nMlad\u00e9 sle\u010dn\u011b nez\u00e1vid\u00edme ()\nAutobusov\u00e1 zast\u00e1vka ve Skotsku. Intervaly autobus\u016f tady budou asi hodn\u011b dlouh\u00e9 ()\nTo mohla b\u00fdt velk\u00e1 r\u00e1na ()\nDoprava v hlavn\u00edm m\u011bst\u011b Banglad\u00e9\u0161e na stupni dva... Ano, u\u017e i sem Google se sv\u00fdm Street View pronikl ()\nJak je\u0161t\u011b nemo\u017en\u011bji by se to dalo vz\u00edt? ()\nTohle rozhodn\u011b st\u00e1lo za to zaznamenat hned dvakr\u00e1t. D\u011bkujeme Google ()\nChr\u00e1n\u00ed si sv\u016fj silikonov\u00fd poklad ()\nTesla uvedla nov\u00fd model ()\nSUV s vy\u0161\u0161\u00edm posezem \u0159idi\u010de a v\u00fdkonem jednoho kon\u011b. Takov\u00e9 jezd\u00ed v Ukrajin\u011b ()\nD\u00edky m\u0159\u00ed\u017ei d\u00edtko z okna nevypadlo. Ale te\u010f ho tam je\u0161t\u011b nezapomenout... ()\nKouzlo?! Levituj\u00edc\u00ed kouzeln\u00edci z Prahy by mohli vypr\u00e1v\u011bt... Na tohle se m\u016f\u017eete zajet pod\u00edvat do Belgie ()\nV D\u00e1nsku maj\u00ed podivn\u00fd pozdrav... ()\nSnov\u00e1 pr\u00e1ce: pl\u00e1\u017eov\u00e1 nat\u00edra\u010d! Tedy a\u017e na ty rukavice... ()\nKam n\u00e1m ty vr\u0161ky od plavek uplavaly? ()\nV\u0161ude to funguje stejn\u011b... Braz\u00edlie ()\nKde se tam vzala? Seka\u010dka na tr\u00e1vu uprost\u0159ed k\u0159i\u017eovatky ()\nMo\u017en\u00e1 utekla odtud ()\nKozy horolezkyn\u011b z Kyrgyzst\u00e1nu ()\nHolky maj\u00ed mejdan na pl\u00e1\u017ei ()\nP\u011bkn\u00e1 pl\u00e1\u017e ()\nNa pl\u00e1\u017e\u00edch je toho k vid\u011bn\u00ed v\u00edce zaj\u00edmav\u00e9ho. Google v\u00edc, pro\u010d tam sv\u00e9 vyslance s bat\u016f\u017ekem a kamerou pos\u00edl\u00e1 ()\nKdy\u017e vid\u00edte auto s podivn\u00fdm h\u0159\u00edbkem na st\u0159e\u0161e a n\u00e1lepkami Googlu, dejte si pozor na ruce! Jinak pak m\u016f\u017eete b\u00fdt na map\u011b zv\u011b\u010dn\u011bni t\u0159eba takto... Pro info: kdyby doty\u010dn\u00fd cht\u011bl, m\u016f\u017ee Google po\u017e\u00e1dat o celkov\u00e9 rozmaz\u00e1n\u00ed, nejen obli\u010deje ()\nHey bro, v\u010dera jsme v baletu d\u011blali tohle... ()\nN\u011bkter\u00e9 reklamy stoj\u00ed za po\u0159\u00e1dn\u00e9 prohl\u00e9dnut\u00ed ()\nZam\u011bstnanci Googlu testuj\u00ed nov\u00fd typ cyklistick\u00e9ho airbagu ()\nAsi se ztratil... ()\nT\u0159\u00edruk\u00e1 \u017eena z Braz\u00edlie ()\nNoha na dovolen\u00e9 v \u0158ecku ()\nTento zvl\u00e1\u0161tn\u00ed druh byl zachycen v Belize ()\nJin\u00fd zaj\u00edmav\u00fd druh z Braz\u00edlie, tentokr\u00e1t sami\u010dka i samec. P\u0159edchoz\u00ed \u010dty\u0159i sn\u00edmky jsou samoz\u0159ejm\u011b chyby, vznikaj\u00ed p\u0159i kompletaci sn\u00edmk\u016f z mnoha objektiv\u016f sn\u00edmac\u00ed sf\u00e9rick\u00e9 kamery ()\nBezpe\u010dnost po Ma\u010farsku ()\nAuto s p\u0159\u00edplatkovou v\u00fdbavou pro ko\u010dky ()\nO stra\u0161ideln\u00e9m ostrov\u011b mrtv\u00fdch panenek v Mexiku u\u017e jste mo\u017en\u00e1 n\u011bkdy sly\u0161eli. Te\u010f si ho m\u016f\u017eete i prohl\u00e9dnout, a to s mo\u017enost\u00ed okam\u017eit\u00e9ho vypnut\u00ed monitoru ()\nTady sp\u00ed \u0160\u00edpkov\u00e1 R\u016f\u017eenka ()\nA m\u00e1 to spo\u010d\u00edtan\u00fd ()\nN\u00e1kla\u010f\u00e1k trpasl\u00edk ()\nIndon\u00e9sk\u00fd autobus pro 20 lid\u00ed a jednu \u017e\u00ed\u017ealu Julii ()\n\u0160koln\u00ed verze indon\u00e9sk\u00e9ho autobusu ()\nA je\u0161t\u011b odleh\u010den\u00e1 \u0161koln\u00ed verze s pl\u00e1t\u011bnou st\u0159echou... ()\nDobr\u00fd den, pros\u00edm v\u00e1s, m\u016f\u017eete n\u00e1s vyfotit? Ale hlavn\u011b a\u0165 vypad\u00e1me n\u011bjak p\u0159irozen\u011b ()\nS vyst\u0159elovac\u00edmi de\u0161tn\u00edky je sranda ()\nTureck\u00fd hotel pro opu\u0161t\u011bn\u00e9 psy a ko\u010dky ()\nRusko... ()\nP\u011bkn\u00e1 silnice ()\nHezk\u00e1 pl\u00e1\u017e ()\nKdy\u017e se \u0159ekne \"Je hladovej, jak pes p\u0159ed masnou\". Braz\u00edlie ()\nMlad\u00fd b\u00fdk nerespektuje semafor a vstupuje na p\u0159echod na \u010dervenou. Co\u017e se tedy ani nelze moc divit... ()\nStalo se v Las Vegas. Z\u016fstane v Las Vegas... ()\nJak by si bezesporu r\u00fdpl Jeremy Clarkson - \u0161koda, \u017ee nesho\u0159el ten karavan ()\nOsel posp\u00edch\u00e1 do pr\u00e1ce... V Senegalu ()\nTihle dva si rad\u011bji po\u010dkaj\u00ed na autobus ()\nAutobus d\u011bl\u00e1 kliky. D\u00edlo \u010desk\u00e9ho um\u011blce Davida \u010cern\u00e9ho pro lond\u00fdnskou Olympi\u00e1du dnes stoj\u00ed v Praze ()\nTref\u00ed se? ()\nDobr\u00fd den! ()\nKdo po kom bude ukl\u00edzet? ()\nN\u00e1dhern\u00e9 v\u00fdhledy na pl\u00e1\u017ei ()\nTyhle tretry se na kolo moc nehod\u00ed ()\nM\u00e1te to za t\u0159i body, palec nahoru! ()", "tags": ["Mapy Google", "Google", "Street View", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Mapy", "Rusko", "Mars", "M\u00f3da", "Mexiko", "Dobr\u00fd den", "Sony Vegas Pro", ".com", "Ko\u010dka", "Nov\u00e1 m\u00f3da", "Nov\u00fd model", "BDS", "Amsterdam", "Hasi\u010di", "Belgie", "Link", "Perth", "Podivnost", "Reklamn\u00ed agentura", "Bizarnost"]}
