{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/necekane-prekvapeni-microsoft-znovu-zacal-prodavat-telefony-lumia/sc-3-a-191999/default.aspx", "title": "Ne\u010dekan\u00e9 p\u0159ekvapen\u00ed: Microsoft znovu za\u010dal prod\u00e1vat telefony Lumia", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Minul\u00fd rok to Microsoft s nab\u00eddkou vlastn\u00edch mobiln\u00edch telefon\u016f vzdal a odp\u00edskal i samotn\u00fd v\u00fdvoj ryze mobiln\u00edho opera\u010dn\u00edho syst\u00e9mu Windows. Telefony Lumia se postupn\u011b vytratily z nab\u00eddky a doposud se u\u017e jen doprod\u00e1valy skladov\u00e9 z\u00e1soby prodejc\u016f. Je te\u010f proto obrovsk\u00fdm p\u0159ekvapen\u00edm, \u017ee se do ofici\u00e1ln\u00edho online obchodu Microsoftu telefony Lumia vr\u00e1tily.Telefony Microsoft ofici\u00e1ln\u011b nab\u00edz\u00ed ve sv\u00e9m  (v \u010cesku je n\u00e1kup hardwaru nedostupn\u00fd). Telefony jsou bez \u00favazku a neblokovan\u00e9. Nad\u0161en\u00ed fanou\u0161k\u016f rychle zkrot\u00ed fakt, \u017ee se nejedn\u00e1 o \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 novinky, ale posledn\u00ed uveden\u00e9 modely, kter\u00fdm t\u00e1hne u\u017e na t\u0159et\u00ed rok od uveden\u00ed. A ceny se p\u0159itom kupodivu dr\u017e\u00ed st\u00e1le docela vysoko.Konkr\u00e9tn\u011b se do nab\u00eddky op\u011bt dostaly tyto modely (ceny po p\u0159epo\u010dtu jsou pro lep\u0161\u00ed p\u0159edstavu dopln\u011bny i o \u010deskou DPH):Na nab\u00eddku upozornil web , ihned si v\u0161\u00edmalo nap\u0159\u00edklad i  a v\u0161ichni se ptaj\u00ed \u2013 pro\u010d? Microsoft zat\u00edm ofici\u00e1ln\u011b neodpov\u011bd\u011bl. Ale nejlogi\u010dt\u011bj\u0161\u00ed vysv\u011btlen\u00ed asi trochu zklame fanou\u0161ky mobiln\u00edch Windows, kte\u0159\u00ed u\u017e se za\u010dali t\u011b\u0161it na reinkarnaci syst\u00e9mu a p\u0159\u00edchod b\u00e1jn\u00e9ho Surface Phonu.Jeden z d\u016fvod\u016f vypl\u00fdv\u00e1 ze situace tak n\u011bjak s\u00e1m \u2013 Microsoft m\u00e1 zjevn\u011b je\u0161t\u011b dost star\u00fdch telefon\u016f ve skladech a je lep\u0161\u00ed je prodat ne\u017e likvidovat. A by\u0165 mobiln\u00ed Windows pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 jen velmi m\u00e1lo lid\u00ed, st\u00e1le je to v sou\u010dtu necel\u00e9ho p\u016fl milionu (viz ) a dost z nich je z firemn\u00edch sf\u00e9ry. Leckde v\u011b\u0159ili mobiln\u00edm Windows natolik, \u017ee pro n\u011b p\u0159ipravili i vlastn\u00ed aplikace a ocen\u00ed, kdy\u017e platforma bude je\u0161t\u011b n\u011bjak\u00fd \u010das fungovat a budou pro ni dostupn\u00e9 telefony.Impulsem pro obnoven\u00ed nab\u00eddky pak m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt i skute\u010dnost, \u017ee Microsoft p\u0159ed dv\u011bma t\u00fddny ozn\u00e1mil ukon\u010den\u00ed podpory star\u0161\u00edch syst\u00e9m\u016f Windows Phone (7.5/8), a to a\u017e natolik, \u017ee na t\u011bchto syst\u00e9mech p\u0159estanou fungovat notifikace. T\u00edm se telefony stanou v b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 praxi nepou\u017eiteln\u00e9. Kdo chce (nebo mus\u00ed) z\u016fstat na platform\u011b, u\u017e nem\u011bl z \u010deho vyb\u00edrat, proto\u017ee v\u00fdrobci t\u0159et\u00edch stran u\u017e Windows Mobile zcela poh\u0159bili a v nab\u00eddce z\u016fstaly jen v\u00fdprodejov\u00fd HP Elite X3 nebo Alcatel Idol 4S. Microsoft tedy nab\u00eddl alternativu.Z cen p\u0159\u00edstroj\u016f je patrn\u00e9, \u017ee zas tolik jich na sklad\u011b nem\u00e1. Za tyto ceny si je koup\u00ed opravdu jen ten, kdo je chce \u010di pot\u0159ebuje kv\u016fli syst\u00e9mu. Jinou mo\u017enost u\u017e aktu\u00e1ln\u011b nem\u00e1. Ale p\u0159ece jen t\u00edm Microsoft d\u00e1v\u00e1 najevo, \u017ee mobiln\u00ed Windows je\u0161t\u011b tak \u00fapln\u011b neodstavil. Podpora syst\u00e9mu samoz\u0159ejm\u011b je\u0161t\u011b trv\u00e1, by\u0165 u\u017e pro n\u011bj nevych\u00e1z\u00ed aktualizace s nov\u00fdmi funkcemi. Ka\u017edop\u00e1dn\u011b po\u0159\u00e1d zcela nevyhasla nad\u011bje, \u017ee to Microsoft s vlastn\u00edm telefonem je\u0161t\u011b jednou zkus\u00ed.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "Windows Phone", "Lumia", "IDC", "Skladov\u00e1 z\u00e1soba", "Gizmodo", "Telefon", "Windows Mobile", "Surface Phone", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e1 praxe", "Nov\u00e1 funkce", "Ne\u010dekan\u00e9 p\u0159ekvapen\u00ed", "T\u0159et\u00ed rok", "P\u0159ekvapen\u00ed", "Obrovsk\u00e9 p\u0159ekvapen\u00ed", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Star\u00fd telefon", "Firemn\u00ed sf\u00e9ra", "T\u0159et\u00ed strana", "DPH", "Platforma", "Sklad"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/silenym-adapterem-lze-z-10-karet-microsd-vytvorit-ssd-rychlost-vas-ale-prekvapi/sc-3-a-191948/default.aspx", "title": "\u0160\u00edlen\u00fdm adapt\u00e9rem lze z 10 karet microSD vytvo\u0159it SSD. Rychlost v\u00e1s ale p\u0159ekvap\u00ed", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "22. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Popul\u00e1rn\u00ed kan\u00e1l Linus Tech Tips se pokusil otestovat speci\u00e1ln\u00ed adapt\u00e9r pro 10 microSD karet, pomoc\u00ed kter\u00e9ho lze vytvo\u0159it plnohodnotn\u00e9 SSD s klasick\u00fdm p\u0159ipojen\u00edm pomoc\u00ed rozhran\u00ed SATA. Jak je na tom v\u00fdkon v porovn\u00e1n\u00ed s b\u011b\u017en\u00fdm SSD? je ur\u010den p\u0159\u00edmo pro nahrazen\u00ed 2,5palcov\u00e9ho disku pomoc\u00ed microSD karet, proto\u017ee deska obsahuje integrovan\u00fd \u0159adi\u010d, kter\u00fd kombinuje kapacity jako u klasick\u00e9ho RAID 0. D\u00edky tomu, \u017ee m\u00e1 i b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed SATA, lze ho pou\u017e\u00edt jako bootovac\u00ed disk.Zapojen\u00ed je ale limitov\u00e1no na po\u010det microSD karet, tak\u017ee m\u016f\u017eete m\u00edt pouze 1, 2, 4, 8 nebo 10 zapojen\u00fdch aktivn\u00edch microSD karet, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e t\u0159\u00edda UHS-1 nen\u00ed podporov\u00e1na. V\u00fdkon je dle o\u010dek\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed tragick\u00fd. Pam\u011b\u0165ov\u00e9 karty jsou toti\u017e obecn\u011b v\u00fdrazn\u011b pomalej\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e integrovan\u00e9 NAND flash \u010dipy v SSD a maj\u00ed i ni\u017e\u0161\u00ed v\u00fddr\u017e.V\u00fdznamnou roli hraje tak\u00e9 \u0159adi\u010d, kter\u00fd je ve v\u011bt\u0161in\u011b dne\u0161n\u00edch SSD u\u017e velmi pokro\u010dil\u00fd, dok\u00e1\u017ee efektivn\u011b \u0159e\u0161it postupn\u00e9 po\u0161kozov\u00e1n\u00ed bun\u011bk v jednotliv\u00fdch \u010dipech, chyt\u0159e vyu\u017e\u00edvat cache t\u0159eba i s dodate\u010dnou rychlou pam\u011bt\u00ed DRAM a podobn\u011b, aby bylo dosa\u017eeno co nejvy\u0161\u0161\u00edch rychlost\u00ed p\u0159i b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch i n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00fdch podm\u00ednk\u00e1ch.I p\u0159i osazen\u00ed deseti rychl\u00fdch microSD karet Kingston do tohoto adapt\u00e9ru (sekven\u010dn\u00ed \u010dten\u00ed jedn\u00e9 karty bylo a\u017e 100 MB/s), bylo sekven\u010dn\u00ed \u010dten\u00ed maxim\u00e1ln\u011b 220 MB/s a sekven\u010dn\u00ed z\u00e1pis jen 134 MB/s. Naprost\u00fdm pr\u016f\u0161vihem bylo ale n\u00e1hodn\u00e9 \u010dten\u00ed a z\u00e1pis, kter\u00e9 bylo v oblasti 5 MB/s, respektive 0,5 MB/s u z\u00e1pisu. V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b tohoto adapt\u00e9ru nav\u00edc ztrat\u00edte kompletn\u011b v\u0161echna data, jakmile dojde k po\u0161kozen\u00ed by\u0165 jen jedn\u00e9 microSD karty.Jedn\u00e1 se tak o typick\u00fd \u201ezbyte\u010dn\u00fd\u201c produkt, kter\u00fd jen t\u011b\u017eko najde re\u00e1ln\u00e9 uplatn\u011bn\u00ed.", "tags": ["SSD", "\u00dalo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b", "Kingston", "Sekven\u010dn\u00ed \u010dten\u00ed", "B\u011b\u017en\u00e9 rozhran\u00ed", "Integrovan\u00fd \u0159adi\u010d", "Re\u00e1ln\u00e9 uplatn\u011bn\u00ed", "Postupn\u00e9 po\u0161kozov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Flash \u010dip", "N\u00e1hodn\u00e9 \u010dten\u00ed", "MicroSD karta", "Sata", "Bootovac\u00ed disk", "Nejvy\u0161\u0161\u00ed rychlost", "Adapt\u00e9r", "Klasick\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed", "Linus tech Tips", "Sekven\u010dn\u00ed z\u00e1pis", "Z\u00e1pis", "Raid", "Rychlost", "Speci\u00e1ln\u00ed adapt\u00e9r", "N\u00edzk\u00e1 v\u00fddr\u017e", "UHS", "Pam\u011b\u0165ov\u00e1 karta"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/hokej-online-jak-sledovat-na-internetu/sc-3-a-187489/default.aspx", "title": "Hokej online: jak sledovat olympijsk\u00e9 z\u00e1pasy na internetu", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "hokejov\u00fd z\u00e1pas \u010cesko - Rusko m\u016f\u017eete sledovat na speci\u00e1ln\u00edm olmypijsk\u00e9m .Pr\u00e1v\u011b prob\u00edhaj\u00ed zimn\u00ed olympijsk\u00e9 hry v jihokorejsk\u00e9m Pchjong\u010dchangu a mezi nejsledovan\u011bj\u0161\u00ed sporty pat\u0159\u00ed pochopiteln\u011b hokej. Kde a jak m\u016f\u017eete sledovat z\u00e1pasy na internetu?Jedin\u00fdm dr\u017eitelem pr\u00e1v pro vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed v Evrop\u011b je pro n\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00ed dv\u011b olympi\u00e1dy , kter\u00e9 je vlastn\u00edkem Eurosportu. Dal\u0161\u00ed n\u00e1rodn\u00ed stanice, v\u010detn\u011b \u010cesk\u00e9 televize, musely odkoupit omezen\u00e9 sublicence. A ty jsou nejen n\u00e1kladn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed, ale p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm maj\u00ed ve srovn\u00e1n\u00ed s p\u0159edchoz\u00edmi roky regulovanou celkovou stop\u00e1\u017e.\u010cT tak dr\u017e\u00ed pr\u00e1va pro vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed jednoho televizn\u00edho kan\u00e1lu a streamov\u00e1n\u00ed toto\u017en\u00e9ho obsahu na webu. U\u017e v\u0161ak nebude mo\u017en\u00e9 na str\u00e1nk\u00e1ch \u010cT sledovat \u0161est kan\u00e1l\u016f jako v So\u010di 2014, na nich\u017e b\u011b\u017eely prakticky v\u0161echny sporty. Z\u00e1rove\u0148 budou zimn\u00ed discipl\u00edny vys\u00edl\u00e1ny pouze na \u010cT Sport, dvojky se OH nedotknou. Znamen\u00e1 to tedy, \u017ee i na internetu najdete pouze to, co bude naps\u00e1no v televizn\u00edm programu \u010cesk\u00e9 televize. Po\u010det odvys\u00edlan\u00fdch hodin se tak radik\u00e1ln\u011b sn\u00ed\u017e\u00ed.Pr\u00e1va pro vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed v Evrop\u011b m\u00e1 prim\u00e1rn\u011b Eurosport spadaj\u00edc\u00ed pod Discovery. Ten tedy letos nahrad\u00ed hlavn\u00ed vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed na webu, kter\u00e9 zaji\u0161\u0165ovala od roku 2008 \u010cesk\u00e1 televize. K dispozici budou v\u0161echny sporty, v\u011bt\u0161ina z nich s \u010desk\u00fdm koment\u00e1\u0159em. Samoz\u0159ejm\u011b ale s jedn\u00edm z\u00e1sadn\u00edm rozd\u00edlem \u2013 p\u016fjde o placenou slu\u017ebu.Z\u00e1jemci si tak budou muset p\u0159edplatit , kter\u00fd vyjde m\u011bs\u00ed\u010dn\u011b na 7 eur (asi 180 korun). Za tuhle \u010d\u00e1stku dostanou kompletn\u00ed vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed z OH na webu a tak\u00e9 v r\u00e1mci aplikac\u00ed pro smartphony \u010di p\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010de jako je Apple TV.Jako bonus potom Eurosport nab\u00eddne i p\u0159enosy ve virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed realit\u011b. Pot\u0159eba budou br\u00fdle GearVR od Samsungu, n\u011bkter\u00fd z model\u016f Mixed Reality pro Windows 10, p\u0159\u00edpadn\u011b jednoduch\u00e9 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed postaven\u00e9 na Cardboardu.Po instalaci aplikace  dostanete mo\u017enost sledovat asi t\u0159i des\u00edtky sportovn\u00edch ud\u00e1lost\u00ed. Chyb\u011bt nebude \u00favodn\u00ed ceremoni\u00e1l, alpsk\u00e9 ly\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed, snowbaordov\u00fd freestyle, skeleton, skoky na ly\u017e\u00edch nebo hokejov\u00e9 fin\u00e1le. K dispozici budou \u017eiv\u00e9 p\u0159enosy v podob\u011b 180stup\u0148ov\u00e9ho videa. Nejd\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed okam\u017eiky potom bude Eurosport nab\u00edzet i jako 360stup\u0148ov\u00e9 video.Krom\u011b  olympi\u00e1dy v Ji\u017en\u00ed Koreji samoz\u0159ejm\u011b budou p\u0159in\u00e1\u0161et \u010derstv\u00e9 informace i b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 zpravodajsk\u00e9 weby. Sv\u016fj speci\u00e1l tak u\u017e m\u00e1 p\u0159ipraven\u00fd t\u0159eba . Tady najdete podrobn\u00fd program s mo\u017enost\u00ed filtrovat \u010deskou \u00fa\u010dast. A mo\u017en\u00e1 nejd\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed jsou potom \u010dasy jednotliv\u00fdch ud\u00e1lost\u00ed v na\u0161em \u010dasov\u00e9m p\u00e1smu. V Pchjong\u010dchangu je toti\u017e o osm hodin v\u00edce.Video ze sout\u011b\u017e\u00ed potom bude dostupn\u00e9 rovn\u011b\u017e na ofici\u00e1ln\u00edm . P\u0159\u00edm\u00e9 p\u0159enosy zde \u010dekat nem\u016f\u017eeme, nicm\u00e9n\u011b nejzaj\u00edmav\u011bj\u0161\u00ed okam\u017eiky z jednotliv\u00fdch ud\u00e1lost\u00ed zde budou zve\u0159ej\u0148ov\u00e1ny.Naopak kompletn\u00ed p\u0159enosy bude mo\u017en\u00e9 sledovat na adrese , nicm\u00e9n\u011b pouze v textov\u00e9 podob\u011b.Krom\u011b webov\u00e9ho prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de nebo televize lze sledovat ZOH i v telefonu \u010di tabletu. Vedle ji\u017e zm\u00edn\u011bn\u00e9ho p\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010de od Eurosportu nab\u00edz\u00ed \u010cesk\u00fd olympijsk\u00fd v\u00fdbor vlastn\u00ed povedenou aplikaci.Ta je dostupn\u00e1 jak pro  tak pro . V n\u00ed je dostupn\u00e9 jak zpravodajstv\u00ed t\u00fdkaj\u00edc\u00ed se \u010desk\u00e9ho t\u00fdmu, tak program nebo podrobnosti o olympijsk\u00fdch parc\u00edch v Brn\u011b a Ostrav\u011b.", "tags": ["\u010cT Sport", "Web", "Facebook", "Windows", "YouTube", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Eurosport", "Sport", "Instagram", "Twitter", "Olympijsk\u00e9 hry", "Android", "Virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed realita", "Ji\u017en\u00ed Korea", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "Evropa", "iOS", "VPN", "Tipy", "Samsung", "Brno", "Rusko", "Apple TV", "Textov\u00e1 podoba", "\u017div\u00e9 vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/mozilla-common-voice-pro-rozpoznavani-reci-bude-dostupny-i-v-cesku-zapojte-se-do-sberu-potrebnych-dat/sc-3-a-192005/default.aspx", "title": "Mozilla Common Voice pro rozpozn\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed \u0159e\u010di bude dostupn\u00fd i v \u010cesku. Zapojte se do sb\u011bru pot\u0159ebn\u00fdch dat", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "V l\u00e9t\u011b minul\u00e9ho roku spustila Mozilla sb\u011br dat pro , open-source projekt s c\u00edlem vybudovat otev\u0159enou platformu pro rozpozn\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed \u0159e\u010di. Prim\u00e1rn\u011b jej zprovoznila v angli\u010dtin\u011b s p\u0159\u00edslibem postupn\u00e9ho p\u0159ib\u00fdv\u00e1n\u00ed dal\u0161\u00edch jazyk\u016f. Nyn\u00ed se d\u00edky tuzemsk\u00e9 komunit\u011b dostalo i na \u010de\u0161tinu a na webu  se kdokoliv m\u016f\u017ee zapojit do prvn\u00ed f\u00e1ze projektu \u2013 sb\u011bru dostate\u010dn\u00e9ho mno\u017estv\u00ed v\u011bt pro pozd\u011bj\u0161\u00ed p\u0159evod.Common Voice funguje na jednoduch\u00e9m principu, kdy u\u017eivatel\u00e9 p\u0159ed\u010d\u00edtaj\u00ed vzorov\u00e9 v\u011bty. \u010c\u00edm v\u00edc vzork\u016f, t\u00edm spolehliv\u011bj\u0161\u00ed bude n\u00e1sledn\u00fd p\u0159evod na text. Pro \u010deskou verzi je v\u0161ak t\u0159eba nejprve sesb\u00edrat alespo\u0148 dva tis\u00edce zm\u00edn\u011bn\u00fdch vzorov\u00fdch v\u011bt. Ty mohou u\u017eivatel\u00e9 odes\u00edlat prim\u00e1rn\u011b ze zdroj\u016f publikovan\u00fdch pod svobodnou licenc\u00ed CC0. T\u011bmi mohou b\u00fdt t\u0159eba knihy, na kter\u00e1 se ji\u017e nevztahuj\u00ed autorsk\u00e1 pr\u00e1va. V r\u00e1mci n\u00e1stroje pro Cherry picking jsou potom vybr\u00e1ny v\u011bty vhodn\u00e9 pro Common Voice.A\u017e dojde k sesb\u00edr\u00e1n\u00ed dostate\u010dn\u00e9ho mno\u017estv\u00ed t\u011bchto v\u011bt, bude spu\u0161t\u011bna druh\u00e1 f\u00e1ze projektu \u2013 sb\u011br nahr\u00e1vek, kde budou u\u017eivatel\u00e9 ony v\u011bty p\u0159ed\u010d\u00edtat.", "tags": ["Open source", "Mozilla", "Autorsk\u00e9 pr\u00e1vo", "V\u011bta", "Pot\u0159ebn\u00e9 data", "N\u00e1sledn\u00fd p\u0159evod", "Voln\u00e9 d\u00edlo", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Prvn\u00ed f\u00e1ze", "Sb\u011br", "Dostate\u010dn\u00e9 mno\u017estv\u00ed", "Otev\u0159en\u00e1 platforma", "Rozpozn\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed", "F\u00e1ze projektu", "Minul\u00fd rok", "Druh\u00e1 f\u00e1ze", "Jednoduch\u00fd princip", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Data", "\u010cesk\u00e1 verze", "Svobodn\u00e1 licence", "Tuzemsk\u00e1 komunita"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/ne-elon-musk-lidem-neposila-ethereum-je-to-podvod/sc-3-a-191952/default.aspx", "title": "Ne, Elon Musk lidem nepos\u00edl\u00e1 ethereum. Je to podvod", "author": "Mark\u00e9ta Mike\u0161ov\u00e1", "date": "22. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Podvodn\u00edci si zase na\u0161li zp\u016fsob, jak z d\u016fv\u011b\u0159iv\u00fdch lid\u00ed vyt\u00e1hnout pen\u00edze. Tentokr\u00e1t k tomu pou\u017eili osobu vizion\u00e1\u0159e , pod jeho\u017e jm\u00e9nem zalo\u017eili fale\u0161n\u00fd \u00fa\u010det na Twitteru a sl\u00edbili, \u017ee lidem rozdaj\u00ed  v hodnot\u011b 4 milion\u016f dolar\u016f. Sta\u010d\u00ed jen, kdy\u017e mu lid\u00e9 po\u0161lou n\u011bjak\u00fd mal\u00fd obnos, aby z\u00edskal adresu jejich pen\u011b\u017eenky. Samoz\u0159ejm\u011b je to nesmysl.Skute\u010dn\u00fd Elon Musk ve st\u0159edu na Twitteru informoval o . P\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek byl relativn\u011b nad\u0161en\u00fd. N\u011bjak\u00e9ho podvodn\u00edka tak napadlo, \u017ee toho vyu\u017eije a zalo\u017eil t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 toto\u017en\u00fd \u00fa\u010det @elonhmusk, ve kter\u00e9m na p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek nav\u00e1zal jednoduch\u00fdm sd\u011blen\u00edm - k p\u0159\u00edle\u017eitosti \u00fasp\u011bchu rozd\u00e1 lidem 5000 kus\u016f etherea. Pokud kryptom\u011bnu lid\u00e9 cht\u011bj\u00ed z\u00edskat, maj\u00ed poslat n\u011bjak\u00fd mal\u00fd obnos, aby Musk z\u00edskal adresu jejich pen\u011b\u017eenky.\u00da\u010det je u\u017e z Twitteru odstran\u011bn\u00fd, zpr\u00e1va vypadala takto:Zn\u00ed to jako jasn\u00fd podvod a podvod to tak\u00e9 je. U\u017e samotn\u00fd princip ned\u00e1v\u00e1 smysl, adresu pen\u011b\u017eenky sta\u010d\u00ed sd\u011blit, nen\u00ed pot\u0159eba z n\u00ed n\u011bco pos\u00edlat. Nicm\u00e9n\u011b mnoho lid\u00ed se nachytalo a podle sledov\u00e1n\u00ed v blockchainu je mo\u017en\u00e9 zjistit, \u017ee podvodn\u00edkovi u\u017e lid\u00e9 poslali ethereum v hodnot\u011b v\u00edce ne\u017e 16 tis\u00edc dolar\u016f.\u00da\u010det lze p\u0159itom velice jednodu\u0161e odhalit. Nen\u00ed verifikovan\u00fd a m\u00e1 jinou adresu. Hlavn\u011b je t\u0159eba \u0159\u00edct, \u017ee i kdy\u017e je Elon Musk zn\u00e1m jako \u0161\u00edlenec, ur\u010dit\u011b by jen tak lidem neposlal skoro 4,3 miliony dolar\u016f. A ur\u010dit\u011b by necht\u011bl, aby mu lid\u00e9 n\u011bco pos\u00edlali.Nen\u00ed to letos poprv\u00e9, co se n\u011bco podobn\u00e9ho stalo. Twitter u\u017e musel zru\u0161it \u00fa\u010dty @elonmus_ a @elonnmuusk, kter\u00e9 se pokou\u0161ely o n\u011bco podobn\u00e9ho.", "tags": ["Kryptom\u011bny", "Ethereum", "Elon Musk", "Twitter", "Podvod", "Pl\u00e1novan\u00fd start", "Tesla", "Starlink", "Dolar", "Mal\u00fd obnos", "Podvodn\u00edk", "\u00da\u010det", "Adresa", "Pen\u011b\u017eenka", "Obnos", "Fale\u0161n\u00fd \u00fa\u010det"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/spacex-ve-stredu-vynese-prvni-dva-satelity-obri-internetove-site-ve-finale-jich-bude-12-tisic/sc-3-a-191890/default.aspx", "title": "Takhle odstartovala dal\u0161\u00ed raketa SpaceX. Vynesla na orbit prvn\u00ed dva satelity ob\u0159\u00ed internetov\u00e9 s\u00edt\u011b Starlink", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "22. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Pl\u00e1novan\u00fd st\u0159ede\u010dn\u00ed start byl kv\u016fli velk\u00e9 s\u00edle v\u011btru odlo\u017een na dne\u0161ek, a to na na\u0161eho \u010dasu. Start rakety Falcon 9, kter\u00e1 mimo jin\u00e9 nesla i dva satelity pro novou satelitn\u00ed internetovou s\u00ed\u0165 Starlink, jste mohli sledovat online. Nyn\u00ed se pod\u00edvejte alespo\u0148 na z\u00e1znam:Prvn\u00ed stupe\u0148 tentokr\u00e1t nep\u0159ist\u00e1val, nov\u011b se ale SpaceX pokus\u00ed zachr\u00e1nit aerodynamick\u00e9 kryty rakety, p\u00ed\u0161e to s\u00e1m Elon Musk na sv\u00e9m Instagramu: Elon Musk  prozradil, \u017ee aerodynamick\u00fd kryt minul z\u00e1chytnou s\u00ed\u0165 o p\u00e1r stovek metr\u016f. Nicm\u00e9n\u011b dopadl neporu\u0161en\u00fd do mo\u0159e. V galerii u\u017e najdete i obr\u00e1zek krytu, jak plave na hladin\u011b oce\u00e1nu. Ve st\u0159edu 21. \u00fanora odstartuje raketa Falcon 9, kter\u00e1 prim\u00e1rn\u011b vynese na ob\u011b\u017enou dr\u00e1hu satelit \u0160pan\u011blsk\u00e9ho ministerstva obrany. Z\u00e1rove\u0148 ale ponese je\u0161t\u011b  \u2013 dva mikrosatelity SpaceX Microsat-2a a Microsat-2b. Ty se stanou prvn\u00edmi d\u00edlky ob\u0159\u00ed skl\u00e1da\u010dky s n\u00e1zvem . Ta se v n\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00edch letech rozroste na , kter\u00e9 budou nab\u00edzet internetov\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed kdekoliv na sv\u011bt\u011b.Cel\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165 se bude skl\u00e1dat ze dvou vrstev satelit\u016f, komunikuj\u00edc\u00edch na rozd\u00edln\u00fdch frekvenc\u00edch. V\u00fd\u0161 se bude pohybovat 4 425 um\u011bl\u00fdch dru\u017eic, kter\u00e9 se us\u00eddl\u00ed 1 126 km nad zemsk\u00fdm povrchem. Ni\u017e\u0161\u00ed vrstvu potom bude tvo\u0159it 7 518 satelit\u016f ve v\u00fd\u0161ce asi 320 km. Tato ob\u0159\u00ed soustava t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 12 tis\u00edc satelit\u016f se bude synchronizovan\u011b pohybovat po ob\u011b\u017en\u00fdch drah\u00e1ch, nep\u016fjde tedy o geostacion\u00e1rn\u00ed dru\u017eice, kter\u00e9 by v\u016f\u010di Zemi setrv\u00e1valy na jednom m\u00edst\u011b.C\u00edlem je p\u0159in\u00e9st internet i do zem\u00ed, kde je slo\u017eit\u00e9 \u010di nemo\u017en\u00e9 vybudovat standardn\u00ed internetovou s\u00ed\u0165. Samoz\u0159ejm\u011b jde rovn\u011b\u017e o velk\u00fd byznys, nebo\u0165 do t\u011bchto oblast\u00ed spadaj\u00ed t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 4 miliardy lid\u00ed. Podle dokument\u016f  o\u010dek\u00e1v\u00e1 SpaceX v\u00edc ne\u017e 40 milion\u016f z\u00e1kazn\u00edk\u016f vyu\u017e\u00edvaj\u00edc\u00ed Starlink pro p\u0159ipojen\u00ed k internetu v roce 2025.B\u011bhem sedmi let by se tak m\u011bla na ob\u011b\u017enou dr\u00e1hu velk\u00e1 \u010d\u00e1st z pl\u00e1novan\u00fdch mikrosatelit\u016f. Krom\u011b toho by v budoucnu satelitn\u00ed internetov\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed Starlink m\u011bly vyu\u017e\u00edvat i v\u0161echny vozy Tesla a budou tak p\u0159ipojeny k internetu kdekoli na sv\u011bt\u011b.Start rakety Falcon 9 bude mo\u017en\u00e9 ve st\u0159edu sledovat na . P\u016fjde o ji\u017e jednou pou\u017eit\u00fd stupe\u0148, kter\u00fd n\u00e1klad na ob\u011b\u017enou dr\u00e1hu vyn\u00e1\u0161el v srpnu 2017. Tentokr\u00e1t se v\u0161ak nedo\u010dk\u00e1me z\u00e1b\u011br\u016f na booster p\u0159ist\u00e1vaj\u00edc\u00ed na pontonech, zam\u00ed\u0159\u00ed toti\u017e rovnou do mo\u0159e.\n", "tags": ["YouTube", "Internet", "Elon Musk", "SpaceX", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "Zem\u011b", "P\u0159ipojen\u00ed k internetu", "Satelit", "Raketa", "Falcon", "\u010cesk\u00fd koment\u00e1\u0159", "Prvn\u00ed satelit", "Velk\u00fd byznys", "S\u00ed\u0165", "Internetov\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed", "Pou\u017eit\u00fd stupe\u0148", "Geostacion\u00e1rn\u00ed dru\u017eice", "Ministerstvo obrany", "Velk\u00e1 s\u00edla", "Ob\u0159\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165", "Potenci\u00e1ln\u00ed z\u00e1kazn\u00edk", "Tesla", "Rozvojov\u00e1 zem\u011b", "Zemsk\u00fd povrch", "Starlink"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/vyvojari-vylezla-z-televizoru-mrtvola-a-honila-ho-po-byte-diky-rozsirene-realite-od-applu/sc-3-a-191967/default.aspx", "title": "V\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159i vylezla z televizoru mrtvola a honila ho po byt\u011b. D\u00edky roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e9 realit\u011b od Applu", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Abhishek Sing se na Twitteru pochlubil dal\u0161\u00edm mo\u017en\u00fdm rozm\u011brem vyu\u017eit\u00ed mobiln\u00ed roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e9 reality. Tu aktu\u00e1ln\u011b vyv\u00edjej\u00ed p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm Apple (ARKit) a Google (ARCore). Nam\u00edsto infantiln\u00edch hern\u00edch demouk\u00e1zek nicm\u00e9n\u011b Singh p\u0159evedl do roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e9 reality jednu z nejepi\u010dt\u011bj\u0161\u00edch hororov\u00fdch sc\u00e9n tohoto stolet\u00ed \u2013 \u010dernovlasou d\u00edvku Samaru, kter\u00e1 vyleze ze studny a skrze obrazovku a\u017e k ob\u011bti.Ano, m\u00e1m samoz\u0159ejm\u011b na mysli americk\u00fd remake The Ring z roku 2002. Singhovo demo p\u0159eveden\u00e9 do  vypad\u00e1 na (sic) rozt\u0159esen\u00e9m mobiln\u00edm videu (to\u010deno iPadem) skv\u011ble a ukazuje zaj\u00edmavou mo\u017enost vyu\u017eit\u00ed pro filmov\u00fd a marketingov\u00fd pr\u016fmysl.P\u0159edstavte si, \u017ee byste si t\u00edmto zp\u016fsobem mohli p\u0159ehr\u00e1t jako bonus n\u011bkter\u00e9 dal\u0161\u00ed slavn\u00e9 kinematografick\u00e9 sc\u00e9ny Titanikem po\u010d\u00ednaje a t\u0159eba\u2026 Klasick\u00fdm Psychem kon\u010de.", "tags": ["Google", "Apple", "Mobility", "Twitter", "Tablety", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e1 realita", "iPad", "Zaj\u00edmav\u00e1 mo\u017enost", "The Ring", "Samara", "Filmov\u00fd pr\u016fmysl", "Realita", "Mrtvola", "Singh", "V\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159", "Televizor", "Byt"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/apple-v-sobotu-otevre-ve-vidni-svuj-obchod-raj-pro-fandy-applu-kousek-za-hranicemi-ceska/sc-3-a-191956/default.aspx", "title": "Apple v sobotu otev\u0159e ve V\u00eddni sv\u016fj obchod. R\u00e1j pro fandy Applu kousek za hranicemi \u010ceska", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Tuto sobotu, otev\u0159e Apple sv\u016fj dal\u0161\u00ed obchod, tentokr\u00e1t kousek za na\u0161imi hranicemi, ve V\u00eddni. Konkr\u00e9tn\u011b jej najdete na K\u00e4rntner Stra\u00dfe v samotn\u00e9m centru m\u011bsta. Dostupn\u00e9 bude k zakoupen\u00ed kompletn\u00ed portfolio produkt\u016f a firma po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 s kon\u00e1n\u00edm p\u0159edn\u00e1\u0161ek a workshop\u016f.Doposud byl design dr\u017een v tajnosti, nyn\u00ed se ale firmy  n\u011bkolika fotografiemi. Rozkl\u00e1d\u00e1 se na dvou patrech v historick\u00e9 budov\u011b. Nejedn\u00e1 se tedy o typickou prosklenou budovu, kterou byste mohli o\u010dek\u00e1vat, typick\u00e9 designov\u00e9 prvky, jako jsou velk\u00e1 okna, b\u00edl\u00e9 plochy a sv\u011btl\u00e9 d\u0159evo, jsou ale i zde p\u0159\u00edtomny.K provozu obchodu Apple najal na 150 zam\u011bstnanc\u016f. To dohromady mluv\u00ed 44 r\u016fzn\u00fdmi jazyky, aby mohli pomoci co nej\u0161ir\u0161\u00edmu spektru z\u00e1kazn\u00edk\u016f i ze zahrani\u010d\u00ed. Workshopy  jsou pak dostupn\u00e9 v\u0161em z\u00e1jemc\u016fm a v\u011bnuj\u00ed se fotografov\u00e1n\u00ed, programov\u00e1n\u00ed, hudb\u011b, um\u011bn\u00ed a dal\u0161\u00edm odv\u011btv\u00edm. K p\u0159ihl\u00e1\u0161en\u00ed m\u016f\u017eete vyu\u017e\u00edt n\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00ed .", "tags": ["Apple", "iPhone", "macOS (OS X)", "iPad", "Apple Watch", "R\u00e1j", "Chicago", "Kompletn\u00ed portfolio", "Velk\u00e9 okno", "Otev\u0159en\u00fd Apple", "V\u00edde\u0148", "Workshop", "Hranice \u010ceska", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Apple Store", "Kousek", "Obchod", "B\u00edl\u00e1 plocha", "Nej\u0161ir\u0161\u00ed spektrum", "Fanda"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jen-cisty-system-a-zadne-aplikace-k-tomu-ubuntu-jde-vzorem-windows-se-to-treba-taky-nauci/sc-3-a-191973/default.aspx", "title": "Jen \u010dist\u00fd syst\u00e9m a \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 aplikace k tomu. Ubuntu jde vzorem, Windows se to t\u0159eba taky nau\u010d\u00ed", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "24. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "P\u0159ipravovan\u00e1 verze opera\u010dn\u00edho syst\u00e9mu Ubuntu 18.04 bude m\u00edt i instala\u010dn\u00ed re\u017eim . Ten znamen\u00e1, \u017ee v syst\u00e9mu z\u016fstanou jen ty nejd\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed sou\u010d\u00e1sti jako je desktopov\u00e9 prost\u0159ed\u00ed a spr\u00e1vce soubor\u016f. Dal\u0161\u00ed aplikace, na kter\u00e9 jsme u \u010dist\u00e9 instalace Ubuntu zvykl\u00ed, se nenainstaluj\u00ed. V\u00edce .Je to dob\u0159e, nebo \u0161patn\u011b? A m\u011bl by se to nau\u010dit i Windows? Odpov\u011bdi nejsou a\u017e tak jednozna\u010dn\u00e9, v\u00edce v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu. ", "tags": ["Video", "Software", "Windows", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Linux", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Ubuntu", "Samostatn\u00fd \u010dl\u00e1nek", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Vestav\u011bn\u00e1 aplikace", "P\u0159ipravovan\u00e1 verze", "Aplikace", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "\u010cist\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Syst\u00e9m", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video", "Zku\u0161en\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Desktopov\u00e9 prost\u0159ed\u00ed", "\u010cist\u00e1 instalace", "Nejd\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed sou\u010d\u00e1st", "Vzor"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/psani-na-mobilech-swype-konci-ale-je-mnoho-jinych-alternativ/sc-3-a-191972/default.aspx", "title": "Psan\u00ed na mobilech: Swype kon\u010d\u00ed, ale je mnoho jin\u00fdch alternativ", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "24. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Psan\u00ed na mobiln\u00edch telefonech je odjak\u017eiva probl\u00e9m. Nejprve se psalo na b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch \u010d\u00edseln\u00fdch kl\u00e1vesnic\u00edch, pak p\u0159i\u0161la \u00e9ra hardwarov\u00fdch minikl\u00e1vesnic, nakonec Apple s iPhonem uk\u00e1zal, \u017ee nejlep\u0161\u00edm \u0159e\u0161en\u00edm bude virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed kl\u00e1vesnice na mobilu. Techniku psan\u00ed na displeji zda\u0159ile inovovala  a techniku \u0161oup\u00e1n\u00ed palcem z\u00e1hy p\u0159ebraly i dal\u0161\u00ed kl\u00e1vesnice. Jak\u00e9 jsou ale jin\u00e9 alternativy? V\u00edce v dne\u0161n\u00ed diskuzi.", "tags": ["Video", "Technika", "Apple", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Mobility", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "iPhone", "Kl\u00e1vesnice", "Virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed kl\u00e1vesnice", "Mobil", "Psan\u00ed", "V\u011bt\u0161ina konkurence", "Alternativa", "Konkurence", "Nejlep\u0161\u00ed \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/microsoftu-se-dari-rozsirovat-nejnovejsi-verzi-windows-10-uz-je-na-85--pocitacu/sc-3-a-191944/default.aspx", "title": "Microsoftu se da\u0159\u00ed roz\u0161i\u0159ovat nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verzi Windows, u\u017e je na 85 % po\u010d\u00edta\u010d\u016f s Des\u00edtkami", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Prozat\u00edm nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed aktualizace Windows 10,  (FCU), p\u0159ibrala dal\u0161\u00edch 10 procentn\u00edch bod\u016f a nyn\u00ed je nainstalov\u00e1na na 85 % po\u010d\u00edta\u010d\u016f s t\u00edmto opera\u010dn\u00edm syst\u00e9mem. S ohledem na bl\u00ed\u017e\u00edc\u00ed se Spring Creators Update ale tohle \u010d\u00edslo ji\u017e p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 stoupat nebude.Pod\u00edl p\u0159edchoz\u00ed verze, Creators Update (CU), se nyn\u00ed dostal na pouh\u00fdch 8,1 %. Automatick\u00e9 aktualizace v r\u00e1mci syst\u00e9mu tak z\u0159ejm\u011b funguj\u00ed a Microsoftu se da\u0159\u00ed udr\u017eet v\u011bt\u0161inu u\u017eivatel\u016f na nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verzi syst\u00e9mu. \u00dapln\u011b prvn\u00ed verzi m\u00e1 toti\u017e jen 0,5 % u\u017eivatel\u016f. FCU tak z\u00edskal jedno z nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edch zastoupen\u00ed, v\u00edce m\u011bl jen , kter\u00fd si nainstalovalo v\u00edce jak 90 % u\u017eivatel\u016f.Nov\u00e1 aktualizace Windows 10, , by m\u011bla dorazit na ja\u0159e, pravd\u011bpodobn\u011b na p\u0159elomu b\u0159ezna a dubna. P\u0159inese n\u011bkolik novinek v\u010detn\u011b p\u0159epracovan\u00e9ho p\u0159ehledu spu\u0161t\u011bn\u00fdch program\u016f a vylep\u0161en\u00ed modern\u00ed prost\u0159ed\u00ed.Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Windows 10", "Spring Creators Update", "Fall Creators Update", "Creators Update", "Aktualizace", "Anniversary Update", "Verze", "P\u0159edchoz\u00ed verze", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "Modern\u00ed prost\u0159ed\u00ed", "Prvn\u00ed verze", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed zastoupen\u00ed", "FCU", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed aktualizace", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Nov\u00e1 aktualizace", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Automatick\u00e1 aktualizace", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verze", "Spu\u0161t\u011bn\u00fd program"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/webova-hra-uci-jak-vybudovat-vlastni-fake-news-imperium-a-jak-se-dezinformacim-branit/sc-3-a-191951/default.aspx", "title": "Webov\u00e1 hra u\u010d\u00ed, jak vybudovat vlastn\u00ed fake news imp\u00e9rium. A jak se dezinformac\u00edm br\u00e1nit", "author": "Mark\u00e9ta Mike\u0161ov\u00e1", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Fake news, dezinformace, hoaxy a jin\u00e9 pochybn\u00e9 zpr\u00e1vy na internetu jsou neoddiskutovateln\u00fdm velk\u00fdm t\u00e9matem dne\u0161ka. Zkoumaj\u00ed je proto i v\u00fdzkumn\u00edci z akademick\u00e9ho prost\u0159ed\u00ed, v\u010detn\u011b lid\u00ed z Cambridge. Ti se nyn\u00ed rozhodli moc fale\u0161n\u00fdch zpr\u00e1v ilustrovat v nov\u00e9 online h\u0159e nazvan\u00e9 , ve kter\u00e9 se hr\u00e1\u010d stane nefal\u0161ovan\u00fdm dezinforma\u010dn\u00edm magn\u00e1tem.C\u00edlem hry, za kterou stoj\u00ed Cambridge Social Decision-Making Lab, je spole\u010dnost nau\u010dit, jak se dezinformac\u00edm br\u00e1nit a odhalit nej\u010dast\u011bji pou\u017e\u00edvan\u00e9 taktiky. \u201eMysl\u00edme si, \u017ee jakmile \u010dlov\u011bk jednou tu taktiku uvid\u00ed, a pou\u017eije ji ve h\u0159e, vybuduje si obrann\u00e9 mechanismy,\u201c popsal \u0161\u00e9f laborato\u0159e Sander van der Linden pro server . \u201eChceme ve\u0159ejnost nau\u010dit, co tito lid\u00e9 d\u011blaj\u00ed, t\u00edm, \u017ee se jimi stanou,\u201c pokra\u010doval.Hr\u00e1\u010di ve h\u0159e operuj\u00ed s virtu\u00e1ln\u00edm Twitterem, na kter\u00e9m pokrucuj\u00ed realitu, rozd\u011bluj\u00ed spole\u010dnost, \u0161\u00ed\u0159\u00ed nesmysly a sb\u00edraj\u00ed followery. Z\u00e1rove\u0148 to mus\u00ed d\u011blat tak, aby je jejich p\u0159\u00edznivci neprokoukli.Celkem hra \u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed nepravd rozd\u011bluje do \u0161esti kl\u00ed\u010dov\u00fdch strategi\u00ed. Jakmile si hr\u00e1\u010d jednu osvoj\u00ed, dostane odznak. V jednom kole se lid\u00e9 nap\u0159\u00edklad stanou fale\u0161n\u00fdm americk\u00fdm prezidentem Donaldem Trumpem a vyhl\u00e1s\u00ed v\u00e1lku Severn\u00ed Koreji. Dokonce i p\u0159idaj\u00ed hashtag #KimJongDone.U ka\u017ed\u00e9ho kroku se hra hr\u00e1\u010de dot\u00e1\u017ee, zda je se sv\u00fdmi kroky \u0161\u0165astn\u00fd, nebo zda c\u00edt\u00ed ur\u010dit\u00fd stud. Pokud se \u010dlov\u011bk ke studu p\u0159izn\u00e1, hra mu okam\u017eit\u011b p\u0159ipomene, \u017ee \u201epokud se chcete st\u00e1t mistrem dezinformac\u00ed, mus\u00ed se tohoto postoje zbavit\u201c.V\u00fdzkumn\u00edci z Cambridge budou \u0161est m\u011bs\u00edc\u016f sb\u00edrat data, jak lid\u00e9 hru hraj\u00ed, a pak vyhodnot\u00ed, jak byla \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u00e1. V\u00fdsledky n\u00e1sledn\u011b zve\u0159ejn\u00ed v odborn\u00e9m \u010dasopise Journal of Risk Research.", "tags": ["Twitter", "Fake News", "Hry", "Donald Trump", "Severn\u00ed Korea", "Imp\u00e9rium", "Bad News", "Hra", "Fale\u0161n\u00e1 zpr\u00e1va", "Webov\u00e1 hra", "Stud", "Obrann\u00fd mechanismus", "Odborn\u00fd \u010dasopis", "Cambridge", "Akademick\u00e9 prost\u0159ed\u00ed", "Dezinformace", "Fake"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/airbnb-chysta-velkou-zmenu-umozni-rezervovat-si-pokoje-i-v-beznych-hotelich/sc-3-a-191963/default.aspx", "title": "Airbnb chyst\u00e1 velkou zm\u011bnu, umo\u017en\u00ed rezervovat si pokoje i v b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch hotel\u00edch", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Airbnb je internetov\u00e1 slu\u017eba pro cestovatele, kter\u00e1 slou\u017e\u00ed jako alternativa b\u011b\u017en\u00fdm hotel\u016fm. Umo\u017e\u0148uje kr\u00e1tkodob\u00fd pron\u00e1jem t\u0159eba cel\u00e9ho bytu, domu, nebo naopak jen pokoje p\u0159\u00edmo u lid\u00ed, kte\u0159\u00ed v dan\u00e9m m\u00edst\u011b \u017eij\u00ed. Nyn\u00ed ale p\u0159ich\u00e1z\u00ed velk\u00e1 zm\u011bna. Firma toti\u017e umo\u017en\u00ed pr\u00e1v\u011b klasick\u00fdm hotel\u016fm vstup na platformu. Informoval o tom .Ji\u017e nyn\u00ed bylo mo\u017en\u00e9 v\u00fdjime\u010dn\u011b na podobnou nab\u00eddku narazit, nyn\u00ed ale dostanou samostatnou sekci. Airbnb se tak sna\u017e\u00ed reagovat na s\u00edl\u00edc\u00ed odpor pr\u00e1v\u011b klasick\u00fdch hotel\u016f, kte\u0159\u00ed se sna\u017e\u00ed bojovat proti roz\u0161i\u0159ov\u00e1n\u00ed slu\u017eby. Ta jim toti\u017e kaz\u00ed byznys. Zat\u00edm se nejedn\u00e1 o tolik siln\u00fd odpor, jako v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b Uberu \u2013 slu\u017eby rovn\u011b\u017e postaven\u00e9 na , v r\u016fzn\u00fdch st\u00e1tech po sv\u011bt\u011b se ale chystaj\u00ed v\u016f\u010di Airbnb nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed regulace a omezen\u00ed. Slu\u017eba jim tak vych\u00e1z\u00ed nen\u00e1padn\u011b vst\u0159\u00edc a z\u00e1rove\u0148 se stane je\u0161t\u011b v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed konkurenc\u00ed pro slu\u017eby typu Booking.com apod. Nab\u00eddka z\u0159ejm\u011b nebude otev\u0159ena pro v\u0161echny, specializovat se bude na \u201eprofesion\u00e1ln\u00ed podniky kter\u00e9 nab\u00edz\u00ed unik\u00e1tn\u00ed styl \u010di t\u00e9ma\u201c.Spole\u010dn\u011b s roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00edm nab\u00eddky p\u0159ich\u00e1z\u00ed i nov\u00e1 kategorie  zahrnuj\u00edc\u00ed ubytov\u00e1n\u00ed vybran\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edmo slu\u017ebou a , kter\u00e9 se specializuje na luxusn\u00ed nemovitosti. Pro \u010dast\u00e9 z\u00e1kazn\u00edky pak chyst\u00e1 program . Ten bude prozat\u00edm spu\u0161t\u011bn ve zku\u0161ebn\u00edm re\u017eimu pro 10 000 u\u017eivatel\u016f a postupn\u011b se roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159\u00ed. P\u0159in\u00e9st m\u00e1 prozat\u00edm d\u00e1le nespecifikovan\u00e9 v\u00fdhody.V\u0161echny tyto zm\u011bny souvis\u00ed s pl\u00e1nem firmy odbavit tento rok na jednu miliardu objedn\u00e1vek.", "tags": ["Startupy", "Airbnb", "Sd\u00edlen\u00e1 ekonomika", "Cestov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Hotel", "Odpor", "Beyond", "Klasick\u00fd hotel", "Cel\u00fd byt", "Podobn\u00e1 nab\u00eddka", "\u010cast\u00fd z\u00e1kazn\u00edk", "Zku\u0161ebn\u00ed re\u017eim", "Business insider", "Samostatn\u00e1 sekce", "Ekonomika", "Pokoj", "Velk\u00e1 konkurence", "Internetov\u00e1 slu\u017eba", "Siln\u00fd odpor", "Nov\u00e1 kategorie", "Luxusn\u00ed nemovitost", "Slu\u017eba", "Velk\u00e1 zm\u011bna", "Profesion\u00e1ln\u00ed podnik"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/celoplanetarni-internet-se-stava-realitou-kazdy-muze-byt-pripojen-ale-i-sledovan/sc-3-a-191976/default.aspx", "title": "Celoplanet\u00e1rn\u00ed internet se st\u00e1v\u00e1 realitou. Ka\u017ed\u00fd m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt p\u0159ipojen, ale i sledov\u00e1n ", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "25. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Raketa Falcon 9 ve \u010dtvrtek na ob\u011b\u017enou dr\u00e1hu mimo jin\u00e9 vynesla dva mikrosatelity Microsat-2a a Microsat-2b. Ty se stanou prvn\u00edmi d\u00edlky ob\u0159\u00ed skl\u00e1da\u010dky s n\u00e1zvem , kter\u00e1 se v n\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00edch letech rozroste na celoplanet\u00e1rn\u00ed internetovou s\u00ed\u0165. Cel\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165 se bude skl\u00e1dat ze dvou vrstev satelit\u016f, komunikuj\u00edc\u00edch na rozd\u00edln\u00fdch frekvenc\u00edch. V\u00fd\u0161 se bude pohybovat 4 425 um\u011bl\u00fdch dru\u017eic, kter\u00e9 se us\u00eddl\u00ed 1 126 km nad zemsk\u00fdm povrchem. Ni\u017e\u0161\u00ed vrstvu potom bude tvo\u0159it 7 518 satelit\u016f ve v\u00fd\u0161ce asi 320 km. Tato ob\u0159\u00ed soustava t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 12 tis\u00edc satelit\u016f se bude synchronizovan\u011b pohybovat po ob\u011b\u017en\u00fdch drah\u00e1ch, nep\u016fjde tedy o geostacion\u00e1rn\u00ed dru\u017eice, kter\u00e9 by v\u016f\u010di Zemi setrv\u00e1valy na jednom m\u00edst\u011b. ", "tags": ["Video", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Internet", "Elon Musk", "Zem\u011b", "Satelit", "Falcon", "Realita", "Cel\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165", "Dr\u00e1ha", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 dru\u017eice", "Rozd\u00edln\u00e1 frekvence", "N\u00edzk\u00e1 vrstva", "Ob\u0159\u00ed skl\u00e1da\u010dka", "Ob\u0159\u00ed soustava", "Microsat", "Internetov\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed", "Orbit", "Geostacion\u00e1rn\u00ed dru\u017eice", "Dru\u017eice", "Starlink", "Zemsk\u00fd povrch", "P\u0159ipojen\u00ed", "N\u00e1sleduj\u00edc\u00ed rok", "Satelitn\u00ed internet"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/prekladac-googlu-neni-jediny-jak-na-preklad-textu-na-internetu/sc-3-a-191856/default.aspx", "title": "P\u0159eklada\u010d Googlu nen\u00ed jedin\u00fd: Jak na p\u0159eklad textu na internetu", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "26. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Google", "Web", "P\u0159eklada\u010d", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Wikipedia", "Chrome", "Edge", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Tipy", "Bing", "Dopl\u0148ky do prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "U\u017eite\u010dn\u00e1 funkce", "Webov\u00e1 slu\u017eba", "P\u0159eklad", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed probl\u00e9m", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdhoda", "Vedlej\u0161\u00ed produkt", "Velk\u00fd n\u00e1skok", "Bingo", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed po\u010det", "Slo\u017eit\u00e1 \u010de\u0161tina", "P\u0159eklad textu", "Nava"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/hokejiste-sice-prohrali-cesi-ale-zvitezili-nix-ohlasil-novy-rekord-6296-gb/s/sc-3-a-191969/default.aspx", "title": "Hokejist\u00e9 sice prohr\u00e1li, \u010ce\u0161i ale zv\u00edt\u011bzili. Nix ohl\u00e1sil nov\u00fd rekord 629,6 Gb/s", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "\u010cesk\u00fd hokejov\u00fd t\u00fdm sice rusk\u00e9 mu\u017estvo neporazil, fanou\u0161ci, kte\u0159\u00ed sledovali z\u00e1pas na sv\u00fdch mobilech, tabletech, laptopech a velk\u00fdch po\u010d\u00edta\u010d\u00edch, si v\u0161ak jedno v\u00edt\u011bzstv\u00ed p\u0159ipsat mohou.Sledovali tak napjat\u011b , \u017ee sami porazili rekord Nixu. Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edm \u010desk\u00fdm  b\u011bhem utk\u00e1n\u00ed prot\u00e9kalo a\u017e , co\u017e je nov\u00e9 maximum.Jakmile v\u0161ak v \u010desk\u00e9 brance skon\u010dily t\u0159i puky, aktivita na \u010desk\u00e9m internetu pohasla a v\u0161ichni se zase vr\u00e1tili k pr\u00e1ci. Je to dobr\u00e9, HDP poroste i v p\u00e1tek. Nix je uzel, kter\u00fd v Praze propojuje zdej\u0161\u00ed oper\u00e1tory, hostingov\u00e9 spole\u010dnosti a dal\u0161\u00ed hr\u00e1\u010de do jak\u00e9hosi \u201en\u00e1rodn\u00edho internetu.\u201c D\u00edky peeringov\u00fdm centr\u016fm (Nix nen\u00ed v \u010cR jedin\u00fd, za zm\u00ednku stoj\u00ed tak\u00e9 , jeho\u017e z\u00e1t\u011b\u017e se pohybuje tak\u00e9 okolo 600 Gb/s) m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt komunikace mezi jednotliv\u00fdmi poskytovateli internetov\u00fdch slu\u017eeb na region\u00e1ln\u00ed \u00farovni rychlej\u0161\u00ed a efektivn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed.", "tags": ["\u010cT Sport", "Internet", "Sport", "Hudba, filmy, seri\u00e1ly", "Olympijsk\u00e9 hry", "Statistiky", "Ji\u017en\u00ed Korea", "Praha", "Multim\u00e9dia", "Hokejista", "N\u00e1rodn\u00ed internet", "\u010cesk\u00fd internet", "\u010cesko-Rusko", "NIX", "Nov\u00fd rekord", "Zdej\u0161\u00ed oper\u00e1tor", "Internetov\u00e1 slu\u017eba", "Hostingov\u00e1 spole\u010dnost", "Velk\u00fd po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Peering cz", "Rekord", "HDP", "Nov\u00e9 maximum", "Maximum"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/i-sitova-kamera-muze-byt-extremni-novinka-canonu-barevne-snima-i-ve-tme-a-stoji-pul-milionu/sc-3-a-191979/default.aspx", "title": "I s\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e1 kamera m\u016f\u017ee b\u00fdt extr\u00e9mn\u00ed: Novinka Canonu barevn\u011b sn\u00edm\u00e1 i ve tm\u011b a stoj\u00ed p\u016fl milionu", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "23. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Canon za\u010dne prod\u00e1vat novou . Jej\u00edm posl\u00e1n\u00edm je neust\u00e1l\u00fd dohled ve dne i v noci, jako u v\u011bt\u0161iny jin\u00fdch s\u00ed\u0165ov\u00fdch kamer. Na rozd\u00edl od nich ale slibuje z\u0159eteln\u00fd obraz v rozli\u0161en\u00ed Full HD i v t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 \u00fapln\u00e9 tm\u011b, a to v barv\u011b a bez \u0161umu.Kamera m\u00e1 plnoform\u00e1tov\u00fd 35mm sn\u00edma\u010d CMOS s rozli\u0161en\u00edm 2,26 Mpx,\nobrazov\u00fd procesor DIGIC DV 4, propriet\u00e1rn\u00ed technologie zpracov\u00e1n\u00ed obrazu a  (zisk 75 dB). D\u00edky tomu m\u016f\u017ee s minim\u00e1ln\u00edm \u0161umem zaznamenat i objekty osv\u011btlen\u00e9 intenzitou men\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e 0,0005 lx. Tedy p\u0159i podstatn\u011b hor\u0161\u00edch podm\u00ednk\u00e1ch, ne\u017e je t\u0159eba m\u011bs\u00ed\u010dn\u00ed svit, jeho\u017e intenzita se b\u011b\u017en\u011b pohybuje mezi polovinou a jedn\u00edm luxem.Kamera najde uplatn\u011bn\u00ed v n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00fdch sledovac\u00edch \u00faloh\u00e1ch, a to jak z hlediska bezpe\u010dnosti, tak za \u00fa\u010delem p\u0159esn\u00e9ho analytick\u00e9ho monitoringu. D\u00edky bajonetov\u00e9mu \u00fachytu EF lze na ni p\u0159ipojovat r\u016fzn\u00e9 objektivy z nab\u00eddky Canonu.Nen\u00ed to nic levn\u00e9ho. P\u0159esn\u00e1 cena zat\u00edm nebyla stanovena, ale m\u011bla by nav\u00e1zat na p\u0159edchoz\u00ed model, kter\u00fd vyjde na necel\u00fdch 580 000 K\u010d.", "tags": ["Internet", "Webkamera", "P\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed", "Kamera", "Canon", "Full HD", "P\u0159edchoz\u00ed model", "P\u016fl milionu", "Rozli\u0161en\u00ed", "\u00dapln\u00e1 tma", "\u0160patn\u00e1 podm\u00ednka", "Intenzita", "Tma", "Propriet\u00e1rn\u00ed technologie", "M\u011bs\u00ed\u010dn\u00ed svit", "P\u0159esn\u00e1 cena", "Neust\u00e1l\u00fd dohled", "S\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e1 kamera", "\u0160um"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/asus-zenbook-pro-kdyz-si-chcete-hrat-na-profesionaly/sc-3-a-191871/default.aspx", "title": "Asus Zenbook Pro: kdy\u017e si chcete hr\u00e1t na profesion\u00e1ly", "author": "Tom\u00e1\u0161 Hol\u010d\u00edk", "date": "20. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Na prvn\u00ed pohled byste to do tohoto \u0161t\u00edhl\u00e9ho notebooku ne\u0159ekli. Dr\u017e\u00ed dnes u\u017e tradi\u010dn\u00ed design Asusu kombinuj\u00edc\u00ed matn\u011b \u010dern\u00e9 nebo modr\u00e9 kovov\u00e9 kryty se st\u0159\u00edbrn\u00fdmi dopl\u0148ky a vypad\u00e1 jako b\u011b\u017en\u00fd 15,6\" tenk\u00fd notebook. Ve skute\u010dnosti je ale uvnit\u0159 v\u00fdkonn\u00fd procesor i slu\u0161n\u00e1 grafick\u00e1 karta, dotykov\u00fd displej se m\u016f\u017ee pochlubit ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00edm perem a nebudete str\u00e1dat ani po str\u00e1nce konektor\u016f.Asus tento notebook nechce c\u00edlit na hr\u00e1\u010de, ale sp\u00ed\u0161e na profesion\u00e1ly vy\u017eaduj\u00edc\u00ed procesorov\u00fd i grafick\u00fd v\u00fdkon. V\u00edc ale m\u00ed\u0159\u00ed na ty, kte\u0159\u00ed cht\u011bj\u00ed poctiv\u00fd v\u00fdkon v elegantn\u00edm t\u011ble. Foto a video profesion\u00e1ly toti\u017e asi zklame, \u017ee se u n\u00e1s prod\u00e1v\u00e1 notebook pouze ve variant\u011b s 8 GB pam\u011bti bez mo\u017enosti dal\u0161\u00edho roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed, pou\u017eit\u00e9 SSD nevyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 rychlej\u0161\u00ed sb\u011brnici NVMe a displej, by\u0165 vypad\u00e1 na pohled l\u00e1kav\u011b s pln\u00fdm pokryt\u00edm sRGB, po prom\u011b\u0159en\u00ed sondou ukazuje jen pr\u016fm\u011brnou p\u0159esnost kalibrace (dE 4,91). Kamera nad displejem dokonce um\u00ed jen 640\u00d7480.Design se ale Asusu povedl, v\u0161e p\u016fsob\u00ed hodnotn\u011b a elegantn\u011b, displej lze pohodln\u011b otev\u0159\u00edt jednou rukou, dokonce dostanete i podsv\u00edcen\u00e9 logo na v\u00edku displeje. Vychyt\u00e1vky p\u0159edstavuj\u00ed stavov\u00e9 diody ve zkosen\u00e9 hran\u011b u touchpadu, kde je uvid\u00edte i p\u0159i zav\u0159en\u00e9m v\u00edku displeje nebo zdvojen\u00e9 reproduktory vedle kl\u00e1vesnice i na spodn\u00ed stran\u011b. \u00dahel otev\u0159en\u00ed displeje u\u017e tak\u00e9 nen\u00ed zdrojem v\u00fdtek a je v pohod\u011b pou\u017eiteln\u00fd pro pr\u00e1ci.A\u010d jde o v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed notebook, kl\u00e1vesnice nem\u00e1 numerick\u00fd blok. Rozlo\u017een\u00ed je tak p\u011bkn\u011b vycentrovan\u00e9, \u0161ipky se nem\u00edchaj\u00ed s jin\u00fdmi tla\u010d\u00edtky a prav\u00fd Shift pat\u0159\u00ed k jedn\u011bm z nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edch. Na Asus tradi\u010dn\u011b najdete vyp\u00edna\u010d v prav\u00e9m horn\u00edm rohu kl\u00e1vesnice. Reaguje okam\u017eit\u011b, ale alespo\u0148 je nutn\u00fd p\u0159\u00edtlak mnohem v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed ne\u017e u okoln\u00edch kl\u00e1ves. B\u011b\u017enou silou jej tedy omylem nestisknete.B\u00edl\u00e9 t\u0159\u00ed\u00farov\u0148ov\u00e9 podsv\u00edcen\u00ed na nejvy\u0161\u0161\u00ed jas u\u017e trochu prosv\u00edt\u00e1 okolo kl\u00e1ves, ale nikdy nem\u011bn\u00ed v\u00fdbornou \u010ditelnost popisk\u016f na kl\u00e1ves\u00e1ch. Sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed p\u0159\u00edjemn\u00e9ho touchpadu se stala \u010dte\u010dka otisk\u016f prst\u016f.Pro p\u0159ipojen\u00ed tu m\u00e1te hned dva USB-C porty v proveden\u00ed Thunderbolt, nechyb\u00ed HDMI, dva klasick\u00e9 USB 3.0 konektory, audio a \u010dte\u010dka karet, by\u0165 jen t\u011bch microSD. Nap\u00e1jen\u00ed zaji\u0161\u0165uje klasick\u00fd velk\u00fd adapt\u00e9r a vzhledem k jeho v\u00fdkonu 135 W mu to nem\u00e1te za zl\u00e9. Aspo\u0148 zajist\u00ed bezprobl\u00e9mov\u00e9 nap\u00e1jen\u00ed v\u00fdkonn\u00fdch vnit\u0159nost\u00ed.Uvnit\u0159 toti\u017e najdete Core i7-7700HQ s grafikou GTX 1050 Ti. D\u00edky tomu m\u016f\u017eete br\u00e1t notebook i jako v\u00fdkonn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed hern\u00ed notebook. Ten\u010d\u00ed proveden\u00ed vede k obav\u00e1m, zda takov\u00fd notebook nebude sahat k n\u011bjak\u00fdm \u00fasporn\u00fdm opat\u0159en\u00edm, aby se p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 nep\u0159eh\u0159\u00edval. Popravd\u011b jsem ale nic takov\u00e9ho nepozoroval. Teploty sice stoupnou, ale dr\u017e\u00ed se v konstantn\u00edch mez\u00edch, ani\u017e by se muselo s\u00e1hnout ke sni\u017eov\u00e1n\u00ed v\u00fdkonu.Konkurentem pro Zenbook UX550VE bude p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm Dell XPS 15, kter\u00fd v podobn\u011b elegantn\u00edm a je\u0161t\u011b men\u0161\u00edm t\u011ble nab\u00edz\u00ed srovnatelnou v\u00fdbavu. Sice jen GTX 1050 bez p\u0159\u00eddavku Ti, zato si ale m\u016f\u017eete u Dellu roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159it pam\u011b\u0165. Asus nab\u00eddne lep\u0161\u00ed zvuk a perem \u010di prsty ovladateln\u00fd FullHD displej (u Dellu je dotykov\u00e1 4K varianta).Asus Zenbook p\u0159edstavuje dobrou kombinaci lep\u0161\u00edho v\u00fdkonu v elegantn\u00edm t\u011ble. Nestav\u00ed na odiv hern\u00ed schopnosti, nezalekne se ale ani vy\u0161\u0161\u00edch n\u00e1rok\u016f na v\u00fdkon. Hlavn\u00ed v\u00fdtka m\u00ed\u0159\u00ed na jen z\u00e1kladn\u00ed a hlavn\u011b neroz\u0161i\u0159itelnou kapacitu pam\u011bti a zbyte\u010dn\u011b pomalej\u0161\u00ed SSD.", "tags": ["Video", "Notebooky", "Testy", "Intel", "Dell", "SSD", "Asus", "USB", "Lenovo", "Kl\u00e1vesnice", "HDMI", "Thunderbolt", "Zkosen\u00e1 hrana", "St\u0159\u00edbrn\u00fd dopln\u011bk", "Podsv\u00edcen\u00e9 logo", "Kl\u00e1vesa", "Elegantn\u00ed t\u011blo", "Procesorov\u00fd v\u00fdkon", "V\u00fdkonn\u00fd procesor", "GTX", "Storm", "Dotykov\u00fd displej", "Pln\u00e9 pokryt\u00ed", "Stavov\u00e1 dioda", "V\u00fdkonn\u00e1 komponenta"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/tezil-bitcoin-a-rusil-tak-lte-signal-t-mobilu-americka-fcc-jej-vycmuchala/sc-3-a-191896/default.aspx", "title": "T\u011b\u017eil bitcoin, a ru\u0161il tak LTE sign\u00e1l T-Mobilu. Americk\u00e1 FCC jej vy\u010dmuchala", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "19. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Bitcoin posledn\u00ed dny op\u011bt roste a t\u011b\u017eba za\u010d\u00edn\u00e1 b\u00fdt znovu zaj\u00edmav\u00e1 pro mal\u00e9 horn\u00edky se specializovan\u00fdmi t\u011b\u017eebn\u00edmi ma\u0161inkami. Jeden z nich z newyorsk\u00e9ho Brooklynu t\u011b\u017eil bitcoin na po\u010d\u00edta\u010di AntMiner S5.Jedn\u00e1 se o star\u0161\u00ed model, kter\u00fd u\u017e jeho v\u00fdrobce Bitmain ani nenab\u00edz\u00ed, n\u00e1stupce  je toti\u017e o \u0159\u00e1d v\u00fdkonn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed (13,5 TH/s). Nicm\u00e9n\u011b je tak\u00e9 o \u0159\u00e1d dra\u017e\u0161\u00ed ( 2 320 USD), zat\u00edmco S5 lze  sehnat za \u010d\u00e1stky okolo 500-600 dolar\u016f.Zp\u011bt ale do Brooklynu. AntMiner k t\u011b\u017eb\u011b nepou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 GPU, ale specializovan\u00e9 \u010dipy navr\u017een\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edmo pro \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed algoritm\u016f konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed kryptom\u011bny ( \u010dipy \u2013 \u010dasto zalo\u017een\u00e9 na ). V tom by probl\u00e9m nebyl, pot\u00ed\u017e je sp\u00ed\u0161e v absenci jak\u00e9koliv homologace.Jin\u00fdmi slovy, kdy\u017e se p\u0159inejmen\u0161\u00edm AntMiner S5 rozjede na pln\u00e9 obr\u00e1tky, jeho \u010dipy (nebo dal\u0161\u00ed elektronika uvnit\u0159) z\u0159ejm\u011b generuj\u00ed ru\u0161iv\u00fd sign\u00e1l na 700 MHz. A ten sign\u00e1l je natolik siln\u00fd, \u017ee pronikne zd\u00ed ven, kde, v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b USA, ru\u0161\u00ed LTE vys\u00edla\u010de T-Mobilu, kter\u00e9 operuj\u00ed na podobn\u00e9 frekvenci.T\u011b\u017ea\u0159 se tak nev\u011bdomky stal ileg\u00e1ln\u00edm jammerem \u2013 ru\u0161i\u010dem na licencovan\u00e9m telekomunika\u010dn\u00edm p\u00e1smu a brzy jej  americk\u00fd feder\u00e1ln\u00ed telekomunika\u010dn\u00ed \u00fa\u0159ad FCC (zpr\u00e1va v ). Ne\u0161\u0165astn\u00edkovi nyn\u00ed hroz\u00ed spr\u00e1vn\u00ed \u0159\u00edzen\u00ed a pokuta.Za zm\u00ednku stoj\u00ed, \u017ee podobn\u00fd osud v\u00e1s samoz\u0159ejm\u011b m\u016f\u017ee potkat i v \u010cesku, kde na spr\u00e1vn\u00e9 vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed r\u00e1diov\u00e9ho p\u00e1sma dohl\u00ed\u017e\u00ed tuzemsk\u00e1 alternativa FCC \u2013 \u010cTU. Jeho partne\u0159i p\u0159itom dok\u00e1\u017eou vysledovat ileg\u00e1ln\u00ed r\u00e1diov\u00e9 vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00ed s obdivuhodnou p\u0159esnost\u00ed a\u017e na \u00farove\u0148 domu a bytov\u00e9 jednotky.Nejde p\u0159itom pouze o trval\u00e9 ru\u0161en\u00ed podobn\u00fdm za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edm, ale i o pou\u017eit\u00ed levn\u00fdch \u010d\u00ednsk\u00fdch r\u00e1diov\u00fdch vys\u00edla\u010d\u016f z eBaye a AliExpressu, kter\u00e9 si obl\u00edbili nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed bastl\u00ed\u0159i. \u010casto se jedn\u00e1 o moduly pro Arduino a jemu podobn\u00e9 prototypovac\u00ed desky, kter\u00e9 komunikuj\u00ed na n\u011bkter\u00e9m ze subgigahertzov\u00fdch kmito\u010dt\u016f (typicky 433 MHz a 868 MHz).Ty jsou sice ur\u010den\u00e9 pro nelicencovan\u00e9 pou\u017eit\u00ed, ov\u0161em p\u0159i dodr\u017een\u00ed . Zejm\u00e9na jde o vys\u00edlac\u00ed v\u00fdkon a dobu str\u00e1venou vys\u00edl\u00e1n\u00edm za jednotku \u010dasu. Pokud nespln\u00edte alespo\u0148 z\u00e1kladn\u00ed vys\u00edlac\u00ed p\u0159edpisy, ob\u00e1lka s pruhem m\u016f\u017ee dorazit i do va\u0161\u00ed schr\u00e1nky.Ostatn\u011b k tomu sam\u00e9mu m\u016f\u017ee doj\u00edt, pokud nad r\u00e1mec normy zv\u00fd\u0161\u00edte i v\u00fdkon sv\u00e9ho Wi-Fi routeru. Zm\u011bnu v\u00fdkonu umo\u017e\u0148uj\u00ed mnoh\u00e9 pokro\u010dilej\u0161\u00ed routery, respektive ty s alternativn\u00edmi firmwary typu OpenWRT/DDWRT apod.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Bitcoin", "USA", "Jammer", "eBay", "Arduino", "T\u011b\u017eba", "\u010cesk\u00fd telekomunika\u010dn\u00ed \u00fa\u0159ad (\u010cT\u00da)", "Router", "T-Mobile", "LTE", "AliExpress", "Spr\u00e1vn\u00e9 vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed", "Sign\u00e1l", "Spr\u00e1vn\u00ed \u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "MHz", "Bitmain", "Brooklyn", "R\u00e1diov\u00e9 p\u00e1smo", "Star\u00fd model", "P\u0159\u00edsn\u00e1 podm\u00ednka", "Ru\u0161iv\u00fd sign\u00e1l", "FCC", "Podobn\u00e9 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "Pln\u00e9 obr\u00e1tky"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/seznam-nabidne-relevantnejsi-vysledky-vyhledavani-a-zobrazi-vice-stranek-z-jednoho-zdroje/sc-3-a-191975/default.aspx", "title": "Seznam nab\u00eddne relevantn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdsledky vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed a zobraz\u00ed v\u00edce str\u00e1nek z jednoho zdroje", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "24. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Seznam chyst\u00e1 zm\u011bnu ve sv\u00e9m vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed. Nov\u011b bude vracet relevantn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed odkazy a kdy\u017e uzn\u00e1 za vhodn\u00e9, uk\u00e1\u017ee jich v\u00edce z jedn\u00e9 dom\u00e9ny. Jedn\u00e1 se o pom\u011brn\u011b velkou zm\u011bnu, ve v\u00fdpisu p\u0159ed rolov\u00e1n\u00edm se \u010dasto uk\u00e1\u017e\u00ed odkazy pouze na jeden web.Zm\u011bna spo\u010d\u00edv\u00e1 ve zm\u011bn\u011bn\u00e9m relevan\u010dn\u00edm modelu, kter\u00fd vyhodnocuje vztah dokument\u016f v indexu v\u016f\u010di vyhled\u00e1van\u00e9mu dotazu. Dle firmy se na m\u011b\u0159en\u00fdch dotazech zlep\u0161ila pr\u016fm\u011brn\u00e1 relevance o 4,5 %, teoreticky tedy nab\u00eddne kvalitn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed odkazy, kter\u00e9 u\u017eivatele opravdu zaj\u00edmaj\u00ed.D\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed je ale souvisej\u00edc\u00ed zm\u011bna, kdy vyhled\u00e1va\u010d bude vracet v\u00edce odkaz\u016f sm\u011b\u0159uj\u00edc\u00edch na stejn\u00fd web. Nebude se tak d\u00edt v\u017edy, ale pouze v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, \u017ee to uzn\u00e1 za vhodn\u00e9. Bohu\u017eel se tak ale stane, \u017ee u t\u011bchto konkr\u00e9tn\u00edch v\u00fdraz\u016f se na prvn\u00ed obrazovce v\u011bt\u0161inou uk\u00e1\u017e\u00ed pouze odkazy z jednoho jedin\u00e9ho webu a pro jak\u00e9koliv dal\u0161\u00ed je nutn\u00e9 sjet n\u00ed\u017ee.P\u0159\u00edklady zm\u011bn ve vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed:Zdroj:  ", "tags": ["Seznam.cz", "Web", "Internet", "Vyhled\u00e1va\u010de", "Odkaz", "V\u00fdsledek vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed", "Seznam", "Stejn\u00fd web", "Velk\u00e1 zm\u011bna", "Prvn\u