{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/apple-park-je-nebezpecny-pro-zamestnance-narazi-do-sklenenych-dveri/sc-3-a-191894/default.aspx", "title": "Apple Park je nebezpe\u010dn\u00fd pro zam\u011bstnance. Nar\u00e1\u017e\u00ed do sklen\u011bn\u00fdch dve\u0159\u00ed", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "20. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Sklo bylo nejobl\u00edben\u011bj\u0161\u00edm materi\u00e1lem Steva Jobse a nejinak je tomu i v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b Jonathana Iva. Ten stoj\u00ed z velk\u00e9 \u010d\u00e1sti za n\u00e1vrhem nov\u00e9ho s\u00eddla  a sklen\u011bn\u00e9 podob\u011b se tak nikdo nem\u016f\u017ee divit. Rozhodn\u011b se ale v posledn\u00edch dnech divilo n\u011bkolik zam\u011bstnanc\u016f, kte\u0159\u00ed se sna\u017eili proj\u00edt neotev\u0159en\u00fdmi sklen\u011bn\u00fdmi dve\u0159mi. Ne\u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u011b. Design\u00e9\u0159i Applu toti\u017e ze sklen\u011bn\u00fdch zd\u00ed nechali odstranit bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed n\u00e1lepky (up\u0159esn\u011bno: tyto n\u00e1lepky si tam po prvn\u00edch n\u00e1razech za\u010dali lepit sami zam\u011bstnanci), nebo\u0165 negativn\u011b ovliv\u0148ovaly design.Web  proto mohl informovat o n\u011bkoliker\u00e9m z\u00e1sahu zdravotnick\u00e9 slu\u017eby, kter\u00e1 musela o\u0161et\u0159it zam\u011bstnance po n\u00e1razu do skla. Zav\u0159en\u00e9 dve\u0159e p\u0159ehl\u00e9dli p\u0159irozen\u011b kv\u016fli tomu, \u017ee v\u011bnovali pozornost iPhonu.Krom\u011b vtipn\u00fdch historek a znovup\u0159ilepen\u00ed v\u00fdstra\u017en\u00fdch n\u00e1lepek v\u0161ak mohou na Apple zam\u00ed\u0159it i n\u011bjak\u00e9 \u017ealoby. Kalifornsk\u00e9 z\u00e1kony p\u0159\u00edmo na tyto p\u0159\u00edpady pamatuj\u00ed a zam\u011bstnavatel\u016fm p\u0159ikazuj\u00ed zajistit dostate\u010dnou ochranu pr\u00e1v\u011b p\u0159ed zran\u011bn\u00edm tohoto typu. ().Apple m\u00e1 s podobn\u00fdmi p\u0159\u00edpady n\u011bkolik zku\u0161enost\u00ed. V roce 2012 si o zav\u0159en\u00e9 sklen\u011bn\u00e9 dve\u0159e Apple Storu v New Yorku zlomila nos t\u0159iaosmdes\u00e1tilet\u00e1 \u017eena a za\u017ealovala spole\u010dnosti o 1 milion dolar\u016f.Z bezpe\u010dnostn\u00edch d\u016fvod\u016f a po n\u011bkolika incidentech musel Apple rovn\u011b\u017e ikonick\u00e9 sklen\u011bn\u00e9 schody na Fifth Avenue opat\u0159it protiskluzov\u00fdmi koberci.", "tags": ["Apple", "iPhone", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Steve Jobs", "Zam\u011bstnanci", "Kalifornsk\u00fd z\u00e1kon", "New York", "Apple Store", "N\u00e1lepka", "Dve\u0159e", "Podobn\u00fd p\u0159\u00edpad", "Dolar", "Apple Park", "Fifth avenue", "Dostate\u010dn\u00e1 ochrana", "Nov\u00e9 s\u00eddlo", "Velk\u00e1 \u010d\u00e1st", "Bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed d\u016fvody"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/vyzkousejte-si-letecky-simulator-v-prohlizeci-ktery-funguje-nad-realnymi-mapami/sc-3-a-191900/default.aspx", "title": "Vyzkou\u0161ejte si leteck\u00fd simul\u00e1tor v prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010di, kter\u00fd funguje nad re\u00e1ln\u00fdmi mapami", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "20. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Je to u\u017e sedm let, co Jakub propadl t\u011b\u017ek\u00e9 z\u00e1vislosti na leteck\u00e9m simul\u00e1toru uvnit\u0159 prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de GEFS (Google Earth Flight Simulator). Vyl\u00e9\u010dil ho a\u017e Google, kdy\u017e ukon\u010dil podporu pluginu pro sv\u016fj Google Earth, na kter\u00e9m b\u011b\u017eel i simul\u00e1tor GEFS. Auto\u0159i GEFS se v\u0161ak s t\u00edmto probl\u00e9mem postupn\u011b vypo\u0159\u00e1dali, p\u0159ejmenovali sv\u016fj simul\u00e1tor na  a ten nyn\u00ed b\u011b\u017e\u00ed na open-source 3D gl\u00f3bu .Cesium b\u011b\u017e\u00ed ve WebGL a HTML5 a z\u00e1le\u017e\u00ed jen na v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159i, jak\u00e9 mapov\u00e9 podklady pou\u017eije \u2013 Google v tomto p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b nahradil p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm Bing, kter\u00fd nab\u00edz\u00ed vlastn\u00ed mapov\u00e9 API.GEFS tedy pod nov\u00fdm jm\u00e9nem nad\u00e1le funguje a dnes se v n\u011bm m\u016f\u017eete prol\u00e9tnout t\u0159eba nad Prahou nebo Brnem v libovoln\u00e9m dopravn\u00edm prost\u0159edku po\u010d\u00ednaje horkovzdu\u0161n\u00fdm bal\u00f3nem a kon\u010de t\u0159eba zrovna dopravn\u00edm velik\u00e1nem A380.V\u0161e b\u011b\u017e\u00ed v HTML5, \u010dili k letu nebudete pot\u0159ebovat \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd dodate\u010dn\u00fd software \u2013 jen prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d s podporou WebGL a po\u010d\u00edta\u010d s adekv\u00e1tn\u00edm grafick\u00fdm \u010dipem, kter\u00fd to v\u0161e ut\u00e1hne. A samoz\u0159ejm\u011b rychlou internetovou linku, proto\u017ee z webu se neust\u00e1le stahuj\u00ed v\u0161echna data v \u010dele s t\u011bmi mapov\u00fdmi.GeoFS je multiplayerov\u00fd syst\u00e9m, na obloze tedy uvid\u00edte dal\u0161\u00ed letce, kte\u0159\u00ed zrovna prokrastinuj\u00ed u po\u010d\u00edta\u010de, a nechyb\u00ed ani mapov\u00fd naviga\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m s autopilotem, tak\u017ee si m\u016f\u017eete v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase nasimulovat t\u0159eba jeden\u00e1ctihodinov\u00fd let z Schipholu do San Franciska.", "tags": ["Google", "Web", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "WebGL", "Simul\u00e1tor", "Zaj\u00edmavosti", "Hry", "Brno", "Letadla", "Bing", "Praha", "HTML5", "API", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d", "Dodate\u010dn\u00fd software", "Leteck\u00fd simul\u00e1tor", "Nov\u00e9 jm\u00e9no", "Schiphol", "GEFS", "Re\u00e1ln\u00fd \u010das", "Earth", "San Francisco", "Mapa", "Jakub", "Cesium"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/vzdelavani-pres-internet/sc-3-a-191965/default.aspx", "title": "Vzde\u030cla\u0301va\u0301ni\u0301 pr\u030ces internet", "author": null, "date": "21. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Nechcete se u\u010dit z knih a jin\u00fdch materi\u00e1l\u016f, kter\u00e9 se v dne\u0161n\u00ed dob\u011b u\u017e mohou zd\u00e1t zastaral\u00e9? Co takhle to zkusit na internetu? Kde p\u0159esn\u011b naj\u00edt ov\u011b\u0159en\u00e9 informace si pov\u00edme v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu. ", "tags": ["Internet", "Tipy", "Jak na Internet", "Vzd\u011bl\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed doba"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/spojene-staty-obvinuji-rusko-ze-do-sveta-vypustilo-zakerny-ransomware/sc-3-a-191910/default.aspx", "title": "Spojen\u00e9 st\u00e1ty obvi\u0148uj\u00ed Rusko, \u017ee do sv\u011bta vypustilo z\u00e1ke\u0159n\u00fd ransomware", "author": "Martin Hod\u00e1s", "date": "20. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "B\u00edl\u00fd d\u016fm , \u017ee podle zji\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed americk\u00fdch vy\u0161et\u0159ovatel\u016f stoj\u00ed Rusko za vypu\u0161t\u011bn\u00edm ransomwaru NotPetya. Ten v \u010dervnu minul\u00e9ho roku ochromil mno\u017estv\u00ed po\u010d\u00edta\u010d\u016f zejm\u00e9na v Evrop\u011b. Stanovisko USA je tak p\u0159idalo britsk\u00fdch vy\u0161et\u0159ovatel\u016f,  agentura Reuters.\u201e\u0160lo o \u010d\u00e1st pokra\u010duj\u00edc\u00edho kremelsk\u00e9ho \u00fasil\u00ed o destabilizaci Ukrajiny,\u201c stoj\u00ed v kr\u00e1tk\u00e9 zpr\u00e1v\u011b USA. Pr\u00e1v\u011b Ukrajina byla kybernetick\u00fdm \u00fatokem nejv\u00edce zasa\u017eena.Ransomware p\u0159itom paradoxn\u011b vyu\u017e\u00edval . Z\u00e1ke\u0159n\u00fd byl tak\u00e9 t\u00edm, \u017ee a\u010dkoliv \u0161lo o vyd\u011bra\u010dsk\u00fd virus, zaplacen\u00ed v\u00fdkupn\u00e9ho ob\u011btem nepomohlo a data z\u016fstala i nad\u00e1le za\u0161ifrovan\u00e1. Podle zji\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed Kaspersky Lab hacke\u0159i z\u0159ejm\u011b ani nem\u011bli postup, jak data op\u011bt de\u0161ifrovat. Jejich prim\u00e1rn\u00edm \u00famyslem zjevn\u011b nebylo \u0161kodliv\u00fdm k\u00f3dem vyd\u011blat, ale \u0161kodit. P\u016fvod \u00fatoku v rusk\u00e9 arm\u00e1d\u011b vid\u00ed i britsk\u00e9 ministerstvo zahrani\u010d\u00ed, kter\u00e9 sv\u016fj n\u00e1zor prezentovalo minul\u00fd t\u00fdden. \u201eTento \u00fatok byl zamaskovan\u00fd jako krimin\u00e1ln\u00ed \u010din, ale jeho \u00fa\u010delem bylo v prvn\u00ed \u0159ad\u011b rozvracet,\u201c uvedli Britov\u00e9. Zat\u00edmco USA slibuj\u00ed mezin\u00e1rodn\u00ed d\u016fsledky, Moskva jakoukoli vinu opakovan\u011b o