{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/microsoft-uvolnil-prvni-testovaci-sestaveni-podzimniho-updatu-windows-10-ten-jarni-je-jiz-za-dvermi/sc-3-a-191836/default.aspx", "title": "Microsoft uvolnil prvn\u00ed testovac\u00ed sestaven\u00ed podzimn\u00edho updatu Windows 10. Ten jarn\u00ed je ji\u017e za dve\u0159mi", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "15. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Microsoft aktu\u00e1ln\u011b fini\u0161uje s jarn\u00ed aktualizac\u00ed  (SCU) a stejn\u011b jako minul\u00fd rok vybran\u00e9mu po\u010dtu betatester\u016f rozes\u00edl\u00e1 prvn\u00ed testovac\u00ed sestaven\u00ed podzimn\u00ed aktualizace. To je zat\u00edm stejn\u00e9 s klasick\u00fdm , novinky lze o\u010dek\u00e1vat v dohledn\u00e9 dob\u011b.SCU je nyn\u00ed t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 hotov a Microsoft dokon\u010dil i aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed Bug Bash, tedy hromadn\u00e9 testov\u00e1n\u00ed a hled\u00e1n\u00ed chyb v nov\u00fdch funkc\u00edch syst\u00e9mu. A pon\u011bvad\u017e se p\u0159i uv\u00e1d\u011bn\u00ed  firm\u011b vyplatilo \u010d\u00e1st betatester\u016f odd\u011blit ke zkou\u0161en\u00ed dal\u0161\u00ed verze syst\u00e9mu, \u010din\u00ed tak i tentokr\u00e1t.V\u0161ichni v klasick\u00e9m programu aktu\u00e1ln\u011b z\u00edskali verzi z kan\u00e1lu . Ti, kte\u0159\u00ed si ponechali zapnut\u00fd z lo\u0148sk\u00e9ho podzimu kan\u00e1l  z\u00edskali verzi  z v\u011btve Redstone 5, co\u017e je ozna\u010den\u00ed pr\u00e1v\u011b pro podzimn\u00ed aktualizaci. Bohu\u017eel je tato mo\u017enost omezena a Microsoft neumo\u017e\u0148uje nov\u00e9 zapojen\u00ed do kan\u00e1lu.Krom  p\u0159inesl aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed build pro ob\u011b v\u011btve nov\u00fd design n\u011bkter\u00fdch emoji, panel pro psan\u00ed emoji do v\u00edce jazyk\u016f a tak\u00e9 mo\u017enost samostatn\u011b testovat n\u011bkter\u00e9 syst\u00e9mov\u00e9 aplikace. Mezi n\u011b nap\u0159\u00edklad pat\u0159\u00ed , Fotky, Sticky Notes, Hodiny, Kalkula\u010dka a dal\u0161\u00ed.(zat\u00edm nebyl n\u00e1zev aktualizace ofici\u00e1ln\u011b potvrzen) by m\u011bl vyj\u00edt letos na ja\u0159e, datum p\u0159edstaven\u00ed ale zat\u00edm Microsoft neuvedl. P\u0159inese dal\u0161\u00ed zm\u011bny designu, Windows Timeline a dal\u0161\u00ed novinky. Podzimn\u00ed aktualizaci pak lze o\u010dek\u00e1vat ke konci roku. Co p\u0159inese za nov\u00e9 funkce a zm\u011bny ale zat\u00edm nen\u00ed jasn\u00e9.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Windows 10", "Spring Creators Update", "Fall Creators Update", "Emoji", "Aktualizace", "Windows Insider", "Betaverze", "Podzimn\u00ed update", "SCU", "Kalkula\u010dka", "Vybran\u00fd po\u010det", "Verze syst\u00e9mu", "Chystan\u00e1 novinka", "Klasick\u00fd program", "Nov\u00e1 funkce", "Kan\u00e1l", "Sticky notes", "Druh\u00e1 polovina", "Podzimn\u00ed aktualizace", "Testovac\u00ed sestaven\u00ed", "Syst\u00e9mov\u00e1 aplikace", "Jarn\u00ed aktualizace", "Margin"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/futlab-kutilove-z-prahy-dostanou-na-jare-novou-high-tech-dilnu/sc-3-a-191832/default.aspx", "title": "FutLab: Kutilov\u00e9 z Prahy dostanou na ja\u0159e novou high-tech d\u00edlnu", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "15. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Brn\u011bnsk\u00e9 Jihomoravsk\u00e9 inova\u010dn\u00ed centrum loni na ja\u0159e otev\u0159elo sv\u016fj FabLab \u2013 nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed \u010deskou d\u00edlnu pro bastl\u00ed\u0159e v\u0161eho druhu. Ti zde najdou prakticky v\u0161e od klad\u00edvek a vrta\u010dek a\u017e po CNC fr\u00e9zku, 3D tisk\u00e1rny a laserovou \u0159eza\u010dku.Podobn\u00fdch d\u00edlen a men\u0161\u00edch hackerspac\u016f je samoz\u0159ejm\u011b v \u010cesku v\u00edce, a\u010dkoliv mnohdy nab\u00edzej\u00ed sp\u00ed\u0161e skromn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdbavi\u010dku. Je to pochopiteln\u00e9, podobn\u00e1 technika nen\u00ed za pusu a v Brn\u011b sponzorsky vypomohl zdej\u0161\u00ed Honeywell.V ka\u017ed\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, \u0159adu  na ja\u0159e roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159\u00ed dal\u0161\u00ed \u2013 tentokr\u00e1t v Praze! \u0158\u00edk\u00e1 si  m\u00e1 podtitul  a n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvn\u00edk\u016fm slibuje vedle z\u00e1kladn\u00edho n\u00e1\u0159ad\u00ed a p\u00e1jek tak\u00e9 3D tisk\u00e1rny Prusa, CNC fr\u00e9zku, laserovou \u0159eza\u010dku nebo t\u0159eba elektrick\u00e9 brusky a barv\u00edc\u00ed pistole. To v\u0161e na plo\u0161e 111 m.Pra\u017esk\u00e1 d\u00edlna se rod\u00ed pod dohledem Daniela Gottwalda, kter\u00fd potvrzuje inspiraci brn\u011bnsk\u00fdm FabLabem a dod\u00e1v\u00e1: \u201eR\u00e1di bychom otev\u0159eli v b\u0159eznu ve\u0159ejnosti. P\u0159ij\u00edt se pod\u00edvat m\u016f\u017ee ka\u017ed\u00fd, d\u00edlna v\u0161ak bude k pou\u017eit\u00ed pro \u010dleny, kte\u0159\u00ed budou platit \u010dlensk\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky.\u201cA\u010dkoliv se podm\u00ednky \u010dlenstv\u00ed st\u00e1le lad\u00ed, k dispozici by mohly b\u00fdt t\u0159i cenov\u00e9 \u00farovn\u011b \u010dlenstv\u00ed a p\u0159\u00edpadn\u011b i mo\u017enost jednor\u00e1zov\u00e9 pr\u00e1ce. D\u00edlna z\u00e1rove\u0148 nechce b\u00fdt pouze d\u00edlnou v prav\u00e9m slova smyslu, ale m\u00e1 v pl\u00e1nu tak\u00e9 nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed workshopy a populariza\u010dn\u00ed akce.", "tags": ["Programov\u00e1n\u00ed", "DIY", "Hacking", "Brno", "Praha", "\u0158eza\u010dka", "Cenov\u00e1 \u00farove\u0148", "Honeywell", "CNC", "D\u00edlna", "Margin", "Webov\u00e1 str\u00e1nka", "Laserov\u00e1 \u0159eza\u010dka", "Prav\u00e9 slovo", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Kutil", "Podobn\u00e1 technika", "Tisk\u00e1rna"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/monitory-pro-rok-2018-obri-uhlopricky-thunderbolt-3-nebo-cestovni-oled/sc-3-a-191830/default.aspx", "title": "Monitory pro rok 2018: ob\u0159\u00ed \u00fahlop\u0159\u00ed\u010dky, Thunderbolt 3 nebo cestovn\u00ed OLED", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "15. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "", "tags": ["Hardware", "Google", "Nvidia", "Android", "Samsung", "Acer", "Dell", "Asus", "Monitory", "USB", "Lenovo", "DisplayPort", "Thunderbolt", "P\u0159\u00edslu\u0161enstv\u00ed", "HDR", "Nov\u00fd monitor", "Profesion\u00e1ln\u00ed monitor", "Quantum Dot", "Velk\u00fd rozm\u011br", "Obnovovac\u00ed frekvence", "Lednov\u00fd veletrh", "HP Omen", "Mal\u00e1 \u00fahlop\u0159\u00ed\u010dka", "OLED", "Barevn\u00fd profil"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/chrome-zacal-blokovat-nejotravnejsi-reklamy-na-webu/sc-3-a-191840/default.aspx", "title": "Chrome za\u010dal blokovat nejotravn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed reklamy na webu", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "16. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Google zapo\u010dal boj za lep\u0161\u00ed web bez otravn\u00fdch reklam. B\u011bhem v\u010derej\u0161ka se u\u017eivatel\u016fm aktivovalo blokov\u00e1n\u00ed t\u011bch inzertn\u00edch prvk\u016f, kter\u00e9 neprojdou parametry stanoven\u00fdmi organizac\u00ed . Prim\u00e1rn\u011b p\u016fjde o automaticky spou\u0161t\u011bn\u00e1 videa se zvukem, celostr\u00e1nkov\u00e9 reklamy s odpo\u010dtem, nebo p\u0159ilepen\u00e9 plochy, kter\u00e9 se posunuj\u00ed spole\u010dn\u011b s rolov\u00e1n\u00edm a p\u0159ekr\u00fdvaj\u00ed samotn\u00fd obsah webu.Funkce je od nyn\u011bj\u0161ka zapnut\u00e1 ve v\u00fdchoz\u00edm stavu a u\u017eivatel ji m\u016f\u017ee deaktivovat v  a sekci . Blokov\u00e1n\u00ed bude na pozad\u00ed prob\u00edhat do jist\u00e9 m\u00edry podobn\u011b jako v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch blokovac\u00edch dopl\u0148k\u016f.P\u0159i otev\u0159en\u00ed webu Chrome ov\u011b\u0159\u00ed, zda se nach\u00e1z\u00ed na \u010dern\u00e9 listin\u011b samotn\u00e9ho Googlu. Pro tyhle p\u0159\u00edpady p\u0159ibyla do komponenty nov\u00e1 polo\u017eka . Pokud web je na tomto blacklistu, pou\u017eije Chrome pro anal\u00fdzu reklam ve\u0159ejn\u011b seznamy a , kter\u00e9 jsou vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1ny pr\u00e1v\u011b b\u011b\u017en\u00fdmi dopl\u0148ky pro blokov\u00e1n\u00ed reklamy. Prvn\u00ed z nich se zam\u011b\u0159uje na viditelnou inzerci, druh\u00fd potom na sledovac\u00ed skripty nap\u0159\u00ed\u010d webem. D\u00edky nim Chrome zjist\u00ed, odkud jsou reklamy stahov\u00e1ny a zablokuje je.Na stran\u011b u\u017eivatele se v takov\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b zobraz\u00ed upozorn\u011bn\u00ed v adresn\u00edm \u0159\u00e1dku, kde se nach\u00e1z\u00ed i mo\u017enost na konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed str\u00e1nce povolit na\u010dten\u00ed v\u0161ech reklam. V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b Androidu se informace o zablokov\u00e1n\u00ed inzerce objev\u00ed u spodn\u00edho okraje displeje. Chrome pro iOS zat\u00edm blokov\u00e1n\u00ed reklam nenab\u00eddne.Seznamy web\u016f, a\u0165 u\u017e t\u011bch z blacklistu Googlu nebo ve\u0159ejn\u00fdch seznam\u016f jsou pr\u016fb\u011b\u017en\u011b stahov\u00e1ny automaticky. Stejn\u011b tak lze ale jejich aktualizaci vynutit ru\u010dn\u011b. K tomu sta\u010d\u00ed zam\u00ed\u0159it na str\u00e1nku chrome://components a zde  u polo\u017eky .", "tags": ["Google", "Web", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "Chrome", "Android", "Reklama", "Otravn\u00e1 reklama", "Blokov\u00e1n\u00ed reklamy", "Ve\u0159ejn\u00fd seznam", "Nov\u00e1 polo\u017eka", "Celostr\u00e1nkov\u00e1 reklama", "Spou\u0161t\u011bn\u00e9 video", "Jist\u00e1 m\u00edra", "Blokov\u00e1n\u00ed", "V\u00fdchoz\u00ed stav", "Safe Browsing", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Rolov\u00e1n\u00ed", "B\u011b\u017en\u00fd dopln\u011bk", "\u010cern\u00e1 listina", "Coalition for Better ADS", "Spodn\u00ed okraj", "Dobr\u00fd web", "Ctrl", "Obsah"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/dickman-chce-6-miliard-dolaru-na-jeho-notebooku-se-nezdaril-upgrade-na-desitky/sc-3-a-191841/default.aspx", "title": "Dickman chce 6 miliard dolar\u016f. Na jeho notebooku se nezda\u0159il upgrade na Des\u00edtky ", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "15. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Frank Dickman z Albuquerque v Nov\u00e9m Mexiku si v minulosti koupil notebook Asus X54L s OEM licenc\u00ed Windows 7 a pozd\u011bji p\u0159e\u0161el na Windows 10. Upgrade na nov\u00fd syst\u00e9m v\u0161ak nedopadl dob\u0159e.Takov\u00e9 v\u011bci se bohu\u017eel ob\u010das st\u00e1vaj\u00ed, o Dickmanovi v\u0161ak p\u0159esto napsala velk\u00e1 technologick\u00e1 m\u00e9dia, proto\u017ee nam\u00edsto toho, aby skrze podporu Asusu z\u00edskal Windows 7 zp\u011bt (nebo si je ),  Microsoft a jeho \u0161\u00e9fa Satyu Nadellu.Dickman je typick\u00fd p\u0159\u00edklad  \u2013 tentokr\u00e1t v podob\u011b fyzick\u00e9 osoby a nikoliv pr\u00e1vnick\u00e9, kter\u00fd ke v\u0161emu pat\u0159i\u010dn\u00fd dokument vyplnil \u0161patn\u011b (schv\u00e1ln\u011b?), a tak se j\u00edm nyn\u00ed bav\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st internetu.Dickman toti\u017e \u00fadajnou \u00fajmu ocenil na 600 milion\u016f dolar\u016f (!), jen\u017ee v dokumentu napsal o nulu v\u00edce, a tak nyn\u00ed \u017ealuje Microsoft o rovn\u00fdch  (PDF) za to, \u017ee mu redmondsk\u00e1 podpora nechce nainstalovat na po\u010d\u00edta\u010d zp\u011bt Windows 7. Mimochodem, Dickman nevyu\u017eil podporu Asusu, proto\u017ee ji pr\u00fd ned\u016fv\u011b\u0159uje.Tu\u0161\u00edme, \u017ee v tomto p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b soud smete celou kauzu ze stolu.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows 10", "USA", "Windows 7", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Asus", "Soudy", "Mexiko", "Notebook", "Typick\u00fd p\u0159\u00edklad", "Fyzick\u00e1 osoba", "Nov\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Satyu Nadellu", "Cel\u00e1 kauza", "Albuquerque", "Margin", "Podpora", "Dolar", "Nov\u00e9 Mexiko", "Miliarda dolar\u016f"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/homepod-muze-poskodit-dreveny-nabytek-apple-ma-reseni-nestavet-ho-na-dreveny-nabytek/sc-3-a-191839/default.aspx", "title": "Homepod m\u016f\u017ee po\u0161kodit d\u0159ev\u011bn\u00fd n\u00e1bytek. Apple m\u00e1 \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed: nestav\u011bt ho na d\u0159ev\u011bn\u00fd n\u00e1bytek", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "15. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Co v\u00edme o reproduktoru Homepod od Applu: hraje perfektn\u011b \u2013 srovnateln\u011b s Hi-Fi reproduktory s o n\u011bkolik tis\u00edc vy\u0161\u0161\u00ed cenou, vestav\u011bn\u00e1 Siri toho um\u00ed  a oprava za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed . Nyn\u00ed se p\u0159id\u00e1v\u00e1 probl\u00e9m, na kter\u00fd nar\u00e1\u017e\u00ed prvn\u00ed u\u017eivatel\u00e9 repr\u00e1ku \u2013 zanech\u00e1v\u00e1 dob\u0159e patrn\u00e9 stopy na d\u0159ev\u011bn\u00e9m n\u00e1bytku, kter\u00fd je o\u0161et\u0159en vrstvou na b\u00e1zi oleje.P\u0159i recenzov\u00e1n\u00ed na to narazili nap\u0159\u00edklad na webu  a webem se \u0161\u00ed\u0159\u00ed i dal\u0161\u00ed fotky od b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch u\u017eivatel\u016f.Apple zareagoval sv\u00fdm typick\u00fdm zp\u016fsobem. Vysv\u011btlil, \u017ee jde o b\u011b\u017enou reakci zp\u016fsobenou silikonov\u00fdmi podlo\u017ekami reproduktoru, kterou umoc\u0148uj\u00ed vibrace. Skvrny sice set\u0159\u00edt nejdou, ale m\u011bly by podle Applu po n\u011bjak\u00e9m \u010dase zmizet. Z\u00e1rove\u0148 ale u\u017eivatel\u016fm doporu\u010duje, aby Homepod um\u00edstili na jin\u00fd povrch. Na str\u00e1nce  dod\u00e1v\u00e1, \u017ee to pro reproduktory se silikonov\u00fdmi podlo\u017ekami nen\u00ed neobvykl\u00e9.Applu bychom s p\u0159iv\u0159en\u00edm obou o\u010d\u00ed odpustili to, \u017ee za\u010dal prod\u00e1vat produkt i s t\u00edmto probl\u00e9mem, o kter\u00e9m musel v\u011bd\u011bt. Je ale zar\u00e1\u017eej\u00edc\u00ed, \u017ee se PR odd\u011blen\u00ed nepou\u010dilo z ned\u00e1vn\u00e9ho fiaska t\u00fdkaj\u00edc\u00ed se omezov\u00e1n\u00ed v\u00fdkonu iPhon\u016f kv\u016fli st\u00e1rnut\u00ed bateri\u00ed. Stejn\u011b jako v tomto p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b Apple nedok\u00e1zal o chyb\u011b informovat dop\u0159edu a \u010dekal a\u017e na okam\u017eik, jestli se za\u010dne \u0159e\u0161it v m\u00e9di\u00edch.", "tags": ["Apple", "Homepod", "iPhone", "Siri", "Podlo\u017eka", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Typick\u00fd zp\u016fsob", "Prvn\u00ed u\u017eivatel", "Margin", "Reproduktor", "B\u011b\u017en\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "N\u00e1bytek"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-rozsiruje-platformu-amp-vyhledavani-ziska-dalsi-klon-snapchat-stories-a-e-maily-budou-interaktivni/sc-3-a-191796/default.aspx", "title": "Google roz\u0161i\u0159uje platformu AMP. Vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed z\u00edsk\u00e1 dal\u0161\u00ed klon Snapchat Stories a e-maily budou interaktivn\u00ed", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "16. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Platforma AMP, tedy accelerated mobile pages, je vyv\u00edjena Googlem jako open source a zam\u011b\u0159uje se na rychl\u00e9 na\u010d\u00edt\u00e1n\u00ed obsahu na mobiln\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edch. Pro b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 webov\u00e9 str\u00e1nky vytv\u00e1\u0159\u00ed speci\u00e1ln\u00ed verzi, na kterou je u\u017eivatel p\u0159esm\u011brov\u00e1n m\u00edsto klasick\u00e9ho webu. Nov\u011b technologie umo\u017en\u00ed i p\u0159id\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed Stories do vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed od Googlu a v  pro zm\u011bnu budou moci b\u00fdt interaktivn\u00ed e-maily. budou fungovat velmi podobn\u011b, jako P\u0159\u00edb\u011bhy v r\u00e1mci Facebooku \u010di Instagramu jen s t\u00edm rozd\u00edlem, \u017ee se budou objevovat ve vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed na Googlu a prozat\u00edm pouze od vybran\u00fdch a schv\u00e1len\u00fdch vydavatel\u016f. Technologii jako takovou ale m\u016f\u017ee vyu\u017e\u00edt kdokoliv.Funk\u010dn\u011b se jedn\u00e1 o prezentaci za sebou jdouc\u00edch obrazovek p\u0159es cel\u00fd displej, kter\u00e9 mohou b\u00fdt vypln\u011bny obr\u00e1zky, textem \u010di animacemi, v\u0161e se zam\u011b\u0159en\u00edm na mobiln\u00ed telefony. Jedn\u00e1 se tak o snahu p\u0159ibl\u00ed\u017eit obsah zejm\u00e9na mlad\u00fdm lidem, kte\u0159\u00ed si obl\u00edbili pr\u00e1v\u011b Snapchat a jednoduchou, barevnou, formu pod\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed informac\u00ed.pak bude fungovat v r\u00e1mci Gmailu. Umo\u017en\u00ed vytv\u00e1\u0159et interaktivn\u00ed e-maily, d\u00edky kter\u00fdm bude mo\u017en\u00e9 si p\u0159idat rovnou upom\u00ednku do kalend\u00e1\u0159e \u010di proklikat aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed nab\u00eddky ubytov\u00e1n\u00ed. Obsah bude moci b\u00fdt aktualizov\u00e1n, dopadne tedy situace, \u017ee p\u0159\u00edjemce si zobrazuje ji\u017e neplatn\u00e9 nab\u00eddky.AMP Stories i AMP for Email jsou aktu\u00e1ln\u011b v uzav\u0159en\u00e9m testov\u00e1n\u00ed, s jejich \u0161ir\u0161\u00edm nasazen\u00edm se po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 v pr\u016fb\u011bhu roku. V\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159i se ale ji\u017e nyn\u00ed mohou pod\u00edvat na  a p\u0159ipravit vlastn\u00ed newslettery a str\u00e1nky.", "tags": ["Google", "Facebook", "Open source", "Instagram", "Vyhled\u00e1va\u010de", "Mobiln\u00ed telefon", "Gmail", "E-mail", "Cel\u00fd displej", "AMP", "Speci\u00e1ln\u00ed verze", "Klon", "Snapchat Stories", "Stories", "\u0160irok\u00e9 nasazen\u00ed", "Margin", "Obsah", "Uzav\u0159en\u00e9 testov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Mobiln\u00ed za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "P\u0159\u00edjemce", "Vyhled\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed", "Platforma", "Mlad\u00fd \u010dlov\u011bk", "Rychl\u00e9 na\u010d\u00edt\u00e1n\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/fotky-z-mobilu-do-pocitace-s-windows-10-ted-uz-to-jde-i-bez-cloudu/sc-3-a-191835/default.aspx", "title": "Fotky z mobilu do po\u010d\u00edta\u010de s Windows 10: te\u010f u\u017e to jde i bez cloudu", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "16. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "V minul\u00e9m roce Microsoft p\u0159edeslal, \u017ee chyst\u00e1 aplikaci pro chytr\u00e9 telefony, kter\u00e1 umo\u017en\u00ed snadn\u00fd p\u0159enos fotografi\u00ed do po\u010d\u00edta\u010de. Ta nyn\u00ed vych\u00e1z\u00ed pro Android a iOS a umo\u017en\u00ed sd\u00edlen\u00ed skrze Wi-Fi, obejde se tedy bez synchronizace s cloudem. je dostupn\u00e1 i v \u010cesku a po sp\u00e1rov\u00e1n\u00ed s aplikac\u00ed  na po\u010d\u00edta\u010di za pomoci QR k\u00f3du umo\u017en\u00ed odeslat vybran\u00e9 soubory. K\u00f3d pro naskenov\u00e1n\u00ed naleznete na po\u010d\u00edta\u010di pod polo\u017ekou Import \u2013 Skrze Wi-Fi. Jedinou podm\u00ednkou je, aby telefon i po\u010d\u00edta\u010d byli na stejn\u00e9 s\u00edti. Aplikace je tak men\u0161\u00ed n\u00e1hradou pro ty, kte\u0159\u00ed nevyu\u017e\u00edvaj\u00ed synchronizaci fotografi\u00ed skrze \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b . Odtud si je toti\u017e Fotky um\u00ed vyt\u00e1hnout automaticky.Aplikaci stahujte pro Android z  a iOS z .P\u0159enos soubor\u016f si m\u016f\u017eete prohl\u00e9dnout v \u010dase 0:40:", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Cloud", "Windows 10", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "Android", "iOS", "App Store", "Fotky", "Wi-Fi", "Fotografov\u00e1n\u00ed", "K\u00f3d", "Mobil", "Minul\u00fd rok", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Jedin\u00e1 podm\u00ednka", "Aplikace", "Synchronizace", "Chytr\u00fd telefon", "Import", "Stejn\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165", "Snadn\u00fd p\u0159enos", "Fotka", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Vybran\u00fd soubor"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/vlc-30-je-hotove-legendarni-prehravac-nabizi-hromadu-novinek/sc-3-a-191791/default.aspx", "title": "VLC 3.0 je hotov\u00e9! Legend\u00e1rn\u00ed p\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010d nab\u00edz\u00ed hromadu novinek", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "13. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Vychla\u010fte \u0161ampus a p\u0159ipravte chleb\u00ed\u010dky, VLC se toti\u017e po letech p\u0159\u00edprav kone\u010dn\u011b do\u010dkalo fin\u00e1ln\u00ed verze . Pokud v\u00e1s to jako na\u0161eho kolegu Davida Polesn\u00e9ho nechalo zcela chladn\u00fdm, v\u011bzte, \u017ee VLC pat\u0159\u00ed k nejpopul\u00e1rn\u011bj\u0161\u00edm alternativn\u00edm a multiplatformn\u00edm multimedi\u00e1ln\u00edm p\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010d\u016fm.Vyzna\u010duje se na jednu stranu sv\u00fdm spart\u00e1nsk\u00fdm rozhran\u00edm (mo\u017eno vylep\u0161it skiny), ale z\u00e1rove\u0148 neskute\u010dn\u00fdm mno\u017estv\u00edm nastaven\u00ed v nitru. A samoz\u0159ejm\u011b plej\u00e1dou funkc\u00ed.A pak je tu samoz\u0159ejm\u011b hromada dal\u0161\u00edch specialit pro n\u00e1ro\u010dn\u00e9 videogeeky. V\u00fdvoj VLC 3.0 trval opravdu dlouho \u2013 zejm\u00e9na podporu Chromecastu auto\u0159i slibovali cel\u00e9 roky, nicm\u00e9n\u011b byla k dispozici pouze v testovac\u00edch verz\u00edch. VLC 3.0 je k dispozici pro Windows, macOS, Linux a dal\u0161\u00ed platformy.", "tags": ["Software", "Windows", "Linux", "Chromecast", "Hudba, filmy, seri\u00e1ly", "VLC", "Multim\u00e9dia", "HDR", "P\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010d", "Cel\u00fd rok", "David Polesn\u00fd", "Neskute\u010dn\u00e9 mno\u017estv\u00ed", "Hardwarov\u00e9 dek\u00f3dov\u00e1n\u00ed", "P\u0159ehr\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed", "Testovac\u00ed verze", "Fin\u00e1ln\u00ed verze", "SMB", "Novinka", "Legend\u00e1rn\u00ed p\u0159ehr\u00e1va\u010d", "Hromada", "S\u00ed\u0165ov\u00fd zdroj", "Hlavn\u00ed novinka"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/snapchat-potrebuje-prilakat-osobnosti-i-inzerenty-poskytne-proto-vice-dat-o-uzivatelich-site/sc-3-a-191846/default.aspx", "title": "Snapchat pot\u0159ebuje p\u0159il\u00e1kat osobnosti i inzerenty, poskytne proto v\u00edce dat o u\u017eivatel\u00edch s\u00edt\u011b", "author": "Mark\u00e9ta Mike\u0161ov\u00e1", "date": "16. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "A\u0165 jste slavn\u00e1 osobnost s miliony sleduj\u00edc\u00edmi, nebo oby\u010dejn\u00fd \u010dlov\u011bk s p\u00e1r kamar\u00e1dy, informace o sv\u00fdch p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvc\u00edch jste dote\u010f na Snapchatu m\u011bli stejn\u00e9. V podstat\u011b jste mohli jen zjistit, kolik lid\u00ed p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky vid\u011blo. To se te\u010f zm\u011bn\u00ed \u2013 slu\u017eba lidem s nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00edm po\u010dtem sleduj\u00edc\u00edch poskytne v\u00edce dat.Informoval o tom web . Snapchat podle n\u011bj novinku chyst\u00e1 pro des\u00edtky tis\u00edc u\u017eivatel\u016f, kte\u0159\u00ed pat\u0159\u00ed mezi ty nejpopul\u00e1rn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed. Mezi nimi mohou b\u00fdt jak slavn\u00e9 osobnosti, tak influence\u0159i ze soci\u00e1ln\u00edch s\u00edt\u00ed. Tito u\u017eivatel\u00e9 vedle toho, \u017ee zjist\u00ed kolik lid\u00ed p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvky vid\u011blo, dostanou nov\u011b informace o demografick\u00fdch charakteristik\u00e1ch jako je jejich v\u011bk, pohlav\u00ed, bydli\u0161t\u011b nebo preferovan\u00e1 t\u00e9mata.Nen\u00ed ale asi p\u0159ekvapiv\u00e9, \u017ee Snapchat v\u011bc nezav\u00e1d\u00ed z dobroty du\u0161e. C\u00edlem je p\u0159il\u00e1kat v\u00edce reklam. Jakmile toti\u017e budou nejobl\u00edben\u011bj\u0161\u00ed lid\u00e9 p\u0159esn\u011b v\u011bd\u011bt, jak\u00e9 maj\u00ed publik\u016fm, mohou l\u00e9pe vyjedn\u00e1vat reklamn\u00ed zak\u00e1zky. Ned\u011bl\u00e1 to sice ze Snapchatu extra skv\u011blou aplikaci, ale m\u016f\u017ee to b\u00fdt d\u016fvod, jak n\u011bkter\u00e9 influencery d\u00e9le udr\u017eet od p\u0159echodu na Instagram.Snapchat by t\u00edm tak\u00e9 z dlouhodob\u00e9ho hlediska mohl z\u00edskat i p\u00e1r nov\u00fdch u\u017eivatel\u016f, co\u017e je v\u011bc, se kterou slu\u017eba bojuje. Bez popul\u00e1rn\u00edch tv\u016frc\u016f bude toti\u017e jen um\u00edrat a mlad\u00ed lid\u00e9 si tam cestu jen tak nenajdou. Tak\u00e9 firmy mohou j\u00e1sat, \u017ee kone\u010dn\u011b za\u010dnou disponovat v\u011bt\u0161\u00edm mno\u017estv\u00ed informac\u00ed o tom, kdo vlastn\u011b nav\u0161t\u011bvuje Snapchat.Vedle demografick\u00fdch \u00fadaj\u016f se tv\u016frci dozv\u00ed kolika minutami lid\u00e9 str\u00e1vili sledov\u00e1n\u00ed p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f za t\u00fdden, m\u011bs\u00edc a rok, pr\u016fm\u011brn\u00fd \u010das str\u00e1ven\u00fd sledov\u00e1n\u00edm a dosah mezi sleduj\u00edc\u00edmi.", "tags": ["Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Snapchat", "Instagram", "Sledov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Data", "Demografick\u00fd \u00fadaj", "U\u017eivatel\u00e9", "Inzerent", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165", "Dlouhodob\u00e9 hledisko", "Web recode", "P\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvek", "Nov\u00fd u\u017eivatel", "Mlad\u00ed lid\u00e9", "Popul\u00e1rn\u00ed tv\u016frce", "Mlad\u00fd \u010dlov\u011bk", "Oby\u010dejn\u00fd \u010dlov\u011bk", "Skv\u011bl\u00e1 aplikace", "Osobnost", "Pr\u016fm\u011brn\u00fd \u010das", "U\u017eivatel s\u00edt\u011b", "S\u00ed\u0165"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/nvidia-chce-vratit-herni-grafiky-hracum-planuje-specialni-tezebni-cipy-turing/sc-3-a-191850/default.aspx", "title": "Nvidia chce vr\u00e1tit hern\u00ed grafiky hr\u00e1\u010d\u016fm. Pl\u00e1nuje speci\u00e1ln\u00ed t\u011b\u017eebn\u00ed \u010dipy Turing", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "16. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Nvidia ozn\u00e1mila rekordn\u00ed finan\u010dn\u00ed \u010dtvrtlet\u00ed a za cel\u00fd rok 2017 vyk\u00e1zala \u010dist\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edjmy ve v\u00fd\u0161i t\u0159\u00ed miliard dolar\u016f. V\u00fdznamn\u00fd pod\u00edl na velk\u00e9m meziro\u010dn\u00edm zlep\u0161en\u00ed m\u00e1 i segment kryptom\u011bn, kter\u00fd je aktu\u00e1ln\u011b bezedn\u00fdm odbyti\u0161t\u011bm grafick\u00fdch karet.Z kr\u00e1tkodob\u00e9ho hlediska je to pro Nvidii zlat\u00fd d\u016fl, z toho dlouhodob\u00e9ho to ale nemus\u00ed b\u00fdt udr\u017eiteln\u00fd stav. V\u00ed to rovn\u011b\u017e CEO firmy Jen-Hsun Huang. Ten minul\u00fd t\u00fdden na konferenci pro investory mluvil o tom, \u017ee kryptom\u011bny jsou re\u00e1ln\u00e1 v\u011bc, kter\u00e1 jen tak nezmiz\u00ed. Z\u00e1rove\u0148 ale dodal, \u017ee hr\u00e1\u010di jsou pro Nvidii v segmentu grafick\u00fdch karet d\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed a podnikne ve\u0161ker\u00e9 kroky pro zlep\u0161en\u00ed dostupnosti produkt\u016f. Firma nejd\u0159\u00edv trochu neur\u010dit\u011b doporu\u010dila obchodn\u00edk\u016fm, aby up\u0159ednost\u0148ovali hr\u00e1\u010de p\u0159ed t\u011b\u017ea\u0159i. Nyn\u00ed to ale vypad\u00e1 na mnohem v\u00fdrazn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed po\u010din \u2013 vlastn\u00ed t\u011b\u017ea\u0159sk\u00fd \u010dip. M\u011bl by n\u00e9st jm\u00e9no Turing.Reuters tento t\u00fdden vydal zpr\u00e1vu o tom, \u017ee Nvidia pl\u00e1nuje dal\u0161\u00ed architekturu s k\u00f3dov\u00fdm ozna\u010den\u00edm Turing. Jen\u017ee nov\u00e9 grafiky \u0159ady GTX 20XX ponesou s velkou pravd\u011bpodobnost\u00ed jm\u00e9no Ampere. Ani Turing v\u0161ak nen\u00ed v\u00fdmysl a jeho existenci nyn\u00ed potvrdil web , nep\u016fjde v\u0161ak o b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 grafiky, ale speci\u00e1ln\u00ed \u010dipy pr\u00e1v\u011b pro t\u011b\u017ea\u0159e.C\u00edl Nvidie je jasn\u00fd \u2013 vyrobit takovou kartu, kter\u00e1 bude efektivn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed na obou konc\u00edch cel\u00e9ho \u0159et\u011bzce. Mus\u00ed b\u00fdt tedy levn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed p\u0159i samotn\u00e9 v\u00fdrob\u011b a z\u00e1rove\u0148 mus\u00ed nab\u00eddnou ni\u017e\u0161\u00ed koncovou cenu pro t\u011b\u017ea\u0159e. V\u00fdkon p\u0159i t\u011b\u017eb\u011b by p\u0159itom m\u011bl b\u00fdt minim\u00e1ln\u011b srovnateln\u00fd s aktu\u00e1ln\u00ed generac\u00ed standardn\u00edch grafik.Pokud by se n\u011bco takov\u00e9ho povedlo, mohla by cel\u00e1 anab\u00e1ze s nedostatkem hern\u00edch grafik dopadnout podobn\u011b jako p\u0159ed \u010dty\u0159mi lety. Tehdy byly nahrazeny beznad\u011bjn\u011b vyprodan\u00e9 karty Radeon R9 jedno\u00fa\u010delov\u00fdmi ASIC \u010dipy. V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b Nvidie se samoz\u0159ejm\u011b bude jednat o v\u00fdpo\u010detn\u00ed kartu, kter\u00e1 bude b\u011b\u017en\u011b pou\u017eiteln\u00e1 pro t\u011b\u017ebu kter\u00e9koliv kryptom\u011bny, nejen jedn\u00e9 konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed, pro jej\u00ed\u017e algoritmus je vyr\u00e1b\u011bn ASIC.Dal\u0161\u00ed parametry ani p\u0159\u00edpadn\u00fd form\u00e1t, v jak\u00e9m bude Nvidia t\u011b\u017ea\u0159sk\u00e9 karty produkovat, samoz\u0159ejm\u011b nezn\u00e1me. Podobn\u011b jako u hern\u00edch karet nov\u00e9 \u0159ady v\u0161ak m\u016f\u017eeme spol\u00e9hat na konferenci GTC, kterou Nvidia po\u0159\u00e1d\u00e1 na konci b\u0159ezna. Pr\u00e1v\u011b tam bychom se m\u011bli o nov\u00fdch kart\u00e1ch pro hran\u00ed i t\u011b\u017ebu dozv\u011bd\u011bt.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Kryptom\u011bny", "Nvidia", "T\u011b\u017eba", "Ampere", "Cel\u00fd rok", "Grafick\u00e1 karta", "Kart", "Nov\u00e1 \u0159ada", "V\u00fdpo\u010detn\u00ed karta", "Grafika", "ASIC", "V\u00fdznamn\u00fd pod\u00edl", "Reuters", "Segment", "\u010cist\u00fd p\u0159\u00edjem", "Alan Turing", "K\u00f3dov\u00e9 ozna\u010den\u00ed", "Dolar", "Speci\u00e1ln\u00ed \u010dip", "\u010cip", "Cel\u00fd \u0159et\u011bzec", "T\u011b\u017ea\u0159", "Nov\u00e1 grafika", "Nov\u00e1 karta"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/apple-music-za-69-korun-pro-studenty-uz-i-v-cesku/sc-3-a-191794/default.aspx", "title": "Apple Music za 69 korun? Pro studenty u\u017e i v \u010cesku", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "13. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Apple dnes v r\u00e1mci dal\u0161\u00edch zem\u00ed zavedl mo\u017enost p\u0159edplatit si hudebn\u00ed slu\u017ebu Music v r\u00e1mci studentsk\u00e9ho tarifu. Ten stoj\u00ed 69 korun na m\u011bs\u00edc, tedy m\u00e9n\u011b ne\u017e polovinu z\u00e1kladn\u00edho tarifu.Nab\u00eddka je ur\u010dena vysoko\u0161kolsk\u00fdm student\u016fm, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e je vy\u017eadov\u00e1no ov\u011b\u0159en\u00ed prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm organizace Unidays. To je pot\u0159eba prov\u00e9st p\u0159i v\u00fdb\u011bru tarifu v r\u00e1mci iTunes nebo aplikace Music v iOS. P\u0159i p\u0159\u00edm\u00e9 n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bv\u011b webu dostanete pouze zpr\u00e1vu o tom, \u017ee slu\u017eba Unidays nen\u00ed v \u010cesku podporov\u00e1na. Po ov\u011b\u0159en\u00ed je hudebn\u00ed slu\u017eba zv\u00fdhodn\u011bna a\u017e na \u010dty\u0159i roky.Apple tak dotahuje Spotify, kter\u00e9 nab\u00edz\u00ed studentsk\u00fd tarif ji\u017e del\u0161\u00ed dobu. \u00da\u010dtuje si za n\u011bj 3 eura, aktu\u00e1ln\u011b tedy asi 76 korun.", "tags": ["Apple", "Hudba, filmy, seri\u00e1ly", "Spotify", "\u010cesko", "Apple Music", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Vysoko\u0161kolsk\u00fd student", "Euro", "Ov\u011b\u0159en\u00ed", "Stud", "Music", "Dlouh\u00e1 doba", "Koruna", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed tarif", "Studenti", "R\u00e1mec", "Hudebn\u00ed slu\u017eba", "Tarif"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/amd-zacalo-prodavat-nejlepsi-apu-za-2600-korun-nabizi-procesor-s-grafikou-pro-zakladni-hrani/sc-3-a-191788/default.aspx", "title": "AMD za\u010dalo prod\u00e1vat nejlep\u0161\u00ed APU. Za 2600 korun nab\u00edz\u00ed procesor s grafikou pro z\u00e1kladn\u00ed hran\u00ed", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "13. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "AMD dnes za\u010dalo prod\u00e1vat dvojici APU postaven\u00fdch na CPU Ryzen a grafick\u00fdch j\u00e1drech Vega. \u00dato\u010d\u00ed nejen velmi v\u00fdhodnou cenou, ale p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm v\u00fdkonem, kter\u00fd v t\u00e9to kategorii p\u0159edv\u00e1d\u00ed integrovan\u00e1 GPU.Oba procesory jsou postaveny na Ryzenu, kter\u00fd zn\u00e1me z jeho mobiln\u00ed verze. V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b dra\u017e\u0161\u00edho modelu  jde o \u010dip v jeho maxim\u00e1ln\u00ed konfiguraci. Nab\u00edz\u00ed tedy \u010dty\u0159i j\u00e1dra a d\u00edky SMT osm v\u00fdpo\u010detn\u00edch jader. Z\u00e1kladn\u00edm taktem je 3,6 GHz a o 300 MHz v\u00edc v boostu. O grafick\u00fd v\u00fdkon se potom star\u00e1 Vega 11 se z\u00e1kladn\u00edm taktem 1 250 MHz. Za tento model chce AMD .Druh\u00fdm modelem je , kter\u00fd se na stran\u011b procesoru li\u0161\u00ed p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm absenc\u00ed SMT. Nab\u00edz\u00ed tedy \u010dty\u0159i j\u00e1dra na z\u00e1kladn\u00ed frekvenci 3,5 GHz a v boostu nab\u00eddne 3,7 GHz. Podobn\u011b jako dra\u017e\u0161\u00ed model je i zde k dispozici tzv. Precision boost, kter\u00fd um\u00ed rovnom\u011brn\u011b zv\u00fd\u0161it v\u00fdkon v\u0161ech jader. AMD tady pou\u017eilo GPU Vega 8 s taktem 1 100 MHz. AMD vsadilo na velmi agresivn\u00ed cenovku \u2013 99 dolar\u016f. V tuzemsk\u00fdch e-shopech tak vyjde na n\u011bjak\u00fdch .K dispozici m\u00e1me prvn\u00ed srovn\u00e1vac\u00ed testy, kter\u00e9 ukazuj\u00ed, \u017ee se tyhle procesory opravdu povedly. Rozhodn\u011b jde o nejlep\u0161\u00ed APU, kter\u00e1 kdy AMD vydalo. P\u0159\u00edmou konkurenc\u00ed jsou procesory Core i3-7100 a v p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b n\u011bkter\u00fdch test\u016f rovn\u011b\u017e Core i5-7400. V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b v\u00edcevl\u00e1knov\u00e9ho v\u00fdkonu m\u00e1 navrch op\u011bt AMD, z \u010deho\u017e t\u011b\u017e\u00ed p\u0159i v\u011bt\u0161in\u011b test\u016f z re\u00e1ln\u00e9ho nasazen\u00ed.Je\u0161t\u011b o kus zaj\u00edmav\u011bj\u0161\u00ed je potom grafick\u00e1 \u010d\u00e1st. Ta toti\u017e i u levn\u011bj\u0161\u00edho modelu s Vegou 8 nab\u00edz\u00ed velmi podobn\u00fd v\u00fdkon jako lowendov\u00e1 GT 1030 od Nvidie. Nap\u0159\u00edklad v Battlefieldu 1 nam\u011b\u0159il web  p\u0159i testov\u00e1n\u00ed pr\u016fm\u011brn\u00fdch 50,2 FPS. Kombinace Core i3-7100 a GT 1030 potom b\u011b\u017eela s pr\u016fm\u011brnou sn\u00edmkovac\u00ed frekvenc\u00ed 52,3 FPS. Jen\u017ee stoj\u00ed o 2 000 korun v\u00edc.Testy webu  potom ukazuj\u00ed, \u017ee jde v tuto chv\u00edli o zdaleka nejv\u00fdkonn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed integrovan\u00e1 \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed. P\u0159i nejni\u017e\u0161\u00edch detailech b\u011b\u017e\u00ed Overwatch na v\u00fdkonn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed variant\u011b 2400G ve Full HD kolem 87 FPS, posledn\u00ed Assasin`s Creed kolem 41 FPS nebo Destiny 2 na 76 FPS.D\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed je, \u017ee p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 neztr\u00e1c\u00ed ani Ryzen 3 2200G s Vegou 8. Sn\u00edmkov\u00e9 frekvence se li\u0161\u00ed v \u0159\u00e1du jednotek a m\u016f\u017ee se tak jednat o z\u00e1klad pro velmi levnou hern\u00ed sestavu p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm pro online tituly.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Nvidia", "AMD", "Procesory", "AMD Zen", "Vega", "Levn\u00fd model", "Sn\u00edmkov\u00e1 frekvence", "Test", "Grafick\u00fd v\u00fdkon", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed hran\u00ed", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed takt", "Drah\u00fd model", "Podobn\u00fd v\u00fdkon", "Mobiln\u00ed verze", "SMT", "Druh\u00fd model", "Full HD", "Re\u00e1ln\u00e9 nasazen\u00ed", "Grafick\u00e1 \u010d\u00e1st", "V\u00fdpo\u010detn\u00ed j\u00e1dro", "GPU Vega", "Maxim\u00e1ln\u00ed konfigurace", "V\u00edcevl\u00e1knov\u00fd v\u00fdkon", "P\u0159\u00edm\u00e1 konkurence"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jak-planovat-pres-internet/sc-3-a-191861/default.aspx", "title": "Jak pl\u00e1novat pr\u030ces internet", "author": null, "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "\u010casto zapom\u00edn\u00e1te, co jste dneska cht\u011bli ud\u011blat? Na internetu si m\u016f\u017eete d\u011blat svoje pozn\u00e1mky. Vyu\u017e\u00edt toho m\u016f\u017eete tak\u00e9 v kolektivu t\u0159eba p\u0159i pl\u00e1nov\u00e1n\u00ed n\u011bjak\u00e9ho projektu. Jak na to se dozv\u00edte v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu. ", "tags": ["Internet", "Tipy", "Jak na Internet", "Pl\u00e1nov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Pozn\u00e1mka", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/mor-se-siri-novy-android-bude-nativne-podporovat-vykousnute-displeje/sc-3-a-191786/default.aspx", "title": "Mor se \u0161\u00ed\u0159\u00ed, nov\u00fd Android bude nativn\u011b podporovat vykousnut\u00e9 displeje", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "13. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Tento rok se do\u010dk\u00e1me nov\u00e9 verze Androidu s po\u0159adov\u00fdm \u010d\u00edslem 9 a p\u00edsmenn\u00fdm ozna\u010den\u00edm P. Ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed seznam novinek se dozv\u00edme z\u0159ejm\u011b na ka\u017edoro\u010dn\u00ed konferenci , ji\u017e nyn\u00ed ale pronikaj\u00ed informace, na co nov\u00e9ho se m\u016f\u017eeme t\u011b\u0161it. Jednou z hlavn\u00edch novinek, krom pozm\u011bn\u011bn\u00e9ho designu, bude i ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed podpora vykrojen\u00fdch displej\u016f, kter\u00fd m\u016f\u017eete zn\u00e1t nap\u0159\u00edklad z .Google tak reaguje na v\u00fdrobce, kte\u0159\u00ed chystaj\u00ed p\u0159id\u00e1n\u00ed t\u011bchto v\u00fdb\u011b\u017ek\u016f, obsahuj\u00edc\u00edch r\u016fzn\u00e9 senzory a kamery, do displeje u sv\u00fdch model\u016f. Doposud jedin\u00fd masov\u011bji prod\u00e1van\u00fd telefon s Androidem a podobn\u00fdm z\u00e1\u0159ezem je Essential Phone, s t\u00edmto neduhem ale po\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 u sv\u00fdch nov\u00fdch telefon\u016f t\u0159eba i Huawei, kter\u00e9mu unikly prvn\u00ed sn\u00edmky nov\u00e9ho modelu . D\u00edky ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed podpo\u0159e tak nebude nutn\u00e9, aby v\u00fdrobci sami upravovali syst\u00e9m tak, aby po\u010d\u00edtal s chyb\u011bj\u00edc\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st\u00ed v notifika\u010dn\u00ed li\u0161t\u011b.Spole\u010dn\u011b s novou verz\u00ed syst\u00e9mu se do\u010dk\u00e1me je\u0161t\u011b v\u011bt\u0161\u00edho prov\u00e1z\u00e1n\u00ed s , kter\u00fd se dost\u00e1v\u00e1 do \u010d\u00edm d\u00e1l v\u00edce nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00edch produkt\u016f. Firma se chce tak\u00e9 zam\u011b\u0159it na zlep\u0161en\u00ed vizu\u00e1ln\u00edho dojmu ze syst\u00e9mu ve snaze zl\u00e1kat u\u017eivatele z konkuren\u010dn\u00edho iOS. Zde je ale nutno podotknout, \u017ee v\u011bt\u0161ina majitel\u016f telefonu s Androidem \u010dist\u00fd syst\u00e9m pod n\u00e1nosem n\u00e1staveb od v\u00fdrobc\u016f nikdy neuvid\u00ed.Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Google", "Android", "iPhone", "Aktualizace", "Huawei", "Nov\u00fd telefon", "Nov\u00fd model", "Displej", "Ka\u017edoro\u010dn\u00ed konference", "Google I/O", "Vizu\u00e1ln\u00ed dojem", "Nov\u00e1 verze", "Chyb\u011bj\u00edc\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st", "Pozm\u011bn\u011bn\u00fd design", "Mor", "Nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed produkt", "MobilMania", "Po\u0159adov\u00e9 \u010d\u00edslo", "Hlavn\u00ed novinka", "Neduh", "Notifika\u010dn\u00ed li\u0161ta", "\u010cist\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "V\u00fdrobce", "Bloomberg", "Prvn\u00ed sn\u00edmek"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/rozpitvany-homepod-takto-vypada-prvni-samostatny-reproduktor-applu-zevnitr/sc-3-a-191785/default.aspx", "title": "Rozpitvan\u00fd Homepod: takto vypad\u00e1 prvn\u00ed samostatn\u00fd reproduktor Applu zevnit\u0159", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Rozborky iPhon\u016f \u010di Macbook\u016f u\u017e jsou pom\u011brn\u011b nudn\u00e9, v\u011bt\u0161inu z pou\u017eit\u00fdch komponent dob\u0159e zn\u00e1me a p\u0159i jejich um\u00edst\u011bn\u00ed do \u00fatrob za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed toho Apple moc nov\u00e9ho nevym\u00fd\u0161l\u00ed. To se ale ned\u00e1 tvrdit o zbrusu nov\u00e9m reproduktoru Homepod. Ten nyn\u00ed rozebrali na  a odhalili, co se v n\u011bm ukr\u00fdv\u00e1.V\u011bt\u0161ina elektroniky je um\u00edst\u011bna pod horn\u00edm krytem, kter\u00fd je p\u0159ilepen \u0159\u00e1dnou vrstvou lepidla. Ta si proto vy\u017e\u00e1dala nah\u0159\u00e1n\u00ed a pot\u00e9 n\u00e1siln\u00e9 odtr\u017een\u00ed. Kryt je z\u00e1rove\u0148 difus\u00e9rem pro sv\u011btlo z LED diod, kter\u00e9 signalizuj\u00ed pracuj\u00edc\u00ed asistentku Siri. T\u00edm iFixit definitivn\u011b vyvr\u00e1til spekulace o tom, \u017ee Homepod obsahuje OLED displej, kter\u00fd v budoucnu nab\u00eddne zobrazov\u00e1n\u00ed b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 grafiky jako jsou ikony. To se rozhodn\u011b nestane, magick\u00e9 vlny jsou tvo\u0159eny jen vhodn\u011b rozpt\u00fdlen\u00fdm sv\u011btlem z devaten\u00e1cti RGB diod.Pod nimi se ukr\u00fdv\u00e1 hlavn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st elektroniky, tedy \u010dipset Apple A8 spole\u010dn\u011b s opera\u010dn\u00ed pam\u011bt\u00ed s kapacitou 1 GB. Pro samotn\u00fd syst\u00e9m a p\u0159\u00edpadn\u011b hudebn\u00ed cache je ur\u010dena pam\u011b\u0165 s kapacitou 16 GB. Do reproduktoru se tak dostalo stejn\u011b velk\u00e9 \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b, jako Apple je\u0161t\u011b p\u0159edloni montoval do prod\u00e1van\u00fdch iPhon\u016f.Mnohem slo\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00ed operaci si potom vy\u017e\u00e1dal p\u0159\u00edstup k samotn\u00e9mu basov\u00e9mu reproduktoru, stejn\u011b jako k sedmi men\u0161\u00edm m\u011bni\u010d\u016fm pro vy\u0161\u0161\u00ed frekven\u010dn\u00ed rozsah. Ka\u017ed\u00fd z nich je vybaven vlastn\u00edm zesilova\u010dem. Uprost\u0159ed se rovn\u011b\u017e nach\u00e1z\u00ed nap\u00e1jec\u00ed zdroj.I kv\u016fli tomu, \u017ee byla p\u0159i pitv\u011b pou\u017eita pilka, horkovzdu\u0161n\u00e1 pistole a skalpel pro roz\u0159\u00edznut\u00ed textiln\u00edho potahu, obdr\u017eel Homepod sk\u00f3re opravitelnosti 1/10. Jak\u00fdkoliv dom\u00e1c\u00ed z\u00e1sah je tak prakticky vylou\u010den.", "tags": ["Apple", "Hudba, filmy, seri\u00e1ly", "Homepod", "iPhone", "MacBook", "Horn\u00ed kryt", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed pam\u011b\u0165", "Nap\u00e1jec\u00ed zdroj", "Hlavn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st", "Nov\u00fd reproduktor", "Displej OLED", "Velk\u00e9 \u00falo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b", "Reproduktor", "Led dioda", "Kryt", "Pou\u017eit\u00e1 komponenta"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/nejnovejsi-prelet-dronem-nad-apple-parkem-uz-odhaluje-i-kola-pro-zamestnance/sc-3-a-191789/default.aspx", "title": "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed p\u0159elet dronem nad Apple Parkem u\u017e odhaluje i kola pro zam\u011bstnance", "author": "Karel Jav\u016frek", "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "S nov\u00fdm m\u011bs\u00edcem tu op\u011bt m\u00e1me \u010derstv\u00fd p\u0159elet nad nov\u00fdm kruhov\u00fdm s\u00eddlem Applu pojmenovan\u00fdm Apple Park. Nov\u00e9 z\u00e1b\u011bry ukazuj\u00ed u\u017e spoustu dokon\u010den\u00fdch \u010d\u00e1st\u00ed a tak\u00e9 n\u011bkolik novinek.Na videu v rozli\u0161en\u00ed 4K od tv\u016frce Matthew Robertse, kter\u00e9 bylo nato\u010den\u00e9 pomoc\u00ed dronu DJI Phantom 4 Pro, lze poprv\u00e9 vid\u011bt zaparkovan\u00e1 kola na r\u016fzn\u00fdch m\u00edstech, kter\u00e1 jsou ur\u010den\u00e1 pro zam\u011bstnance. D\u00edky nim se mohou rychleji p\u0159em\u00edstit po cel\u00e9m s\u00eddle \u010di do bl\u00edzk\u00e9ho okol\u00ed. P\u0159ece jen je to budova obrovsk\u00e1 a ch\u016fze je dost pomal\u00e1.V bl\u00edzkosti fitness centra u\u017e byly dokon\u010den\u00e9 tenisov\u00e9 kurty, volejbal s p\u00edskem a dal\u0161\u00ed rekrea\u010dn\u00ed travnat\u00e9 plochy. Na star\u0161\u00ed z\u00e1b\u011bry z p\u0159edchoz\u00edch m\u011bs\u00edc\u016f se m\u016f\u017eete pod\u00edvat na .", "tags": ["Apple", "YouTube", "Drony", "DJI", "Zam\u011bstnanci", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed p\u0159elet", "Nov\u00fd z\u00e1b\u011br", "\u010cerstv\u00fd p\u0159elet", "Cola", "Z\u00e1b\u011br", "Matthew Roberts", "Nov\u00fd m\u011bs\u00edc", "DJI Phantom", "Cel\u00e9 s\u00eddlo", "P\u0159elet", "Fitness centrum", "Apple Park", "P\u0159edchoz\u00ed m\u011bs\u00edc"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/oprava-homepodu-je-poradne-draha-stoji-temer-stejne-jako-novy-reproduktor/sc-3-a-191784/default.aspx", "title": "Oprava Homepodu je po\u0159\u00e1dn\u011b drah\u00e1. Stoj\u00ed t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 stejn\u011b jako nov\u00fd reproduktor", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "13. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Apple si za Homepod \u0159ekne ve Spojen\u00e9m kr\u00e1lovstv\u00ed o 319 liber, tedy asi 9 100 korun. To je za perfektn\u011b hraj\u00edc\u00ed reproduktor se zabudovanou asistentkou (by\u0165 zat\u00edm ne moc dob\u0159e funguj\u00edc\u00ed) adekv\u00e1tn\u00ed \u010d\u00e1stka. Apple si v\u0161ak \u00fa\u010dtuje enormn\u00ed sumu za p\u0159\u00edpadnou opravu mimo z\u00e1ru\u010dn\u00ed lh\u016ftu.Pokud z\u00e1kazn\u00edk bude cht\u00edt opravit nebo vym\u011bnit Homepod po uplynut\u00ed t\u00e9to doby, zaplat\u00ed 268 liber (asi 7 650 korun). Tedy pouze o patn\u00e1ct set m\u00e9n\u011b, ne\u017e stoj\u00ed samotn\u00fd nov\u00fd reproduktor.Alespo\u0148 z \u010d\u00e1sti se daj\u00ed tyhle trable omezit zakoupen\u00edm p\u0159\u00edplatkov\u00e9ho z\u00e1ru\u010dn\u00edho programu Apple Care. Za ten si Apple \u00fa\u010dtuje dal\u0161\u00edch 39 liber. T\u00edm z\u00edsk\u00e1 z\u00e1kazn\u00edk jednak prioritn\u00ed podporu a tak\u00e9 zv\u00fdhodn\u011bn\u00e9 podm\u00ednky servisu.I vzhledem k vysok\u00e9 cen\u011b opravy se d\u00e1 o\u010dek\u00e1vat, \u017ee v\u011bt\u0161ina servisn\u00edch z\u00e1sah\u016f bude prob\u00edhat v\u00fdm\u011bnou za nov\u00fd kus. Ostatn\u011b b\u011b\u017en\u00e1 oprava v dom\u00e1c\u00edch podm\u00ednk\u00e1ch mo\u017en\u00e1 nen\u00ed. Web iFixit mu dal sk\u00f3re opravitelnosti 1/10.", "tags": ["Apple", "Hudba, filmy, seri\u00e1ly", "Homepod", "P\u0159\u00edpadn\u00e1 oprava", "Spojen\u00e9 kr\u00e1lovstv\u00ed", "Prioritn\u00ed podpora", "Nov\u00fd reproduktor", "Libra", "Oprava", "Nov\u00fd kus", "Dom\u00e1c\u00ed podm\u00ednka", "Hraj\u00edc\u00ed reproduktor", "Apple car", "Z\u00e1kazn\u00edci", "Reproduktor", "Z\u00e1ru\u010dn\u00ed lh\u016fta", "Servisn\u00ed z\u00e1sah"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/samsung-konecne-opravil-sve-matouci-emoji-a-pridal-hovinku-usmev/sc-3-a-191797/default.aspx", "title": "Samsung kone\u010dn\u011b opravil sv\u00e9 matouc\u00ed emoji a p\u0159idal hov\u00ednku \u00fasm\u011bv", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "13. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Samsung je zn\u00e1m\u00fd t\u00edm, \u017ee m\u00e1 svou vlastn\u00ed sadu emoji, kter\u00e1 je pon\u011bkud sv\u00e9r\u00e1zn\u00e1 a n\u011bkter\u00e9 konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed emoce a p\u0159edm\u011bty vykl\u00e1d\u00e1 zcela jinak, ne\u017e by m\u011blo b\u00fdt. Nejde te\u010f t\u0159eba o barvi\u010dky a sm\u011br pohledu postavi\u010dek, ale jejich v\u00fdraz. Nyn\u00ed to ale vypad\u00e1, \u017ee Samsung si dlouhodobou chybu uv\u011bdomil a p\u0159edstavil novou sadu, kter\u00e1 v\u011bt\u0161inu proh\u0159e\u0161k\u016f opravuje.Mezi nejzn\u00e1m\u011bj\u0161\u00ed pat\u0159ily rozhodn\u011b cookies, kter\u00e9 m\u00edsto klasick\u00fdch kulat\u00fdch su\u0161enek na telefonech od Samsungu vypadaly jako slan\u00e9 \u010dtvercov\u00e9 krekry, \u010di o\u010di v sloup vypadaj\u00edc\u00ed sp\u00ed\u0161e jako zv\u011bdav\u00fd obli\u010dej.P\u0159i pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed takto rozd\u00edln\u00fdch emoji mohlo snadno doj\u00edt k nedorozum\u011bn\u00ed, na ostatn\u00edch platform\u00e1ch se toti\u017e zobrazily tak, jak m\u011bly. Sv\u00e9 o tom m\u016f\u017ee pov\u011bd\u011bt nap\u0159\u00edklad zn\u00e1m\u00e1 here\u010dka Jessica Chastain, kter\u00e1 pr\u00e1v\u011b jeden z doty\u010dn\u00fdch emotikon\u016f pou\u017eila ve sv\u00e9m tweetu. Nov\u00e1 sada vych\u00e1z\u00ed spole\u010dn\u011b s rozhran\u00edm Samsung Experience 9.0.Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Google", "Samsung", "Bulv\u00e1r a vt\u00edpky", "Emoji", "Unicode", "Sada", "Zn\u00e1m\u00e1 here\u010dka", "Sloup", "Emoce", "Nov\u00e1 sada", "Ostatn\u00ed platforma", "\u00dasm\u011bv"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/na-hromade-ceskych-webu-se-nachazel-skript-tezici-kryptomeny-webmasteri-o-tom-netusili/sc-3-a-191817/default.aspx", "title": "Na hromad\u011b \u010desk\u00fdch web\u016f se nach\u00e1zel skript t\u011b\u017e\u00edc\u00ed kryptom\u011bny. Webmaste\u0159i o tom netu\u0161ili", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "T\u011b\u017eko \u0159\u00edci, jestli to auto\u0159i  tu\u0161ili, anebo to byl p\u0159\u00edmo z\u00e1m\u011br, nicm\u00e9n\u011b kdy\u017e loni na podzim spustili t\u011b\u017ebu kryptom\u011bn jako slu\u017ebu pro webmastery, p\u0159\u00edle\u017eitosti se okam\u017eit\u011b chopili tak\u00e9 .O CoinHivu jsme u\u017e psali, tak\u017ee jen stru\u010dn\u011b p\u0159ipomenu, \u017ee sta\u010d\u00ed do webov\u00e9 str\u00e1nky vlo\u017eit p\u00e1r \u0159\u00e1dk\u016f Javascriptu a u\u017eivatel za\u010dne b\u011bhem n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvy t\u011b\u017eit kryptom\u011bnu . U web\u016f s dostate\u010dn\u011b vysokou n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvnost\u00ed a \u010dasem str\u00e1ven\u00fdm na str\u00e1nce (t\u0159eba \u017div\u011b.cz) by se u\u017e mohlo jednat o docela zaj\u00edmav\u00fd alternativn\u00ed p\u0159\u00edjem.I proto n\u011bkte\u0159\u00ed zast\u00e1nci kryptom\u011bn o t\u00e9to monetizaci p\u0159em\u00fd\u0161leli jako o alternativ\u011b ke klasick\u00e9 reklam\u011b. Nutno konstatovat, \u017ee tyto idealistick\u00e9 vize vydr\u017eely jen p\u00e1r t\u00fddn\u016f, ne\u017e Coinhive zastavily tradi\u010dn\u00ed blok\u00e1tory reklam.P\u0159\u00edle\u017eitosti se nicm\u00e9n\u011b brzy chopila ona \u0161ed\u00e1 z\u00f3na na internetu a t\u011b\u017eebn\u00ed skript se za\u010dal objevovat na mnoha webech, ani\u017e by to jejich majitel\u00e9 v\u016fbec tu\u0161ili. T\u0159eba tak, \u017ee se t\u011b\u017eebn\u00ed k\u00f3d ocitl v n\u011bkter\u00fdch (t\u0159eba i kompromitovan\u00fdch) dopl\u0148c\u00edch pro popul\u00e1rn\u00ed redak\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my jako WordPress aj.Samotn\u00fd CoinHive proti podobn\u00fdm praktik\u00e1m nijak nevystupoval, proto\u017ee si z t\u011b\u017eby p\u0159irozen\u011b bere n\u011bjak\u00e9 to procento, \u010dili \u010d\u00edm v\u00edce prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010d\u016f t\u011b\u017e\u00ed, t\u00edm l\u00e9pe.Bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed expert Michal \u0160pa\u010dek si , \u017ee se t\u011b\u017eebn\u00ed skript vyskytoval i na mnoha tuzemsk\u00fdch webech a vzhledem k jeho specifick\u00e9mu um\u00edst\u011bn\u00ed bez v\u011bdom\u00ed autor\u016f.Nenach\u00e1zel se toti\u017e standardn\u011b v t\u011ble str\u00e1nky, ale nejsp\u00ed\u0161e n\u011bjak\u00fd dopln\u011bk pro redak\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my se jej pokou\u0161el vkl\u00e1dat do tagu . Podobn\u011b napaden\u00e9 weby na tuzemsk\u00e9 dom\u00e9n\u011b d\u00edky tomu m\u016f\u017eete snadno dohledat t\u0159eba v Googlu s parametry a  Sta\u010d\u00ed do vyhled\u00e1va\u010de zadat tuto formulku:Samotnou slu\u017ebu CoinHive z tohoto d\u016fvodu st\u00e1le \u010dast\u011bji blokuj\u00ed antivirov\u00e9 programy a nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed podnikov\u00e9 filtra\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my \u2013 t\u0159eba FortiGuard. T\u011b\u017eko \u0159\u00edci, jestli je to v po\u0159\u00e1dku, samotn\u00e1 slu\u017eba CoinHive je toti\u017e naprosto legitimn\u00ed.Pokud webmaster podobn\u00fd k\u00f3d na sv\u00e9 str\u00e1nky um\u00edst\u00ed v\u011bdom\u011b, nen\u00ed na tom nic ileg\u00e1ln\u00edho \u010di nemor\u00e1ln\u00edho. Etick\u00fd probl\u00e9m je to pouze tehdy, pokud se tak d\u011bje bez v\u011bdom\u00ed surfa\u0159e a skript na pozad\u00ed p\u0159\u00edli\u0161n\u011b vyt\u011b\u017euje jeho procesor.", "tags": ["Google", "Web", "Kryptom\u011bny", "Malware", "Monero", "\u010cesko", "T\u011b\u017eba", "Javascript", "Specifick\u00e9 um\u00edst\u011bn\u00ed", "Michal \u0160pa\u010dek", "Miner", "Webov\u00e1 str\u00e1nka", "\u010cesk\u00fd Web", "Webmaster", "Str\u00e1ven\u00fd \u010das", "T\u011b\u017eebn\u00ed skript", "Etick\u00fd probl\u00e9m", "Napaden\u00fd web", "Mnoh\u00e9 weby", "Tuzemsk\u00e1 dom\u00e9na", "Podobn\u00fd k\u00f3d", "\u0160ed\u00e1 z\u00f3na", "Podobn\u00e1 praktika", "Klasick\u00e1 reklama", "Vysok\u00e1 n\u00e1v\u0161t\u011bvnost"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/drony-dji-jsou-jen-hloupe-hracky-ze-skydio-r1-si-sednete-na-zadek/sc-3-a-191829/default.aspx", "title": "Drony DJI jsou jen hloup\u00e9 hra\u010dky, ze Skydio R1 si sednete na zadek!", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "M\u00e1te doma amat\u00e9rskou kvadrokopt\u00e9ru? Tak ji vyho\u010fte do popelnice a za\u010dn\u011bte \u0161et\u0159it na  \u2013 dlouho o\u010dek\u00e1van\u00fd dron od in\u017een\u00fdr\u016f, kte\u0159\u00ed se mimo jin\u00e9 pod\u00edleli i na projektu Wing pod st\u0159echou laborato\u0159e Google X.V \u010dem se R1 li\u0161\u00ed od b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch komer\u010dn\u00edch model\u016f?  Inteligentn\u00ed? To je dnes u\u017e tro\u0161ku kli\u0161\u00e9, proto\u017ee v\u011bt\u0161ina v\u00fdrobc\u016f a jejich market\u00e9r\u016f pova\u017euje za \u201esmart\u201c prakticky cokoliv s bateri\u00ed uvnit\u0159.Skydio R1 je ale pon\u011bkud jin\u00fd p\u0159\u00edb\u011bh. Tato kvadropt\u00e9ra se toti\u017e m\u016f\u017ee pochlubit . Prakticky ka\u017ed\u00fd dron st\u0159edn\u00ed a vy\u0161\u0161\u00ed kategorie dnes nab\u00edz\u00ed jednoduch\u00e9ho autopilota, tak\u017ee um\u00ed sledovat n\u011bjak\u00fd objekt a t\u0159eba okolo n\u011bj rotovat.Principi\u00e1ln\u011b se v\u0161ak jedn\u00e1 o relativn\u011b jednoduch\u00fd syst\u00e9m s n\u011bkolika d\u00e1lkom\u011bry,  a GPS. Skydio R1 k tomu pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 data z  rozm\u00edst\u011bn\u00fdch po cel\u00e9m obvodu kvadrokopt\u00e9ry a t\u0159in\u00e1ctou pro z\u00e1znam samotn\u00e9ho obrazu ve 4K! No, a o hardwarov\u00fd v\u00fdkon se nakonec star\u00e1 deska  od Nvidie \u2013 kapesn\u00ed superpo\u010d\u00edta\u010d s 256 j\u00e1dry CUDA p\u0159esn\u011b pro tento typ elektroniky.Na trhu je sice u\u017e jej\u00ed nov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed model TX2 s j\u00e1drem Pascal, nicm\u00e9n\u011b i star\u0161\u00ed (a proto levn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed) generace s j\u00e1drem Maxwell zvl\u00e1dne tato data zpracovat v re\u00e1ln\u00fd \u010das, analyzovat pomoc\u00ed neuronov\u00fdch s\u00edt\u00ed a v\u00fdsledkem je autopilot, kter\u00fd se vyhne ka\u017ed\u00e9 v\u011btvi\u010dce.Skydio R1 je tak pravd\u011bpodobn\u011b jedin\u00fd dron, kter\u00fd si sebou m\u016f\u017ee vz\u00edt biker na kdejak\u00fd zalesn\u011bn\u00fd singletrail, na za\u010d\u00e1tku d\u00e1t dronu povel, aby jej p\u0159i j\u00edzd\u011b nat\u00e1\u010del a dal mu volnost. V\u00fdsledek? Pod\u00edvejte se na videa. Nev\u00edme o \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9m jin\u00e9m dronu na trhu, kter\u00fd by um\u011bl n\u011bco podobn\u00e9ho.R1 pomoc\u00ed po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9ho vid\u011bn\u00ed rozpozn\u00e1 osobu, kterou m\u00e1 nat\u00e1\u010det, dle jej\u00edho pohybu neust\u00e1le p\u0159edv\u00edd\u00e1, jak\u00fdm sm\u011brem d\u00e1le zam\u00ed\u0159\u00ed a ke v\u0161emu si neust\u00e1le p\u0159epo\u010d\u00edt\u00e1v\u00e1 3D model sv\u00e9ho okol\u00ed, d\u00edky kter\u00e9mu se alespo\u0148 dle uk\u00e1zkov\u00fdch vide\u00ed vyhne prakticky jak\u00e9koliv p\u0159ek\u00e1\u017ece i uprost\u0159ed hust\u00e9ho lesa. A to v\u0161e p\u0159i rychlosti pohybu .Mimochodem, kolik tato legrace vlastn\u011b stoj\u00ed? P\u0159iplat\u00edte si. Skydio R1 je toti\u017e na americk\u00e9m trhu k dispozici za , co\u017e po p\u0159epo\u010dtu \u010din\u00ed p\u0159es 51 tis\u00edc korun (nemluv\u011b o DPH a clu).", "tags": ["Google", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Nvidia", "Strojov\u00e9 u\u010den\u00ed", "Drony", "Neuronov\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165", "DJI", "Kvadrokopt\u00e9ra", "Uk\u00e1zkov\u00e9 video", "Jednoduch\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Nov\u00fd model", "Ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed p\u0159edstaven\u00ed", "Zorn\u00e9 pole", "Hardwarov\u00fd v\u00fdkon", "Pascal", "Imo", "Cel\u00fd obvod", "J\u00e1dro", "Americk\u00fd trh", "DPH", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9 vid\u011bn\u00ed", "CUDA", "Wing", "Zadek", "Autopilot"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/nova-konference-nejen-pro-it-manazery-mandayit/sc-3-a-191792/default.aspx", "title": "Nov\u00e1 konference (nejen) pro IT mana\u017eery Manday.it", "author": null, "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Konference Manday.it, kter\u00e1 prob\u011bhne v pond\u011bl\u00ed 19. \u00fanora 2018 v Praze, je nov\u00fdm p\u0159\u00edr\u016fstkem do rodiny odborn\u00fdch konferenc\u00ed Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9 \u0161koly Gopas. V n\u011bkolika aspektech se od t\u011bch ostatn\u00edch ale li\u0161\u00ed: p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm je ur\u010den\u00e1 zejm\u00e9na pro CIO, vedouc\u00ed provozu IT, \u010di \u0161\u00e9fy velk\u00fdch projekt\u016f. Trochu netradi\u010dn\u00ed je i jej\u00ed \u201ezhu\u0161t\u011bn\u00e1\u201c podoba. Po dopoledn\u00edm bloku p\u0159edn\u00e1\u0161ek zam\u011b\u0159en\u00fdch na t\u00e9mata GDPR, DevOps, ITIL procesy, budou odpoledne n\u00e1sledovat praktick\u00e9 workshopy. P\u0159edn\u00e1\u0161et a n\u00e1sledn\u011b v\u00e9st jednotliv\u00e9 workshopy budou t\u0159i p\u0159edn\u00ed odborn\u00edci na danou problematiku: Martin Vitou\u0161, Ond\u0159ej \u0160eve\u010dek a Radovan Citterberg.\u201eJak\u00fd je stav DevOps v \u010cech\u00e1ch? Tak jako v\u0161ichni cht\u011bli b\u00fdt je\u0161t\u011b ned\u00e1vno \u201aagile\u2018, tak cht\u011bj\u00ed b\u00fdt nyn\u00ed \u201adevops\u2018. Hodn\u011b firem v \u010cesk\u00e9 republice o DevOps mluv\u00ed a sna\u017e\u00ed se zjistit, o \u010dem to cel\u00e9 je,\u201c konstatuje Martin Vitou\u0161, odborn\u00fd lektor Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9 \u0161koly Gopas s velk\u00fdmi zku\u0161enostmi z oblasti strategick\u00e9ho, projektov\u00e9ho, procesn\u00edho a osobn\u00edho \u0159\u00edzen\u00ed. \u201eProbl\u00e9m je, \u017ee DevOps nen\u00ed jednozna\u010dn\u011b popsan\u00e1 metoda jako t\u0159eba ITIL, ale sp\u00ed\u0161 filozofie. Z toho d\u016fvodu si ka\u017ed\u00e1 firma pod t\u00edmto v\u00fdrazem p\u0159edstavuje n\u011bco jin\u00e9ho. Tak\u00e9 nejde o pouhou o automatizaci proces\u016f, jak se \u0159ada lid\u00ed myln\u011b domn\u00edv\u00e1. Aby DevOps n\u00e1stroje opravdu fungovaly a p\u0159in\u00e1\u0161ely firm\u011b p\u0159\u00edslu\u0161n\u00e9 benefity, je pot\u0159eba i n\u011bco dal\u0161\u00edho - pr\u00e1ce s lidmi, postupn\u00e1 zm\u011bna firemn\u00ed kultury, zm\u011bny v architektu\u0159e informa\u010dn\u00edch syst\u00e9m\u016f, stabiln\u00ed a jednoduch\u00e9 procesy. A pr\u00e1v\u011b na to se zam\u011b\u0159\u00edme na konferenci Manday.it.\u201cS bl\u00ed\u017e\u00edc\u00edm se kv\u011btnem 2018 je hork\u00fdm t\u00e9matem p\u0159\u00edprava na evropskou sm\u011brnici GDPR. Spln\u011bn\u00ed jej\u00edch po\u017eadavk\u016f z\u00e1vis\u00ed na \u00fa\u010dinn\u00e9 spolupr\u00e1ci managementu s IT i podnikov\u00fdmi pr\u00e1vn\u00edky. Nejde o IT projekt, ale IT mus\u00ed poskytnout nahoru podporu rozhodov\u00e1n\u00ed a dol\u016f implementaci ur\u010den\u00fdch bezpe\u010dnostn\u00edch opat\u0159en\u00ed. \u201eBez toho, abyste v\u011bd\u011bli, jak\u00e9 m\u00e1te osobn\u00ed \u00fadaje, kde se povaluj\u00ed, kdo s nimi pracuje a kdo by s nimi pracovat m\u011bl, \u010di kam se p\u0159ed\u00e1vaj\u00ed, nem\u016f\u017eete \u0159\u00eddit jejich bezpe\u010dnost,\u201c \u0159\u00edk\u00e1 Ond\u0159ej \u0160eve\u010dek, odborn\u00edk na IT bezpe\u010dnost Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9 \u0161koly Gopas. \u201eV r\u00e1mci workshopu si na z\u00e1klad\u011b jednoduch\u00e9ho p\u0159\u00edkladu uk\u00e1\u017eeme, jak to zvl\u00e1dnout.\u201cV\u011bt\u0161ina firem \u0159e\u0161\u00ed p\u0159i \u0159\u00edzen\u00ed IT stejn\u00e9 probl\u00e9my. Jak v ka\u017edodenn\u00edm provozu mohou pomoci doporu\u010den\u00ed schov\u00e1vaj\u00edc\u00ed se za zkratkou ITIL? \u201eITIL obsahuje spoustu proces\u016f, kter\u00e9 by se daly v IT pou\u017e\u00edt,\u201c \u0159\u00edk\u00e1 Radovan Citterberg a dod\u00e1v\u00e1: \u201eV\u011bt\u0161ina z nich se t\u00fdk\u00e1 pouze IT. Nicm\u00e9n\u011b n\u011bkter\u00e9 z nich zaji\u0161\u0165uj\u00ed efektivn\u00ed spolupr\u00e1ci mezi IT a businessem, a pr\u00e1v\u011b na n\u011b se pod\u00edv\u00e1me.\u201cV\u00edce informac\u00ed ke konferenci ManDay.it naleznete na ", "tags": []}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/jizerska-50-je-ve-street-view-projedte-ji-z-gauce-a-bez-omrzlin/sc-3-a-191799/default.aspx", "title": "Jizersk\u00e1 50 je ve Street View! Proje\u010fte ji z gau\u010de a bez omrzlin", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "O v\u00edkendu vypukne v po\u0159ad\u00ed u\u017e 51. ro\u010dn\u00edk slavn\u00e9ho ly\u017ea\u0159sk\u00e9ho z\u00e1vodu . D\u00edky spolupr\u00e1ci s Googlem si ji letos m\u016f\u017ee poprv\u00e9 projet i rozmazlen\u011bj\u0161\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st geekosf\u00e9ry, kter\u00e1 sice nem\u00e1 b\u011b\u017eky, ale za to se m\u016f\u017ee pochlubit solidn\u00edm p\u0159ipojen\u00edm k internetu. .Organiz\u00e1to\u0159i z\u00e1vodu projeli pades\u00e1tikilometrovou trasu na sn\u011b\u017en\u00e9m sk\u00fatru s p\u0159ipevn\u011bnou panoramatickou kamerou Street View teprve kr\u00e1tce po Nov\u00e9m roce a Google b\u011bhem p\u00e1r t\u00fddn\u016f publikoval proj\u00ed\u017e\u010fku v map\u00e1ch.Jedn\u00e1 se o prvn\u00ed pou\u017eit\u00ed sn\u011b\u017en\u00e9ho sk\u00fatru p\u0159i mapov\u00e1n\u00ed Street View v \u010cesk\u00e9 republice. Tuto techniku Google a jeho partne\u0159i doposud pou\u017e\u00edvali jen ve velk\u00fdch zahrani\u010dn\u00edch ly\u017ea\u0159sk\u00fdch are\u00e1lech.Al\u017eb\u011bta Houzarov\u00e1 z \u010desk\u00e9ho Googlu douf\u00e1, \u017ee Jizersk\u00e1 50 ve Street View nepot\u011b\u0161\u00ed pouze peciv\u00e1ly, ale p\u0159im\u011bje lidi skute\u010dn\u011b vyrazit na sn\u011b\u017enou stopu: \u201e ", "tags": ["Mapy Google", "Google", "Sport", "Street View", "Mapy", "\u010cesko", "GIS", "Turistika", "Kartografie", "Mapa", "Sn\u011b\u017en\u00fd sk\u00fatr", "Gau\u010d", "Nov\u00fd rok", "Mapov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Prvn\u00ed pou\u017eit\u00ed", "Sk\u00fatr", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Z\u00e1vod", "Cel\u00e1 trasa"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/youtube-red-brzy-ceka-velka-expanze-dost-pravdepodobne-se-dockame-i-v-cesku/sc-3-a-191819/default.aspx", "title": "YouTube Red brzy \u010dek\u00e1 velk\u00e1 expanze. Dost pravd\u011bpodobn\u011b se do\u010dk\u00e1me i v \u010cesku", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "P\u0159edplacen\u00e1 slu\u017eba YouTube Red se brzy roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159\u00ed do stovky nov\u00fdch zem\u00ed a je tedy velmi pravd\u011bpodobn\u00e9, \u017ee mezi nimi bude i \u010cesko. O expanzi se zm\u00ednila \u0161\u00e9fka YouTube Susan Wojcicki v rozhovoru pro . Bohu\u017eel Susan Wojcicki neprozradila konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed datum, kdy by k expanzi m\u011blo doj\u00edt a pochopiteln\u011b nezmi\u0148ovala ani konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed v\u0161echny zem\u011b, do kter\u00fdch se slu\u017eba roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159\u00ed. Aktu\u00e1ln\u011b v\u0161ak funguje pouze v p\u011bti \u2013 v Austr\u00e1lii, Ji\u017en\u00ed Koreji, Mexiku, na Nov\u00e9m Z\u00e9land\u011b a v USA. Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed do \u010ceska je t\u00e9m\u011b\u0159 jist\u00e9, napov\u00edd\u00e1 tomu i p\u0159ipraven\u00e1 lokalizace str\u00e1nky slu\u017eby.   YouTube Red umo\u017e\u0148uje p\u0159ehr\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed vide\u00ed na YouTube bez reklam, nav\u00edc d\u00e1v\u00e1 p\u0159\u00edstup k exkluzivn\u00edmu obsahu, umo\u017e\u0148uje stahovat videa pro offline p\u0159ehr\u00e1n\u00ed a hudbu dovol\u00ed poslouchat na pozad\u00ed. Pr\u00e1v\u011b hudba by se m\u011bla st\u00e1t st\u011b\u017eejn\u00edm l\u00e1kadlem slu\u017eby, tvrd\u00ed Susan Wojcicki. Je to dal\u0161\u00ed indicie k d\u0159\u00edv\u011bj\u0161\u00edm spekulac\u00edm, \u017ee by v budoucnu m\u011blo doj\u00edt ke slou\u010den\u00ed p\u0159edplatn\u00e9ho YouTube Red a Hudby Google Play. Aktu\u00e1ln\u011b stoj\u00ed YouTube Red 9,99 dolar\u016f m\u011bs\u00ed\u010dn\u011b, tj. cca 205 K\u010d. V r\u00e1mci YouTube Red p\u0159itom dostanete p\u0159\u00edstup i k p\u0159edplacen\u00e9 hudebn\u00ed slu\u017eb\u011b Hudba Google Play. Jen\u017ee pozor, v podm\u00ednk\u00e1ch slu\u017eby je uvedeno, \u017ee pokud m\u00e1te aktu\u00e1ln\u011b p\u0159edplatn\u00e9 slu\u017eby Hudba Google Play, automaticky t\u00edm pak z\u00edsk\u00e1te i p\u0159\u00edstup do YouTube Red! Vzhledem k tomu, \u017ee Hudba Google Play vyjde jen na 149 K\u010d, je to v\u00fdhodn\u00e1 cesta k YouTube bez reklam.  ", "tags": ["Google", "YouTube", "Hudba, filmy, seri\u00e1ly", "USA", "P\u0159edplatn\u00e9", "Ji\u017en\u00ed Korea", "Austr\u00e1lie", "Mexiko", "Expanze", "P\u0159\u00edstup", "P\u0159edplacen\u00e1 slu\u017eba", "Nov\u00fd Z\u00e9land", "Hudba", "Recode", "Brzk\u00e1 spekulace", "Exkluzivn\u00ed obsah", "Red", "Nov\u00e1 zem\u011b", "St\u011b\u017eejn\u00ed l\u00e1kadlo", "Dolar", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Play", "Velk\u00e1 expanze", "Slu\u017eba"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/luminar-2018-udela-z-fotek-skvosty-i-kyce-nemusite-pritom-rozumet-jak-to-dela/sc-3-a-191800/default.aspx", "title": "Luminar 2018 ud\u011bl\u00e1 z fotek skvosty i k\u00fd\u010de, nemus\u00edte p\u0159itom rozum\u011bt, jak to d\u011bl\u00e1", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "14. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "S fotografick\u00fdmi editory je to jako s chytr\u00fdmi pra\u010dkami. \u010c\u00edm sofistikovan\u011bj\u0161\u00ed za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed, t\u00edm v\u00edce voleb, a nakonec stejn\u011b v\u0161echno peru \u201ena \u010dty\u0159icet\u201c a netu\u0161\u00edm, k \u010demu slou\u017e\u00ed t\u011bch dal\u0161\u00edch 45 prac\u00edch program\u016f. Podobn\u011b tak od fotografick\u00e9ho programu nepot\u0159ebuji p\u0159ehr\u0161el funkc\u00ed \u2013 chci do n\u011bj prost\u011b nahr\u00e1t fotografii, klepnout na tla\u010d\u00edtko \u201eVylep\u0161it\u201c a pot\u00e9 s otev\u0159en\u00fdmi \u00fasty z\u00edrat, jak jsem skv\u011bl\u00fd fotograf. A pr\u00e1v\u011b to slibuje Luminar 2018.GIMP, Photoshop, Zoner Photo Studio, Affinity Photo a hromada dal\u0161\u00edch program\u016f nab\u00edz\u00ed skv\u011bl\u00e9 univerz\u00e1ln\u00ed n\u00e1stroje a stovky funkc\u00ed, pomoc\u00ed kter\u00fdch m\u016f\u017eete prom\u011bnit pod\u00e1n\u00ed libovoln\u00e9ho pixelu sn\u00edmku, nicm\u00e9n\u011b faktem z\u016fst\u00e1v\u00e1, \u017ee nejpou\u017e\u00edvan\u011bj\u0161\u00edm grafick\u00fdm n\u00e1strojem je Instagram a svat\u00e1 trojice: vyfotit, klepnout, sd\u00edlet.D\u016fvod je jednoduch\u00fd. . A ruku na srdce, pokud z dovolen\u00e9 p\u0159ivezete 1 325 fotografi\u00ed (v\u010detn\u011b 168 naprosto stejn\u00fdch z\u00e1pad\u016f Slunce), ur\u010dit\u011b se s ka\u017edou nebudete cht\u00edt piplat dlouh\u00e9 hodiny. Chcete to jedno tla\u010d\u00edtko a nejv\u00fd\u0161e p\u00e1r posuvn\u00edk\u016f.Touto cestou se vydal i  \u2013  za pozoruhodn\u00fdch , co\u017e sice nen\u00ed m\u00e1lo, ov\u0161em nen\u00ed to ani mnoho; software se st\u00e1le vejde do psychologick\u00e9 hladiny 2 000 K\u010d, okolo kter\u00e9 se pohybuje cena v\u011bt\u0161iny amat\u00e9rsk\u00e9ho a poloprofesion\u00e1ln\u00edho kreativn\u00edho softwaru.Za tuto \u010d\u00e1stku z\u00edsk\u00e1te program, ve kter\u00e9m otev\u0159ete jakoukoliv fotografii, klepnete jako v Instagramu na n\u011bkterou z efektov\u00fdch miniatur a je hotovo. Fajn, pro\u010d ale za podobnou legraci v\u016fbec platit, kdy\u017e je Instagram zdarma a tuto roli spln\u00ed i cel\u00fd z\u00e1stup bezplatn\u00fdch aplikac\u00ed? Proto\u017ee Luminar je takov\u00fd .To znamen\u00e1, \u017ee t\u011bch miniatur s filtry nenab\u00edz\u00ed deset, ani dvacet ale  a jsou rozd\u011blen\u00e9 do n\u011bkolika tematick\u00fdch galeri\u00ed. Mimochodem, pokud by v\u00e1m z\u00e1kladn\u00ed v\u00fdbava nesta\u010dila, je tu webov\u00fd , kter\u00fd nab\u00edz\u00ed sta\u017een\u00ed dal\u0161\u00edch zdarma, nebo za poplatek.Za druh\u00e9, otev\u0159ete v n\u011bm prakticky cokoliv po\u010d\u00ednaje oblig\u00e1tn\u00edm JPEG a kon\u010de . A kone\u010dn\u011b do t\u0159etice, komu nesta\u010d\u00ed jeden klik a chce od editoru p\u0159eci jen n\u011bco v\u00edc, dostane to.Ka\u017ed\u00fd filtr lze proto dodate\u010dn\u011b a do nejmen\u0161\u00edho detailu upravit, nechyb\u00ed oprava geometrie, aberace a dal\u0161\u00edch vad objektiv\u016f. Filtry m\u016f\u017eete z\u00e1rove\u0148 skl\u00e1dat do vrstev a vytv\u00e1\u0159et tak mnohem komplexn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdsledek. T\u00edmto p\u0159\u00edstupem zase Luminar p\u0159ipom\u00edn\u00e1 Lightroom od Adobe.Nakonec nechyb\u00ed ani retu\u0161ovac\u00ed \u0161t\u011btce, pomoc\u00ed kter\u00fdch m\u016f\u017eete snadno ze sc\u00e9ny smazat objekty, kter\u00e9 tam nemaj\u00ed co d\u011blat. Luminar se je pokus\u00ed \u0161etrn\u011b odstranit s ohledem na okoln\u00ed sc\u00e9nu, tak\u017ee kdy\u017e ke smaz\u00e1n\u00ed ozna\u010d\u00edte t\u0159eba sloup elektrick\u00e9ho veden\u00ed, dopo\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 odpov\u00eddaj\u00edc\u00ed pozad\u00ed a sloup zmiz\u00ed podobn\u00fdm zp\u016fsobem, jak to um\u00ed t\u0159eba velk\u00fd Photoshop. Chv\u00edli to sice trv\u00e1, ale v\u00fdsledek je ve v\u011bt\u0161in\u011b p\u0159\u00edpad\u016f perfektn\u00ed. Nejedn\u00e1 se tedy o \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 primitivn\u00ed klonovac\u00ed raz\u00edtko.Ale dost \u0159e\u010d\u00ed. Obr\u00e1zek vyd\u00e1 za tis\u00edc slov, a tak , jak vypad\u00e1 pr\u00e1ce v Luminaru v praxi. Mezi sn\u00edmky se m\u016f\u017eete navigovat \u0161ipkami na kl\u00e1vesnici.", "tags": ["Software", "Windows", "Instagram", "macOS (OS X)", "Fotky", "Slunce", "Fotografov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Adobe", "Adobe Photoshop", "Grafick\u00fd editor", "Zoner Photo Studio", "Filtr", "HDR", "JPEG", "Adobe Lightroom", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed filtr", "Chytr\u00e1 pra\u010dka", "Kompletn\u00ed nastaven\u00ed", "Cel\u00fd z\u00e1stup", "Panel", "Sofistikovan\u00e9 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "Retu\u0161ovac\u00ed \u0161t\u011btec", "PDF", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed v\u00fdbava", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed prost\u0159ed\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/gastronomie-na-internetu/sc-3-a-191859/default.aspx", "title": "Gastronomie na internetu", "author": null, "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Chcete se vydat n\u011bkam do restaurace, ale o okol\u00ed nem\u00e1te v\u016fbec p\u0159ehled? Na internetu si m\u016f\u017eete vyhledat p\u0159ilehl\u00e9 lok\u00e1ly a hlavn\u011b se do\u010d\u00edst, jak\u00e9 s nimi maj\u00ed zku\u0161enosti jin\u00ed lid\u00e9 a jestli stoj\u00ed za to se tam v\u016fbec obt\u011b\u017eovat. Kam pro takov\u00e9 informace chodit si \u0159ekneme v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu. ", "tags": ["Internet", "Tipy", "Jak na Internet", "Lok\u00e1l", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video", "Gastronomie"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/googlu-se-to-nepodarilo-ted-chce-svymi-chytrymi-brylemi-vaunt-zabodovat-zase-intel/sc-3-a-191751/default.aspx", "title": "Googlu se to nepoda\u0159ilo. Te\u010f chce sv\u00fdmi chytr\u00fdmi br\u00fdlemi Vaunt zabodovat zase Intel", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "11. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Kdy\u017e Google poprv\u00e9 p\u0159edstavil sv\u00e9 chytr\u00e9 br\u00fdle Glass, byla to technologick\u00e1 senzace. P\u0159esto v\u0161ak bylo brzo a technologie je\u0161t\u011b nedosahovala dostate\u010dn\u00e9 miniaturizace. Intel si mysl\u00ed, \u017ee u\u017e to zvl\u00e1dne a uk\u00e1zal prototyp chytr\u00fdch br\u00fdl\u00ed Vaunt. Na prvn\u00ed pohled vypadaj\u00ed naprosto hloup\u011b, co\u017e je skv\u011bl\u00e1 zpr\u00e1va.", "tags": ["Video", "Google", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Intel", "Google Glass", "Br\u00fdle", "Prototyp", "Laserov\u00fd projektor", "Prvn\u00ed pohled", "Vaunt", "Skv\u011bl\u00e1 zpr\u00e1va", "Miniaturizace", "Glass", "Projektor", "Papu\u010de", "Chytr\u00e9 br\u00fdle", "Hipster"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/facebook-umozni-sdilet-s-prateli-seznamy-treba-prani-pod-stromecek-ci-nakupni-seznam/sc-3-a-191827/default.aspx", "title": "Facebook umo\u017en\u00ed sd\u00edlet s p\u0159\u00e1teli seznamy. T\u0159eba p\u0159\u00e1n\u00ed pod strome\u010dek \u010di n\u00e1kupn\u00ed seznam", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "15. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Pokud pot\u0159ebujete sd\u00edlet na Facebook seznam va\u0161ich tajn\u00fdch p\u0159\u00e1n\u00ed, destinac\u00ed ide\u00e1ln\u00edch k dovolen\u00e9 \u010di jen n\u00e1kupn\u00ed seznam (proto\u017ee jste sklerotici a na profilu jej najdete v\u017edycky), m\u00e1te nyn\u00ed mo\u017enost. Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165 zav\u00e1d\u00ed pr\u00e1v\u011b tuto funkci, kter\u00e1 v\u00e1m umo\u017en\u00ed sd\u00edlet jak\u00fdkoliv seznam mezi sv\u00e9 p\u0159\u00e1tele.Seznam m\u016f\u017ee m\u00edt n\u011bkolik polo\u017eek a lze jej doplnit tematick\u00fdm  a podpo\u0159it barevn\u00fdm pozad\u00edm. Facebook novinkou pokra\u010duje v zam\u011b\u0159en\u00ed na obsah generovan\u00fd samotn\u00fdmi u\u017eivateli a ne str\u00e1nkami, \u010d\u00edm\u017e chce zlep\u0161it \u010das str\u00e1ven\u00fd na s\u00edti. Dostupn\u00e1 bude celosv\u011btov\u011b, aktu\u00e1ln\u011b doch\u00e1z\u00ed k postupn\u00e9mu \u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed.Zdroj: ", "tags": ["Facebook", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Mobiln\u00ed aplikace", "P\u0159\u00e1n\u00ed", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165", "Seznam", "N\u00e1kupn\u00ed seznam", "S\u00ed\u0165", "Strome\u010dek", "Pozad\u00ed", "P\u0159\u00edtel", "TechCrunch", "Str\u00e1ven\u00fd \u010das", "Barevn\u00e9 pozad\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-odhalil-jak-uci-umelou-inteligenci-pouziva-k-tomu-videohry/sc-3-a-191760/default.aspx", "title": "Google odhalil, jak u\u010d\u00ed um\u011blou inteligenci. Pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 k tomu videohry", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "11. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "AI t\u00fdm Googlu, DeepMind, zodpov\u011bdn\u00fd za v\u00fdvoj um\u011bl\u00e9 inteligence a jej\u00ed pochopen\u00ed lidsk\u00e9ho my\u0161len\u00ed, odhalil nov\u00fd zp\u016fsob, jak neuronovou s\u00ed\u0165 u\u010d\u00ed multitaskingu a um\u011bn\u00ed d\u011blat n\u011bkolik \u00fakon\u016f najednou. Pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 k tomu  a p\u0159ekvapiv\u011b i videohry.T\u00fdm m\u00e1 za sebou hned n\u011bkolik zaj\u00edmav\u00fdch pokus\u016f s um\u011blou inteligenc\u00ed a ten nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed nese n\u00e1zev , nebo tak\u00e9 . Kombinuje tr\u00e9ninkov\u00fd re\u017eim, postaven\u00fd na k\u00f3du ak\u010dn\u00ed hry Quake III od studia ID Software a rozhran\u00ed, na kter\u00e9m b\u011b\u017e\u00ed star\u00e9 hry z platformy Atari. 57 her najednou, abychom byli p\u0159esn\u00ed.Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence prost\u0159ednictv\u00edm programu IMPALA hraje paraleln\u011b celou \u0159adu videoher a pos\u00edl\u00e1 informace od t\u00fdmu virtu\u00e1ln\u00edch \"hr\u00e1\u010d\u016f\" k t\u00fdmu virtu\u00e1ln\u00edch \"u\u010dedn\u00edk\u016f\". Je to jako kdyby hr\u00e1lo hru 30 \u017eiv\u00fdch hr\u00e1\u010d\u016f s t\u00edm, \u017ee ve\u0161ker\u00e9 zku\u0161enosti dostane do hlavy jeden \"vyvolen\u00fd\". V\u00fdsledky jsou p\u016fsobiv\u00e9.N\u00ed\u017ee se m\u016f\u017eete pod\u00edvat, jak hraje testovac\u00ed level \u017eiv\u00fd hr\u00e1\u010d:A zde m\u016f\u017eete porovnat, jak se jej zkou\u0161\u00ed um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence skrze program IMPALA:C\u00edlem tohoto programu je nau\u010dit um\u011blou inteligenci zpracov\u00e1vat tis\u00edce jednotliv\u00fdch sn\u00edmk\u016f a situac\u00ed najednou, neboli multitasking, a IMPALA je zd\u00e1 se skv\u011bl\u00fdm zp\u016fsobem, jak toho doc\u00edlit. Jedin\u011b pak bude mo\u017en\u00e9 neuronov\u00e9 s\u00edt\u011b vyu\u017e\u00edt v projektech, jako je samo\u0159\u00edd\u00edc\u00ed auto \u010di dal\u0161\u00edch autonomn\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edch, kter\u00e9 by mohly potenci\u00e1ln\u011b po\u0161kodit prost\u0159ed\u00ed \u010di u\u017eivatele samotn\u00e9ho.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Software", "Google", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Um\u011bl\u00e1 inteligence", "Neuronov\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165", "DeepMind", "Samo\u0159\u00edd\u00edc\u00ed auto", "Skv\u011bl\u00fd zp\u016fsob", "Id Software", "Cel\u00e1 \u0159ada", "Videohra", "Ak\u010dn\u00ed hra", "\u00dakon", "Pokro\u010dil\u00fd algoritmus", "Nov\u00fd zp\u016fsob", "Atari", "Multitasking", "Inteligence", "Star\u00e1 hra", "Zaj\u00edmav\u00fd pokus", "Quake III"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/apple-chce-vyrobit-stylus-kterym-budete-moci-kreslit-v-prostoru/sc-3-a-191759/default.aspx", "title": "Apple chce vyrobit stylus, kter\u00fdm budete moci kreslit v prostoru", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "11. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Apple p\u0159edned\u00e1vnem zaregistroval , kter\u00fd by mohl b\u00fdt indici\u00ed, kam se hodl\u00e1 ub\u00edrat budoucnost jeho stylusu a bezdotykov\u00e9ho ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed celkov\u011b. Podle popisu by toti\u017e m\u011blo j\u00edt o \"\".To v z\u00e1sad\u011b znamen\u00e1, \u017ee bychom mohli v budoucnu pou\u017e\u00edvat stylus pro interakci s Macbookem, iPadem a dal\u0161\u00edmi za\u0159\u00edzen\u00edmi Applu p\u0159\u00edmo ve vzduchu bez kontaktu s displejem. Doc\u00edlit by se toho m\u011blo vyu\u017eit\u00edm pohybov\u00fdch senzor\u016f, kter\u00e9 by registrovaly pohyb stylusu v prostoru, tak\u017ee by \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd povrch nebyl pot\u0159eba.Podobn\u00fd zp\u016fsob ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed u\u017e se bude bl\u00ed\u017eit m\u00e1v\u00e1n\u00ed rukou z filmu Minority Report, jen m\u00edsto rukavic budeme pou\u017e\u00edvat stylus. Rozhodn\u011b jde o skv\u011bl\u00fd n\u00e1pad, ot\u00e1zkou ale je, co Apple s t\u00edmto konceptem ud\u011bl\u00e1. Je toti\u017e v\u0161eobecn\u011b zn\u00e1m\u00e9, \u017ee patenty ne v\u017edy kon\u010d\u00ed \u00fasp\u011b\u0161n\u00fdm produktem.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Software", "Apple", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "MacBook", "Patenty", "iPad", "Bezdotykov\u00e9 ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed", "\u00dasp\u011b\u0161n\u00fd produkt", "Pohybov\u00fd senzor", "Povrch", "Skv\u011bl\u00fd n\u00e1pad", "Prostor", "Patent", "Nov\u00fd patent", "Ovl\u00e1d\u00e1n\u00ed", "Podobn\u00fd zp\u016fsob", "Dotykov\u00e1 obrazovka", "Stylus", "Kontakt"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/vytvorili-jsme-cernou-diru-behem-par-let-znici-slunecni-soustavu-ale-jen-v-simulaci/sc-3-a-191767/default.aspx", "title": "Vytvo\u0159ili jsme \u010dernou d\u00edru. B\u011bhem p\u00e1r let zni\u010d\u00ed slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavu (ale jen v simulaci)", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "11. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "\u00danorov\u00e1 zakabon\u011bn\u00e1 obloha sice moc p\u0159\u00edle\u017eitost\u00ed ke sledov\u00e1n\u00ed hv\u011bzd ned\u00e1v\u00e1, ale za p\u00e1r m\u011bs\u00edc\u016f je tu op\u011bt l\u00e9to a s n\u00edm p\u0159ijdou i \u010dast\u011bj\u0161\u00ed pohledy vzh\u016fru. A kdo v\u00ed, mo\u017en\u00e1 i n\u011bjak\u00e9 to filozofick\u00e9 p\u0159em\u00edt\u00e1n\u00ed nad existencion\u00e1ln\u00edmi ot\u00e1zkami o vesm\u00edru. .Co to znamen\u00e1 mal\u00e1 \u010dern\u00e1 d\u00edra? Dejme tomu, \u017ee by m\u011bla v pr\u016fm\u011bru sm\u011b\u0161n\u00e9 t\u0159i kilometry a do slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavy by zam\u00ed\u0159ila kdesi mezi ob\u011b\u017enou drahou Saturnu a Uranu. Tedy ve vzd\u00e1lenostech od Zem\u011b, kam um\u011bl\u00e9 sondy cestuj\u00ed dlouh\u00e9 roky p\u0159i doslova astronomick\u00fdch rychlostech mnoha des\u00edtek kilometr\u016f za sekundu.Fajn, tak\u017ee co by se stalo? Doba pokro\u010dila a v\u00fdkon po\u010d\u00edta\u010d\u016f se dramaticky zv\u00fd\u0161il, tak\u017ee nam\u00edsto n\u011bkolika semestr\u016f str\u00e1ven\u00fdch na Astronomick\u00e9m \u00fastavu UK nebo t\u0159eba \u00dastavu teoretick\u00e9 fyziky a astrofyziky MU sta\u010d\u00ed s\u00e1hnout po n\u011bkter\u00e9m ze softwarov\u00fdch simul\u00e1tor\u016f slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavy.K t\u011bm nejzda\u0159ilej\u0161\u00edm (a p\u0159itom st\u00e1le pro b\u011b\u017en\u00e9 smrteln\u00edky) pat\u0159\u00ed . Je natolik dobr\u00fd, \u017ee t\u011bch , kter\u00e9 si auto\u0159i \u00fa\u010dtuj\u00ed, je snad i m\u00e1lo. Platit m\u016f\u017eete i bitcoinem a to bez zdlouhav\u00e9ho \u010dek\u00e1n\u00ed skrze platebn\u00ed br\u00e1nu Coinbase. Kryptom\u011bnou jsem nakonec zaplatil i j\u00e1, p\u0159i\u0161el o \u010d\u00e1stku  a za \u010dtvrt hodinky jsem u\u017e m\u011bl simul\u00e1tor na po\u010d\u00edta\u010di.Universe Sandbox 2 je v\u00fdukov\u00fd software, tak\u017ee se sna\u017e\u00ed, aby v\u0161e vypadalo jednodu\u0161e, hezky, fotorealisticky, ale z\u00e1rove\u0148 \u2013 pokud tu\u0161\u00edte, co vlastn\u011b d\u011bl\u00e1te \u2013 m\u016f\u017eete nastavit prakticky jak\u00fdkoliv parametr let\u00edc\u00edho  vesm\u00edrem.Vedle real-time simulace aktu\u00e1ln\u00edho stavu slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavy si z\u00e1rove\u0148 m\u016f\u017eete prohl\u00e9dnout p\u0159ipraven\u00e9 situace pro des\u00edtky historick\u00fdch i naprosto hypotetick\u00fdch ud\u00e1lost\u00ed. V nab\u00eddce je tak t\u0159eba posledn\u00ed \u00fapln\u00e9 zatm\u011bn\u00ed Slunce nad USA z lo\u0148sk\u00e9ho srpna nebo simulace, jak by to vypadalo, kdyby okolo Zem\u011b krou\u017eily rovnou dva M\u011bs\u00edce.A kdy\u017e by to byla nuda, sta\u010d\u00ed hmotnost M\u011bs\u00edce zn\u011bkolikan\u00e1sobit, tro\u0161ku animaci zrychlit a za p\u00e1r sekund a za tkliv\u00fdch t\u00f3n\u016f ambientn\u00edch smy\u010dc\u016f, kter\u00e9 jsou sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed planet\u00e1ria, uvid\u00edte, jak se upraven\u00fd M\u011bs\u00edc bo\u0159\u00ed do Zem\u011b a jej\u00ed povrch se zbarv\u00ed do ruda. Brzy teplota p\u0159es\u00e1hne 4 000 stup\u0148\u016f a v\u0161echno vybuchne.Universe Sandbox 2 dok\u00e1\u017ee simulovat v podstat\u011b cokoliv \u2013 tedy co se pohybu t\u00fd\u010de. Chcete nechat explodovat Jupiter a sledovat, jak jeho zbytky v p\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u00edch pades\u00e1ti letech ovlivn\u00ed celou slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavu? Jist\u011b, \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd probl\u00e9m. Chcete zahubit Australany, a tak na nejmen\u0161\u00ed kontinent hod\u00edte kilometrovou sk\u00e1lu odkudsi z p\u00e1su asteroid\u016f? Jist\u011b, \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd probl\u00e9m! Chcete kdesi za Plutem odp\u00e1lit supernovu a simulaci zpomalit t\u0159eba na p\u00e1r ms/s, abyste z toho v\u016fbec n\u011bco m\u011bli? Jist\u011b, \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd probl\u00e9m.Chcete vyslat do Slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavy tu na\u0161i sl\u00edbenou \u010dernou d\u00edru? Jasn\u011b, ani to samoz\u0159ejm\u011b nen\u00ed \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd probl\u00e9m! Poj\u010fme tedy na to.Na  jsem se do\u010detl, \u017ee nejmen\u0161\u00ed doposud zn\u00e1m\u00e1 \u010dern\u00e1 d\u00edra je vlastn\u011b docela cval\u00edk. Je sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed bin\u00e1rn\u00edho syst\u00e9mu  a krm\u00ed se energi\u00ed neboh\u00e9 hv\u011bzdy, ob\u011b t\u011blesa toti\u017e navz\u00e1jem rotuj\u00ed kolem spole\u010dn\u00e9ho t\u011b\u017ei\u0161t\u011b v agonick\u00e9m tane\u010dku. Tato \u010dern\u00e1 d\u00edra m\u00e1 hmotnost 3,8 Slunc\u00ed a pr\u016fm\u011br 24 kilometr\u016f.Uf, to je moc! J\u00e1 chci kamsi za Saturn poslat n\u011bco mnohem men\u0161\u00edho \u2013 sl\u00edben\u00e9 t\u0159\u00edkilometrov\u00e9 zrnko. Universe Sandbox 2 m\u00e1 pro tyto p\u0159\u00edpady tla\u010d\u00edtko , pomoc\u00ed kter\u00e9ho mohu do syst\u00e9m vlo\u017eit prakticky cokoliv po\u010d\u00ednaje kule\u010dn\u00edkovou koul\u00ed (ano, v\u00e1\u017en\u011b!) a kon\u010de ob\u0159\u00ed hv\u011bzdou.J\u00e1 si vyberu \u010dernou d\u00edru o , jej\u00ed\u017e pr\u016fm\u011br odpov\u00edd\u00e1 pr\u00e1v\u011b . Ve\u0161ker\u00e9 parametry mohu samoz\u0159ejm\u011b kdykoliv zm\u011bnit.V dal\u0161\u00edm kroku mus\u00edm definovat pohyb. \u010cern\u00e1 d\u00edra m\u016f\u017ee krou\u017eit okolo Slunce, mohu ji tak\u00e9 postavit n\u011bkam do prostoru s nulovou v\u00fdchoz\u00ed hybnost\u00ed (v\u016f\u010di dan\u00e9 soustav\u011b), anebo ji vyst\u0159el\u00edm n\u011bjak\u00fdm sm\u011brem.A p\u0159esn\u011b to dnes ud\u011bl\u00e1m! Kamerou se nasm\u011bruji do m\u00edsta startu a hled\u00e1\u010dkem zac\u00edl\u00edm do bodu, kam m\u00e1 d\u00edra putovat. Z\u00e1rove\u0148 ji nastav\u00edm po\u010d\u00e1te\u010dn\u00ed rychlost 10 km/s.P\u0159i p\u0159\u00edprav\u011b simulace mus\u00edm b\u00fdt obez\u0159etn\u00fd, na rozd\u00edl od b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch planet\u00e1ri\u00ed se toti\u017e nemohu vr\u00e1tit v \u010dase. Kdy\u017e uprav\u00edm simulaci na rychlost n\u011bkolika dn\u016f za sekundu a pro\u0161vihnu n\u011bjakou ud\u00e1lost, nebudu moci sko\u010dit zp\u011bt \u2013 leda \u017ee bych simulaci se stejn\u00fdmi parametry spustil zase od za\u010d\u00e1tku.Tak, konec \u0159e\u010d\u00ed, jdeme na to. Je sobota 10. \u00fanora 2018 a kr\u00e1tce okolo \u010dtvrt\u00e9 hodiny odpoledn\u00ed se kdesi daleko za ob\u011b\u017enou drahou Pluta z ni\u010deho nic objevila \u010dern\u00e1 d\u00edra s pr\u016fm\u011brem 3 km a hmotnost\u00ed jednoho Slunce. V\u011bdci ji dali jm\u00e9no .Nikdo netu\u0161\u00ed, kde se tam vzala, nicm\u00e9n\u011b dal\u0161\u00ed v\u00fdpo\u010dty odhal\u00ed, \u017ee se p\u0159ibli\u017euje rychlost\u00ed 10 km/s a slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavu protne kdesi na \u00farovni ob\u011b\u017en\u00e9 dr\u00e1hy Saturnu.P\u0159\u00edtomnost sice mali\u010dk\u00e9ho, ale nesm\u00edrn\u011b t\u011b\u017ek\u00e9ho t\u011blesa okam\u017eit\u011b za\u010dne ovliv\u0148ovat ve\u0161kerou hmotu v \u0161ir\u00e9m okol\u00ed; jako by se na druh\u00e9 stran\u011b slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavy z \u010dista jasna objevilo dal\u0161\u00ed Slunce. Jen ho nevid\u00edme.Uplyne n\u011bkolik dlouh\u00fdch let, planety ob\u00edhaj\u00ed Slunce zd\u00e1nliv\u011b stejn\u011b jako d\u0159\u00edv, p\u0159esto se v\u0161ak mnoho v\u011bc\u00ed zm\u011bnilo. Slunce a Bo\u017eenka se vz\u00e1jemn\u011b p\u0159ibli\u017euj\u00ed, \u010d\u00edm\u017e se za\u010d\u00ednaj\u00ed deformovat ob\u011b\u017en\u00e9 dr\u00e1hy prakticky v\u0161ech t\u011bles. T\u0159\u00edkilometrov\u00e1 \u010dern\u00e1 d\u00edra je p\u0159itom st\u00e1le ve vzd\u00e1lenosti bezm\u00e1la 100 AU od Slunce (tedy ve 100\u00d7 v\u011bt\u0161\u00ed vzd\u00e1lenosti, ne\u017e je st\u0159edn\u00ed vzd\u00e1lenost Zem\u011b od Slunce).Zem\u011b st\u00e1le ob\u00edh\u00e1 okolo Slunce, i kdy\u017e slapov\u00e9 s\u00edly \u010dern\u00e9 d\u00edry jsou st\u00e1le mocn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed. P\u00ed\u0161e se rok 2031. Budeme muset tro\u0161ku zrychlit simulaci!Kv\u011bten 2042. Od objeven\u00ed \u010dern\u00e9 d\u00edry uplynulo 24 let a ta u\u017e v na\u0161em pozorovac\u00edm m\u011b\u0159\u00edtku zachytila krajn\u00ed planety Uran a Saturn, kter\u00e9 ji byly nejbl\u00ed\u017ee. Jejich trajektorie d\u00e1v\u00e1 tu\u0161it, \u017ee nejsp\u00ed\u0161e opou\u0161t\u011bj\u00ed soustavu Slunce a stanou se ob\u011b\u017enicemi Bo\u017eenky.Slunce nakonec Uran udr\u017e\u00ed, av\u0161ak Saturn s hromadou sv\u00fdch m\u011bs\u00edc\u016f nad\u00e1le ob\u00edh\u00e1 okolo \u010dern\u00e9 d\u00edry. V pon\u011bkud prek\u00e9rn\u00ed situaci jsou pak n\u011bkter\u00e9 dal\u0161\u00ed velk\u00e9 planety, u kter\u00fdch jejich osud zat\u00edm nen\u00ed \u00fapln\u011b jasn\u00fd. Nap\u0159\u00edklad Jupiter nyn\u00ed se sv\u00fdmi m\u011bs\u00edci let\u00ed osamocen\u011b vesm\u00edrem a ke v\u0161emu p\u0159i\u0161el o Europu, kter\u00e1 se stala samostatnou ob\u011b\u017enic\u00ed Slunce.A to ne tak ledajakou! Slunce obl\u00e9tne jednou za 4,5 roku, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e na p\u00e1r m\u011bs\u00edc\u016f by mohla i rozmrznout, dostane se toti\u017e bl\u00edzko ke zdroji energie a\u017e na \u00farove\u0148 ob\u011b\u017en\u00e9 dr\u00e1hy Zem\u011b.SpaceX n\u011bkdej\u0161\u00edho slavn\u00e9ho pr\u016fkopn\u00edka Elona Muska chyst\u00e1 meziplanet\u00e1rn\u00ed sondu, kter\u00e1 m\u00e1 definitivn\u011b odhalit, co se odehr\u00e1v\u00e1 pod zten\u010duj\u00edc\u00edm se ledov\u00fdm p\u0159\u00edkrovem planetky, kter\u00e1 byla kdysi m\u011bs\u00edcem Jupiteru.Oba slune\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my se na sklonku 21. stolet\u00ed relativn\u011b ust\u00e1l\u00ed, cestuj\u00ed vedle sebe galaxi\u00ed, a pokud lidstvo nezahubila n\u011bkter\u00e1 z mal\u00fdch planetek, kterou tento tane\u010dek vymr\u0161til z p\u016fvodn\u00ed dr\u00e1hy, na\u0161i prapravnuci u\u017e maj\u00ed \u00fapln\u011b jin\u00e9 u\u010debnice s n\u00e1kresy slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavy.A to je v\u0161e? Ano. A nebyla to tro\u0161ku nuda? Dobr\u00e1 tedy! Do simulace samoz\u0159ejm\u011b m\u016f\u017eeme libovoln\u011b vstupovat p\u0159esouvat objekty v prostoru a m\u011bnit jejich parametry. A jeliko\u017e se n\u00e1m bl\u00ed\u017e\u00ed konec \u010dl\u00e1nku, m\u016f\u017eeme skoncovat i se slune\u010dn\u00ed soustavou. Pr\u016fm\u011br \u010dern\u00e9 d\u00edry narostl na 295 kilometr\u016f a z relativn\u011b ne\u0161kodn\u00e9ho  se stal mezihv\u011bzdn\u00fd . A to doslova. Jak\u00e9koliv t\u011bleso, kter\u00e9 se dostane do jeho bl\u00edzkosti a Bo\u017eenka jej nepohlt\u00ed, z\u00edsk\u00e1 obrovskou rychlost a\u017e n\u011bkolika tis\u00edc km/s a je doslova vyst\u0159eleno do mezihv\u011bzdn\u00e9ho prostoru.Bo\u017eenka okam\u017eit\u011b p\u0159eb\u00edr\u00e1 roli srdce nov\u00e9 soustavy, okolo kter\u00e9 ob\u00edh\u00e1 naprosto v\u0161e v\u010detn\u011b Slunce. A okolo Slunce st\u00e1le ob\u00edh\u00e1 n\u011bkolik mal\u00fdch planet v\u010detn\u011b Zem\u011b. Slapov\u00e9 s\u00edly jsou obrovsk\u00e9, ale v\u0161e je\u0161t\u011b st\u00e1le funguje. Alespo\u0148 z na\u0161eho \u00fahlu pohledu. Co se p\u0159esn\u011b d\u011bje na Zemi, je pod rozli\u0161ovac\u00ed schopnost Simul\u00e1toru, nicm\u00e9n\u011b o lehkou atmosf\u00e9ru podle jeho dat planeta je\u0161t\u011b nep\u0159i\u0161la.To jsem nem\u011bl d\u011blat. Zem\u011b u\u017e nen\u00ed. Zmizela ze simulace prakticky okam\u017eit\u011b b\u011bhem n\u011bkolika milisekund od spu\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed. Ostatn\u00ed planety a Slunce zat\u00edm m\u011bly \u0161t\u011bst\u00ed \u2013 byly v lep\u0161\u00ed poloze. Prol\u00e9tly okolo \u010dern\u00e9 d\u00edry obrovskou rychlost\u00ed, ov\u0161em \u010derstv\u011b vypo\u010d\u00edtan\u00e9 trajektorie jejich ob\u011b\u017en\u00fdch drah nev\u011bst\u00ed nic dobr\u00e9ho. Jen co si je Bo\u017eenka p\u0159it\u00e1hne zp\u011bt, bude to nejsp\u00ed\u0161e jejich definitivn\u00ed konec.Slunce unik\u00e1 rychlost\u00ed 500 km/s, ale nakonec p\u0159eci jen zpomaluje. Ostatn\u00ed t\u011blesa s men\u0161\u00ed masou postupn\u011b zanikaj\u00ed a s nimi i cel\u00e1 n\u011bkdej\u0161\u00ed slune\u010dn\u00ed soustava.Gravitace Bo\u017eenky definitivn\u011b v\u00edt\u011bz\u00ed nad mate\u0159skou hv\u011bzdou, kter\u00e1 se vrac\u00ed zp\u011bt, zrychluje a n\u011bkolik milion\u016f kilometr\u016f p\u0159ed samotn\u00fdm horizontem ud\u00e1lost\u00ed jej gravitace \u010dern\u00e9 d\u00edry drt\u00ed na kusy.Z velk\u00fdch planet p\u0159e\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 jen Jupiter, kter\u00fd bude dal\u0161\u00ed miliony let ob\u00edhat okolo \u010dern\u00e9 d\u00edry, ne\u017e se nakonec i on s\u00e1m definitivn\u011b vypa\u0159\u00ed, po ka\u017ed\u00e9m p\u0159ibl\u00ed\u017een\u00ed toti\u017e ztrat\u00ed \u010d\u00e1st hmoty. A to je konec.Universe Sandbox 2 je skv\u011bl\u00e1 hra\u010dka, ale i u\u010debnice, kter\u00e1 za t\u011bch p\u00e1r stovek rozhodn\u011b stoj\u00ed. K\u00e9\u017e by byly podobn\u00e9 programy samoz\u0159ejmou v\u00fdbavou hodin fyziky na ka\u017ed\u00e9 \u0161kole.", "tags": ["Software", "Vesm\u00edr", "Budoucnost", "Steam", "USA", "SpaceX", "Zem\u011b", "M\u011bs\u00edc", "Slune\u010dn\u00ed soustava", "Slunce", "Jupiter", "Simulace", "Saturn", "\u010cern\u00e9 d\u00edry", "Uran", "Pluto", "Velk\u00e1 vzd\u00e1lenost", "Historick\u00e1 ud\u00e1lost", "Sandbox", "Zdlouhav\u00e9 \u010dek\u00e1n\u00ed", "Podobn\u00fd program", "Dolar", "Ledov\u00fd p\u0159\u00edkrov", "Definitivn\u00ed konec", "\u0160ir\u00e9 okol\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/nova-sit-dostane-rychly-internet-do-letadel-kombinuje-satelit-a-lte-vysilace-stoji-i-v-cr/sc-3-a-191761/default.aspx", "title": "Nov\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165 dostane rychl\u00fd internet do letadel. Kombinuje satelit a LTE, vys\u00edla\u010de stoj\u00ed i v \u010cR", "author": "Filip K\u016f\u017eel", "date": "11. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Dlouh\u00e9 roky byly mobily na palub\u011b letadla tabu. Te\u010f se stav\u00ed speci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b, kombinuje se LTE a satelit, aby m\u011bli pasa\u017e\u00e9\u0159i rychl\u00fd internet. Nebudou jej p\u0159ij\u00edmat p\u0159\u00edmo ze s\u00edt\u011b EAN (European Aviation Network), k t\u00e9 se p\u0159ipoj\u00ed letadlo a pro cestuj\u00edc\u00ed rozsv\u00edt\u00ed Wi-Fi s\u00ed\u0165 (kterou pochopiteln\u011b zpoplatn\u00ed).EAN je n\u00e1dhern\u00e1 technologie. Poslechn\u011bte si, pro\u010d jej\u00ed geostacion\u00e1rn\u00ed satelit do vesm\u00edru nevynesl popul\u00e1rn\u00ed SpaceX, ale raketa Ariane. Kdy letadlo bere internet z vesm\u00edru a kdy z pozemn\u00edch vys\u00edla\u010d\u016f? A jak se vlastn\u011b dostane internet do satelitu?", "tags": ["Video", "Technologie", "Internet", "SpaceX", "P\u0159ipojen\u00ed k internetu", "Satelit", "LTE", "T\u00fdden mobiln\u011b", "Letadlo", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Pozemn\u00ed vys\u00edla\u010d", "Ariane", "Dlouh\u00fd rok", "EAN", "Speci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165", "Nov\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165", "Rychl\u00fd internet", "Wi-fi s\u00ed\u0165", "Vys\u00edla\u010d"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/rusti-jaderni-inzenyri-namisto-simulace-atomovych-bomb-tezili-bitcoin/sc-3-a-191775/default.aspx", "title": "Ru\u0161t\u00ed jadern\u00ed in\u017een\u00fd\u0159i nam\u00edsto simulace atomov\u00fdch bomb t\u011b\u017eili bitcoin", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Ka\u017ed\u00fd, kdo m\u00e1 p\u0159\u00edstup k v\u00fdkonn\u00e9mu \u2013 opravdu v\u00fdkonn\u00e9mu \u2013 po\u010d\u00edta\u010di, si mo\u017en\u00e1 v posledn\u00edch m\u011bs\u00edc\u00edch v souvislosti s kryptom\u011bnovou m\u00e1ni\u00ed v duchu p\u0159edstavoval, kolik by se na takov\u00e9 ma\u0161in\u011b asi dalo vyt\u011b\u017eit bitcoin\u016f. V\u011bt\u0161ina nejsp\u00ed\u0161e skon\u010dila jen u sn\u016f, nicm\u00e9n\u011b zam\u011bstnanc\u016fm \u00fastavu experiment\u00e1ln\u00ed fyziky v rusk\u00e9m Sarov\u011b bylo l\u00edto, \u017ee jejich superpo\u010d\u00edta\u010de le\u017e\u00ed ladem, a tak je p\u0159ipojili k internetu a za\u010dali t\u011b\u017eit.Snad by to nebyl a\u017e tak v\u00e1\u017en\u00fd p\u0159e\u010din, kdyby Sarov nebyl \u201ezak\u00e1zan\u00fdm m\u011bstem\u201c sov\u011btsk\u00e9ho a dnes rusk\u00e9ho jadern\u00e9ho programu, do kter\u00e9ho se cizinec dostane jen s obt\u00ed\u017eemi, jedn\u00e1 se toti\u017e o maxim\u00e1ln\u011b st\u0159e\u017een\u00e9 m\u00edsto. Z toho d\u016fvodu jsou tamn\u00ed superpo\u010d\u00edta\u010de se souhrnn\u00fdm v\u00fdkonem v\u00edce ne\u017e 1 PFLOPS odpojen\u00e9 od internetu a tento stav st\u0159e\u017e\u00ed bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed slu\u017eba FSB.A pr\u00e1v\u011b ta podle  (via ) zachytila pokusy o p\u0159ipojen\u00ed superpo\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00fdch cluster\u016f k internetu. N\u00e1sledn\u00fd audit pak odhalil i pravd\u011bpodobnou t\u011b\u017ebu kryptom\u011bn, a\u010dkoliv rusk\u00e9 \u00fa\u0159ady si podrobnosti pochopiteln\u011b nech\u00e1vaj\u00ed pro sebe.", "tags": ["Kryptom\u011bny", "Internet", "Bitcoin", "Rusko", "T\u011b\u017eba", "Simulace", "Atomov\u00e1 bomba", "Sov\u011btsk\u00fd svaz", "Jadern\u00fd \u00fatok", "Ars Technica", "Superpo\u010d\u00edta\u010de", "Souhrnn\u00fd v\u00fdkon", "In\u017een\u00fdr", "Bomba", "Superpo\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00fd cluster", "Bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed slu\u017eba", "Rusk\u00fd \u00fa\u0159ad"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/cesky-internet-slavi-26-let-jak-se-to-vlastne-cele-prihodilo/sc-3-a-186127/default.aspx", "title": "\u010cesk\u00fd internet slav\u00ed 26 let. Jak se to vlastn\u011b cel\u00e9 p\u0159ihodilo?", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Nakupte bal\u00f3nky, \u0161ampus a p\u0159ipravte chleb\u00ed\u010dky, z\u00edtra toti\u017e slav\u00edme. Co se d\u011bje? Ale, jen takov\u00e1 drobnost: . Matado\u0159i prvn\u00ed tuzemsk\u00e9 internetov\u00e9 generace za\u010d\u00ednaj\u00ed pov\u00e1\u017eliv\u011b \u0161ediv\u011bt, z uhrovit\u00fdch geek\u016f se stali sv\u011bdomit\u00ed otcov\u00e9 a nejeden kudrnat\u00fd program\u00e1tor, kter\u00fd tehdy tr\u00e1vil voln\u00fd \u010das na BBS a Gopheru, dnes vlastn\u00ed firmu s miliardov\u00fdmi obraty. T\u0159eba Ivo Luka\u010dovi\u010d.Poj\u010fme si tedy p\u0159ipomenout, jak to tehdy v\u0161echno za\u010d\u00ednalo, jak to bylo z dne\u0161n\u00edho \u00fahlu pohledu jen t\u011b\u017eko p\u0159edstaviteln\u00e9 a kde stoj\u00ed po\u010d\u00e1tky toho, d\u00edky \u010demu\u017e dnes teenage\u0159i nehltaj\u00ed Davida Hasselhoffa, Brendu a Kelly, ale .Zat\u00edmco historie glob\u00e1ln\u00edho internetu a jeho p\u0159edch\u016fdce ARPANET sah\u00e1 hluboko do 60. let minul\u00e9ho stolet\u00ed, ta \u010deskoslovensk\u00e1 se za\u010dala ps\u00e1t ve \u010dtvrtek . Slavnostn\u00ed akt, kter\u00e9ho se v posluch\u00e1rn\u011b \u010d. 256 Fakulty elektrotechnick\u00e9 \u010cVUT \u00fa\u010dastnili i z\u00e1stupci americk\u00e9 NSF, fakticky propojil \u010deskou akademickou s\u00ed\u0165 s internetem skrze uzel v rakousk\u00e9m Linci.Prvn\u00ed experiment\u00e1ln\u00ed zahrani\u010dn\u00ed p\u0159enosy dosahovaly rychlost\u00ed z\u00e1vratn\u00fdch   a jednalo se v podstat\u011b o b\u011b\u017en\u00fd zahrani\u010dn\u00ed telefon\u00e1t. D\u00edky podpo\u0159e americk\u00e9 nadace George Mellon Foundation v\u0161ak mohli \u010de\u0161t\u00ed internetov\u00ed pr\u016fkopn\u00edci zakoupit lep\u0161\u00ed hardwarovou v\u00fdbavu a modemy a rychlost na pevn\u00e9 lince se nav\u00fd\u0161ila na tehdy slu\u0161n\u00fdch . Univerzita v Linci byla p\u0159ipojen\u00e1 do evropsk\u00e9 akademick\u00e9 s\u00edt\u011b EARN a tehdej\u0161\u00ed \u010ceskoslovensko se tak stalo sou\u010d\u00e1st\u00ed mladi\u010dk\u00e9ho internetu.Americk\u00fd internet se rodil jako akademick\u00fd projekt sponzorovan\u00fd v\u011bdeckou nadac\u00ed NSF, kter\u00e1 do n\u011bj necht\u011bla vpustit komer\u010dn\u00ed subjekty. Akademik\u016fm se nen\u00ed \u010demu divit, p\u00e1te\u0159n\u00ed linky t\u00e9 doby toti\u017e byly pomal\u00e9 a v\u011bdci se re\u00e1ln\u011b ob\u00e1vali, \u017ee by komer\u010dn\u00ed provoz s\u00ed\u0165 p\u0159\u00edli\u0161 zahltil.Ke komercializaci tedy doch\u00e1zelo postupn\u011b a prakticky  zhruba do konce 80. let, kdy se za oce\u00e1nem za\u010dali objevovat prvn\u00ed neakademi\u010dt\u00ed poskytovatel\u00e9 internetu, kte\u0159\u00ed vyu\u017e\u00edvali v\u00e1gn\u00ed definice komer\u010dn\u00edho provozu. V roce 1992 jim pak pomohl i Kongres, kter\u00fd p\u0159ijal legislativu, jen\u017e umo\u017enila do s\u00edt\u011b p\u0159ipojit i ur\u010dit\u00e9 komunity, kter\u00e9 se vysloven\u011b nev\u011bnovaly v\u00fdzkumu.V\u00fdsadn\u00ed postaven\u00ed NSF jako\u017eto kormideln\u00edka internetu nebylo bezd\u016fvodn\u00e9. Po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9 s\u00edt\u011b na p\u0159elomu 80. a 90. let samoz\u0159ejm\u011b bujely po cel\u00e9m sv\u011bt\u011b, americk\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165 (NSFNET) ale byla zdaleka nejrozs\u00e1hlej\u0161\u00ed, a tak se v\u0161ichni cht\u011bli p\u0159ipojit k jej\u00edm p\u00e1te\u0159n\u00edm link\u00e1m.NSF tedy m\u011bla nesporn\u00e9 pr\u00e1vo na dohled a p\u0159\u00edsn\u00e9 podm\u00ednky, k \u010demu v\u0161emu se takov\u00fd propojen\u00fd internet bude pou\u017e\u00edvat, co\u017e platilo i o mladi\u010dk\u00e9m \u010deskoslovensk\u00e9m internetu, kter\u00fd tu byl pro akademiky a nikoliv pro .Pr\u00e1v\u011b to je d\u016fvod, pro\u010d svou prvn\u00ed p\u00e1te\u0159n\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165 v \u010cesku nebudoval z\u00e1stup komer\u010dn\u00edch oper\u00e1tor\u016f, ale Oblastn\u00ed v\u00fdpo\u010detn\u00ed centrum vysok\u00fdch \u0161kol, kter\u00e9mu \u0161\u00e9foval Jan Gruntor\u00e1d, a kter\u00e9 se v roce 1996 p\u0159etavilo v CESNET. Sdru\u017een\u00ed vysok\u00fdch \u0161kol a Akademie v\u011bd \u010cR od t\u00e9 doby koordinuje \u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed internetu na akademick\u00fdch pracovi\u0161t\u00edch. Pokud se p\u0159ipojujete k internetu t\u0159eba na kolej\u00edch, surfujete pov\u011bt\u0161inou pr\u00e1v\u011b na \u0161pi\u010dkov\u00e9 infrastruktu\u0159e CESNETu.Jak u\u017e jsem napsal v\u00fd\u0161e, a\u010dkoliv byl internet zpo\u010d\u00e1tku ryze akademick\u00fd, zejm\u00e9na v z\u00e1mo\u0159\u00ed se p\u0159esto ji\u017e na sklonku 80. let objevovali prvn\u00ed komer\u010dn\u00ed oper\u00e1to\u0159i. \u010cesko v\u0161ak m\u011blo jedno specifikum, kter\u00e9 odlo\u017eilo postupnou komercializaci internetu o n\u011bkolik zbyte\u010dn\u00fdch let \u2013 licen\u010dn\u00ed monopol.Ten a\u017e do roku 1995 dr\u017eel Eurotel Praha, s.r.o.a exkluzivitu na provoz datov\u00fdch komunika\u010dn\u00edch s\u00edt\u00ed m\u011bl jednodu\u0161e proto, \u017ee se tehdej\u0161\u00ed \u00fa\u0159edn\u00ed apar\u00e1t domn\u00edval, \u017ee s touto ochranou do \u010ceska sp\u00ed\u0161e doraz\u00ed pot\u0159ebn\u00e9 investice na stavbu nov\u00fdch s\u00edt\u00edEurotel sice datovou infrastrukturu skute\u010dn\u011b budoval, ale samotn\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed k internetu nenab\u00edzel. Byl to za\u010darovan\u00fd kruh. V roce 1995 nicm\u00e9n\u011b firma prodala svoji datovou divizi NexTel, kter\u00e1 m\u011bla v\u0161e na starost, SPT Telecomu (pozd\u011bji \u010cesk\u00e9mu Telecomu), \u010d\u00edm\u017e p\u0159estala platit p\u016fvodn\u00ed exkluzivn\u00ed licence a trh se kone\u010dn\u011b otev\u0159el v\u0161em.Rok 1995 je p\u0159elomov\u00fd i v glob\u00e1ln\u00edm kontextu. Internet se toti\u017e postupn\u00fdm p\u0159ipojov\u00e1n\u00edm dal\u0161\u00edch a dal\u0161\u00edch s\u00edt\u00ed decentralizoval, liberalizoval a kone\u010dn\u011b i komercializoval a NSF ve veden\u00ed nahradily p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm organizace ICANN a IANA, kter\u00e9 dohl\u00ed\u017eej\u00ed na syst\u00e9m p\u0159id\u011blov\u00e1n\u00ed IP adres a dom\u00e9nov\u00fdch jmen nejvy\u0161\u0161\u00edho \u0159\u00e1du, kam pat\u0159\u00ed i \u010desk\u00e1 CZ.Zhruba tou dobou se tak\u00e9 definitivn\u011b prosadila internetov\u00e1 technologie  jist\u00e9ho britsk\u00e9ho v\u00fdzkumn\u00edka z CERNu Tima Bernerse-Leeho a miliony, des\u00edtky milion\u016f a pak i stovky milion\u016f a miliardy surfa\u0159\u016f po cel\u00e9m sv\u011bt\u011b objevily kouzlo takzvan\u00fdch webov\u00fdch str\u00e1nek napsan\u00fdch v jazyce HTML, kter\u00e9 dok\u00e1zaly podobn\u011b jako noviny nebo \u010dasopis zobrazit na monitoru form\u00e1tovan\u00fd text a grafiku sta\u017eenou ze serveru na druh\u00e9 stran\u011b planety.Pr\u00e1v\u011b onen p\u0159elom mezi \u010dernob\u00edlou a barevnou \u00e9rou, ke kter\u00e9 v \u010desk\u00fdch podm\u00ednk\u00e1ch do\u0161lo v druh\u00e9 polovin\u011b 90. let, byl mo\u017en\u00e1 ze v\u0161eho nejzaj\u00edmav\u011bj\u0161\u00ed. Zat\u00edmco v jednu chv\u00edli jste v textov\u00e9m re\u017eimu DOSu, Windows nebo na unixov\u00fdch syst\u00e9mech koukali, co si st\u00e1hnete z FTP server\u016f, co se zrovna d\u011bje v diskuz\u00edch na BBSk\u00e1ch a co p\u00ed\u0161ou akademici na Gopheru, r\u00e1zem tu byl World Wide Web a jeden jedin\u00fd program \u2013 , kter\u00fd se pro p\u0159\u00ed\u0161t\u00edch dvacet let stal univerz\u00e1ln\u00edm oknem do internetu a v podstat\u011b nahradil a zabil des\u00edtky star\u0161\u00edch technologi\u00ed. Jednou z m\u00e1la prehistorick\u00fdch technologi\u00ed, kter\u00e1 dnes sv\u00fdm internetov\u00fdm objemem st\u00e1le konkuruje protokolu HTTP, je snad pouze e-mail.S liberalizac\u00ed internetu se naplno rozjel i hon na dom\u00e9ny. Kdyby se \u010ceskoslovensko na sklonku roku 1992 nerozpadlo, dnes budeme m\u00edt adresu . Nakonec to ale dopadlo tro\u0161ku jinak, a tak dnes spr\u00e1vce \u010desk\u00e9 dom\u00e9ny eviduje bezm\u00e1la .P\u0159itom ani ty si v po\u010d\u00e1tku nemohl po\u0159\u00eddit jen tak kdekdo. K pln\u00e9 liberalizaci do\u0161lo a\u017e v roce 1997, kdy zdej\u0161\u00ed internetov\u00ed hr\u00e1\u010di z \u0159ad oper\u00e1tor\u016f zalo\u017eili sdru\u017een\u00ed CZ.NIC a otev\u0159eli trh s dom\u00e9nami naprosto ka\u017ed\u00e9mu. Cena sice byla zpo\u010d\u00e1tku z\u00e1vratn\u00e1, brzy v\u0161ak ro\u010dn\u00ed pron\u00e1jem klesl na \u010d\u00e1stku okolo stokoruny, a tak jsou dnes v\u0161echny atraktivn\u00ed kombinace ji\u017e d\u00e1vno rozebran\u00e9.Zbytek u\u017e zn\u00e1te. V roce 1995 za\u010dal pomalu vznikat Seznam,  jako tehdej\u0161\u00ed zpravodajsk\u00e1 elektronick\u00e1 p\u0159\u00edloha Computeru z Invexu a na p\u0159elomu tis\u00edcilet\u00ed se za\u010dalo \u0161\u00ed\u0159it instantn\u00ed broadbandov\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed i do dom\u00e1cnost\u00ed. Drah\u00fd vyt\u00e1\u010den\u00fd internet prakticky vymizel a tuzem\u0161t\u00ed oper\u00e1to\u0159i dnes v mnoha lokalit\u00e1ch b\u011b\u017en\u00fdm smrteln\u00edk\u016fm nab\u00edzej\u00ed i gigabitov\u00e9 p\u0159ipojen\u00ed \u2013  ne\u017e na onom po\u010d\u00e1tku \u010desk\u00e9ho internetu.B\u011bhem dvaceti let vytvo\u0159il internet miliony nov\u00fdch pracovn\u00edch m\u00edst, dramaticky pozm\u011bnil rychlost \u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00ed informac\u00ed, p\u0159inesl slu\u017ebu WWW a soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b a prom\u00edtl se prakticky do v\u0161ech aspekt\u016f lidsk\u00e9ho \u017eivota. Z dopl\u0148kov\u00e9 akademick\u00e9 slu\u017eby se stala technologie, kterou dnes mnoz\u00ed pova\u017euj\u00ed za p\u0159irozen\u00e9 lidsk\u00e9 pr\u00e1vo a stejnou samoz\u0159ejmost jako elekt\u0159ina.", "tags": ["Web", "Historie", "Windows", "Internet", "Wikipedia", "Investice", "IT Osobnosti", "Dom\u00e9na", "Praha", "CERN", "Arpanet", "Ivo Luka\u010dovi\u010d", "Invex", "Tim Berners-Lee", "Linec", "US West", "Icann", "BBS", "Ro\u010dn\u00ed pron\u00e1jem", "Zdroj", "Datov\u00e1 infrastruktura", "Franti\u0161ek Fuka", "P\u0159\u00edsn\u00fd dohled", "Slavnostn\u00ed akt", "\u010cesk\u00e1 s\u00ed\u0165"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/velmi-male-a-lehke-takove-maji-byt-bryle-pro-virtualni-realitu-od-applu-naznacuje-patent/sc-3-a-191763/default.aspx", "title": "Velmi mal\u00e9 a lehk\u00e9. Takov\u00e9 maj\u00ed b\u00fdt br\u00fdle pro virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed realitu od Applu, nazna\u010duje patent", "author": "Daniel P\u00e1nek", "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Nen\u00ed tajemstv\u00edm, \u017ee chyst\u00e1 Apple vlastn\u00ed br\u00fdle pro virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed i roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159enou realitu, Tim Cook na to ostatn\u011b u\u017e n\u011bkolikr\u00e1t upozor\u0148oval. Dokonce dodal, \u017ee technologie, kterou firma pot\u0159ebuje pro vytvo\u0159en\u00ed po\u017eadovan\u00fdch br\u00fdl\u00ed, zat\u00edm ani neexistuje. To v\u0161ak znamen\u00e1, \u017ee Apple piln\u011b pracuje na n\u011b\u010dem nov\u00e9m a dost mo\u017en\u00e1 pot\u0159ebnou technologii vyv\u00edj\u00ed.Poukazuje na to , kter\u00fd byl zaregistrov\u00e1n na americk\u00e9m patentov\u00e9m \u00fa\u0159ad\u011b. Jedn\u00edm ze z\u00e1kladn\u00edch c\u00edl\u016f je podle v\u0161eho v\u00fdroba br\u00fdl\u00ed \u010di headsetu, kter\u00fd je mnohem leh\u010d\u00ed a pohodln\u011bj\u0161\u00ed na ka\u017edodenn\u00ed no\u0161en\u00ed. Modern\u00ed br\u00fdle, jako je HoloLens \u010di Oculus Rift, jsou toti\u017e st\u00e1le velmi kostrbat\u00e9 a velk\u00e9.Apple by r\u00e1d u sv\u00fdch br\u00fdl\u00ed vyu\u017eil tzv. katadioptrick\u00e9ho syst\u00e9mu, kter\u00fd pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 zaoblen\u00e9 \u010do\u010dky a zrcad\u00e9lka pro kombinaci lomu sv\u011btla a jeho odrazu do jedin\u00e9ho celku. Podobn\u00fd syst\u00e9m se pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 u optick\u00fdch teleskop\u016f, mikroskop\u016f a dal\u0161\u00edch za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed a v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159i by t\u00edm mohli dos\u00e1hnout podstatn\u00e9ho zleh\u010den\u00ed a zten\u010den\u00ed designu br\u00fdl\u00ed.Prozat\u00edm to samoz\u0159ejm\u011b m\u016f\u017eeme br\u00e1t pouze jako spekulaci, jeliko\u017e registrace patent\u016f nemus\u00ed nutn\u011b znamenat, \u017ee je nov\u00e9 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed ve v\u00fdvoji \u010di v\u016fbec na cest\u011b. Apple by v\u0161ak byl s\u00e1m proti sob\u011b, kdyby nenasko\u010dil na rozjet\u00fd vlak virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed a roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e9 reality.", "tags": ["Hardware", "Apple", "Budoucnost", "Technologie", "Mobility", "Virtu\u00e1ln\u00ed realita", "Oculus Rift", "Roz\u0161\u00ed\u0159en\u00e1 realita", "Tim Cook", "Patenty", "Br\u00fdle", "HoloLens", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed c\u00edl", "Pot\u0159ebn\u00e1 technologie", "Jedin\u00fd celek", "Nov\u00fd patent", "Rozjet\u00fd vlak", "Realita", "Nov\u00e9 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed", "Optick\u00fd teleskop", "Patent", "Ka\u017edodenn\u00ed no\u0161en\u00ed", "Podobn\u00fd syst\u00e9m"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/tyden-zive-kabriolet-ve-vesmiru-intel-vaunt-a-papuce-s-autopilotem/sc-3-a-191752/default.aspx", "title": "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b: Kabriolet ve vesm\u00edru, Intel Vaunt a papu\u010de s autopilotem", "author": "David Polesn\u00fd", "date": "11. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Kabriolet Elona Muska odcestoval do meziplanet\u00e1rn\u00edho prostoru. Na m\u00edst\u011b \u0159idi\u010de sed\u00ed Starman a v p\u0159ihr\u00e1dce nechyb\u00ed Stopa\u0159\u016fv pr\u016fvodce galaxi\u00ed a ru\u010dn\u00edk. Intel se pochlubil sv\u00fdmi chytr\u00fdmi br\u00fdlemi Glass, my jsme si vyzkou\u0161eli \u0161pi\u010dkov\u00fd trackball a na z\u00e1v\u011br okomentujeme situaci na trhu s chytr\u00fdmi papu\u010demi.", "tags": ["Video", "Vesm\u00edr", "T\u00fdden \u017div\u011b", "Intel", "SpaceX", "Google Glass", "Falcon Heavy", "Br\u00fdle", "Logitech", "Elon Musk", "Kabriolet", "Glass", "Parkovac\u00ed asistent", "Autopilot", "Nissan", "Chytr\u00e9 br\u00fdle", "Papu\u010de", "Meziplanet\u00e1rn\u00ed prostor", "Starman"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/mobilni-pripojeni-a-sitova-neutralita/sc-3-a-191860/default.aspx", "title": "Mobiln\u00ed p\u0159ipojen\u00ed a s\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e1 neutralita", "author": null, "date": "13. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Je spousta druh\u016f mobiln\u00edho p\u0159ipojen\u00ed. Ob\u010das se v tom nevyzn\u00e1 ani samotn\u00fd poskytovatel. Pak je tady ale je\u0161t\u011b s\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e1 neutralita, se kterou mus\u00ed po\u010d\u00edtat. O \u010dem se tady vlastn\u011b bav\u00edme se dozv\u00edte v tomto videu.", "tags": ["Tipy", "P\u0159ipojen\u00ed k internetu", "S\u00ed\u0165ov\u00e1 neutralita", "Jak na Internet", "Neutralita", "Poskytovatel", "P\u0159ipojen\u00ed", "Spousta druh\u016f", "Mobiln\u00ed p\u0159ipojen\u00ed"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/applu-unikly-zdrojove-kody-ios-vcetne-zabezpeceni-iboot-zneuziti-nastesti-moc-nehrozi/sc-3-a-191776/default.aspx", "title": "Applu unikly zdrojov\u00e9 k\u00f3dy iOS v\u010detn\u011b zabezpe\u010den\u00ed iBoot. Zneu\u017eit\u00ed na\u0161t\u011bst\u00ed moc nehroz\u00ed", "author": "Patrik Macko", "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Na GitHubu se objevila \u010d\u00e1st zdrojov\u00e9ho k\u00f3du opera\u010dn\u00edho syst\u00e9mu iOS 9 a sou\u010d\u00e1sti iBoot, co\u017e zjevn\u011b nebyl zam\u00fd\u0161len\u00fd z\u00e1m\u011br Applu. O incidentu  server Apple Insider.iBoot m\u00e1 na starosti r\u016fzn\u00e9 verifika\u010dn\u00ed \u00fakoly a star\u00e1 se nap\u0159\u00edklad tak\u00e9 o ov\u011b\u0159en\u00ed podpisu j\u00e1dra syst\u00e9mu p\u0159i jeho startu. R\u016fzn\u00ed odborn\u00edci se shodli na tom, \u017ee jde pravd\u011bpodobn\u011b o nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed \u00fanik citliv\u00fdch dat zdrojov\u00e9ho k\u00f3du v historii.A\u010dkoliv unikl\u00e1 zdrojov\u00e1 data poch\u00e1zej\u00ed z opera\u010dn\u00edho syst\u00e9mu, kter\u00fd je star\u00fd n\u011bkolik let, podle r\u016fzn\u00fdch bezpe\u010dnostn\u00edch expert\u016f st\u00e1le m\u016f\u017ee \u00fanik p\u0159edstavovat ur\u010dit\u00e1 bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed rizika. N\u011bkter\u00e9 sou\u010d\u00e1sti iBoot se toti\u017e st\u00e1le mohou nach\u00e1zet i v nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00edm syst\u00e9mu iOS 11. K incidentu se vyj\u00e1d\u0159il i samotn\u00fd Appl a potvrdil, \u017ee ve skute\u010dnosti jde o sou\u010d\u00e1st zdrojov\u00e9ho k\u00f3du platformy iOS 9 z roku 2015. Rizika zneu\u017eit\u00ed jsou podle firmy jen minim\u00e1ln\u00ed, proto\u017ee star\u0161\u00ed verze syst\u00e9mu vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 jen mal\u00e9 procento lid\u00ed. Aktualizovan\u00e9 informace  Cnet.\u201eBezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed na\u0161ich produkt\u016f si nezakl\u00e1daj\u00ed na utajen\u00ed na\u0161ich zdrojov\u00fdch k\u00f3d\u016f. V na\u0161ich produktech je integrovan\u00fdch hned n\u011bkolik vrstev hardwarov\u00e9 \u010di softwarov\u00e9 ochrany. Nav\u00edc v\u017edy doporu\u010dujeme, aby si majitel\u00e9 sv\u00e9 p\u0159\u00edstroje aktualizovali na nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verzi opera\u010dn\u00edho syst\u00e9mu, d\u00edky \u010demu\u017e maj\u00ed k dispozici v\u017edy nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed prost\u0159edky ochrany,\u201c uvedla kalifornsk\u00e1 firma ve sv\u00e9m prohl\u00e1\u0161en\u00ed.", "tags": ["Apple", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Bezpe\u010dnost", "iPhone", "iOS", "GitHub", "K\u00f3d", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed verze", "Syst\u00e9m", "Mal\u00e9 procento", "Kalifornsk\u00e1 firma", "Citliv\u00e1 data", "Bezpe\u010dnostn\u00ed \u0159e\u0161en\u00ed", "Apple Insider", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "Verze syst\u00e9mu", "Zneu\u017eit\u00ed", "Nejnov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "Zdrojov\u00fd k\u00f3d", "CNET", "Zabezpe\u010den\u00ed", "Hardwarov\u00e1 ochrana", "Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed \u00fanik", "Star\u00e1 verze"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/facebook-pozval-moderatory-do-londyna-dorazili-i-cesi-rozda-jim-miliony-dolaru/sc-3-a-191753/default.aspx", "title": "Facebook pozval moder\u00e1tory do Lond\u00fdna. Dorazili i \u010ce\u0161i. Rozd\u00e1 jim miliony dolar\u016f", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Facebook chce profesionalizovat sv\u00e9 komunity, a tak do nich nalije miliony dolar\u016f a know-how. Nejv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165  spr\u00e1vce vybran\u00fdch skupin, kte\u0159\u00ed se mohli registrovat v nomina\u010dn\u00edm kole, a p\u0159edstavila zde .V r\u00e1mci dota\u010dn\u00edho programu bude Facebook vypisovat nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed formy stipendia pro moder\u00e1tory, aby sv\u00e9 skupiny zu\u0161lech\u0165ovali a kvalitn\u011b vedli \u2013 tento model principi\u00e1ln\u011b p\u0159ipom\u00edn\u00e1 partnersk\u00fd program YouTubu, kter\u00fd se zase sna\u017e\u00ed kultivovat a profesionalizovat youtuberskou sc\u00e9nu.V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b Facebooku nep\u016fjde o \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9 drobn\u00e9 \u2013 soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165 podpo\u0159\u00ed program \u0159\u00e1dov\u011b v des\u00edtk\u00e1ch milion\u016f dolar\u016f, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e ti nejvlivn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed moder\u00e1to\u0159i s region\u00e1ln\u00edm p\u0159esahem mohou z\u00edskat a\u017e milion dolar\u016f na financov\u00e1n\u00ed sv\u00fdch n\u00e1vrh\u016f. V podstat\u011b se z nich mohou st\u00e1t moder\u00e1to\u0159i na pln\u00fd \u00favazek.Na setk\u00e1n\u00ed facebookov\u00fdch skupin v Lond\u00fdn\u011b se nominovali i n\u011bkte\u0159\u00ed p\u0159edstavitel\u00e9 z \u010ceska. Nap\u0159\u00edklad moder\u00e1to\u0159i skupin , , ,  a .", "tags": ["Web", "Facebook", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b", "Investice", "Program", "Nejr\u016fzn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed forma", "Pln\u00fd \u00favazek", "Partnersk\u00fd program", "Facebookov\u00e1 skupina", "Dolar", "Czechitas", "Lond\u00fdn", "\u010cesk\u00e1 republika", "Dota\u010dn\u00ed program", "Moder\u00e1tor", "Skupina", "Mili\u00f3n dolar\u016f", "YouTube", "Vybran\u00e1 skupina"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/nvidia-freestyle-post-processing-ve-hrach-v-realnem-case-a-trochu-taky-cheatovani/sc-3-a-191773/default.aspx", "title": "Nvidia Freestyle: post-processing ve hr\u00e1ch v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase. A trochu taky cheatov\u00e1n\u00ed", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Nvidia p\u0159idala do sv\u00e9 platformy Experience dal\u0161\u00ed funkci pro hr\u00e1\u010de. Vedle toho, \u017ee um\u00ed optimalizovat hry pro konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed sestavu nebo zajistit okam\u017eit\u00fd z\u00e1znam d\u00edky Shadowplay, je nyn\u00ed mo\u017en\u00e9 tak\u00e9 v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase ovliv\u0148ovat grafick\u00e9 efekty v re\u00e1ln\u00e9m \u010dase. Krom\u011b toho, \u017ee lze stylizovat obraz d\u00edky mnoha \u00faprav\u00e1m, m\u016f\u017ee j\u00edt o drobn\u00fd cheat v kompetitivn\u00edch hr\u00e1ch.Nov\u00e1 funkce  je prozat\u00edm dostupn\u00e1 v r\u00e1mci testu, je ji proto pot\u0159eba povolit. V r\u00e1mci Geforce Experience proto v nastaven\u00ed za\u0161krtn\u011bte mo\u017enost . N\u00e1sledn\u011b u\u017e sta\u010d\u00ed spustit jednu z  a v n\u00ed kdykoliv stisknout kl\u00e1vesovou zkratku Alt + F3. T\u00edm se otev\u0159e bo\u010dn\u00ed panel s nastaven\u00edm v\u0161ech dostupn\u00fdch efekt\u016f.N\u011bkter\u00e9 z nich jsou \u010dist\u011b styliza\u010dn\u00ed a obdobou filtr\u016f na Instagramu. Jen m\u00e1lokdo by asi cht\u011bl hr\u00e1t hry v \u010dernob\u00edl\u00fdch odst\u00ednech, s vin\u011btac\u00ed nebo v s\u00e9piov\u00e9m odst\u00ednu. Naopak pro po\u0159izov\u00e1n\u00ed screenshot\u016f se m\u016f\u017ee hodit nastaven\u00ed hloubky ostrosti. Simulovat lze rozost\u0159en\u00ed vzd\u00e1len\u00fdch objekt\u016f, v\u010detn\u011b nastaven\u00ed \u00farovn\u011b bokehu nebo jeho vrchol\u016f.Velmi p\u0159\u00ednosnou funkc\u00ed ale bude Freestyle pro ty, kte\u0159\u00ed se v\u011bnuj\u00ed kompetitivnmu hran\u00ed a to p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm v titulech jako je CS:GO nebo PubG.Nejd\u016fle\u017eit\u011bj\u0161\u00edm efektem tady bude projasn\u011bn\u00ed tmav\u00fdch odst\u00edn\u016f obrazu. To umo\u017en\u00ed snadn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed zpozorov\u00e1n\u00ed soupe\u0159e v tmav\u00fdch roz\u00edch nebo st\u00ednech strom\u016f na otev\u0159en\u00e9 map\u011b. Mnoz\u00ed hr\u00e1\u010di tyto vlastnosti nastavovali p\u0159\u00edmo na monitorech, kter\u00e9 \u010dasto tyto funkce nab\u00edz\u00ed. Nyn\u00ed je to ale mo\u017en\u00e9 ovlivnit v r\u00e1mci softwaru pro grafickou kartu. Podobn\u011b si lze potom pohr\u00e1t i se samotnou expozic\u00ed celkov\u00e9ho obrazu.Dal\u0161\u00edm d\u016fle\u017eit\u00fdm parametrem, kter\u00fd lze ve Freestyle ovlivnit, je ostrost. Jej\u00ed zv\u00fd\u0161en\u00ed ocen\u00ed op\u011bt hr\u00e1\u010di her s velkou otev\u0159enou mapou, kde je d\u00edky tomu mo\u017en\u00e9 l\u00e9pe spat\u0159it soupe\u0159e v d\u00e1lce. Samoz\u0159ejm\u011b se to nesm\u00ed p\u0159ehnat, v takov\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b u\u017e m\u00e1 \u00faprava opa\u010dn\u00fd efekt.Proto\u017ee jde o softwarovou \u00fapravu a o jistou formu postprocesu, je t\u0159eba po\u010d\u00edtat s dopadem na v\u00fdkon. Majitel\u00e9 karet jako jsou GTX 1060 a nov\u011bj\u0161\u00ed, se nemus\u00ed b\u00e1t v\u00fdrazn\u00e9ho propadu sn\u00edmkov\u00fdch frekvenc\u00ed. My jsme otestovali Freestyle na GTX 1070 Ti, kde zapnut\u00ed efekt\u016f nem\u011blo \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd vliv na po\u010det vykreslovan\u00fdch sn\u00edmk\u016f za sekundu. Naopak p\u0159i pou\u017eit\u00ed na star\u0161\u00ed sestav\u011b s GTX 760, u\u017e byl dopad v\u00fdrazn\u00fd. I bez Freestyle je s touto kartou hran\u00ed PubG na hran\u011b, s jejich zapnut\u00edm se ale stane nehrateln\u00fdm.Rovn\u011b\u017e je t\u0159eba pamatovat na to, \u017ee jde o experiment\u00e1ln\u00ed funkci. Ne v\u017edy jsou v podporovan\u00fdch hr\u00e1ch dostupn\u00e9 v\u0161echny efekty. Nap\u0159\u00edklad v CS:GO nefunguje simulace mal\u00e9 hloubky ostrosti.Z Freestyle se ka\u017edop\u00e1dn\u011b stane d\u016fle\u017eit\u00e1 funkce pro online hr\u00e1\u010de. Doposud si mnoz\u00ed pom\u00e1hali softwarem t\u0159et\u00edch stran jako je , ten ale postupn\u011b za\u010d\u00ednaj\u00ed za\u0159azovat vydavatel\u00e9 her na seznam zak\u00e1zan\u00fdch dopl\u0148k\u016f. Naopak zak\u00e1zat funkci v ovlada\u010d\u00edch grafick\u00e9 karty bude slo\u017eit\u00e9.", "tags": ["Instagram", "Nvidia", "Hry", "Funkce", "Kl\u00e1vesov\u00e1 zkratka", "Cheatov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Vzd\u00e1len\u00fd objekt", "Sn\u00edmkov\u00e1 frekvence", "Celkov\u00fd obraz", "Shadowplay", "Nov\u00e1 funkce", "Opa\u010dn\u00fd efekt", "Bo\u010dn\u00ed panel", "T\u0159et\u00ed strana", "N\u00edzk\u00e9 FPS", "D\u016fle\u017eit\u00e1 funkce", "Okam\u017eit\u00fd z\u00e1znam", "Mal\u00e1 hloubka", "Freestyle", "Grafick\u00e1 karta", "Jist\u00e1 forma", "Grafick\u00fd efekt", "Ostrost", "GeForce Experience", "Experiment\u00e1ln\u00ed funkce"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-webmasteri-do-leta-prejdete-na-https-nebo-vase-weby-oznacime-jako-nebezpecne/sc-3-a-191742/default.aspx", "title": "Google: Webmaste\u0159i, do l\u00e9ta p\u0159ejd\u011bte na HTTPS, nebo va\u0161e weby ozna\u010d\u00edme jako nebezpe\u010dn\u00e9!", "author": "Jakub \u010c\u00ed\u017eek", "date": "9. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "HTTP se na webu pomalu st\u00e1v\u00e1 minulost\u00ed a ka\u017ed\u00fd po\u0159\u00e1dn\u00fd web dnes pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 p\u0159inejmen\u0161\u00edm z\u00e1kladn\u00ed certifik\u00e1t a \u0161ifrov\u00e1n\u00ed HTTPS. Google na zaveden\u00ed \u0161ifrovan\u00e9ho webu bude tla\u010dit st\u00e1le v\u00edce, po\u010d\u00ednaje Chrome 68 toti\u017e bude v\u0161echny weby na prost\u00e9m HTTP  \u2013 jako nezabezpe\u010den\u00e9, rizikov\u00e9, d\u011brav\u00e9, potenci\u00e1ln\u011b nebezpe\u010dn\u00e9\u2026Chromium/Chrome 68 by m\u011blo b\u00fdt dle pl\u00e1nu hotov\u00e9 v \u010dervenci, webmaste\u0159i tedy maj\u00ed je\u0161t\u011b p\u016fl roku, aby se p\u0159izp\u016fsobili.Pokud z\u016fstanou na HTTP, Google je pochopiteln\u011b nebude nijak blokovat, nicm\u00e9n\u011b zm\u00ednka o nezabezpe\u010den\u00e9m webu m\u016f\u017ee odradit samotn\u00e9ho u\u017eivatele. Absence HTTPS z\u00e1rove\u0148 m\u016f\u017ee sn\u00ed\u017eit pozici webu ve vyhled\u00e1va\u010di, proto\u017ee zabezpe\u010den\u00ed je jednou z rozhodovac\u00edch metrik PageRanku p\u0159i hodnocen\u00ed jeho kvality.P\u0159echod na HTTPS s d\u016fv\u011bryhodn\u00fdm certifik\u00e1tem by dnes nem\u011bl b\u00fdt pro \u017e\u00e1dn\u00fd web probl\u00e9m a to v\u010detn\u011b t\u011bch mal\u00fdch, pr\u00e1v\u011b pro n\u011b toti\u017e v minulosti vznikla slu\u017eba bezplatn\u00fdch certifik\u00e1t\u016f z\u00e1kladn\u00ed \u00farovn\u011b .Spr\u00e1vci webov\u00fdch server\u016f jej relativn\u011b snadno nasad\u00ed na Apache, Nginx, Lighttpd, IIS a dal\u0161\u00ed, no a majitel\u00e9 b\u011b\u017en\u00fdch webhosting\u016f pak musej\u00ed doufat v to, \u017ee tento nebo t\u0159eba jin\u00fd bezplatn\u00fd certifik\u00e1t nab\u00eddnou p\u0159\u00edmo hostingov\u00e9 spole\u010dnosti.", "tags": ["Software", "Google", "Web", "Internet", "Prohl\u00ed\u017ee\u010de", "Bezpe\u010dnost", "Chrome", "HTTPS", "Nebe", "\u0160ifrovan\u00fd web", "Apache", "Nezabezpe\u010den\u00fd web", "Webov\u00fd server", "Hostingov\u00e1 spole\u010dnost", "Bezplatn\u00fd certifik\u00e1t", "IIS", "Certifik\u00e1t", "L\u00e9to", "Ne\u0161ifrovan\u00fd web", "D\u016fv\u011bryhodn\u00fd certifik\u00e1t", "Minulost", "Nginx", "Z\u00e1kladn\u00ed \u00farove\u0148"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/windows-10-bezi-i-na-raspberry-pi-pouzitelne-to-ale-neni/sc-3-a-191781/default.aspx", "title": "Windows 10 b\u011b\u017e\u00ed i na Raspberry Pi, pou\u017eiteln\u00e9 to ale nen\u00ed", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "12. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Windows 10 lze na Raspberry Pi dostat ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed cestou pouze v podob\u011b embedovan\u00e9ho syst\u00e9mu ve verzi IoT. Ta je ale ur\u010dena p\u0159edev\u0161\u00edm pro \u0159\u00edd\u00edc\u00ed elektroniku a b\u011b\u017en\u00e9mu desktopov\u00e9mu syst\u00e9mu je pom\u011brn\u011b vzd\u00e1lena. To se ale ned\u00e1 \u0159\u00edct o verzi Win PE, kterou nyn\u00ed v\u00fdvoj\u00e1\u0159 s  zprovoznil pr\u00e1v\u011b na Raspberry Pi 3.Na Twitteru se pochlubil sn\u00edmky b\u011b\u017e\u00edc\u00edho syst\u00e9mu, kter\u00fd pracuje na ARMov\u00e9m procesoru v r\u00e1mci \u010dipsetu BCM2837. Ten poh\u00e1n\u00ed pr\u00e1v\u011b t\u0159et\u00ed generaci miniaturn\u00edho po\u010d\u00edta\u010de. Samoz\u0159ejm\u011b jde prim\u00e1rn\u011b o experiment, kter\u00fd m\u00e1 uk\u00e1zat, \u017ee Windows 10 lze zprovoznit i mimo x86 platformu. Pou\u017eit\u00e1 verze  je Microsoftem prim\u00e1rn\u011b vyd\u00e1v\u00e1na jako z\u00e1chrann\u00fd syst\u00e9m na flashku. Vyu\u017e\u00edv\u00e1 v\u0161ak v\u011bt\u0161inu toto\u017en\u00fdch komponent jako plnohodnotn\u00fd desktopov\u00fd syst\u00e9m.V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b jeho zprovozn\u011bn\u00ed na Raspberry Pi se samoz\u0159ejm\u011b nejedn\u00e1 o re\u00e1ln\u011b pou\u017eiteln\u00fd syst\u00e9m. Jednak z d\u016fvodu, \u017ee syst\u00e9m dok\u00e1\u017ee vyu\u017e\u00edvat pouze jedno ze \u010dty\u0159 v\u00fdpo\u010detn\u00edch jader procesoru a tak\u00e9 proto, \u017ee po n\u011bkolika minut\u00e1ch dojde k restartu a chybov\u00e9 hl\u00e1\u0161ce o nepodporovan\u00e9m CPU. Fraje\u0159ina je to ale velk\u00e1.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Opera\u010dn\u00ed syst\u00e9my", "Twitter", "Raspberry Pi", "T\u0159et\u00ed generace", "\u0158\u00edd\u00edc\u00ed elektronika", "Ofici\u00e1ln\u00ed cesta", "Miniaturn\u00ed po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "Verze", "B\u011b\u017e\u00edc\u00ed syst\u00e9m", "Armov\u00fd procesor", "Pou\u017eiteln\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Chybov\u00e1 hl\u00e1\u0161ka", "Z\u00e1chrann\u00fd syst\u00e9m", "Procesor", "Pou\u017eit\u00e1 verze", "Syst\u00e9m"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/lenovo-svolava-thinkpady-x1-carbon-kvuli-spatne-dotazenemu-sroubku-hrozi-pozar/sc-3-a-191716/default.aspx", "title": "Lenovo svol\u00e1v\u00e1 Thinkpady X1 Carbon. Kv\u016fli \u0161patn\u011b dota\u017een\u00e9mu \u0161roubku hroz\u00ed po\u017e\u00e1r", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "8. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Lenovo za\u010dalo svol\u00e1vat majitele notebook\u016f Thinkpad X1 Carbon, kter\u00e9 byly vyrobeny od prosince 2016 do \u0159\u00edjna 2017. V\u00fdjime\u010dn\u00fd servis m\u00e1 zajistit opravu drobn\u00e9 z\u00e1vady, kter\u00e1 v\u0161ak m\u016f\u017ee m\u00edt v\u00e1\u017en\u00e9 n\u00e1sledky. Podle  z\u016fstal z v\u00fdroby jeden ze \u0161roubk\u016f uvnit\u0159 po\u010d\u00edta\u010de nedota\u017een\u00fd a hroz\u00ed po\u0161kozen\u00edm baterie.V p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b, \u017ee by se vinou mechanick\u00e9ho zat\u00ed\u017een\u00ed \u0161roubek povolil v\u00edce a za\u010dal by zasahovat do baterie, dal\u0161\u00edm nam\u00e1h\u00e1n\u00edm materi\u00e1lu by mohl zp\u016fsobit jej\u00ed po\u0161kozen\u00ed. P\u0159i tom by hrozilo nadm\u011brn\u00e9 zah\u0159\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed a p\u0159\u00edpadn\u00fd vzplanut\u00ed.Lenovo proto z\u0159\u00eddilo , na kter\u00e9m lze zkontrolovat, zda se z\u00e1vada t\u00fdk\u00e1 konkr\u00e9tn\u00edho stroje. Sta\u010d\u00ed vybrat p\u0159esn\u00fd typ stroje a opsat s\u00e9riov\u00e9 \u010d\u00edslo. N\u00e1sledn\u011b se u\u017eivatel dozv\u00ed, kde m\u00e1 kontaktovat podporu.Lenovo nem\u00e1 zpr\u00e1vy o tom, \u017ee by popsan\u00fd probl\u00e9m opravdu zp\u016fsobil po\u017e\u00e1r, nicm\u00e9n\u011b hovo\u0159\u00ed o t\u0159ech p\u0159\u00edpadech, kdy \u0161roubek baterii naru\u0161il a ta se za\u010dala nadm\u011brn\u011b zah\u0159\u00edvat. I proto v \u017e\u00e1dn\u00e9m p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b nedoporu\u010duje dal\u0161\u00ed pou\u017e\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed notebooku.", "tags": ["Notebooky", "Baterie", "Lenovo", "V\u00e1\u017en\u00fd n\u00e1sledek", "Z\u00e1vada", "Speci\u00e1ln\u00ed str\u00e1nka", "Stroj", "Notebook", "P\u0159esn\u00fd typ", "Po\u0161kozen\u00ed", "Nadm\u011brn\u00e9 zah\u0159\u00edv\u00e1n\u00ed", "Po\u017e\u00e1r", "S\u00e9riov\u00e9 \u010d\u00edslo", "ThinkPad x", "\u0160roubek", "Popsan\u00fd probl\u00e9m"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/google-chce-konkurovat-geforce-now-spusti-streamovani-her-v-nove-sluzbe-yeti/sc-3-a-191725/default.aspx", "title": "Google chce konkurovat Geforce Now, spust\u00ed streamov\u00e1n\u00ed her v nov\u00e9 slu\u017eb\u011b Yeti", "author": "Stanislav Jan\u016f", "date": "9. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Ur\u010dit\u011b si vzpom\u00edn\u00e1te na Onlive, slu\u017ebu, kter\u00e1 slibovala streamov\u00e1n\u00ed her i na low-endov\u00e1 za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed. Na stejn\u00e9m principu dnes funguje i Geforce Now od Nvidie nebo men\u0161\u00ed projekty jako , kde lze streamovat hry z vlastn\u00edho po\u010d\u00edta\u010de. Do t\u00e9hle kategorie by se m\u011bl zanedlouho zapojit i Google s projektem Yeti. Informoval web .Platforma by m\u011bla st\u00e1t na principu m\u011bs\u00ed\u010dn\u00edho p\u0159edplatn\u00e9ho, nebude tedy pot\u0159eba kupovat jednotliv\u00e9 hry. D\u00e1 se v\u0161ak p\u0159edpokl\u00e1dat, \u017ee bude omezen nap\u0159\u00edklad po\u010det her, kter\u00e9 bude mo\u017eno hr\u00e1t za m\u011bs\u00edc.Google pravd\u011bpodobn\u011b bude sm\u011b\u0159ovat slu\u017ebu prim\u00e1rn\u011b pro Chromecasty a za\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed s Android TV. P\u016fjde tak o p\u0159\u00edmou konkurenci pr\u00e1v\u011b pro Geforce Now.  Podrobn\u011bj\u0161\u00ed informace v\u0161ak zat\u00edm nem\u00e1me, ke spu\u0161t\u011bn\u00ed by nicm\u00e9n\u011b m\u011blo doj\u00edt minim\u00e1ln\u011b v testovac\u00ed f\u00e1zi je\u0161t\u011b tento rok.", "tags": ["Google", "Chromecast", "Nvidia", "Android", "Hry", "Hra", "Stejn\u00fd princip", "M\u011bs\u00ed\u010dn\u00ed p\u0159edplatn\u00e9", "Yeti", "P\u0159\u00edm\u00e1 konkurence", "Slu\u017eba", "Mal\u00fd projekt", "Informace", "Streamov\u00e1n\u00ed", "Testovac\u00ed f\u00e1ze", "GeForce NOW", "Kitguru", "Nov\u00e1 slu\u017eba"]}
{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/word-vam-sam-nachysta-zaklad-zivotopisu-data-si-vycucne-z-linkedin/sc-3-a-191710/default.aspx", "title": "Word v\u00e1m s\u00e1m nachyst\u00e1 z\u00e1klad \u017eivotopisu. Data si vycucne z LinkedIn", "author": "Vladislav Kluska", "date": "8. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "Budou to letos dva roky, co Microsoft , teprve a\u017e te\u010f doch\u00e1z\u00ed k n\u011bjak\u00e9mu propojen\u00ed s kancel\u00e1\u0159sk\u00fdm bal\u00edkem Office. M\u00e1te-li p\u0159edplatn\u00e9, budete moci vyu\u017e\u00edt data z t\u00e9to soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00edt\u011b pro snaz\u0161\u00ed vytvo\u0159en\u00ed sv\u00e9ho \u017eivotopisu. Funkce je prozat\u00edm dostupn\u00e1 pouze pro p\u0159edplatitele  ve vybran\u00fdch zem\u00edch.K jej\u00edmu fungov\u00e1n\u00ed nen\u00ed t\u0159eba m\u00edt na LinkedInu vlastn\u00ed profil. V\u0161e je toti\u017e postaven\u00e9 na tom, \u017ee se m\u016f\u017eete pro inspiraci pod\u00edvat na p\u0159edp\u0159ipraven\u00e9 \u017eivotopisy a porovnat sv\u016fj \u017eivotopis s po\u017eadavky na jednotliv\u00e9 pozice, po kter\u00fdch se aktu\u00e1ln\u011b d\u00edv\u00e1te.Funkce je aktu\u00e1ln\u011b dostupn\u00e1 pro u\u017eivatele Office 365 s aktu\u00e1ln\u00edm Wordem 2016. Mezi dal\u0161\u00ed podm\u00ednky pak pat\u0159\u00ed nastaven\u00fd region ve Windows na Austr\u00e1lii, Braz\u00edlii, Kanadu, \u010c\u00ednu, Indii, Japonsko, Nov\u00fd Z\u00e9land, Singapur, Jihoafrickou republiku, nebo USA, p\u0159i\u010dem\u017e jazyk po\u010d\u00edta\u010de mus\u00ed b\u00fdt nastaven na angli\u010dtinu.", "tags": ["Microsoft", "Windows", "Linkedin", "USA", "Office 365", "\u010c\u00edna", "Microsoft Office", "Austr\u00e1lie", "Microsoft Word", "Japonsko", "Indie", "Nov\u00fd Z\u00e9land", "Kanada", "Soci\u00e1ln\u00ed s\u00ed\u0165", "Funkce", "Singapur", "Jihoafrick\u00e1 republika", "\u017divotopis", "Vybran\u00e1 zem\u011b", "Data", "Braz\u00edlie", "Z\u00e1klad", "Kancel\u00e1\u0159sk\u00fd bal\u00edk", "Office", "Snadn\u00e9 vytvo\u0159en\u00ed"]}
