{"url": "https://www.zive.cz/clanky/vyvoj-a-architektura-pocitace/sc-3-a-191740/default.aspx", "title": "V\u00fdvoj a architektura po\u010d\u00edta\u010de", "author": null, "date": "6. \u00fanora 2018", "content": "M\u00e1te mezery ve vzd\u011bl\u00e1n\u00ed ohledn\u011b v\u00fdvoje a architektury po\u010d\u00edta\u010dov\u00e9 technologie? Potom jste tady spr\u00e1vn\u011b, proto\u017ee p\u0159esn\u011b tohle t\u00e9ma rozeb\u00edr\u00e1me v dne\u0161n\u00edm videu. ", "tags": ["Tipy", "Jak na Internet", "Architektura", "Dne\u0161n\u00ed video", "Po\u010d\u00edta\u010d", "V\u00fdvoj"]}
